अक्<BR>अक् 1. P. (कुटिलायाङ् गतौ K. वक्रगते V. cf. अग्) flexuose,<BR>tortuose ire (cf. gr. ἀγϰή, ἀγϰαί, ἀγϰών, lat.<BR>angulus).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

