अकत्थन<BR>अकत्थन (KARM. ex अ priv. et कत्थन a r. कत्थ् s. अन)<BR>non gloriosus, se non jactans. IN. 4.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अकस्मात्<BR>अकस्मात् (AVY. ex अ priv. et ablat. interrogativi किम्,<BR>secundum analogiam adverbiorum साक्षात् et समन्तात्,<BR>v. gr. 675.) sine causa, subito. N. 21.22. HIT. 18.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अकाम<BR>अकाम (BAH. ex अ priv. et काम) invitus. N. 20.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अकार<BR>अकार m. (ex अ sonus a et कार faciens) littera a. BH. 10.33.<BR>(v. gr. 4.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अकाल|अकालः<BR>अकाल (BAH. ex अ priv. et काल tempus) intempestivus.<BR>SU. 1.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अकूपार<BR>अकूपार m. (cujus ripa ulterior non vilis i. e. non propinqua<BR>sed remota est, latus; BAH. ex अ priv. et कूपार<BR>quod ipsum est BAH. ex कू, producto ex कु q. v., et<BR>पार; cf. दूरपार) mare. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अकृतबुद्धि<BR>अकृतबुद्धि (BAH. ex अकृत et बुद्धि) non factum intellectum<BR>habens, i. e. intellectu destitutus (cf. composita,<BR>quae a जात incipiunt).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

