अकृतात्मन्<BR>अकृतात्मन् (BAH. ex अकृत et आत्मन्) non factam animam<BR>habens, animâ privatus, i. e. improbus, insanus.<BR>N. 12.82. BH. 15.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

