अक्लिष्टकार<BR>अक्लिष्टकार (KARM. ex अक्लिष्ट inturbatus, non interruptus,<BR>indefessus — a r. क्लिश् praef. अ, s. त — et कार<BR>actio, nisus) indefessus nisus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्लिष्टकारिन्<BR>अक्लिष्टकारिन् (a praec. s. इन्) indefessum nisum habens.<BR>IN. 2.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्ष्<BR>अक्ष् 1. et 5. P. (सङ्घाते K. व्याप्तिसंहत्योः V.) coacervare,<BR>occupare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्ष|अक्षं|अक्षः<BR>अक्ष m. (v. ईक्ष् videre)<BR>1) oculus, in fine compositorum<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">Page002-a+ 36</a>]<BR>pro अक्षि — v. gr. 681. — e. c. पिङ्गाक्ष q. v. (gr.<BR>ὌΣΣΟ, ὌΚΚΟ per assimilationem ex ὌΞΟ, lat. oculus<BR>abjecto s, goth. augô — Th. augan — contra legem<BR>quâ plerumque tenues in aspiratas sunt conversae, quam<BR>ob rem auhô exspectaveris, cujus au ex vi euphonica litterae<BR>h explicari posset, ita ut genuinum a in u sit attenuatum<BR>(*) — sicut e. c. in lith. ugni-s = अग्नि ignis — vocali<BR>u vero, propter sequens h, a euphonicum sit<BR>praefixum; russ. òko; v. अक्षि).<BR>2) talus. N. 7.5.<BR>3) rota<BR>(cf. lat. axis = अक्षि q. v.; gr. ἈΞΟΝ = अक्षन् q. v.;<BR>germ. vet. ahsa, nostrum Achse; lith. aʃzis ejecto क्, ʃz<BR>= ष्).<BR>4) currus.<BR>5) secundum Wils. a kind of seed<BR>used for rosaries (Eloeocarpus).<BR>6) dica, lis.<BR>(*) V. librum meum „Vocalismus” p. 227. n. 16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=001-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षदर्शक|अक्षदर्शकः<BR>अक्षदर्शक m. (TATP. e praec. sgnf. 6. et दर्शक qui videt)<BR>judex. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षन्<BR>अक्षन् Thema defectivum, quo suppletur अक्षि oculus (gr. 165.<BR>cf. goth. Th. AUGAN, unde nomin. augô).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षम|अक्षमः<BR>अक्षम (KARM. ex अ priv. et क्षम potens, a r. क्षम् s. अ)<BR>impotens. SA. 4.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षमात्र<BR>अक्षमात्र n. (ex अक्ष oculus et मात्र n. mensura, in fine<BR>compositorum significans solus, v. quoque suffixum<BR>मात्र, gr. 652.) temporis punctum, momentum. अक्षमात्रेण<BR>momento, statim. A. 8.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षमाला<BR>अक्षमाला f. (ex अक्ष sgnf. 5. et माला sertum floreum)<BR>«a rosarie» DEV. 2.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षय|अक्षयः<BR>अक्षय (BAH. ex अ priv. et क्षय m. exitium) liber ab exitio,<BR>sempiternus. N. 2.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षयत्व<BR>अक्षयत्व n. (a praec. s. त्व) Abstractum praecedentis, Unvergänglichkeit.<BR>HIT. 1.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षय्य<BR>अक्षय्य (KARM. ex अ priv. et क्षय्य fragilis, a r. क्षि s. य,<BR>gr. 629.) quod exstingui non potest, immortalis, perennis.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षर|अक्षरं|अक्षरः<BR>अक्षर n. (KARM. ex अ priv. et क्षर periens, a r. क्षर् s. अ)<BR>1) quod non perit, immortale, sempiternum ({#na kzaratI<BR>'ty akzaram#}, sic schol. Srîdharasvâminus ad BH. 8.3.).<BR>2) littera, syllaba.<BR>3) एकम् अक्षरम् (unum immortale)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">Page002-b+ 37</a>]<BR>syllaba sanctissima ओम्, quae tribus suis litteris tres<BR>deos altissimos exprimit, scilicet litterâ अ, quae cum<BR>sequente उ in ओ coalescit, deum Vischnum, उ Sivum<BR>et म् Brahmam. BH. 10.25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षवती<BR>अक्षवती f. (ab अक्ष m. talus, s. वत् in fem.) talarius lusus.<BR>N. 26.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षान्ति|अक्षांति|अक्षांतिः|अक्षान्तिः<BR>अक्षान्ति f. (KARM. ex अ priv. et क्षान्ति patientia) invidia.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षि<BR>अक्षि n. oculus (nom. irr. v. gr. 165. et अक्ष; lith. aki-s).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अक्षौहिणी<BR>अक्षौहिणी f. exercitus completus, justum peditum, equitum,<BR>curruum et elephantorum numerum continens.<BR>Secundum Wils. ex अक्ष currus et ऊहिणी collectio,<BR>vocalibus अ et ऊ irregulariter coalescentibus in औ pro<BR>ओ).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

