अखिल|अखिलं<BR>अखिल (non vacuum habens, BAH. ex अ priv. et खिल<BR>n. inane, vacuum) omnis, universus, totus. अखिलेन<BR>adv. omnino. N. 6.8. SU. 3.8. A. 3.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्<BR>अग् 1. P. (कुटिलायाङ् गतौ K. वक्रगते V.) tortuose, flexuose<BR>ire; cf. अक्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग|अगः<BR>अग m. (KARM. ex अ priv. et ग iens, a r. गा s. अ)<BR>1) arbor.<BR>2) mons.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

