अगाध|अगाधं|अगाधः<BR>अगाध (secundum Wils. BAH. ex अ priv. et गाध locus, situs<BR>cf. nostrum Boden-los. Derivari etiam potest a rad.<BR>गाह् submergi, quae primitive गाध् sonuisse videtur,<BR>v. gr. comp. 23.) valde profundus. N. 6.13. — (Huc<BR>fortasse pertinent gr. ἀγαϑός et goth. gôths (Th. gôda,<BR>abjecto a initiali) sicut scr. वरीयस् melior, वरिष्ठ optimus<BR>cum उरु magnus, latus cohaerent; v. gr. comp. 298.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्नि|अग्निः<BR>अग्नि m.<BR>1) ignis.<BR>2) Agnis, deus ignis (lat. igni-s, lith.<BR>ugni-s, slav. ognj, goth. auhn̕-s hypocaustum, fornax<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-a" target="_blank">Page003-a+ 37</a>]<BR>v. Graff I. p. 176.; huc etiam pertinere videntur gr.<BR>αἴγλη, ἀγλαός).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=002-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्निचित्<BR>अग्निचित् m. (ex अग्नि et चित् colligens a r. चि adjecto<BR>त्, v. gr. 643.) ignis cultor, qui ignem sacrum sustinet.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्निमत्|अग्निमन्त्<BR>अग्निमत् (igne praeditus ab अग्नि suff. मत्) igni<BR>deditus, ignem colens. N. 12.50.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्निपुरोगम<BR>अग्निपुरोगम (BAH. ex अग्नि, et पुरोगम antecedens, e<BR>पुरस् in fronte et गम iens) cui Agnis antecedit, Agnem<BR>tanquam antecedentem habens. N. 5.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्निशिख|अग्निशिखं|अग्निशिखः<BR>अग्निशिख m. n. (BAH. ex अग्नि et शिखा flamma) crocus.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्निहोत्र|अग्निहोत्रं|अग्निहोत्रः<BR>अग्निहोत्र n. (TATP. ex अग्नि et होत्र n. q. v.) ignis sacer,<BR>qui perpetuo alitur. SU. 2.14. SA. 1.8. N. 12.96.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्र|अग्रं|अग्रः<BR>अग्र n.<BR>1) cuspis, cacumen, vertex. N. 8.9. Loc. अग्रे ante,<BR>coram, c. gen. N. 23.21. (cf. gr. ἄϰϱον).<BR>2) Adj. insignis,<BR>eximius. A. 1.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अग्रज|अग्रजः<BR>अग्रज m. (e praec. et ज natus) primogenitus, frater natu<BR>maximus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

