अङ्गराग|अंगराग|अङ्गरागः<BR>अङ्गराग m. (ex अङ्ग n. et राग m. color) odoratum unguentum,<BR>nisi potius, quod vocis origini magis conveniret, fucus,<BR>pigmentum. (Wils. explicat: Perfuming the<BR>body after cleansing; smearing it with unguents of sandal<BR>etc. HEM. 3.299.) IN. 5.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=003-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

