अञ्जलि|अंजलिः|अञ्जलिः<BR>अञ्जलि m. manuum junctio, implicatio (Wils. explicat:<BR>The cavity formed by putting the hands together and hollowing<BR>the palms, as if to receive water, etc.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=005-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

