अतथोचित<BR>अतथोचित (KARM. ex अ priv. et तथोचित, KARM. e तथा<BR>sic et उचित dignus, merens, a r. उच्) non sic dignus,<BR>non hac re dignus, non hoc merens. H. 1.33. N. 15.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=005-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतन्द्रित|अतंद्रित<BR>अतन्द्रित (KARM. ex अ priv. et तन्द्रित, quod separatim<BR>non invenitur, lassitudine affectus, lentus, negligens, a<BR>तन्द्रा f. s. इत)<BR>1) indefessus.<BR>2) non lentus, non negligens.<BR>N. 15.14. 17.46. 20.36. M. 45.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=005-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतप्ततपस्<BR>अतप्ततपस् (BAH. ex अतप्त - ex अ priv. et तप्त part. pass.<BR>a r. तप् q. v. - et तपस् n. q. v.). Non absoluta sacra<BR>tormenta habens (nicht gebüʃste Bufse, nicht vollbrachte<BR>fromme Selbstqual habend). IN. 1.17. 2.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=005-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतस्<BR>अतस् (a stirpe pronominali अ, gr. 270., s. तस्)<BR>1) inde,<BR>hinc, illinc. N. 9.23.<BR>2) ideo, igitur, itaque. BR. 2.30.<BR>SA. 5.11.<BR>3) in comparationibus pro ablativo pronominis<BR>इदम् substantive posito usurpatur. H. 1.29. 35. — Ante<BR>निमित्तम् (causâ, propter) genitivi fungitur vice:<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">Page006-a+ 37</a>]<BR>अतो निमित्तम् hujus causâ. Adverbia परम् ultra,<BR>ulterius, et ऊर्ड्वम् sursum, post अतस् tempus futurum<BR>indicant: अतःपरम् BH. 2.12. अत ऊर्ड्वम् N. 25.15.<BR>BH. 12.8. inde in posterum. — Adv. परम् post अतस्<BR>ad locum quoque refertur: N. 9.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=005-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतस|अतसः<BR>अतस m. (r. अत् s. अस) aër, ventus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतसी<BR>अतसी f. linum, Wils. «cummon flax». AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अति<BR>अति Praep. praef. (ut mihi videtur a stirpe pronominali अ<BR>s. ति ut इति ita ab इ)<BR>1) in compositione cum radicibus:<BR>super, supra, trans, ultra.<BR>2) in compos. cum nominibus:<BR>id. et valde (lat. at in atavus, v. gr. comp. 425.)<BR>probabiliter etiam et, quod ad अथ quoque referri possit;<BR>germ. vet. anti, unti, inti, unde, indi etc., angl. and,<BR>nostrum und, insertâ nasali; gr. ἔτι, ἀντί, lat. ante; lith.<BR>ant super, goth. and partim ad अति ἀντι partim ad<BR>अधि pertinere videtur, respondet ei in prima sgfc. nostrum<BR>ent- et ant- in antworten, entsprechen etc.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतिथि|अतिथिः<BR>अतिथि m. hospes, Gast. DR. 3.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतिथित्व<BR>अतिथित्व n. (a praec. s. त्व) hospitalis exceptio. DR. 3.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतिपात|अतिपातः<BR>अतिपात m. (r. पत् praef. अति transscendere, violare, s.<BR>अ) actio transscendendi, violatio, neglectio, derelictio.<BR>SAK. 6.11.: अन्यकार्यातिपात alius negotii derelictio.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतिमात्र|अतिमात्रं<BR>अतिमात्र (AVY. ex अति et मात्र n. modus, mensura) ultra<BR>modum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतियशस्<BR>अतियशस् Adj. (BAH. ex अति et यशस् n. qui ultra gloriam<BR>est, gloriam superat) valde celeber, valde gloriosus.<BR>N. 8.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

