अतिशयिन्<BR>अतिशयिन् (ex अति et शयिन् a r. शी jacere s. इन् nisi<BR>a substantivo अतिशय abundantia s. इन्) immodicus,<BR>effusus. UR. 93.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतिसर्ज<BR>अतिसर्ज m. (r. सृज् dimittere praef. अति s. अ) donatio.<BR>A. 5.53. RAGH. 10.43.; cf. अतिसर्जन.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतिसर्जन|अतिसर्जनं|अतिसर्ज्जनं<BR>अतिसर्जन n. (r. सृज् dimittere praef. अति s. अन) donatio.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतीव<BR>अतीव (ex अति et इव sicut, hic pleon.) valde. IN. 5.9.<BR>N. 1.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अतुल|अतुलः<BR>अतुल (BAH. ex अ priv. et तुला f. similitudo) similitudinis<BR>expers, incomparabilis. IN. 3.10. H. 3.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्ता<BR>अत्ता f. mater (cf. goth. atta Th. attan pater et aithei Th.<BR>aithein mater).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्यद्भुत<BR>अत्यद्भुत (BAH. ex अति et अद्भुत n. q. v., quodultra miraculum<BR>est) valde miraculosus, prodigiosus, stupendus.<BR>SU. 1.23. N. 20.25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्यन्तम्<BR>अत्यन्तम् (AVY. ex अति et अन्त m. n. finis) ultra modum.<BR>N. 16.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्यय|अत्ययः<BR>अत्यय m. (r. इ, praef. अति s. अ) discessus, abitio, inde<BR>obitus, mors; cum तप calor: तपात्यय caloris discessus<BR>vel obitus, inde secundum HEM. pluviosum anni<BR>tempus. SAK. 49.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्यर्थम्<BR>अत्यर्थम् (AVY. ex अति et अर्थ m. res) ultra modum. SU. 3.25.<BR>N. 11.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्र<BR>अत्र (a stirpe pronominali अ - gr. 270. - s. त्र) hic, illic.<BR>In lingua scenica saepe praefigitur voci भवत् et ejus<BR>fem. भवती.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्रि|अत्रिः<BR>अत्रि m. hostis, inimicus, adversarius.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अथ<BR>अथ (ut mihi videtur, a stirpe pronominali अ suff. थ sicut<BR>कथम् a क)<BR>1) at, in initio sententiae. N. 2.28. 5.1.<BR>2) et, etiam. IN. 1.18. 2.13. BR. 2.3.<BR>3) tunc, illo tempore.<BR>SU. 4.15. H. 1.21. 22., confer तदा.<BR>4) deinde,<BR>tum, post. N. 1.25. SU. 1.18.<BR>5) explet. praecipue ante<BR>वा q. v. (lat. at).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अथवा<BR>अथवा (अथ + वा)<BR>1) vel, sive, saepissime.<BR>2) attamen.<BR>SAK. 8.5. HIT. 23.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अथो<BR>अथो (अथ + उ)<BR>1) deinde, tum. IN. 3.2. SU. 1.12. BH. 4.35.<BR>2) et, etiam. BR. 1.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अद्<BR>अद् 2. P. edere (अद्मि, lith. edmi, slav. jamj pro jadmj,<BR>3. p. pl. jadjatj, gr. comp. 460.; gr. ἔδω, lat. edo, goth.<BR>rad. AT unde praes. ita, praet. at, v. gramm. comp. p. 115.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अद|अदः<BR>अद Adj. et Nom. agentis in fine comp. (r. अद् s. अ) edens.<BR>H. 2.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=006-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अदक<BR>अदक Adj. et Nom. agentis in fine comp. (r. अद् s. अक)<BR>edens. H. 2.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

