अदस्<BR>अदस् Pron. demonstr. (nom. m. f. असौ, n. अदस् gr. 271.)<BR>hic, ille.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अदृश्यत्|अदृश्यन्त्<BR>अदृश्यत् (ex अ priv. et दृश्यत् part. pass. praes. a r. दृश्<BR>s. अत् gr. 597.) quod non cernitur.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अदृष्टपूर्व|अदृष्टपूर्व्व<BR>अदृष्टपूर्व (KARM. ex अदृष्ट non visus et पूर्वम् prius, gr. 680.)<BR>antea non visus. N. 13.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

