अद्भुत|अद्भुतं|अद्भुतः<BR>अद्भुत<BR>1) admirabilis. BH. 18.76.<BR>2) n. mirum, miraculum,<BR>portentum, prodigium. SU. 1.11. Fortasse forma corrupta<BR>est vocis अतिभूत (quod est ultra id, quod existit),<BR>suppresso इ et correpto ऊ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अद्भुतकर्मन्|अद्भुतकर्म्मन्<BR>अद्भुतकर्मन् (BAH. e praec. et कर्मन् n.) miro facto ortus,<BR>ad. litt. mirum factum habens. IN. 1.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अद्भुतोपम<BR>अद्भुतोपम (BAH. ex अद्भुत et उपमा similitudo) miraculi<BR>similitudinem habens, mirificus. A. 3.41.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

