अद्रोह|अद्रोहः<BR>अद्रोह m. (KARM. ex अ priv. et द्रोह odium) vacuitas odii,<BR>amor, benevolentia. SA. 5.34. BH. 16.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधन<BR>अधन (BAH. ex अ priv. et धन n.) non divitias habens,<BR>pauper.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधम|अधमः<BR>अधम (ut mihi videtur, a stirpe pronominali अ s. धम pro<BR>superl. suff. तम, gr. comp. p. 393.)<BR>1) inferior, infimus<BR>(lat. infimus insertâ nasali, cum f pro ध् sicut e. c. in<BR>fumus = धूम).<BR>2) vilis, abjectus. DR. 5.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधर|अधरं|अधरः<BR>अधर (ex अ s. धर pro तर, v. अधम) inferior (cf. slav.<BR>dalje infra, dalû in profundum, abjecto a et r mutato<BR>in l, sic goth. dala-thrô ab imo, v. gr. comp. p. 398.; lat.<BR>infra, inferior, v. अधम).<BR>2) labium inferius; अधरौ labia.<BR>URV. 64.9. 68.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधर्म|अधर्मः|अधर्म्म|अधर्म्मः<BR>अधर्म m. (KARM. ex अ priv. et धर्म m.) injustum, nefas,<BR>peccatum. BR. 2.34. BH. 18.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधस्<BR>अधस् (ut mihi videtur a stirpe pronominali अ s. धस् pro<BR>तस्, v. अधम)<BR>1) Adv. infra, subter, subtus. IN. 5.10.<BR>2) Praep. cum gen. sub. UP. 10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधस्तात्<BR>अधस्तात् (a praec. s. स्तात् gr. 652.) sub c. genit. HIT. 111.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधि|अधिः<BR>अधि Praef. (ut mihi videtur a stirpe pron. अ s. धि, quod<BR>cum gr. ϑι in ὅϑι, πόϑι etc. convenit) super, ad (lat.<BR>ad et verisimiliter aes in aes-timo mutato d in s propter<BR>sequens t, et i vocali τᴕ̃ अधि regressâ in antecedentem<BR>syllabam. Huc etiam retulerim usque i. e. us-que pro<BR>ad-que secundum analogiam τᴕ̃ esca pro ed-ca a rad.<BR>ED, et a mutato in u propter sequens s, sicut e. c. in<BR>edimus = अद्मस्. E germanicis linguis huc trahimus<BR>goth. et angl. at, porro goth. and pro nonnullis ejus significationibus,<BR>et und usque, insertâ nasali, sicut in<BR>nostro und = अति q. v.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिक|अधिकं|अधिकः<BR>अधिक (ab अधि s. क) superior, major. BR. 1.18. 30. N. 11.16., sehr groʃs. N. 23.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिकम्<BR>अधिकम् (acc. praec.) supra, plus, amplius; c. acc. N. 21.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिकरण्य|अधिकरण्यं<BR>अधिकरण्य n. (ab अधिकरण praevalens, praepollens s. य)<BR>auctoritas, dignitas, praestantia. HIT. 97.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिकार|अधिकारः<BR>अधिकार m. (a r. कृ praef. अधि s. अ) munus, officium,<BR>dignitas, administratio. HIT. 49.17. 18. 61.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिकारिन्<BR>अधिकारिन् (a praec. s. इन्) munere aliquo fungens, muneri<BR>alicui praepositus. HIT. 61.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिगम|अधिगमः<BR>अधिगम m. (r. गम् praef. अधि s. अ) aditus, adventus,<BR>accessus. UR. 89.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिगमन|अधिगमनं<BR>अधिगमन n. (r. गम् s. अन) id. N. 24.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिज्य<BR>अधिज्य (BAH. ex अधि ad et ज्या nervus arcûs) nervo instructus.<BR>SAK. 30.6. 38.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=007-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधित्यका<BR>अधित्यका f. (ut videtur, ex perdito primitivo अधित्य - quod<BR>ipsum descendit ab अधि s. त्य cui respondet lat. s.<BR>tiu-s τᴕ̃ propitiu-s (*) et gr. σσο, per assimilationem ex<BR>σϳο, τᴕ̃ πεϱισσός - s. क in fem.) regio in montis vertice<BR>(cf. उपत्यका). HIT. 101.18.<BR>(*) V. Gramm. comp. p. 400.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=008-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिप|अधिपः<BR>अधिप m. (r. पा s. अ) dominus, imperator, moderator. In<BR>fine comp. N. 5.29. 24.42.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=008-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अधिपति|अधिपतिः<BR>अधिपति m. (KARM. ex अधि et पति dominus) dominus<BR>supremus, imperator, rex. N. 12.33.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=008-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

