अन्तर्|अंतर्<BR>अन्तर् Praep. praef. interdum separ. (ut mihi videtur, a<BR>stirpe pronominali अन abjecto अ s. तर्, sicut प्रातर्<BR>a प्र et zend. 𐬀𐬭𐬆𐬥𐬌 extra a 𐬥𐬌𐬱 ex, v. gr. comp. 293.<BR>et Burnoufii «Yaçna» p. XCIX.)<BR>1) inter, intus, in<BR>medio. SA. 5.106. BH. 5.24. 8.22. N. 24.34. c. gen. BH. 13.15.<BR>2) sub, v. अन्तर्भूमि, अन्तर्भूमिगत, अन्तर्हित<BR>(lat. inter, goth. undar, nostrum unter, slav. vn-ûtrj (*)<BR>intra).<BR>(*) De û pro an v. gr. comp. 255.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=011-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अन्तर|अंतर|अन्तरं<BR>1. अन्तर n. (ut equidem puto, a stirpe pron. अन s. comp.<BR>तर)<BR>1) interius, interior pars, medium. H. 4.44. N. 12.103. 21.10.<BR>2) intervallum, interjectum spatium. A. 9.6.<BR>BH. 11.20.<BR>3) differentia, discrimen. BH. 13.34.<BR>4) occasio,<BR>opportunitas. N. 7.2. 13.59.<BR>5) causa. DR. 5.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=011-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अन्तर|अंतर|अन्तरं<BR>2. अन्तर (v. praec. et cf. goth. anthar, Th. anthara alius;<BR>lith. antra-s secundus; lat. alter; v. अन्य) alius. N. 13.33.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=011-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

