अन्य|अन्यः<BR>अन्य (gr. 274.) alius (goth. alji-s, Th. alja, lat. aliu-s, gr.<BR>ἄλλο-ς per assimilationem ex ἄλϳο-ς, ita Prâkr. अण्ण et<BR>germ. vet. alles aliter ex aljes; cf. etiam ἔνιοι (= अन्ये),<BR>ἐνίοτε; slav. in, Th. ino, v. gr. comp. 374.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=012-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

