अप्<BR>अप् f. (nom anom. plur. num. v. gr. 207.) aqua. SU. 2.14.<BR>N. 12.63. (lat. aqua mutatâ labiali in gutturalem; goth.<BR>ahva flumen; germ. vet. aha, et affa in fine comp. v.<BR>Graff I.159.; lith. uppê flumen; huc etiam cum Johannsenio<BR>- Latein. Wortbildung p. 41. - refero lat. am-nis<BR>pro ap-nis - v. अप्नस् - commutatâ tenui cum nasali<BR>ejusdem organi, sicut in somnus pro sopnus; huc etiam<BR>retulerim gr. ἀϕϱός).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अप|अपः<BR>अप Praep. praef. ab, de (gr. ἀπό, lat. ab, goth. af, angl.<BR>of, germ. vet. af-tar post cum suff. compar. - v. gr. comp. 294.<BR>- goth. af-tarô retro, a tergo; cf. etiam lith. apaćia<BR>pars inferior, apaćioj infra, apatinnis inferior; huc<BR>etiam retulerim slav. insep. o de, abjecto p).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अपकर्तृ|अपकर्त्तृ<BR>अपकर्तृ m. (r. कृ facere, praef. अप s. तृ) qui alqm. offendit,<BR>adversarius, inimicus. HIT. 90.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अपकारता<BR>अपकारता f. (ab अपकार, a r. कृ s. अ, qui offensionem,<BR>injuriam infert, s. ता) offensio. N. 21.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अपकारिन्<BR>अपकारिन् m. (r. कृ s. इन्) qui aliquem offendit, adversarius,<BR>inimicus. HIT. 27.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अपकृत<BR>अपकृत (part. pass. a r. कृ praef. अप s. त)<BR>1) offensus.<BR>2) n. offensio, laesio, violatio. H. 4.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अपगम|अपगमः<BR>अपगम m. (r. गम् ire s. अ) abscessio, separatio. HIT. 43.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

