अपचय|अपचयः<BR>अपचय m. (r. चि colligere s. अ) deminutio, expensum.<BR>HIT. 105.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

