अपटीक्षेप|अपटीक्षेपः<BR>अपटीक्षेप m. (e praec. et क्षेप) secundum Wils. «precipitate<BR>entrance on the stage, indicating hurry and agitation,<BR>also read अपटाक्षेप»; v. etiam Lenzium ad URV. 3.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=013-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

