अप्रियंवद<BR>अप्रियंवद (e praec. - v. gr. 645. suff. अ - et वद a r. वद्<BR>s. अ, loquens, dicens) injucundum dicens. H. 4.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=014-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

