अबल|अबलं|अबलः<BR>अबल (BAH. ex अ priv. et बल vis) debilis (fort. goth.<BR>ubils Th. ubila, nostrum übel, angl. evil; nisi haec ad<BR>अधर = lat. inferu-s pertinent, mutatâ aspiratâ in mediam,<BR>secundum generalem consonantium permutandarum<BR>legem. Sanscr. ब् autem in germ. item est b, unde<BR>goth. radix band ligare = बन्ध् q. v.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=014-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

