अभि<BR>अभि Praep. praef. et sep. (ut videtur, a stirpe pronom. अ s.<BR>भि, quod convenit cum casuum terminationibus भ्यम्,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=015-a" target="_blank">Page015-a+ 37</a>]<BR>भिस्, भ्याम्, भ्यस्) ad, versus. (Gr. ἀμϕί insertâ nasali<BR>sicut in ἄμϕω contra उभौ; lat. ob, amb; germ. vet.<BR>umbi, nostrum um; slav. ob; cf. etiam adverb. slav. абїе<BR>abje statim. Huc quoque retulerim nostrum bei, goth.<BR>bî, abjecto a initiali, sicut in sanscr. praeter अपि etiam<BR>पि dicitur; porro praefixum be, goth. bi.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=014-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

