अभ्यास|अभ्यासः<BR>अभ्यास m. (r. अस् cl. 1. q. v. s. अ)<BR>1) propinquitas, vicinitas.<BR>N. 9.10. DR. 8.13.<BR>2) exercitatio, usus, experientia.<BR>BH. 12.12. 18.36.<BR>3) educatio, disciplina, institutio.<BR>HIT. 5.14. 7.4. Scribitur etiam अभ्याश. (Cf. {#aByasta,<BR>aByasana, aByasya#} apud Wils. ed. 2.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=016-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

