अर्घ्<BR>अर्घ् 1. A. (हिंसायाम् K. मूल्ये V.) offendere, laedere, occidere;<BR>constare, pretium habere, dignum esse. (Fortasse<BR>huc pertinet nostrum arg, ärgern, germ. vet. arg,<BR>ark, et inserto a: arag, arak avarus, pravus, impius,<BR>subst. arg malum.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्घ|अर्घः<BR>अर्घ m. (r. अर्घ् s. अ)<BR>1) pretium.<BR>2) donum honorificum,<BR>quod diis eximiisque hospitibus offertur, constans ex<BR>octo rebus, nempe ex oryza, sacro gramine durva dicto,<BR>floribus etc. cum aqua, aut ex aqua sola in parvo<BR>vase. SA. 3.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्घ्य|अर्घ्यं<BR>अर्घ्य (r. अर्घ् s. य)<BR>1) Adj. venerandus.<BR>2) m. i. q. praec.<BR>sign. 2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्च्<BR>अर्च् 1. P. A. 10. P. honorare, venerari, colere. IN. 3.1. 4.3. 5.<BR>N. 18.19.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">Page018-b+ 37</a>]<BR>c. अभि i. q. simpl. BH. 18.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्चिष्मत्|अर्चिष्मन्त्<BR>अर्चिष्मत् (a sq. s. मत्)<BR>1) Adj. flammans. UR. 37.7.<BR>2) m. ignis. HEM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्चिस्|अर्च्चिस्<BR>अर्चिस् f. (r. अर्च् s. इस्) splendor, flamma. IN. 1.35. H. 1.49.<BR>(cf. अर्क्, अर्क).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्ज्<BR>अर्ज् 1. P. 10. P. A.<BR>1) colligere, coacervare, adipisci, acquirere.<BR>N. 26.4. IN. 3.7.<BR>2) facere, perficere (प्रयत्ने<BR>K. संस्कारे V.): स्वर्जितङ् कर्म bene facta actio. RAM. ed. Ser. I.34.38.;<BR>स्वार्जितन् तपस् a mement ipso effecta<BR>castigatio. RAM. ed. Ser. I.47.13. (fortasse lat.<BR>urgo et arguo, gr. ἔϱγω nisi hoc est pro Ϝέϱγω =<BR>वृज् vel pro σέϱγω = सृज्).<BR>c. उप i. q. simpl. sign. 1. HIT. 33.21. MAN. 9.208.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्जन|अर्जनं|अर्ज्जनं<BR>अर्जन n. (r. अर्ज् s. अन) Nom. actionis τᴕ̃ अर्ज् sgnf. 1.<BR>HIT. 34.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्जुन|अर्जुनं|अर्जुनः<BR>अर्जुन m. (ut videtur, a r. अर्ज् s. उन)<BR>1) nomen arboris<BR>(Wils. Terminalia alata glabra).<BR>2) nomen unius<BR>Pândavorum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्णव|अर्णवः|अर्ण्णव<BR>अर्णव m. mare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्थ्<BR>अर्थ् 10. P. (v. अर्थ) petere, postulare (gr. αἰτέω dissoluto<BR>r in vocalem i, cf. अर्थ).<BR>c. प्र petere, appetere, desiderare, concupiscere. BR. 2.11. 12.13. 16.<BR>IN. 5.33. SU. 1.26. 3.11.<BR>c. सम् cogitare, putare, existimare. UR. 18.9. 18.5.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्थ|अर्थः<BR>अर्थ m. (r. अर्थ् s. अ, nisi potius अर्थयामि est Denominativum<BR>vocis अर्थ)<BR>1) res, materia. BR. 1.16. 2.2. 6. N. 8.4. 12.90. 15.3. 18.15.<BR>BH. 2.6. 8. transl. sensus.<BR>2) divitiae, opes. N. 17.47. BH. 2.6.<BR>3) commodum,<BR>utilitas, fructus. BH. 3.18.<BR>4) causa, ratio. N. 15.13.<BR>Acc. instr. dat. et loc. - अर्थम्, अर्थेन, अर्थाय, अर्थे - praepositionis<BR>vice funguntur, ut latinum causâ, gratiâ,<BR>c. gen. aut in compositione cum nomine recto. N. 23.10.<BR>BR. 1.27. 29. 2.3. H. 4.28. — In fine compositorum अर्थ<BR>cum significatione res nonnunquam redundat. A. 4.16.<BR>SA. 4.25. (gr. αἰτία).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्थकृत्<BR>अर्थकृत् (rem, commodum faciens, e praec. et कृत्<BR>faciens, q. v.) utilis, commodus, frutuosus. IN. 5.56.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=018-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्थिन्<BR>अर्थिन् (a r. अर्थ् s. इन्) petens, desiderans, egens, pauper.<BR>N. 13.11. 50. BH. 7.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=019-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्थीय<BR>अर्थीय (ab अर्थ s. ईय) causam, originem habens, commotus,<BR>pendens ex alq. r., positus in alq. r., obnoxius alicui.<BR>BH. 17.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=019-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्थेप्सु<BR>अर्थेप्सु (ex अर्थ et ईप्सु q. v.) divitiarum cupidus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=019-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्थेप्सुता<BR>अर्थेप्सुता f. (a praec. s. ता) status ejus, qui divitiarum cupidus<BR>est, divitiarum cupido. BR. 1.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=019-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्द्|अर्द्द्<BR>अर्द् 1. P. A. vexare. (Haec radix hucusque in part. pass. in<BR>त solum inventa est, cum praef. आ conjuncta, formans<BR>आर्दित et आर्त abjecto द् secundum gr. 615. Littera<BR>त् formae आर्त secundum gr. 103. duplicari potest,<BR>igitur primum त् in आर्त्त non pro transformatione euphonica<BR>litterae द् accipiendum est. Ubi आर्दित et<BR>आर्त vocem in अ aut आ exeuntem sequuntur, propter<BR>vocales coalescentes ab अर्दित et अर्त non distingui<BR>possunt; cum autem आर्त in positionibus non ambiguis<BR>inveniatur, in ambiguis quoque locis आर्दित et आर्त intelligenda<BR>esse censeo.) H. 1.4. 2.3. 5. N. 8.24. 12.106. 108.<BR>IN. 5.44. (Lat. ardeo, quod fortasse sensum primitivum<BR>radicis अर्द् exhibet).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=019-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्द्ध<BR>अर्द्ध, अर्ध<BR>1) Adj. dimidius.<BR>2) n. dimidium, dimidia pars.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=019-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्द्धचन्द्र<BR>अर्द्धचन्द्र m. (e praec. et चन्द्र m. luna)<BR>1) semiplena luna.<BR>2) sagitta, cujus acumen semiplenae lunae formam habet.<BR>DR. 9.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=019-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अर्द्धरात्र<BR>अर्द्धरात्र m. (ex अर्द्ध et रात्र, in fine comp. pro रात्रि, nox)<BR>media nox.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=019-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

