अल्प|अल्पं<BR>अल्प Adj. (v. gr. 251 et 280.) parum, paulum, exiguus. IN. 5.13.<BR>N. 25.13. (Huc retulerim lith. alpstù, ap-alpstù<BR>animus me liquit ich falle in Ohnmacht; praet. alp-aù,<BR>fut. alp-su, v. gr. comp. 498.; alkstù, praet. alk-aù, fut.<BR>alk-su fame uri ejusdem originis esse videtur, permutatâ<BR>labiali cum gutturali. Fortasse etiam gr. ὀλίγος huc<BR>pertinet, mutatâ tenui in mediam et inserto i sicut in<BR>δολιχός contra दीर्घ longus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=020-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

