अल्पदर्शन<BR>अल्पदर्शन (parum visus habens, BAH. ex अल्प et<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=020-b" target="_blank">Page020-b+ 37</a>]<BR>दर्शन n. visus) parum valens visu, parum intelligens,<BR>imprudens, stultus. H. 1.45.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=020-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

