अश्व|अश्वः<BR>अश्व m. equus (lat. equus, gr. ἵππος ex ἵϰϰος, per assimilationem<BR>ex ἵϰϜος, zend. 𐬀𐬯𐬞𐬀 aśpa - gr.<BR>comp. 50. - lith. áʃzwa equa, russ. kobyla, abjecto<BR>अ, व् mutato in b et inserto o sicut in sobàka canis =<BR>श्वन्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=023-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

