अष्टाङ्ग|अष्टांग<BR>अष्टाङ्ग n. (DVIGU ex अष्टन् et अङ्ग membrum) octo membra.<BR>Wils. «eight parts of the body, the hands. breast,<BR>forehead, eyes, throat and middle of the back; or four<BR>first, with the knees and feet; or these six with the words<BR>and mind».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=024-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

