अहार्य|अहार्य्य|अहार्य्यं|अहार्य्यः<BR>अहार्य m. (non capiendus, non abripiendus, ex अ<BR>priv. et हार्य a r. हृ s. य) mons. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=027-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अहि|अहिः<BR>अहि m. (r. अंह् ire s. इ) serpens (lat. anguis, gr. ἔνχε-λυς<BR>et ὄϕις, cum aspiratae saepe inter se permutentur; lith.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=027-b" target="_blank">Page027-b+ 19</a>]<BR>ungury-s, russ. ûgorj anguilla; ita nostrum Aal convenit<BR>cum scr. व्याल serpens).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=027-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अहिंसा<BR>अहिंसा f. (ex अ priv. et हिंसा offensio, a r. हिंस् suff. आ)<BR>mansuetudo, clementia, benevolentia. BH. 10.5. N. 6.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=027-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

