अहो<BR>अहो Interj. admirationis et lamentationis, ah! eheu. N. 3.17. 13.31.<BR>BR. 1.35. SA. 2.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=027-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अहोरात्र|अहोरात्रः<BR>अहोरात्र m. (DVANDV. ex अहस् q. v. et रात्र pro रात्रि gr. 681.<BR>nox) dies et nox. N. 12.61. 89. v. gr. 659.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=027-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

