आ<BR>आ Praep. praef.<BR>1) ad, v. gr. 111.<BR>2) in conjunctione cum<BR>ablat. substantivi, usque ad, tenus, aut cum inclusione<BR>aut cum exclusione rei. BH. 8.16. SAK. 21.4. In compositione<BR>cum vocibus quae colorem indicant idem valet quod<BR>lat. sub et nostrum suffixum lich, e. c. अनील subniger,<BR>schwärzlich.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=027-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आं<BR>आं Interj. nae, profecto, sane; sequente ज्ञातम् cognitum:<BR>UR. 2.2. SAK. 43.1.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=027-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

