आचमनीय|आचमनीयं<BR>आचमनीय n. (r. चम् praef. आ os eluere, s. अनीय) ori<BR>eluendo inserviens aqua. IN. 3.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=028-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आचार|आचारः<BR>आचार m. (r. चर् s. अ)<BR>1) actio; agendi, vivendi ratio,<BR>mores. BH. 3.6. 9.30.<BR>2) honesta vita, mores boni, morum<BR>probitas. SA. 6.16. (hibern. acara «convenience,<BR>conveniency, use», nisi pertinet ad r. कृ unde आकार; v.<BR>Pikt. p. 87.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=028-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

