आछादन|आच्छादन|आच्छादनं<BR>आछादन n. (r. छद् tegere s. अन)<BR>1) actio tegendi, inumbratio.<BR>SA. 3.20.<BR>2) vestis, vestitus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=028-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

