आडम्बर|आडंबरः|आडम्बरः<BR>आडम्बर m.<BR>1) clangor instrumentorum musicalium.<BR>2) elephantorum<BR>rugitus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=028-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आढक|आढकं|आढकः<BR>आढक m. modus frumentarius: «a measure of grain equal<BR>to 4 Prasthas, or containing nearly 7 pounds, 11 ounzes<BR>Avoirdupois». HIT. 5.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=028-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

