आतङ्क|आतंक|आतंकः|आतङ्कः<BR>आतङ्क m. (r. तङ्क् in miseria vivere s. अ)<BR>1) aegritudo.<BR>2) timor. DEV. 12.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=029-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आततायिन्<BR>आततायिन् (ex आतत extensus - a r. तन् s. त - et आयिन्<BR>iens a r. इ s. इन्) Adj. et Subst. m. scelestus, fur, praedo.<BR>BH. 1.36.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=029-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आतप|आतपः<BR>आतप m. (r. तप् calefacere, urere, s. अ) calor, ardor solis.<BR>UR. 62.13. 90.10. SAK. 43.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=029-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आतपत्र|आतपत्रं<BR>आतपत्र n. (a solis ardore tuens, e praec. et त्र a r.<BR>त्रा s. अ; cf. तनुत्र) umbella, «a large umbrella of silk<BR>or leaves». IN. 2.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=029-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

