आतोद्य|आतोद्यं<BR>आतोद्य n. (r. तुद् pulsare, percutere, s. य) instrumentum<BR>musicale. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=029-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आत्त<BR>आत्त v. दा praef. आ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=029-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

