आद्यन्तवत्|आद्यन्तवन्त्<BR>आद्यन्तवत् (ab आद्यन्त n. - DVAND. ex आदि et अन्त s.<BR>वत्) initium et finem habens. BH. 5.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आधार|आधारः<BR>आधार m. (r. धृ s. अ)<BR>1) fulcrum, fultura, transl. praesidium,<BR>subsidium. DEV. 11.3. HIT. 41.7.<BR>2) fossa aquaria,<BR>canalis. AM. (अम्भसां यत्र धारणम्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आधि|आधिः<BR>आधि m. (r. ध्यै meditari abjecto ऐ et य् mutato in इ) sollicitudo.<BR>N. 18.11. (Piktetius confert hibern. ead «zèle,<BR>jalousie»).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आधिपत्य|आधिपत्यं<BR>आधिपत्य n. (ab अधिपति dominus, imperator) dominium,<BR>imperium. BH. 2.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनक|आनकः<BR>आनक m. tympanum. BH. 1.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनन|आननं<BR>आनन n. (r. अन् spirare vel anomale producto अ vel<BR>praefixo praep. आ)<BR>1) os. BH. 11.24.<BR>2) facies, vultus.<BR>IN. 5.37.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनन्द|आनंदः|आनन्दः<BR>आनन्द m. (r. नन्द् gaudere s. अ) gaudium, laetitia, voluptas.<BR>HIT. 42.8. UR. 63.10.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनन्दथु|आनंदथु|आनन्दथुः<BR>आनन्दथु m. (r. नन्द् s. अथु) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनन्दन|आनंदन|आनन्दनं<BR>आनन्दन n. (r. नन्द् gaudere in form. caus. s. अन) actio<BR>exhilarandi, oblectandi. HIT. 43.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनयन|आनयनं<BR>आनयन n. (r. नी s. अन) adductio. N. 24.29.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनाय|आनायः<BR>आनाय m. (r. नी ducere s. अ) rete. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनील|आनीलः<BR>आनील (ex आ usque ad et नील niger) subniger, nigricans.<BR>UR. 84.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनुपूर्व्य|आनुपूर्व्यं<BR>आनुपूर्व्य n. (ab अनुपूर्व quod secundum ordinem est - BAH.<BR>ex अनु secundum et पूर्व n. prius - s. य, v. gr. 650.) ordo.<BR>A. 10.35. (cf. अनुपूर्वेण).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनृण्य|आनृण्यं<BR>आनृण्य n. Subst. abstr. ab अनृण q. v. s. य. SA. 5.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आनृशंस्य|आनृशंस्यं<BR>आनृशंस्य n. (ab अनृशंस non malitiosus - ex अ priv. et<BR>नृशंस - s. य, v. gr. 650.) humanitas, benignitas. N. 17.43.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आप्<BR>आप् 5. P.<BR>1) attingere alqm. locum, pervenire, venire.<BR>NALOD. 2.22.<BR>2) adipisci, nancisci. IN. 4.13. H. 2.31.<BR>BH. 3.2. (Lat. apio, aptus = आप्त, adipiscor, opto,<BR>quod sensu convenit cum DESID. ईप्स् pro आप्स्; opus,<BR>opera, ubi respiciendum, verba motionis in sanscrito<BR>saepissime etiam actionem significare; conferatur etiam<BR>capio, c̕-apio, cujus c ad praepositionem pertinere videtur, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-a" target="_blank">Page031-a+ 37</a>]<BR>porro cum Pottio, qui tamen capio rejicit, coepi ex<BR>co-ipi et côpula; gr. ἅπτω et, nisi fallor, πϱέπω quod<BR>facile ex composito प्राप्, correptâ vocali, oriri potuit;<BR>etiam πϱυμνός, πϱέμνον, mutato π in nasalem ejusdem<BR>ordinis (cf. σεμνός pro σεβνός) et formâ et sensu non<BR>repugnant nostrae radici, quae cum सम् format समाप्त<BR>finitus; germ. vet. uoban, nostrum üben, v. supra memoratum<BR>opus, opera et cf. Pott. I.255. et Graff I.70.).<BR>c. अभि i. q. simpl.; in forma caus. अभीप्स् (v. gr. 540.)<BR>desiderare. RAM. I.47.3.: स्वर्गङ् गन्तुम् अभीप्सति;<BR>I.31.31.: सेनापतिम् अभीप्सन्तः.<BR>c. अव i. q. simpl. H. 1.2. IN. 5.58. BR. 2.31. SU. 4.4.<BR>c. अव praef. सम् id. RAM. I.50.29.: ब्रह्मत्वं समवाप्स्यसि.<BR>c. प्र id. IN. 1.12. 4.4. 5.31. BH. 2.57. Form. caus. A. 4.23.<BR>c. प्र praef. अनु (अनुप्राप्) venire, pervenire. IN. 5.17. 34. H. 1.1.<BR>c. प्र praef. सम् (सम्प्राप्) id.<BR>IN. 5.4. H. 2.24. 4.27. BR. 1.23. N. 13.35. 21.1.<BR>c. प्र praef. उप + सम् (उपसम्प्राप्) id. N. 10.5.<BR>c. वि occupare, complecti, implere. BH. 10.16. 11.20. A. 10.53.<BR>c. सम् id. BH. 11.40. - समाप्त finitus. — Caus. perficere,<BR>e. c. यज्ञं समापयितुम् RAM. I.48.25.<BR>c. सम् praef. परि (परिसमाप्) id. BH. 4.33.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=030-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपक्व|आपक्वं<BR>आपक्व (ex आ usque ad et पक्व) semicoctus, semimaturus.<BR>AM. (Hib. âpuigh maturus).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपगा<BR>आपगा f. (ex आप aqua quod separatum non invenitur - v.<BR>अप् - et ग iens in fem.) fluvius. N. 12.36.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपण|आपणः<BR>आपण m. (r. पण् q. v. praef. आ s. अ) forum. SU. 2.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपत्ति|आपत्तिः<BR>आपत्ति f. (r. पद् ire s. ति) infortunium, calamitas. MED.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपद्<BR>आपद् f. (r. पद् ire) id. BR. 1.19. 34. (Hib. âpadh mors,<BR>âpthach mortalis).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपद्धर्म|आपद्धर्मः|आपद्धर्म्म<BR>आपद्धर्म m. (TATP. ex अपद् et धर्म) infortunii officium;<BR>Wils. «practice or profession other than that proper to<BR>caste, but allowable in time of distress». BR. 2.26. v.<BR>MAN. 10.81. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

