आपस्<BR>आपस् n. (ut videtur, a r. आप्, unde etiam अप्, quod in<BR>casibus fortibus plenam radicis formam servavit)<BR>1) aqua,<BR>2) peccatum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

