आपात|आपातः<BR>आपात m. (r. पत् cadere s. अ) actio decidendi, delabandi,<BR>irruendi, incursus, impetus. H. 2.9. de dentibus; UP. 6.<BR>de sagittis (cf. वाणनिपात A. 7.10.); A. 7.10. de equis.<BR>2) praesens momentum. MED.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपातदुःसह<BR>आपातदुःसह (KARM. e praec. et दुःसह q. v.) impetu<BR>difficilis sustentu. H. 2.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपान|आपानं<BR>आपान n. (ex आ et पान potus) locus potatorius. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपीड|आपीडः<BR>आपीड m. (r. पीड् s. अ) sertum, quod capitis vertici annectitur.<BR>A. 10.38. N. 12.103.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपीन|आपीनं|आपीनः<BR>आपीन n. (fortasse ab अप्, quod hîc lac significaret - cf.<BR>क्षीर, पयस् - s. ईन cum Vriddhi; nisi a पी bibere praef.<BR>आ, vel, secundum Wils. ex praep. आ et पीन pinguis)<BR>uber, οὖϑαϱ. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपूपिक|आपूपिकं|आपूपिकः<BR>आपूपिक m. (ex अपूप placenta, libum, s. इक) pistor. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आपोमय<BR>आपोमय (ex आपस् aqua s. मय) aquosus, aqua praeditus.<BR>DEV. 1.75. ubi आपोमयं pro अपोमयं legendum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आप्त|आप्तः<BR>आप्त (r. आप् s. त)<BR>1) obtentus, acceptus.<BR>2) aptus, idoneus<BR>(lat. aptus) v. sq.<BR>3) familiaris, consiliorum particeps.<BR>DEV. 1.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आप्तकारिन्<BR>आप्तकारिन् (KARM. e praec. et कारिन् faciens, agens, a r.<BR>कृ s. इन्) apte agens, familiaris. N. 8.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आप्तदक्षिण<BR>आप्तदक्षिण (BAH. ex आप्त aptus aut impetratus et दक्षिणा<BR>f. donum quod Brahmanis in solemnibus sacrificiis impertitur)<BR>apto sacrificali dono instructus. N. 5.46. 26.37.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आप्य|आप्यं<BR>आप्य Adj. (ab अप् aqua s. य) aquosus, aquaticus, humidus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आप्यायित|आप्यायितः<BR>आप्यायित (fortasse descendit ab आप्याय् humectare, rigare<BR>- ut DENOM. a praec. suff. य, gr. 585. - suff. त; etiam<BR>ab obsoleta radice प्यै vel प्याय् crescere, augere, suff.<BR>त deduci potest) primitive humefactus, rigatus significare<BR>videtur, vel, si a प्यै, प्याय् descendit, qui crevit,<BR>adultus, auctus; transl. recreatus, refectus, fortunatus.<BR>HIT. 25.2. RAM. I.56.15. N. 24.52.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=031-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आप्लव|आप्लवः<BR>आप्लव m. (r. प्लु praef. आ lavare, submergere, s. अ) lavatio,<BR>«bathing». AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आप्लाव|आप्लावः<BR>आप्लाव m. (r. प्लु s. अ) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आबाधा<BR>आबाधा f. (r. बाध् s. आ) vexatio, molestia, afflictatio. A. 2.17.<BR>H. 4.12. Scribitur quoque आवाधा.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आभरण|आभरणं<BR>आभरण n. (r. भृ ferre, s. अन) ornamentum, ornatus. H. 2.23.<BR>SA. 3.19. (Sic gr. ϕᾶϱος pallium a ferendo nominatur.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आभा<BR>आभा f. (r. भा splendere)<BR>1) splendor.<BR>2) similitudo. H. 4.48.<BR>N. 13.63. 21.9. (Hib. aoibh «likeness, similitude»;<BR>aoibe «neatness, elegance»; aoibheal «a spark of fire».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आभास्<BR>आभास् (in fine compositorum, gr. 642.; a r. भास्) collustrans.<BR>BH. 13.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आभील|आभीलं|आभीलः<BR>आभील (ut videtur, a भी timor s. ल vel इल, vel ईल - gr. 652.<BR>- praef. आ)<BR>1) Adj. terribilis, formidolosus.<BR>2) m.<BR>dolor. AM. (Hib. abhéil «terrible, dreadfull».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आभोग|आभोगः<BR>आभोग m. (r. भुज् edere s. अ) plenitas (secundum AM. =<BR>परिपूर्णता). SAK. 7.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आम|आमं|आमः<BR>आम<BR>1) Adj. crudus, incoctus, v. sq. (Hib. amh «raw, unsodden,<BR>crude, unripe». Piktet p. 14.).<BR>2) m. (a r. अम्<BR>aegrotum esse s. अ) aegritudo.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आमकुम्भ|आमकुम्भः<BR>आमकुम्भ m. (e praec. et कुम्भ) vas aquarium ex argilla<BR>incocta. HIT. 124.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आमत्य<BR>आमत्य n. (ab आमत n. cogitatum - a r. मन् s. त - s. य)<BR>cogitatio, sententia, consilium. SA. 7.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आमनस्य|आमनस्यं<BR>आमनस्य n. (quod a sensu mentis abstrahit, ex<BR>अमनस् mentis expers, s. य) tormentum, cruciatus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आमय|आमयं|आमयः<BR>आमय m. (r. अम् aegrotum esse) morbus (v. अनामय).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आमयाविन्<BR>आमयाविन् (ex आमया fem. praec. s. विन्) aegrotus.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आमर्ष|आमर्षः<BR>आमर्ष m. (ex अमर्ष q. v. s. अ) ira, iracundia. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आमात्य|आमात्यः<BR>आमात्य m. (ab अमात्य q. v.) qui est a consiliis.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आमिष|आमिषं<BR>आमिष m. n.<BR>1) caro. BR. 2.12.<BR>2) voluptas. DR. 8.38.<BR>(cf. मांस, lith. miesá caro).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आम्नाय|आम्नायः<BR>आम्नाय m. (r. म्ना meditari s. य) nomen Vêdorum. N. 12.59.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आम्भस|आंभस<BR>आम्भस (ab अम्भस् aqua, s. अ) quosus. M. 43. (hîc neutrum [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">Page032-b+ 37</a>]<BR>sensu aqua substantive positum est: {#sarvam AmBasam<BR>evA ''sIt KaYca dyOSca#} universum erat aqua et<BR>aër et coelum).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आम्र|आम्रः<BR>आम्र m. nomen arboris, «the mango tree, Magnifera Indica».<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आय|आयः<BR>आय m. (r. या ire s. अ) reditus, quaestus. HIT. 61.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयत|आयतः<BR>आयत (r. यम् s. त) longus. IN. 2.24. N. 11.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयतन|आयतनं<BR>आयतन n. (r. यत् s. अन)<BR>1) habitatio, sedes, domicilium.<BR>HIT. 26.10.<BR>2) altare, ara, etiam tectum, receptaculum<BR>ad peragendum sacrificium. IN. 5.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयति|आयतिः<BR>आयति f. (r. यम् s. ति)<BR>1) longitudo.<BR>2) potestas. AM.<BR>(= प्रभाव).<BR>3) tempus futurum. AM.; HIT. 60.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयत्त|आयत्तः<BR>आयत्त (r. यत् s. त)<BR>1) propensus, pronus, propitius. H. 54.5.<BR>2) subjectus, obnoxius. HIT. 69.17. 130.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयत्ति|आयत्तिः<BR>आयत्ति f. (r. यत् s. ति)<BR>1) inclinatio, propensio, favor.<BR>2) actio se subjiciendi alicui, servitus, obedientia. cf.<BR>आयत्त.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयस|आयसं<BR>आयस Adj. (ab अयस् ferrum s. अ) ferreus. A. 9.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयाम|आयामः<BR>आयाम m. (r. यम् s. अ)<BR>1) refrenatio, retentio. BH. 4.29.<BR>2) longitudo cf. आयति.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयामवत्|आयामवन्त्<BR>आयामवत् (a praec. s. वत्) longus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयास|आयासः<BR>आयास m. (r. यस् anniti, operam dare, s. अ) contentio,<BR>labor. BH. 18.24.<BR>2) aerumna, miseria, calamitas.<BR>DR. 6.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयुध|आयुधं|आयुधः<BR>आयुध m. (r. युध् pugnare s. अ) telum, arma.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयुष्मत्|आयुष्मन्त्<BR>आयुष्मत् (a sq. मत् gr. 101^a).) longam vitae aetatem<BR>promittens, longa aetate gaudens, ad summam senectutem<BR>veniens. N. 15.12. 16.29. UR. 92.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आयुस्<BR>आयुस् n. (r. इ ire s. उस्<BR>1) aetas.<BR>2) vitae tempus. SA. 2.23. 25. 27. 6.19. 41.<BR>(dor. αἰές; fortasse etiam αἰών huc<BR>trahendum est, quanquam alio suffixo formatum, cf. Pott. I.114.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

