आयोधन|आयोधनं<BR>आयोधन n. (r. युद् s. अन)<BR>1) pugna, proelium.<BR>2) locus<BR>pugnae. DR. 8.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आरक्त<BR>आरक्त v. रञ्ज् praef. आ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आरक्त<BR>आरक्त (ex praep. आ et रक्त ruber) subruber. UR. 60.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=032-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आरण्यक<BR>आरण्यक (ab अरण्य silva s. क)<BR>1) Adj. silvester.<BR>2) m.<BR>silvicola, eremita.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

