आरम्भ|आरंभः|आरम्भः<BR>आरम्भ m. (r. रभ् praef. आ incipere, inserto म्, s. अ) inceptio.<BR>BH. 3.4. 12.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आरव|आरवः<BR>आरव m. (r. रु sonare s. अ) sonus, clamor. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आरात्<BR>आरात् Adv.<BR>1) procul.<BR>2) prope. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आराति|आरातिः<BR>आराति m. hostis, inimicus. AM. (cf. अराति).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आराधन|आराधनं<BR>आराधन n. (r. राध् praef. आ in forma caus. colere, s. अन)<BR>cultus, veneratio, actio exhilarandi (AM. तोषणे). N. 5.21.<BR>UR. 90.8.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आराम|आरामः<BR>आराम m. (r. रम् gaudere s. अ)<BR>1) gaudium. BH. 3.16. 5.24.<BR>2) hortus. AM. (Gr. ἠϱέμα, ἔϱημος? v. r. रम् praef.<BR>वि et Pott. I.262.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आराव|आरावः<BR>आराव m. (r. रु sonare, s. अ) clamor, tumultus, strepitus.<BR>HIT. 111.20. N. 13.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आरुरुक्षु<BR>आरुरुक्षु (r. रुह् in form. desid. रुरुक्ष्, s. उ) ascendendi cupidus.<BR>BH. 6.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आरोग्य|आरोग्यं<BR>आरोग्य n. (ex अरोग q. v. s. य) sanitas. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

