आरोह|आरोहः<BR>आरोह m. (r. रुह् praef. आ ascendere, s. अ)<BR>1) vectus equo,<BR>elephanto, etc. DR. 8.7. 22.<BR>2) medium feminae corpus,<BR>«the waist».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्जव|आर्जवं<BR>आर्जव n. (a ऋजु rectus, erectus, s. अ, gr. 650.) Abstractumvocis<BR>ऋजु rectus: «straightness», transl. sinceritas.<BR>HIT. 66.10. BH. 13.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्त|आर्त्त|आर्त्तः<BR>आर्त aut आर्त्त (r. अर्द् vexare q. v. praef. आ s. त) vexatus,<BR>afflictus, praecipue in fine comp. H. 1.4. 2.5. Extra<BR>compositionem, afflictus, tristis, miser. N. 12.108. 13.64.<BR>BH. 7.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्तव|आर्त्तव|आर्त्तवं|आर्त्तवः<BR>आर्तव (a ऋतु s. अ, v. gr. 650.) anni tempori consentaneus.<BR>H. 1.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्ति|आर्तिः|आर्त्ति|आर्त्तिः<BR>आर्ति aut आर्त्ति f. (r. अर्द् q. v. praef. आ s. ति) dolor,<BR>moestitia, tristitia, angor. SU. 1.16. 3.1. BR. 1.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्दन<BR>आर्दन m. (r. अर्द् vexare praef. आ suff. अन) vexator.<BR>BH. 1.39.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्दित<BR>आर्दित (r. अर्द् vexare praef. आ s. त) vexatus, afflictus.<BR>H. 2.3. N. 12.106. Cf. आर्त्त.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्द्र|आर्द्रं<BR>आर्द्र madidus, uvidus, humidus. H. 4.55. (sequitur ex hoc<BR>vocabulo, radicem अर्द् vel आर्द् extitisse, quae irrigare<BR>vel simile quid significaverit et accurate cum gr. ἄϱδω<BR>convenit).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्य|आर्य्य|आर्य्यः<BR>आर्य (ut videtur, a r. ऋ vel simpl. vel cum praep. आ comp.<BR>s. य, nisi corruptum est ex आर्च्य vel अर्च्य a r. अर्च्<BR>q. v.) venerandus, nobilis, generosus. H. 4.30. BH. 2.2.<BR>HIT. 117.1. 4. (Cf. germ. vet. êra, nostrum Ehre).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आर्यपुत्र|आर्यपुत्रः|आर्य्यपुत्त्रः|आर्य्यपुत्र<BR>आर्यपुत्र m. (e praec. et पुत्र filius) in lingua scenica maritus.<BR>UR. 31.2.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आलम्भ|आलंभः|आलम्भः<BR>आलम्भ m. (r. लभ् insertâ nasali, s. अ) occisio, caedes.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आलय|आलयं|आलयः<BR>आलय m. (r. ली s. अ) domicilium, domus, sedes. N. 7.18.<BR>DR. 1.13. SA. 6.44. BH. 8.15. A. 5.25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आलवाल|आलवालं<BR>आलवाल m. fossa aquaria circa arboris radicem. UR. 34.2.<BR>(cf. आवाल).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आलस्य|आलस्यं|आलस्यः<BR>आलस्य n. (ab अलस piger s. य) pigritia, ignavia, inertia.<BR>BH. 14.8. 18.39. HIT. 45.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=033-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

