आवाप|आवापः<BR>आवाप m. (r. वप् s. अ)<BR>1) fossa aquaria circa arboris radicem.<BR>AM.<BR>2) armilla. HEM. v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

