आवाल|आवालं<BR>आवाल m. (r. वल् s. अ) fossa aquaria circa arboris radicem.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आवास|आवासः<BR>आवास m. (r. वस् s. अ) habitatio, domus. HEM. (Hib.<BR>aras id. arasaim habito, mutato v in r, v. gr. comp. 20. et<BR>cf. goth. razn domus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आविर्<BR>आविर् v. आविस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आविल<BR>आविल (deduci solet a r. विल् s. अ) turbidus. N. 13.7.<BR>(Secundum Haughtonium etiam «sinful, guilty» quod in<BR>memoriam mihi reducit nostrum übel, goth. ubils Th.<BR>ubila, angl. evil, quae supra (p. 14.) cum अबल et अधर<BR>comparavimus. Litterae व् et ब् autem saepissime inter<BR>se permutantur et quodvis sanscritum व् in lingua<BR>bengalica sonat b, ubi vocabulum nostrum âbilo effertur.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आविस्<BR>आविस् Adv. insep. palam, manifesto. Componitur cum radicibus<BR>भू esse et कृ facere ad exprimendum apparere, in<BR>conspectum venire, oriri; manifestare. HIT. 63.12. UR. 6.12.<BR>आविर्भूते शशिनि. Huc retulerim lat. or in orior<BR>ejectâ syllabâ vi, fere sicut malo pro mavolo. Probabiliter<BR>आविस् ex origine est praepositio inseparabilis,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">Page034-b+ 37</a>]<BR>quae significaverit ex, ita ut आविष्कृ proprie sit herausmachen<BR>«facere ut aliquis egrediatur ex occulto», et<BR>आविर्भू heraussein, herauswerden, «foras esse, foras<BR>fieri». Res si ita se habet, explicaverim ex hac praepositione<BR>lat. et gr. ex, ἐξ, ejecto î et v mutato in gutturalem,<BR>sicut e. c. in vixi e vivsi, in facio = भावयामि, v.<BR>gr. comp. 19. Pottius tamen formas ex, ἐξ deducit ab<BR>idem valente scr. वहिस्, quae explicatio egregie cadit<BR>in linguam graecam, quippe quae in initio vocum semivocalem<BR>v ubique expulerit. Latina autem lingua eam<BR>constanter servavit, quam ob rem etiam Pottius formas<BR>ἐξ, ex non directe ad वहिस् sed ad suppositum अवहिस्<BR>retulit. E goth. lingua ad आविस् traxerim praep.<BR>plerumque praefixam us, germ. vet. ar, ur, ir, ër, nostrum<BR>er, - Grimm III.253. - quas formas ab आविस्<BR>ita derivatas esse censeo, ut media syllaba vi sit ejecta, â<BR>initiale autem in vocalem leviorem sit conversum; lith.<BR>iʃz ex; hib. as ex.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आवृत्ति|आवृत्तिः<BR>आवृत्ति f. (r. वृत् s. ति) reditus, recessus. A. 5.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आवेग|आवेगः<BR>आवेग m. (r. विज् s. अ) sollicitudo, consternatio, perturbatio.<BR>UR. 31.2.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आश<BR>आश m. (r. अश् s. अ) cibus, in comp. c. प्रातर् q. v. (Hib.<BR>es, nisi hoc a lat. esca, v. Pikt. p. 64.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशंसा<BR>आशंसा f. (r. शंस् praef. आ sperare, s. आ) spes. UR. 9.3.infr.<BR>(cf. आशिस्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशङ्का|आशंका<BR>आशङ्का f. (r. शङ्क् s. आ) timor. SAK. 7.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशय|आशयः<BR>आशय m. (r. शी dormire, jacere, s. अ) cubile, sedes, domicilium.<BR>BH. 15.8. HIT. 39.8. V. महाशय.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशा<BR>आशा f. spes. SA. 3.11. BH. 16.12. (cf. आशिस्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशावत्|आशावन्त्<BR>आशावत् (a praec. s. वत्) spe praeditus, sperans. HIT. 22.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशिन्<BR>आशिन् (r. अश् edere, s. इन्) edens. BH. 3.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशिरःपादम्<BR>आशिरःपादम् (AVY. ex आ usque ad et शिरस् + पाद in<BR>comp. DVANDV. v. gr. 660.) inde a capite usque ad pedes,<BR>ad litteram: usque ad caput et pedes. UP. 51.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशिस्<BR>आशिस् f.<BR>1) spes. BH. 4.21. 6.10.<BR>2) fausta precatio, benedictio.<BR>SA. 4.12. (prior significatio a rad. शंस् praef.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">Page035-a+ 37</a>]<BR>आ sperare - cf. आशंसा - altera a शास् fausta precari,<BR>benedicere, mutatâ vocali radicali in इ, derivatur.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=034-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशी<BR>आशी f. serpentis dens eminens; v. आशीविष.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशीर्वाद|आशीर्वादः|आशीर्व्वादः<BR>आशीर्वाद m. (TATP. ex अशिस् - v. gr. 73. et 192. - et वाद<BR>sermo) fausta precans dictum, benedictio. N. 18.21. IN. 2.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशीविष|आशीविषः<BR>आशीविष m. (BAH. ex आशी et विष venenum) serpens.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशु|आशुः<BR>आशु Adv. celeriter, cito. (Neutrum perditi Adjectivi cu<BR>gr. ὠϰύς respondet; lat. acu-pedeus apud Festum. Huc<BR>etiam cum Pottio 2.54. trahimus aqui-la, ita ut τῶ उ<BR>vocis आशु vocalis i sit adjecta sicut e. c. in tenui-s e<BR>तनु; etiam accipiter, quod male ab accipiendo deducitur;<BR>est velociter volans vel potius veloces alas habens<BR>(ὠϰύπτεϱος), ita ut acci ortum sit assimilatione ex<BR>aqvi sicut e. c. gr. τέσσαϱες et prâcr. चत्तारो = चत्वारस्,<BR>v. gr. comp. 312. E german. vet. huc retulerim<BR>Verba âhtian, âhtên, âhtôn persequi, quae a Substantivo<BR>âh-ta persecutio, proscriptio, quod est nostrum Acht,<BR>descendunt. In Sanscrito ipso vox अश्व equus originem<BR>trahere videtur ex nostro आशु, ita ut sit correpta ex<BR>आश्व vel आशव et equus a velocitate sit nominatus,<BR>cui qualitati etiam nomina तुरग, तुरङ्ग et तुरङ्गम debet.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशुग|आशुगः<BR>आशुग m. (e praec. et ग iens, a r. गा suff. अ)<BR>1) ventus.<BR>2) sagitta.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशुत्व|आशुत्वं<BR>आशुत्व n. (ab आशु s. त्व) celeritas.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आशुशुक्षणि|आशुशुक्षणिः<BR>आशुशुक्षणि m. (celeriter siccans ex आशु et शुक्षणि<BR>a r. शुष् adjectâ sibilante, quâ cum Desiderativis convenit,<BR>suff. अनि)<BR>1) ignis. AM.<BR>2) aër, ventus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आश्चर्य|आश्चर्य्य|आश्चर्य्यं<BR>आश्चर्य (r. चर् praef. आ adjecto श् euphonico - v. gr. min. 111. ann. 2.<BR>- s. य<BR>1) Adj. mirus, mirabilis.<BR>2) Subst. n.<BR>miraculum. N. 23.14. BH. 2.29. 11.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आश्चर्यमय<BR>आश्चर्यमय Adj. (a praec. s. मय) miraculosus, mirabilis.<BR>BH. 11.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आश्रम|आश्रमं|आश्रमः<BR>आश्रम m. (r. श्रम् s. अ) eremitarum sedes.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आश्रय|आश्रयः<BR>आश्रय m. (r. श्रि ire, s. अ)<BR>1) aditio, appropinquatio,<BR>(praesertim tutelae, defensionis, patrocinii causâ), actio<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-b" target="_blank">Page035-b+ 37</a>]<BR>confugiendi, refugiendi ad aliquem.<BR>2) perfugium, refugium,<BR>domicilium, domus.<BR>3) vicinitas.<BR>4) fraus, fallacia,<BR>dolus. BH. 4.20. SA. 6.7. IN. 4.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आश्रयाश|आश्रयाशः<BR>आश्रयाश m. (ex आश्रय domus et आश edens) ignis. HIT. 76.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आष्ट्र|आष्ट्रं<BR>आष्ट्र n. aether, coelum. (A. 10.53. pro आष्ट्रैश् cum ed.<BR>Calc. legendum est आस्यैश्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आस्<BR>आस् 2. A.<BR>1) sedere. BR. 1.2. N. 1.18. BH. 2.54. 3.6.<BR>2) esse (ita स्था stare item significat esse). N. 16.30.<BR>HIT. 44.11. UR. 70.19.: तूष्णीम् एवा ऽऽस्ते; 92.8.:<BR>आयुष्मान् आस्ताम् अयम्; in Pass. HIT. 57.17.: {#tUzRIm<BR>AsyatAm#}. (Gr. ἧ(σ)-μαι, ἧσ-ται; e lat. lingua<BR>cum Pottio huc traxerim âsa, unde serior forma<BR>âra, porro â-nus pro âs-nus (cf. आसन). Fortasseradix<BR>verbi substantivi अस् correpta est ex आस्).<BR>c. अधि<BR>1) insidere c. acc. loci. UR. 62.13.: {#jamBUviwapam<BR>ADyAste#}.<BR>2) tenere, inhabitare.<BR>2) tenere, inhabitare. SA. 7.7. MAN. 7.77.<BR>RAM. ed. Ser. I.57.2.<BR>c. अनु i. q. simpl. N. 7.3.<BR>c. उत् v. उदासीन.<BR>c. उप<BR>1) assidere. SA. 6.25. In Passivo: SAK. 45.14.<BR>2) colere, venerari, ministrare, servire. BH. 9.15. (schol.<BR>उपासते सेवन्ते), 12.2. 6. N. 26.33.<BR>3) peragere, perficere.<BR>RAM. ed. Ser. I.29.21.: स्वयंवरम् उपास्महे.<BR>4) perferre, tolorare. DR. 4.20.<BR>c. उप praef. परि (पर्युपास्)<BR>1) circumsedere, trop. colere.<BR>N. 1.11. (पर्युपासच् छचीम् secundum prim. classem<BR>PAR. pro पर्युपास्त शचीम्). BH. 9.22. 12.1. 3.<BR>2) adesse, interesse, e. c. pugnae. A. 8.20.<BR>c. सम् simul, junctim sedere. SA. 6.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आस|आसः<BR>आस m. (r. अस् conjicere, s. अ) arcus. HEM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आसक्त|आसक्तं|आसक्तः<BR>आसक्त v. सज्ज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

आसङ्ग|आसंग|आसङ्गं<BR>आसङ्ग m. (r. सञ्ज् s. अ) Subst. abstr. adhaesio, trop. addictum,<BR>deditum, studiosum esse. BH. 4.20. (cf. सङ्ग).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

