आसन|आसनं|आसनः<BR>आसन n. (r. आस् s. अन)<BR>1) sessio. N. 2.4.<BR>2) mora, commoratio.<BR>HIT. 119.17.<BR>3) sedes, sedile. SA. 3.6. IN. 2.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=035-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

