इङ्ख्|इंख्<BR>इङ्ख् 1. P. (गतौ, grammatici scribunt इख्, v. gr. 110^a).)<BR>ire. (cf. ईङ्ख् et hib. imchim «I go on, proceed,<BR>march».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इङ्ग्|इंग्<BR>इङ्ग् 1. P. A. (Grammatici scribunt इग्, gr. 110^a).) se movere,<BR>vacillare. M. 29. BH. 6.19. 14.23. (hib. ing «a<BR>stir, move»).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इङ्ग|इंग|इङ्गं|इङ्गः<BR>इङ्ग Adj. (r. इङ्ग् s. अ) se movens. M. 29. (cf. अङ्ग् et<BR>gr. ἐπείγω et v. इख्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इङ्गित|इंगित|इङ्गितं<BR>इङ्गित n. (r. इङ्ग् s. त) gestus. N. 2.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इङ्गुद|इंगुद|इंगुदः|इङ्गुदः<BR>इङ्गुद m. nomen plantae. N. 12.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इच्छा<BR>इच्छा f. (r. इछ्, gr. 88., s. आ) desiderium. BH. 5.28. 7.27.<BR>(Hib. ithche «a petition, request, favor».).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इच्छु|इच्छुः<BR>इच्छु Adj. (r. इछ् s. उ) desiderans.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इछ्|इच्छ्<BR>इछ् 6. P. (इच्छामि gr. 88.) desiderare, optare. In temp.<BR>specialibus solum usurpatur, ubi radicis इष्, quae his<BR>temp. caret, locum tenet. v. इष्. (Germ. vet. eiscôm<BR>posco, peto, nostrum heische; lith. jeszkau quaero; fortasse<BR>etiam germ. vet. forscôm inquiro - nostrum forsche<BR>- huc pertinet, ita ut sit pro for-iscôm; v. Pott. I.269.<BR>et Graff. I.493.; de sc pro छ् v. gr. comp. 14.; e<BR>graeca lingua huc trahi possit αἶσχος, ita ut cum particula<BR>negativa sit conflatum - sicut dedecus - et proprie<BR>significet non desiderandum, cum σχ pro छ् sicut<BR>in σχίζω = छिद्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इज्<BR>इज् v. यज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इज्या<BR>इज्या f. (r. यज् q. v. s. या) sacrificium. BH. 9.25. 11.53.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इट्<BR>इट् 1. P. (गत्याम्) ire (ortum esse videtur ex trita radice<BR>अट्, attenuato अ in इ, quâ in re formae इट् et अट्<BR>eandem rationem inter se tenent quam goth. Praesentia<BR>veluti lisa lego eorumque Praeterita sing. quae primitivum<BR>a servarunt, sicut las, v. gr. comp. 109^a).<BR>1) p. 116.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इट्चर|इट्चरः<BR>इट्चर m. (ad voluntatem iens ex इष् desiderans - v.<BR>gr. 74. - et चर iens) taurus libertate gaudens. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इडा<BR>इडा f. i. q. इला ex quo ortum esse dicitur, quum ड् fere<BR>sicut र् pronuncietur, र् autem et ल् saepissime inter se<BR>permutentur.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इत्<BR>इत् ut mihi videtur, neutrum stirpis pronominalis ई, quod<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-b" target="_blank">Page038-b+ 37</a>]<BR>in dialecto Vêd. aliis tertiae personae pronominibus adjungitur;<BR>v. Addenda ad gr. cr. 270. et gr. comp. 360.<BR>(Lat. id, goth. ita, germ. vet. iz, nostrum es).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतर|इतरः<BR>इतर (a stirpe pronominali इ s. तर, gr. 277.) alius. BH. 3.21.<BR>(lat. iterum, v. gr. comp. 292.; hib. itir id.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतरेतर|इतरेतरं<BR>इतरेतर (ex इतर + इतर, sensu et constructione cum<BR>अन्योन्य q. v. convenit, a quo in formatione eo solum<BR>dissidet, quod prius इतर, quanquam nominativum exprimat,<BR>vera vocis stirps est, nisi इतरेतर in {#itarA +<BR>itara#} dissolvere mavis, ita ut, quod mihi magis placet,<BR>prius compositi membrum Nominat. fem. sit, qui aliorum<BR>generum quoque vice fungatur) i. q. अन्योन्य q. v.<BR>A. 9.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतस्<BR>इतस् Adv. (a stirpe pronominali इ s. तस् gr. 652.)<BR>1) hinc,<BR>ab hoc loco. N. 2.13. 12.121. 18.18. BH. 14.1.<BR>2) in<BR>comparativis constructionibus saepe ablativi अस्मात् substantive<BR>positi locum tenet. H. 1.5. BH. 5.7.<BR>3) ante ततस्,<BR>aut इतस् repetitum, interposito च, accusativi, directionem<BR>versus locum exprimentis, vel locativi vim habet,<BR>et tum prius इतस् significat huc vel hîc, posterius<BR>illuc vel illic. N. 10.4. 11.13. 19. DR. 8.25. Etiam<BR>semel positum इतस् interdum huc et hîc significat.<BR>SAK. 8.9. 40.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इति|इतिः<BR>इति Adv. (ut equidem puto, a stirpe pronom. इ s. ति) sic.<BR>BH. 18.78. UR. 16. Saepissime hoc adverbium, aut supplendo<BR>aut apposito verbo dicere vel cogitare, usurpatur<BR>ad indicandum sermonem vel cogitationem directe<BR>introductam, et plerumque introducta verba sequitur,<BR>nonnunquam etiam eis interponitur. H. 4.21. BR. 3.4.<BR>SU. 1.23. 32. SA. 1.23. DR. 1.10. 7.27. A. 9.30. 31. RAM. ed. Ser. III.44.12. 14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतिकर्तव्यता|इतिकर्त्तव्यता<BR>इतिकर्तव्यता f. (Abstractum vocis इतिकर्तव्य sic faciendum<BR>s. ता) rei faciendae status. SA. 3.7. HIT. 42.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतिमात्र<BR>इतिमात्र (BAH. e praec. et मात्र n. mensura, modis) talem<BR>mensuram i. e. qualitatem, conditionem habens, talis.<BR>BR. 3.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतिहास|इतिहासः<BR>इतिहास m. narratio, historia ex antiquissimo tempore.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-a" target="_blank">Page039-a+ 36</a>]<BR>SU. 1.1. (Ut videtur, ex इति sic, expletivo ह et आस<BR>fuit, quod hac in compositione substantivi naturam assumsit.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=038-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इत्थम्<BR>इत्थम् (ex perdito Neutro इत् = lat. id - quod hac in formatione<BR>Thematis loco fungitur - v. gr. 263. - s. थम् cui<BR>respondet lat. tem in i-tem, au-tem, gr. comp. 425.) sic,<BR>ita. SAK. 50.4. HIT. 75.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इत्यर्थम्<BR>इत्यर्थम् Adv. (ex इति sic et अर्थम् propter) ideo, hanc<BR>ob causam. BR. 3.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इत्वर|इत्वरः<BR>इत्वर (r. इ ire s. वर, inserto त्)<BR>1) iens, peregrinans.<BR>2) vilis, abjectus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इत्वरी<BR>इत्वरी f. (Fem. praeced.) femina impudica. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इदम्<BR>इदम् Pronom. demonstr. (Nom. m. अयम्, f. इयम्, n.<BR>इदम्, v. gr. 270. et cf. lat. idem) hic. Hoc pronomen,<BR>ubi ad sermonem spectat, semper verbis dicendis anteponitur,<BR>quâ in re, quod primus Rückertus ingeniose observavit<BR>(*), ab एतत् et एतावत् se distinguit, quippe quae<BR>ad res narratas referuntur; e. c. N. 6.5.: उवाचेऽदं वचनम्<BR>dixit hunc sermonem, qui sequentibus versibus<BR>continetur; 7.4.: आहेऽदम् एहि दीव्य नलेन वै dixit<BR>hoc: veni, lude cum Nalo; N. 3.25.: {#etadarTam aham<BR>Badre prezitaH surasattamEH . etac CrutvA SuBe budDiN<BR>kuruzva#} hujus (quod dixi) causâ ego, beata! missus a Deorum<BR>optimis; hoc audito, pulchra! consilium fac. Violatur<BR>tamen haec lex N. 9.15. ubi वाक्यम् एतद् spectat<BR>ad verba sequentia. — Nonnunquam nominativus hujus<BR>pronominis adverbiorum pronominalium loco fungitur, ita<BR>ut e. c. UR. 46.10. dicatur अयम् अस्मि hic sum pro<BR>इहा ऽस्मि hîc sum; SAK. 51.3.: अयं स hic is pro {#iha<BR>sa#} hîc is; H. 1.34.: से ऽयम् ea haec pro सेऽह ea hîc;<BR>1.36.: सो ऽयम् is hic pro स इह is hîc; 1.38.: {#tO…<BR>imO#} uterque hic pro तौ…इह uterque hîc. Has locutiones<BR>per attractionis vim explicandas esse censeo,<BR>quam Subjectum sententiae, vel pronomine separato vel<BR>Verbi terminatione indicatum, in alias expressiones pronominales<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">Page039-b+ 36</a>]<BR>exercet. Ita res se habet in pronomine तत्,<BR>cujus casus obliqui non raro per attractionis vim Nominativi<BR>item in Nominativum vertuntur, ita ut Adverbiorum<BR>aut Conjunctionum loco fungantur; e. c. BR. 2.13. et H. 3.4.:<BR>सा ऽहम् ideo ego = तेनाऽहम्; BR. 2.34.: {#sa…<BR>aham#} ideo ego; BR. 1.7.: सा चिन्तये ideo cogito; SAK. 40.4.infr.:<BR>स भवान् ideo tu; DR. 5.12.: {#sA kzipram<BR>AtizWa gajam#} ideo cito ascende elephantum. — Eodem<BR>modo Pronomen एतत् usurpatur, e. c. H. 3.19.: {#eza<BR>tAn…hanizyAmi#} ideo hos occidam; A. 3.24.: {#eza te<BR>…darpaM hanmi#} ideo tuam superbiam deleo; H. 4.15.b.:<BR>एष त्वाम्…निहन्मि dum te occido. Ita quoque Relativum<BR>attractionis vi est subjectum, non solum Nominativi<BR>sed etiam obliquorum casuum, e. c. RAM. ed. Schl. I.59.5.:<BR>यस् त्वम् quia tu; H. 1.35.: योहम् quod ego<BR>«daʃs ich»; 1.47. 22.: यस्य मे quia mei; H. 3.19.: {#yAn<BR>imAn#} quia hos. (*)<BR>(*) Berlin. Jahrb. Jul. 1831. p. 89.<BR>(*) Cf. Rückert l. c. p. 92.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इदानीम्<BR>इदानीम् (e stirpe pronom. इ s. दानीम् nisi potius e perdito<BR>Adverbio इदा - secundum analogiam vocum {#tadA,<BR>yadA#} etc. - s. नीम्, v. gr. 652. suff. दानीम्) nunc. HIT. 5.20.;<BR>explet. SA. 2.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इध्म|इध्मं|इध्मः<BR>इध्म n. (r. इन्ध् urere ejecto न् s. म) lignum. AM. (Hib.<BR>adhmad nititur formâ gunatâ, cf. zend. 𐬀𐬈𐬯𐬨𐬀 aêśma<BR>et v. Pikt. p. 19.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन|इनः<BR>इन m.<BR>1) sol.<BR>2) dominus. AM. (Hib. ion sol.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्|इंद्<BR>इन्द् 1. P. (परमैश्वर्ये, scribunt इद्, gr. 110^a).) regere, imperare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्दिरा|इंदिरा<BR>इन्दिरा f. (r. इन्द् s. इर in fem.) nomen deae Lakshmiae.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्दीवर|इंदीवर|इंदीवरं|इन्दीवरं<BR>इन्दीवर n. lotus caerulea (Nymphaea caerulea). IN. 1.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्दु|इंदुः|इन्दुः<BR>इन्दु m. luna.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्दुशेखर|इन्दुशेखरः<BR>इन्दुशेखर m. (lunâ coronatus, BAH. ex इन्दु et शेखर<BR>sertum floreum, quod capiti imponitur). nomen Sivi.<BR>UP. 20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=039-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्र|इंद्रः|इन्द्रः<BR>इन्द्र m. (r. इन्द् s. र)<BR>1) in fine compositorum princeps,<BR>dominus, imperator. IN. 1.1. 5.62. H. 3.18.<BR>2) nomen<BR>principis deorum inferioris ordinis i. e. omnium<BR>praeter Brahmam, Vischnum et Sîvum. Deus est aëris<BR>et tempestatis, etiam unus est mundi custodum (लोकपालानाम्)<BR>et ut talis orientalem plagam regit. N. 4.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्रगोप|इन्द्रगोपः<BR>इन्द्रगोप m. (ex इन्द्र et गोप q. v.) scarabaeorum species,<BR>Wils. «a kind of lady bird». UR. 61.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्रद्रु|इन्द्रद्रुः<BR>इन्द्रद्रु m. (ex इन्द्र et द्रु arbor) nomen arboris cujusdam<BR>(Pentaptera arjuna). AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्रप्रस्थ|इंद्रप्रस्थ|इन्द्रप्रस्थं<BR>इन्द्रप्रस्थ m. (ex इन्द्र et प्रस्थ planities in montis vertice)<BR>nomen antiquae urbis Dehli.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्रसेन|इन्द्रसेनः<BR>इन्द्रसेन m. (BAH. ex इन्द्र et सेना exercitus) nom. pr.<BR>DR. 8.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्राणी|इंद्राणी<BR>इन्द्राणी f. (ex इन्द्र s. आनी, v. gr. min. 218.) nomen Indri<BR>uxoris.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्रायुध|इन्द्रायुधं<BR>इन्द्रायुध m. (ex इन्द्र et आयुध telum, arma) arcus coelestis.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्द्रिय|इंद्रिय|इन्द्रियं<BR>इन्द्रिय n. (ut videtur, ex इन्द्र s. इय) sensus (videndi, audiendi<BR>etc.). BH. 3.40. 10.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्ध्|इंध्<BR>इन्ध् 7. A. (दीप्तौ K. द्युतौ V.) lucere, flammare, flagrare.<BR>MAN. 8.115.: यम् इद्धो न दहत्य् अग्निः quem flagrans<BR>ignis non urit. (Gr. αἴϑω cum Guna immobili<BR>v. «Vocalismus» p. 196. - ἰϑαϱός; fortasse<BR>αἰϑήϱ, Αἴτ-νη, Pottius etiam Ἥϕ-αισ-τος confert; lat. aes-tus,<BR>aes-tas; germ. vet. eit ignis.<BR>c. सम् accendere, in dialecto Vêd. Ros. Sp. p. 20.3.: {#sam<BR>agnim inDate naraH#} ignem accendunt viri.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इन्धन|इंधन|इन्धनं<BR>इन्धन n. (r. इन्ध् s. अन) lignum. N. 13.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इभ|इभः<BR>इभ m. elephantus. AM. (Ag. Benary ingeniose huc trahit<BR>gr. ἐλ-έϕας, praefixo articulo semitico, et lat. ebur.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इभ्य|इभ्यः<BR>इभ्य (a praec. s. य) dives. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इम्व्<BR>इम्व् 1. P. (व्याप्तौ K. व्याप्तिप्रीणनयोः V., scribunt इव्,<BR>gr. 110^a).) occupare, exhilarare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इयत्|इयन्त्<BR>इयत् (in casibus fortibus इयन्त्, a stirpe pronom. इ s.<BR>अत् e वत् abjecto व्) tantum, tot. UR. 76.18.: {#iyantam<BR>kAlam#}. Huc traxerim lat. -iens, -ies in totiens,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">Page040-b+ 37</a>]<BR>toties, quotiens, quoties, et in Adverbiis numeralibus veluti<BR>quinquies, v. gr. comp. 324.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इयम्<BR>इयम् f. haec, ea, v. इदम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इयाय<BR>इयाय (r. इ, v. gr. 432. 436.) DR. 8.49.: समियाय.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इयीत<BR>इयीत (r. इ, gr. 346.) A. 2.16.: अधीयीत.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इयेष<BR>इयेष (r. इष्, v. gr. 432.) N. 26.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इरम्मद|इरंमद|इरम्मदः<BR>इरम्मद m. fulguratio, fulgetrum. AM.: = मेघज्योतिस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इरा<BR>इरा f.<BR>1) aqua.<BR>2) potus fervidus.<BR>3) sermo, loquela.<BR>4) terra. AM.: भूवाक्सुराप्सु स्यात् (cf. इला et hib.<BR>ire «ground, land, a field»).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इल्<BR>इल्<BR>1) 6. P. (गतौ K. शये गतौ क्षेपे V.) ire; jaculari; jacere,<BR>cubare.<BR>2) 10. P. (प्रेरणे K. क्षेपे V.) mittere; jaculari.<BR>(Germ. vet. îllu, îllo - per assimil. ex îlju - no strum<BR>eile; cambro-brit. il progressio, motus; gr. ἐλάω.<BR>Radix sanscr. orta esse videtur ex अर् - v. ऋ - mutato<BR>र् in ल् et अ attenuato in इ, eâdem ratione quâ supra<BR>इट् ex अट् explicavimus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इला<BR>इला f. (r. इल् s. आ)<BR>1) vacca.<BR>2) terra.<BR>3) sermo, loquela.<BR>AM. (गोभूवाचः), cf. इडा.<BR>4) in Vêdis cibus.<BR>Ros. Sp. p. 24.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इव<BR>इव (ut mihi videtur, a stirpe pronom. इ + व, sicut {#ava,<BR>eva#} ex अ, ए + व, v. gr. comp. §. 381. p. 552.) sicut.<BR>(semper rem cum qua alia comparatur, aut proxime aut<BR>aliis vocibus separatum, sequitur; quodsi res quae comparationi<BR>inservit, adjectivo instructa est, इव plerumque<BR>medium inter substantivum et adjectivum locum tenet,<BR>vel hoc vel illud sequens. Ex hac adamata et frequentissima<BR>constructione fortasse explicandum est, quod<BR>nonnunquam adjectivum, quod sensu ad rem comparatam<BR>pertinet, formâ et positione ad rem transfertur cum<BR>quâ illa comparatur, ut N. 26.30.: {#BrAjamAna ivA'dityo<BR>vapuzA#} sicut splendens sol, corpore, pro {#BrAjamAna<BR>Aditya iva vapuzA#} corpore splendens (erat) sicut sol,<BR>quod poëta dicere videtur velle; cf. quoque IN. 1.29.<BR>Nonnunquam redundat, aut Adjectivum, praesertim Participium<BR>praes. Adverbii naturâ afficit, e. c. N. 2.22.:<BR>नचिराद् इव brevi. H. 2.16.: त्वरमाणे ऽव…जगाम<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-a" target="_blank">Page041-a+ 28</a>]<BR>festinanter ivit; 2.23.: विलज्जमानेऽव नता pudenter<BR>inclinata. 4.1.: प्रहसन्न् इव…वचनम् अब्रवीत् ridens<BR>sermonem dixit. (Hoc Adverbium pronominale<BR>recognoverim in goth. hvaiva quomodo, sive sit dissolvendum<BR>in hva-iva - quasi क इव - sive in hvai-'va;<BR>porro in Adverbiis goth. in ba desinentibus, ut frôda-ba<BR>prudenter, hardu-ba dure; et in Adverbiis lith. in ipo vel<BR>ip desinentibus, ut taipo vel taip sic, quasi त इव, kaipo<BR>vel kaip quomodo? quasi क इव, v. gr. comp. 383. p. 555.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=040-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इष्<BR>1. इष् 4. P. ire. (Huc retulerim gr. ἀΐσσω quasi आ इष्यामि,<BR>assimilatione mutato य् in σ v. gr. comp. 501.).<BR>c. अनु 1. P. interdum A. quaerere. IN. 11.18.: अन्वेषमाणा;<BR>12.10.: अन्वेषती; 12.30.: अन्वेषसि (v. इष्<BR>6. praef. अनु).<BR>c. प्र Caus. (प्रेषयामि) mittere. IN. 5.32. H. 1.47. N. 3.7.<BR>c. प्र praef. सम् Caus. (सम्प्रेषयामि) id. H. 4.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इष्<BR>2. इष् 6. P. (in special. temp. substituitur इछ्, gr. 337.<BR>praet. red. इयेष gr. 432.) desiderare, velle. BR. 2.3. 3.4.<BR>N. 9.32. 26.17. — Part. इष्ट desideratus, carus,<BR>dilectus. BR. 2.25. N. 12.96. 16.32. BH. 18.64. (Gr.<BR>πϱο-ΐσσομα, πϱο-ΐϰ-της, πϱο-ΐξ sicut supra<BR>ἀΐσσω; ἰό-της, ῑ̔́-μεϱος nisi utrumque ad ई q. v. pertinet; v.<BR>etiam इछ् et Pott. I.269.).<BR>c. अनु quaerere. BH. 2.49. MAN. 11.232. DR. 8.38. (cf.<BR>इष् ire, praef. अनु).<BR>c. प्रति i. q. simpl. SA. 3.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इषिका<BR>इषिका f. v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इषीका<BR>इषीका f. (ut mihi videtur, a r. ईक्ष् videre, s. इक in fem.,<BR>producto इ in ई, ita ut sit pro इक्षीका) pupilla, praesertim<BR>elephanti. AM. Scribitur etiam इषिका.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इषु|इषुः<BR>इषु m. f. (r. इष् ire s. उ) sagitta (cf. gr. ἰ(σ)ός, quo scr.<BR>इष exspectaveris).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इषुधि|इषुधिः<BR>इषुधि m. (e praec. et धि tenens, a r. धा s. इ, v. gr. 645.)<BR>pharetra. A. 3.21. (in du.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इष्ट|इष्टं|इष्टः<BR>इष्ट Part. pass.<BR>1) ab इष् desiderare.<BR>2) a यज् deos colere,<BR>sacrificare, gr. 613.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इष्टक<BR>इष्टक m. et इष्टका f. later coctus. HIT. 39.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इष्टतस्<BR>इष्टतस् Adv. (ab इष्ट optatum s. तस्) ad voluntatem. IN. 2.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इष्टि|इष्टिः<BR>इष्टि f.<BR>1) (a r. इष् desiderare s. ति) desiderium.<BR>2) (a r.<BR>यज् s. ति) sacrificium. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इष्य|इष्यं|इष्यः<BR>इष्य m. (r. इष् desiderare s. य) ver. HEM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इष्वास|इष्वासं|इष्वासः<BR>इष्वास m. (ex इषु sagitta et आस q. v.) arcus. BH. 1.4. 17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इह<BR>इह (a stirpe pron. इ s. ह, quod primitive sonuit ध, =<BR>gr. ϑα et zend. dha)<BR>1) hîc, ibi. BR. 1.21. DR. 6.23.<BR>N. 5.10. 11. BR. 3.5.: इह वा…उतवा प्रेत्य aut hîc<BR>(in hoc terrestri mundo) aut post mortem (i. e. in illo<BR>mundo). — Locativi अस्मिन् loco fungitur SA. 2.21.:<BR>यदि सन्ती ऽह केचन si sunt in eo quaepiam vitia;<BR>HIT. 104.15.: इह समये hoc tempore.<BR>2) huc. IN. 4.6.<BR>(Zend. 𐬌𐬜𐬀 idha hîc; gr. ἰϑᾱ vel ἰϑαι in ἰϑα-γενής, ἰϑαι-γενής,<BR>cf. Hartung «Casus» p. 117. et M.<BR>Schmidt «De pron. gr. et lat.» p. 16.; goth. ith si, nam,<BR>vero, gr. comp. 420.; fortasse lat. igi-tur pro igi-tus ex<BR>इह + तस्, v. gr. comp. 421.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ई<BR>1. ई 4. A. (गतौ) ire.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ई<BR>2. ई 2. P. (कान्तिगतिव्याप्तिक्षेपप्रजनखादनेषु) desiderare;<BR>ire; occupare; jaculari; generare; edere. In<BR>Rosenii Vêdorum specimine p. 14. invenitur forma ATM.<BR>ईमहे quod Rosenius per precamur vertit; non minus<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-1b" target="_blank">Page041-1b+ 5</a>]<BR>tamen quadrat sensus desideramus; sic l. c. p. 24. not. 2.:<BR>तमित् सहित्व ईमहे eum in societatem desideramus.<BR>(Gr. ἰό-της, ῑ̔́-μεϱος nisi sunt mutilata ex<BR>ἰσότης, ἵσμερος, v. 2. इष्.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईक्ष्<BR>ईक्ष् 1. A. (Praet. augm. 1. ऐक्षे, gr. 318. Hanc radicis formam [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-a" target="_blank">Page042-a+ 37</a>]<BR>ortam esse puto ex अक्ष्, unde अक्ष et अक्षि oculus<BR>et radix gr. ὈΠ videre, intueri, spectare. BH. 6.29.<BR>PAT. 10.: ऐक्षत; IN. 5.39. (Vocibus quas supra cum<BR>अक्ष comparavimus, addendum est goth. haih-s, Th.<BR>haiha unoculus, de quo egimus in gr. comp. 308. annot.).<BR>c. अधि id. HIT. 129.22.<BR>c. अप<BR>1) respicere, considerare. RAM. III.3.58. 20.: {#yayA<BR>nA 'pekzyate rAjA#}.<BR>2) exspectare. UR. 22.8.infr. 64.4.<BR>c. अव<BR>1) videre, intueri, observare. H. 1.50. 2.6. A. 4.38.<BR>N. 23.11. PAT. 25.<BR>2) respicere. BR. 3.14. N. 12.16. SA. 4.33.<BR>c. अव praef. अनु (अन्ववेक्ष्)<BR>1) videre.<BR>RAM. III.70.59.: विप्रद्रुतान् सर्वान् यूथपान् अन्ववैक्षत.<BR>2) contemplari. MAN. 6.65.: सूक्ष्मताञ्चाऽन्ववे क्षेत.<BR>c. अव praef. प्रति (प्रत्यवेक्ष्)<BR>1) videre.<BR>2) respicere. RAM. I.29.28.: न धर्मम् प्रत्यवेक्षते.<BR>c. अव praef. सम् (समवेक्ष्)<BR>1) videre. GHAT. 19.:<BR>मधुनः समवेक्ष्य कालताम्.<BR>2) visitare. GHAT. 13.:<BR>किम् इतिच मां समवेक्षसे न दीनाम्.<BR>c. उत् videre, conspicere, intueri. A. 6.6. SA. 5.63.<BR>c. उप<BR>1) id. N. 22.5.<BR>2) ignoscere, indulgere, tolerare.<BR>MAH. Exord. 137.: द्युतादीन् अनयान्…उपैक्षत.<BR>3) spernere, repudiare, negligere. RAM. III.66.24.:<BR>चिरन् ना ऽर्हति माम् उपेक्षितुम्.<BR>c. निस् (निर्) conspicere, intueri, spectare, contemplari.<BR>H. 4.41. BH. 1.22. SA. 4.32.: निरीक्षमाणा (sic<BR>cum ed. Calc. legendum pro निरीक्ष्यमाणा).<BR>c. परि explorare. N. 24.3.: Caus. MAN. 7.194.: {#tAYca<BR>samyak parIkzayet#}.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. IN. 2.26. DR. 2.1.: प्रेक्षमाणा (sic cum<BR>ed. Calc. pro प्रेक्ष्यमाणा legendum). — Part. praes. P. invenitur. H. 3.7.: प्रेक्षत्यास् ते.<BR>c. प्र praef. अनु (अनुप्रेक्ष्) id. DR. 5.23.<BR>c. प्र praef. अभि (अभिप्रेक्ष्) intueri, adspicere. DR. 8.39. 9.18.<BR>c. प्र praef. आ (आप्रेक्ष्) i. q. simpl. H. 3.21.<BR>c. प्र praef. सम् (सम्प्रेक्ष्) id. N. 6.2. 19.36. BR. 2.18. BH. 6.13.<BR>c. प्र praef. अभि + सम् (अभिसम्प्रेक्ष्) id. H. 2.28. DR. 8.57.<BR>c. प्रति exspectare. IN. 1.13. N. 20.17. M. 39.<BR>c. प्रति<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">Page042-b+ 36</a>]<BR>praef. सम् (सम्प्रतीक्ष्) id. RAM. III.76.29.: {#tvAn<BR>nagarI sampratIkzate#}.<BR>c. वि videre. N. 26.21. BH. 11.22.<BR>c. वि praef. अभि (अभिवीक्ष्) id.<BR>c. वि praef. उत् (उद्वीक्ष्)<BR>1) id. RAM. III.48.80.<BR>2) respicere. RAM. III.45.33.: उद्वीक्षमाणा भर्तारम्<BR>c. वि praef. उप (उपवीक्ष्) i. q. simpl. RAM. III.45.33.<BR>c. वि praef. प्रति (प्रतिवीक्ष्)<BR>id. RAM. I.14.37.<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) videre, observare. H. 4.5. 26. N. 16.9. 23.5.<BR>2) respicere. BR. 2.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=041-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईक्षण|ईक्षणं<BR>ईक्षण n. (r. ईक्ष् s. अन)<BR>1) visus, conspectus. HIT. 129.19.<BR>2) oculus. N. 11.27. 12.30. 16.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईङ्ख्|ईंख्<BR>ईङ्ख् 1. P. (scribunt ईख्, gr. 110^a).) ire, transire. In<BR>dialecto Vêd. haec radix etiam cl. 10^mae normam<BR>sequitur, e. c. य ईङ्खयन्ति पर्वतान् qui transeunt montes,<BR>v. Ros. Sp. p. 9. not.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईज्<BR>ईज् 1. A. (गतौ K. कुत्से गतौ V.) ire; contemnere, reprehendere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईजे<BR>ईजे v. यज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईञ्ज्<BR>ईञ्ज् 1. P. A. (scribunt ईज्, gr. 110^a).) i. q. ईज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईड्<BR>ईड् 2. P. 10. A. laudare, celebrare. In Vêdis invenitur<BR>forma ईल् cl. 2. A. mutato ड् in ल्, nisi vice versâ ईड्<BR>ortum est ex ईल्. Ros. Sp. p. 10.1.: {#tvAm…martAsa<BR>Ilate#} te homines celebrant.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईड्य<BR>ईड्य (r. ईड् s. य) laudandus, celebrandus. DR. 5.3. BH. 11.44.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईति|ईतिः<BR>ईति f. (ut videtur, a r. ई s. ति)<BR>1) temporis calamitas.<BR>2) habitatio in exteris locis. AM. (डिम्बप्रवासयोः).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईदृक्<BR>ईदृक् v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईदृश्<BR>ईदृश् (N. m. n. ईदृक्, f. ईदृशी, e stirpe pron. इ, producto<BR>इ in ई, et दृश् = gr. λίϰ in ὁμῆλιξ, v. gr. 287. et gr.<BR>comp. 415.) talis. BH. 11.49.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईदृश|ईदृशः<BR>ईदृश (e stirpe pron. इ, producto इ in ई, et s. दृश prâcr.<BR>दिस vel रिस = gr. λιϰο in τηλίϰος etc., goth. LEIKA<BR>in hvêleik̕-s qualis? nostro welcher, svaleik̕-s talis, nostro<BR>solcher; slav. liko, N. m. lik e. c. tolik talis; lat. li in<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-a" target="_blank">Page043-a+ 37</a>]<BR>tâlis, quâlis; v. gr. comp. 415. sq.) talis. N. 13.72. 19.15.<BR>BH. 6.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=042-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईप्स्<BR>ईप्स् Desid. irr. a r. आप् q. v., gr. 540.<BR>c. परि quaerere. DR. 8.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

