ईर्षु<BR>ईर्षु (v. ईर्क्ष्य्) invidus, invidens. HIT. 13.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईर्ष्य्<BR>ईर्ष्य् 1. P. (v. ईर्क्ष्य्) invidere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईर्ष्या<BR>ईर्ष्या f. invidia. AM. (v. ईर्षा).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

