ईलित|ईलितः<BR>ईलित (Part. pass. praec. s. त) celebratus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईश्<BR>ईश् 2. A. dominari, imperare, Wils. «to possess power,<BR>property or authority». (Fortasse huc pertinet goth.<BR>aigan habere cum Gunâ et anomalâ Mediâ pro Aspiratâ,<BR>quam ex scr. श् et gr. ϰ - v. ईश्वर - exspectaveris;<BR>germ. vet. eigan, Adj. eigan proprius - nostrum<BR>eigen - êh-t, Th. êh-ti f. possessio, facultas, substantia,<BR>opes, reditus, praedium.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईश|ईशं|ईशः<BR>ईश m. (r. ईश् s. अ)<BR>1) dominus. IN. 5.32. SU. 3.19.<BR>2) cognomen<BR>Sivi. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईशान|ईशानं|ईशानः<BR>ईशान m. (Part. praes. a r. ईश् s. आन) nomen Sivi.<BR>DEV. 8.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईशानी<BR>ईशानी f. (Fem. praec.) nomen Durgae, Sivi uxoris. DEV. 8.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईश्वर|ईश्वरं|ईश्वरः<BR>ईश्वर m. (r. ईश् s. वर)<BR>1) dominus. H. 3.1. N. 2.6. BH. 4.6.<BR>2) nomen Sivi. AM.<BR>3) Adj. potens, capax, par.<BR>cum Infin. DEV. 1.64. HIT. 75.14. (Huc retulerim gr.<BR>ϰύϱιος abjectâ vocali initiali et correptâ syllabâ व in v<BR>sicut e श्वन् fit शुनस् etc. = ϰυν-ός gr. 225.; terminatio<BR>ιο-ς convenit cum suffixo Derivativi ऐश्वर्य, q. v. Vox<BR>ϰῦϱος autem alius originis est, v. शूर्. Fortasse germ.<BR>vet. herro (nostrum Herr) per assimil. ex herjo, huc pertinet;<BR>hib. aesfhear, aesar deus, v. Pikt. p. 20.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईश्वरी<BR>ईश्वरी f. (Fem. praecedentis)<BR>1) domina.<BR>2) nomen Durgae,<BR>v. ईशानी.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=043-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

