ईह्<BR>ईह् 1. A.<BR>1) desiderare.<BR>2) adniti, contendere, quaerere,<BR>petere. BH. 7.22. 16.12. (Huc trahi possit gr. ἰσχύς,<BR>ita ut sit pro ἰχύσ, propter adamatam conjunctionem<BR>litterarum σ et χ.)<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) desiderare, समीहित n. optatum, desiderium.<BR>HIT. 44.7.<BR>2) assequi, adipisci. HIT. 103.2.<BR>3) peragere, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=044-b" target="_blank">Page044-b+ 5</a>]<BR>perficere. RAM. I.11.33.: {#yajYakarma samIhantAm<BR>BavantaH#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=044-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ईहा<BR>ईहा f. (r. ईह् s. आ)<BR>1) desiderium.<BR>2) nisus, appetitus,<BR>consectatio. HIT. 37.6.: वित्तेहा.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=044-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

