उक्ष्<BR>उक्ष् 1. P. conspergere, humectare. SA. 6.5. शोणितोक्षित<BR>sanguine conspersus. (Lith. ûkana tempestas pluvia,<BR>cf. etiam hib. uisg, uisge «water, a river», uisgeach<BR>«aquatic, watery, fluid, moist, pluvial», transpositis litteris<BR>क्, ष्, nisi uisg pertinet ad r. विष् irrigare, unde<BR>उक्ष् ortum esse possit, ejecto i et additâ sibilante, ratione<BR>habitâ euphoniae legis 99.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=044-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

उक्षन्<BR>उक्षन् m. (ut videtur, a r. वह्, correpto व in उ, gr. 455.,<BR>adjectâ sibilante, s. अन्) bos, taurus, in Vêdis etiam<BR>equus. Ros. Sp. p. 8.5. (Goth. auhsa, Th. auhsan,<BR>germ. vet. auhso, Th. auhson, auhsun, notrum Ochs,<BR>lat. vacca ut videtur per assimil. e vacsa cf. Pott. I.234.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=044-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

