उत्कट|उत्कटं|उत्कटः<BR>उत्कट (e praep. उत् s. कट v. gr. 652.)<BR>1) multus. HIT. 23.15.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=046-a" target="_blank">Page046-a+ 37</a>]<BR>2) ebrius, furiosus. H. 4.38. N. 13.8.<BR>3) m. elephantus<BR>coitûs appetens.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=045-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

