उत्सुक|उत्सुकः<BR>उत्सुक (ex उत् et सुक quod separatum non invenitur et<BR>fortasse a partic. insep. सु descendit)<BR>1) Adj. desiderans,<BR>desiderio confectus. UR. 8.3. 45.9. 65.7. 9. N. 21.7.<BR>SAK. 51.3.<BR>2) Subst. in fine compos. BAH. e. c. निरुत्सुक<BR>liber a desiderio. SAK. 30.5.: {#mamA'pi kaRvasutAm<BR>anusmftya mfgayAm prati nirutsukaY cetaH#};<BR>A. 10.14. — समुत्सुक qui est cum desiderio, desiderio<BR>confectus. UR. 7.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=047-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

