उर्द्<BR>उर्द् 1. P. (माने K. मितिक्रीडास्वादे V.) metiri; lunder;<BR>gustare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=052-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

उर्व्<BR>उर्व् 1. P. (हिंसायाम्) ferire, laedere, occidere. (Hae<BR>radix ex idem valente अर्व् orta esse videtur, attnuato<BR>अ in उ, quâ in re ambae radices eandem rationem<BR>inter se habent quam gothica Praeterita sing. et pl.<BR>veluti band, bundum, et sanscr. करोमि ejusque duet pl.<BR>कुर्वस्, कुर्मस्; v. gr. comp. 490.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=052-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

