उष्ट<BR>उष्ट m. (r. उष् s. त्र) camelus, ut videtur, a tolerando calore<BR>sic nominatus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=053-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

उष्ण|उष्णः<BR>उष्ण (forma irr. a r. उष् s. न, v. gr. 94^a).)<BR>1) calidus, fervidus.<BR>H. 2.11.<BR>2) m. fervidum anni tempus. AM. (Huc<BR>trahi possit goth. auhn̕-s fornax, hypocaustum, nisi<BR>pertinet ad अग्नि, v. उषस्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=053-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

