ऊधस्<BR>ऊधस् n. uber, οὖϑαϱ. AM. (Gr. οὖϑαϱ, anglo-sax. uder,<BR>germ. vet. ûtar, nostrum Euter, hib. uit, uitche, lat.<BR>ûber (*).)<BR>(*) Latina lingua saepe adhibet f pro sanscr. ď et gr. ϑ;<BR>in vocum medio autem aspiratae praefert mediam (v. gr. comp. 18.)<BR>unde etiam ruber pro rufer respondet graeco ἐρυϑρός.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

