ऊन|ऊनं<BR>ऊन<BR>1) deminutus, minus, v. gr. 258. SA. 4.26.: {#saMvatsaraH<BR>kiYcidUnaH#} (sic legendum pro किञ्चिद् ऊनः) pauo<BR>minus annus.<BR>2) debilis. RAGH. 2.14.: {#Unan na sattveG<BR>aDiko vavADa#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

