ऊर्ज्<BR>ऊर्ज् 10. P. (बलप्राणधरणयोः K. जीवने बले V.) valere,<BR>robustum, validum esse; vivere. ऊर्जित validus, potens.<BR>RAM. I.1.115.: ऊर्जितशासन; HIT. 131.19.:<BR>रिपुर् ऊर्जितः. (Fortasse lat. urgeo, nisi hoc pertinet ad<BR>अर्ज् q. v.; hib. orc «a prince, a hero», orcaim «I kill,<BR>destroy» v. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्ज्<BR>ऊर्ज् m. (r. ऊर्ज् s. अ)<BR>1) vis, robur, potestas.<BR>2) vis genitalis.<BR>3) mensis Kârtika, October-November. (Hib.<BR>uirge «the private parts of a man».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

