ऊर्णा<BR>ऊर्णा f. (ut videtur, e वर्णा a r. वृ tegere, correptâ syllabâ<BR>व in ऊ; secundum Wils. ab ऊर्णु q. v.) lana (Lith. wilna,<BR>russ. vòlna, goth. vulla per assimil., germ. vet. wolla,<BR>lat. villus, gr. ἔϱος, ἔϱιον, ἐϱέα, εἶϱος, εἶϱιον; hib. olann.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्णायु|ऊर्णायुः|ऊर्ण्णायु<BR>ऊर्णायु m. (a praec. s. यु)<BR>1) aries. AM.<BR>2) lodix lanea. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्णु|ऊर्ण्णु<BR>ऊर्णु 2. P. A. (आछादने; ut videtur, a r. वृ tegere adjecto<BR>charactere 5tae classis, et correptâ syllabâ वर्, quae<BR>primitiva forma est radicis वृ, in ऊर्) tegere, cf.<BR>ऊर्णा.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्द्ध<BR>ऊर्द्ध v. ऊद्ध्व.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्द्ध्व<BR>ऊर्द्ध्व vel ऊर्ध्व, v. gr. 105. (ut videtur, a r. ऋध् vel वृध् crescere,<BR>ita ut ortum sit ex अर्द्ध्व vel वर्द्ध्व sicut supra {#UrRA,<BR>UrRu#} ex वर्णा, वर्णु) erectus, altus. (Cf. lat. arduus, gr.<BR>ὀϱϑός, hib. ard «a height, top, summit»)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्द्ध्वकेश<BR>ऊर्द्ध्वकेश (BAH. e ऊर्द्ध्व et केश capillus) erectos capillos habens.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्द्ध्वबाहु<BR>ऊर्द्ध्वबाहु (BAH. ex ऊर्द्ध्व et बाहु m. brachium) erecta, sursum<BR>porrecta brachia habens. SU. 1.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्द्ध्वम्<BR>ऊर्द्ध्वम् aut ऊर्द्ध्वम् Adv. (ab ऊर्द्ध्व signo accus.) sursum. IN. 1.31<BR>Post अतस्, post, in posterum (v. अतस्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्द्ध्वाङ्गुलि<BR>ऊर्द्ध्वाङ्गुलि (BAH. ex ऊर्द्ध्व et अङ्गुलि f. digitus) erectos<BR>digitos habens. H. 2.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊर्मि|ऊर्मिः|ऊर्म्मि|ऊर्म्मिः<BR>ऊर्मि f. (fortasse correptum e वर्मि - v. ऊर्णा, ऊर्णु - ita<BR>ut descindat a r. वृ tegere s. मि, sicut भूमि a भू) unda,<BR>fluctus. M. 41. (Lith. wilni-s, germ. vet. wella, ut videtur,<BR>per assiml. ex welna.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=054-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊष्<BR>ऊष् 1. P. (रुजायाम् K. रेगे V.) aegrotum esse.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊष|ऊषं|ऊषः<BR>ऊष m. solum salsum. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊषर|ऊषरः<BR>ऊषर (a praec. s. र) solum salsum habens locus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊषवत्|ऊषवन्त्<BR>ऊषवत् (ab ऊष s. वत्) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊह्<BR>ऊह् 1. P. A. concludere, colligere. HIT. 52.15.: {#anuktam<BR>apy Uhati paRqito janaH#}; 88.2.: {#varRAkArapratiDvAnanetragAtravikArataH<BR>. apy Uhanti manas tajjYAH#}.<BR>In utroque loco fortasse अपि tanquam praepositio radici<BR>est praefigendum: अप्यूहति, अप्यूहन्ति. (Hib.<BR>uige «knowledge, skill, ingenuity, understanding», v.<BR>ऊह; primitiva significatio hujus radicis, quae ex वह्<BR>orta esse possit, colligere, coacervare, accumulare<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-b" target="_blank">Page055-b+ 11</a>]<BR>esse videtur, unde समूह multitudo, अपोह् et<BR>व्यपोह् auferre, demere; cf. lat. augeo, goth. auka, id.<BR>hib. ugtar «augmentation».)<BR>c. अप auferre, demere. UR. 42.2.: मनसिजं रुजम्… अपोहितुम्.<BR>c. अप praef. वि (व्यपोह्) id. UR. 5.71.:<BR>यो मे दर्पम् व्यपोहति; SAK. 43.7.: {#sa hi viGnAn<BR>vyapohati#}.<BR>c. वि in ordinem redigere. MAN. 7.191.: व्यूहेन व्यूह्य;<BR>BH. 1.2.: दृष्ट्वा तु पाण्डवानीकम् व्यूढम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऊह|ऊहः<BR>ऊह m. (r. ऊह् s. अ) actio colligendi, concludendi. AM.<BR>(Hib. uga «choice, election».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋ<BR>1. ऋ 1. et 3. P. (अरामि, इयर्मि v. gr. 369.; primitiva hujus<BR>radicis forma est अर्, quae syllaba et in hac et in<BR>aliis radicibus, quae apud grammaticos vocalem ऋ continent,<BR>in formis non gunatis corripitur in ऋ, quae<BR>vocalis nusquam est primitiva, sed semper orta ex र्, antecedente<BR>vel subsequente quâpiam vocali, ut e. c. शृणोमि<BR>a r. श्रु, abjecto उ, quo facto consonans र् vocalis<BR>naturam induit (*)) ire, perveire, transl. adipisci (v. r.<BR>इ). NALOD. 1.32.: ताङ् गाम्…आर ad illam regionem<BR>pervenit; 42.: न रिरंसाम् आर non gaudium adepta est.<BR>— Caus. अर्पय् (gr. 521.) facere ut aliquis eat, perveniat;<BR>1) movere, dirigere, conjicere. BH. 8.7. 12.14.:<BR>मय्य् अर्पितमनोबुद्धि; DR. 5.19.: शरान् अर्पयितुम्<BR>sagittas mittere.<BR>2) uti aliquâ re, impendere, adhibere.<BR>H. 4.47. (Goth. airus nuntius mihi ortum esse videtur<BR>ex primitivâ hujus radicis formâ अर्, attenuato अ<BR>in इ et anteposito a ex generali euphoniae lege q. v. gr.<BR>comp. 82.; hib. ria vel do ria «he will come, arrive», ria<BR>«running, speed», riach «he came», riachtaim «I arrive»,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-1b" target="_blank">Page055-1b+ 21</a>]<BR>ar «guiding, conducting»; v. r. इल्. Ad formam<BR>caus. अर्पय् quae cum सम् composita tradere significat,<BR>referri possit germ. vet. arbjan hereditare, kierpit<BR>possessio, goth. arbi Th. arbja hereditas, quanquam<BR>ex generali consonantium permutandarum lege<BR>pro sanscr. प् exspectaveris goth. f; amant vero Liquidae<BR>conjunctionem cum Mediis. Ad inusitatam, ex tritâ<BR>lege formatam formam caus. आरयामि pertinere videtur<BR>lat. aro, goth. arja, id., germ. vet. erru - per assimil. ex<BR>erju - lith. arù, slav. orjû, ita ut a movendo solo nominata<BR>sint; cf. Graff I.402. Etiam gr. ἈΡ, αἴϱω a movendo<BR>nominatum et cum scr. अर् cognatum esse videtur.)<BR>c. सम् caus. tradere. HIT. 7.14.: {#tasya vizRuSarmaRo…<BR>putrAn samarpitavAn#}; 40.12.: स्वामिना ऽऽनीय समर्पितव्या;<BR>42.3.: कुलीनां युवतीम् आनीय समर्पय.<BR>(*) Fusius de vocalium ṛ et ṝ origine disserui in libro meo<BR>„Vocalismus” p. 157. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋ<BR>2. ऋ 5. P. (हिंसायाम्) offendere, ferire, laedere, vexare,<BR>occidere. (Hib. ar «slaughter, destruction, plague;<BR>the slain in fight»; fortasse etiam aor «a satire; a<BR>curse».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋक्<BR>ऋक् v. ऋच्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=055-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋकथ<BR>ऋकथ (r. ऋच् s. थ, nisi correptum ex idem valente रिकथ)<BR>divitiae, opes. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋक्ष्<BR>ऋक्ष् 5. P. (जिघांसायाम् K. वधे v.) occidere, occidendi<BR>cupidum esse.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋक्ष|ऋक्षं|ऋक्षः<BR>ऋक्ष m. (fortasse a r. ऋक्ष् s. अ, vel a r. ऋष् ire s. स, mutato<BR>ष् in क्) ursus (ऋक्ष ex अर्क्ष, v. ऋ et cf. gr.<BR>ἄρϰτος, hib. art, lat. ursus, ejecto क्; lith. lokys per metathesin<BR>ex olkys, mutato r in l.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋक्षवत्|ऋक्षवन्त्<BR>ऋक्षवत् m. (a praec. s. वत्) nomen montis cujusdam. N. 9.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋग्यजुःसामवेदिन्<BR>ऋग्यजुःसामवेदिन् (a ऋग्यजुःसामवेद s. इन्) Vêdos<BR>Rić (vulgo Rik) Yajus et Sâma habens aut noscens.<BR>IN. 2.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋच्<BR>ऋच् 6. P. (संवरणे K. नुत्याम् V.) tegere; laudare, celebrare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋच्<BR>ऋच् f. (nom. ऋक्) nomen unius quatuor Vêdorum. BH. 9.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋछ्|ऋच्छ्<BR>ऋछ् 6. P. (ऋच्छमि gr. 38.) ire, adire. BH. 2.72.: {#brahmanirvARam<BR>fcCati#}; 5.29.: शान्तिम् ऋच्छति; MAN. 12.55.:<BR>चण्डालपुक्कशानाञ्च…योनिम् ऋच्छति; N. 4.7.<BR>ubi in ed. Calc. legitur मृत्युम् ऋच्छति, v. ann.<BR>ad h. l.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋज्<BR>ऋज् 1. A. (गतौ K. गतिस्थैर्योर्जनार्जने V.) ire; firmum<BR>esse; validum, robustum esse; acquirere. (Primitive<BR>idem atque अर्ज्, v. ऋ; lat. rego rectus, goth. raih-ts,<BR>nostrum recht, v. sq., gr. ὀ-ϱέγω, hib. righim «I reach,<BR>arrive, stretch».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋजु<BR>ऋजु (sic etiam in fem.; a praec. s. उ) rectus (hib. aroch,<BR>v. ऋ).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋण्<BR>ऋण् 8. P. (गतौ) ire (ut videtur ex ऋ adjecto charactere<BR>cl. 5. unde ऋ-णोमि); cf. goth. rinnan r. RANN, nostrum<BR>rinnen.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋण|ऋणं<BR>ऋण n. (secundum Wils. a r. ऋ s. न) debitum, aes alienum.<BR>HIT. 5.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋत्<BR>ऋत् 1. P. (स्पर्धनैश्वर्यघृणागतिषु) ire; aemulari, certare;<BR>imperare; vituperare. (Haec radix orta esse videtur<BR>ex ऋ - अर् - adjecto त्. Huc retulerim rad. goth.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-b" target="_blank">Page056-b+ 36</a>]<BR>LITH ire - leitha, laith, lithum - mutato r in l et litteris<BR>transpositis pro ilth ex alth, arth, attenuato a in i, sicut<BR>in r. KIN germinare = जन्; hib. rith «course, flight,<BR>gallop, race», rithim «I run, range, strull, rush».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋत|ऋतं|ऋतः<BR>ऋत (ut videtur, a r. ऋ s. त) verus. N. 2.21. BH. 10.14.<BR>SA. 5.98.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋति|ऋतिः<BR>ऋति f. (r. ऋ s. ति)<BR>1) itio.<BR>2) via.<BR>3) felicitas. (Hib.<BR>raith «prosperity, encrease, profit, benefit, good»; raite<BR>«ways, passages, roads»; fortasse lat. rîte a th. rîti, nostrum<BR>Art, v. Graff. I.403.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋतीया<BR>ऋतीया f. (r. ऋत् s. ईया) vituperatio, reprehensio. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋतु|ऋतुः<BR>ऋतु m. (r. ऋ s. तु)<BR>1) anni tempus. BH. 10.35. (*)<BR>2) mensis.<BR>3) menstrua (Ita अमस् tempus a r. अम् ire; c. ऋतु<BR>cf. hib. raithe «a quarter of a year»; huc etiam traxerim<BR>hib. alt - ex primitivâ formâ अर्तु mutato r in l<BR>1)<BR>«time».<BR>2) «a joint, an article»; lat. ar-tus et ri-tus,<BR>ita ut utrumque a movendo sit nominatum).<BR>(*) Wils. ad hanc vocem: The Hindu year is divided into<BR>six seasons, each consisting of two months. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋतुमती<BR>ऋतुमती f. (a praec. s. मत् in fem.) mulier menstruans.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋतुपर्ण|ऋतुपर्णः<BR>ऋतुपर्ण m. (ex ऋतु et पर्ण) n. pr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=056-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

