ऋभुक्षिन्<BR>ऋभुक्षिन् m. (Nom. ऋभुक्षास् a Th. ऋभुक्षस्, reliqui casus<BR>fortes, Vocativo excepto, descendunt a Th. ऋभुक्षन्,<BR>debilissimi casus a ऋभुक्ष्) cognomen Indri.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=057-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

