एकैक<BR>एकैक (एक + एक) quivis singulus. HIT. 4.11.: {#yOvanan<BR>DanasampattiH praButvam avivekatA . ekEkam apy<BR>anarTAya kimu yatra catuzwayam#}; A. 7.6.: {#tAn aham<BR>viviDEr vAREH…aByaGnam ekEkan daSaBiH SarEH#} — Interdum<BR>alterutra compositi pars ad diversam rem vel<BR>personam refertur et diversam casuum rationem exprimit;<BR>e. c. DR. 8.17.: {#tomarEr aBivarzantO…ekEkena<BR>vipAWena jaGne mAdravatIsutaH#} unum unâ sagittâ occidit.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=058-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

