एतत्<BR>1. एतत्, एतद् Pron. (Th. एत, Nom. m. एष, एषो, एषः,<BR>f. एषा, n. एतत्, v. gr. 269. et gr. comp. 369.) is, hic,<BR>iste, ille. N. 21.30. 32.22. 1.3.; v. इदम्. (Hib. ise «he,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">Page059-a+ 37</a>]<BR>himself», isa et isi «she, herself» conveniunt cum {#eza,<BR>ezA#}; et eadh «he, it» cum एत.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=058-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एतत्<BR>2. एतत् Adv. (acc. neut. praec.) nunc. N. 21.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एतर्हि<BR>एतर्हि (ab एत s. र्हि nisi potius a perdito Adv. एतर् s. हि<BR>pro धि = gr. ϑι in ὅϑι, πόϑι etc. (v. gr. comp. 381.)<BR>nunc, hoc tempore. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एतादृश<BR>एतादृश (v. ईदृश et gr. 287.) talis. DR. 5.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एतावत्|एतावन्त्<BR>एतावत् (gr. 283.)<BR>1) hic, iste, ille, talis. BR. 1.8. N. 4.31.<BR>DR. 6.25. DEV. 1.74. HIT. 11.5. 44.8.<BR>2) Adv. tam.<BR>HIT. 27.15.: एतावद् दूरम् उत्पतति. V. annot. ad<BR>N. 4.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एध्<BR>एध् 1. A.<BR>1) augere, praesertim in constructione cum accus.<BR>सुखम्. MAN. 4.170.: नेऽहाऽसौ सुखम् एधते; 5.45.:<BR>न क्वचित् सुखम् एधते; HIT. 110.8.: {#dvAv etO suKam<BR>eDete#}.<BR>2) augeri, creascere. MAN. 7.208.: {#hiraRyaBUmisamprAptyA<BR>pArTivo na taTE'Date#}. (Gr.<BR>οἶδος, οἰδάω; fortasse etiam huc pertinet lat. aes-culus, ita ut a<BR>crescendo, non ab edendo sit nominata, mutato d in s,<BR>sicut in es-ca ex ed-ca, v. A. Benary p. 239.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एध|एधः<BR>एध m. (r. इन्ध् ejecto न्, s. अ) lignum. AM., v. इन्धन et<BR>इध्म, एधस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एधस्<BR>एधस् n. (r. इन्ध् ejecto न्, s. अस्) lignum. BH. 4.37.; v.<BR>praec.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एन|एनः<BR>एन Pron. (solum in nonnullis casibus obliquis invenitur;<BR>f. एना, n. acc. एनत्, v. gr. 269. et gr. comp. 369.) is,<BR>hic, iste, ille. N. 22.2. 4. UR. 71.17. (Goth. ain-s Th.<BR>aina unus, fortasse etiam jains Th. jaina ille, si j est antepositum,<BR>sicut saepe in linguis slavicis, v. gr. comp. 255.n.;<BR>lat. vet. oinos, unde serius ûnus; gr. ἙΝ abjectâ<BR>vocali finali, v. gr. comp. 308.; huc etiam trahimus conj.<BR>lat. enim = acc. एनम् vel एनाम्, v. gr. comp. 370.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एनस्<BR>एनस् n. peccatum. MED.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एरण्ड|एरंडः|एरण्डः<BR>एरण्ड n. nomen arboris cujusdam, «Palma Christi or<BR>ricinnus communis». AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एव|एवं<BR>एव (e stirpe pronom. ए + व sicut अव, इव ex अ, इ;<BR>videtur esse Instrumentalis analogiam sequens linguae<BR>Zendicae - gr. comp. 158. - ita ut correptum sit ex एवा,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-b" target="_blank">Page059-b+ 36</a>]<BR>a stirpe demonstrativâ एव, quae in ligua Zend. plenam<BR>conservavit declinationem, sub formâ aêva, quod unus<BR>significat - v. gr. comp. 308. - sicut Praepos. अव in<BR>Zend. est Demonstrativum cum integrâ declinatione.<BR>In Sanscrito autem Th. एव, praeter correptam Instrumentalis<BR>formam, solum Accusativum retinuit एवम्,<BR>quod sic, hoc modo significat.)<BR>1) sic. N. 11.10. 12.114. 17.43.<BR>2) solum, tantummodo. HIT. 11.4. 30.15. 35.15.<BR>N. 19.19.a.b. 22.16. BR. 2.30. H. 4.7.15. (cf.<BR>Zend. 𐬀𐬈𐬎𐬎𐬀 aêva unus, gr. οἶος ex οἶϜος, nisi<BR>ortum est ex οἶνος = एन, q. v., oinos).<BR>3) jam. SA. 4.32.:<BR>मृतम् एव हि तम् मेने; SAK. 27.3.infr.: {#mahaty<BR>eva pratyUze…praboDye#}.<BR>4) adhuc, noch. N. 23.21.<BR>5) quidem, zwar. BH. 7.18.: {#udArAH sarva evE'te jYAnI<BR>tv AtmE'va me matam#}.<BR>6) post pronomina interdum<BR>significat ipse vel valet particulam dem in compositione<BR>cum is, e. c. N. 2.13.: एतस्मिन्न् एव काले तु hoc ipso<BR>tempore vero, vel eodem…; N. 19.19.: {#yAn (aSvAn)<BR>manyase samarTAMs tvaN kzipran tAn eva yojaya#}; 4.28.:<BR>माम् एव…वृणोति; 5.19. 20.21.: {#tam eva pradiSantu<BR>me#}.<BR>7) nempe. N. 4.26. 18.20. 23.14. 17.<BR>8) saepissime<BR>etiam, non raro antecedente च; de चैऽव vero, autem v.<BR>च. (Goth. aiv Th. aiva, germ. vet. eo, io, nostrum je, v.<BR>gr. comp. 381.; lat. aevum a similitudine dictum esse videtur,<BR>sicut scr. समा annus; fortasse etiam goth. ibus<BR>aequalis, germ. vet. ebanêr, nostrum ebener huc pertinet,<BR>mutato व् in b, v. p. 21. s. v. अवर.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एवंरूप<BR>एवंरूप (BAH. ex एवम् et रूप n. forma, pulchritudo) talem<BR>formam, talem pulchritudinem habens. N. 6.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एवंविध<BR>एवंविध v. एवम्विध.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एवङ्गुण<BR>एवङ्गुण (BAH. ex एवम् sic et गुण virtus) tales virtutes<BR>habens. N. 6.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एवम्<BR>एवम् (v. एव) sic, ita. BR. 3.2. SU. 3.28. N. 6.13. 11.34.<BR>itaque.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एवंविध<BR>एवंविध (BAH. ex एवम् et विध m. aut विधा f. species)<BR>talem speciem habens. BH. 11.53.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=059-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एष्<BR>एष् 1. A. (गतौ) ire (proprie idem est atque इष्, cum<BR>Gunâ, secundum generalem 1^mae cl. legem).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एष|एषः<BR>एष, एषा v. एतत्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एषा<BR>एषा f. (r. इष् s. आ) desiderium.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

एषिन्<BR>एषिन् (a r. इष् s. इन्) desiderans, in fine comp. SU. 2.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐकमत्य|ऐकमत्यं<BR>ऐकमत्य n. (ab एकमति una opinio, s. य) unanimitas,<BR>consensus. HIT. 19.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐकान्तिक|ऐकांतिक<BR>ऐकान्तिक Adj. (ab एकान्त s. इक) totus, plenus. BH. 14.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐक्य|ऐक्यं<BR>ऐक्य n. (ab एक s. य) unitas. DEV. 2.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐणेय|ऐणेयं<BR>ऐणेय m. (ab एण s. एय) fortasse idem atque एण q. v. DR. 4.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐन्द्र|ऐंद्र|ऐन्द्रं<BR>ऐन्द्र Adj. (ab इन्द्र s. अ) quod Indri Dei est, aut ad eum<BR>spectat. A. 4.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐन्द्री<BR>ऐन्द्री f. (a praec. signo fem. ई)<BR>1) nxor Indri.<BR>2) nomen<BR>Durgae. DEV. 8.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐरावत|ऐरावतं|ऐरावतः<BR>ऐरावत m. (ex इरावत् s. अ; इरावत् significat a aquam<BR>habens, mare, nubes, ab इरा aqua s. वत्) nomen<BR>elephanti Indri et plagae septentrionalis. IN. 1.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐल|ऐलः<BR>ऐल m. (ab इला Buddhi uxore, s. अ) cognomen regis Pururavasis.<BR>UR. 83.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐशान<BR>ऐशान (ah ईशान Sivus, plagae inter septentriones et<BR>orientem sitae custos) inter septentriones et orientem<BR>situs, nordöstlich.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐशानी<BR>ऐशानी f. (Fem. praec.) plaga inter septentriones et orientem<BR>sita.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐश्वर<BR>ऐश्वर (ab ईश्वर dominus s. अ) augustus. BH. 9.5. 11.3. 8.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐश्वर्य|ऐश्वर्यं|ऐश्वर्य्य|ऐश्वर्य्यं<BR>ऐश्वर्य n. (ab ईश्वर dominus s. य, v. gr. 650.) imperium, potestas,<BR>dominatio, dominium. N. 9.18. BH. 2.43. N. 17.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऐषमस्<BR>ऐषमस् Adv. (ut videtur, ex एष hic, cum Vriddhi, et अमस<BR>tempus, abjecto अ initali et finali) hoc anno. AM.<BR>(Quod ad formationem hujus compositi attinet conferatur<BR>gr. σῆτες, σήμεϱον, v. तत् et gr. comp. 345.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओ<BR>ओ Interj.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओक|ओकं|ओकः<BR>ओक m. (ut videtur, a r. उच् convenire s. अ, v. gr. 645.<BR>suff. अ) domus. AM., v. ओकस्. (Lith. ûki-s Th. ûkja<BR>habitatio in heredio rûstico; ûkininkas hospes, Wirth;<BR>de gr. οἶϰος v. वेश.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओकस्<BR>ओकस् m. (v. praec.) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओख्<BR>ओख् 1. P. (शोषणालमर्थयोः) siccari; ornare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओघ|ओघः<BR>ओघ m. (ut mihi videtur, a r. ऊह् colligere s. अ, mutato<BR>ह् in घ्, nisi घ् est primitiva hujus radicis consonans;<BR>ita मेघ a मिह् vel primit. मिभ्)<BR>1) multitudo, copia,<BR>turba. AM.; IN. 4.17.: गुणौघ; 1.26.: वार्योघ quod etiam<BR>ad sq. sgn. referri potest.<BR>2) flumen, cursus, aquarum<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2b" target="_blank">Page060-2b+ 11</a>]<BR>fluctus. MAN. 9.54. (Cf. gr. ὄχ-λος, ejectâ diphthongi<BR>ओ parte posteriore et posito ο pro अ; v. r. ऊह्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओङ्कार|ओंकार|ओंकारः|ओङ्कारः<BR>ओङ्कार m. (ex ओम् q. v. et कार faciens) syllaba mystica<BR>sanctissima OM. BH. 9.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओण्<BR>ओण् 1. P. (अपनये K. अपसारने V.) abducere, auferre.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओज्<BR>ओज् 10. P. (बलतेजसोः) validum esse; splendere, v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओजस्<BR>ओजस् n. (a praec. s. ओस्)<BR>1) vis, robur, potestas. BH. 15.13.<BR>2) splendor. DH. 7.2. M. 2. N. 5.35.; v. ओजस्विता.<BR>(Cf. gr. ὑγιής; hib. og «young, yuvenile,<BR>fresh»; oig «a chapion» oighe «fullnss, entireness;<BR>virginity».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=060-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओजस्विन्<BR>ओजस्विन् (a praec. s. विन्)<BR>1) validus, robustus, potens.<BR>2) splendidus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=061-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओजस्विता<BR>ओजस्विता f. (a praec. s. ता) i. q. ओजस्. UR. 44.4.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=061-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ओतु|ओतुः<BR>ओतु m. felis. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=061-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

