कक्<BR>कक् 1. A. (लौल्ये K. इच्छागर्भचापले V.) vacillare; desiderare.<BR>(*)<BR>(Huc trahi possit lat. vacillo, ita ut ortum<BR>sit e qVacillo abjectâ gutturali, sicut vermis e<BR>qVermis = कृमि, et vivo e uivo e gVivo = जीव्, goth. qviv̕-s<BR>vivus; gutturales enim et in lat. et in germ. saepe sibi<BR>adjunxerunt semivocalem v, quo facto, non raro ipsae<BR>evanuerunt, sicut e. c. in nostro wer = goth. hva-s,<BR>scr. et lith. ka-s; v. gr. comp. 389.)<BR>(*) Adde superbum esse, si pro garbʽa, quod hîc minime<BR>quadrat, legendum est garva. Wils. hanc radicem explicat<BR>per<BR>1) to be proud.<BR>2) to be unsteady.<BR>3) to be thirsty.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=062-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

