कण्टक|कंटक|कंटकं|कंटकः|कण्टकः<BR>कण्टक m. n. (r. कण्ट् s. अ)<BR>1) spina, ut videtur a crescendo<BR>dicta, nisi r. कण्ट् significavit pungere, sicut<BR>ϰεντέω quod probabiliter cum कण्ट् cohaeret. SA. 6.5.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=063-b" target="_blank">Page063-b+ 37</a>]<BR>2) hostis. N. 26.20. (Cf. gr.<BR>ϰεντέω, ϰεσ-τὸς, ϰέσ-τϱον.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=063-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

