कण्ठ्|कंठ्<BR>कण्ठ् 1. et 10. P. (scribitur कठ्, gr. 110^a).) dolere, lugere,<BR>moerere. (Fortasse huc pertinent gr. ΠΑΘ, ΠΕΝΘ, πέπονϑα, πένϑος;<BR>lat. patior; mutatâ guttuali in labialem.)<BR>c. उत् id. v. उत्कण्ठा, उत्कण्ठित. Caus. GHAT. 5.:<BR>उत्कण्ठयन्ति पथिकान् जलदाः स्वनन्तः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=063-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

