कर्हिचित्<BR>कर्हिचित् (a praec. s. चित्) unquam; plurimum in constructione<BR>cum न ad exprimendum nunquam. N. 1.21. 17.3. 19.7. 22.16.<BR>Sine न, N. 24.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=067-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कल्<BR>1. कल् 1. A. (सङ्ख्याने K. सङ्ख्यरुतौ V.) numerare;<BR>sonare. (Conf. lat. calculo, forma redupl.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=067-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कल्<BR>2. कल् 10. P. (Haec radix plerumque vocalem brevem<BR>retinet, interdum eam producit, unde e. c. MAH. 1.6670. et 6681.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=068-a" target="_blank">Page068-a+ 37</a>]<BR>काल्यमाना agitata, v. etiam compositionem<BR>cum प्र.)<BR>1) agitare, concutere, vibrare. MAH. 2.8.:<BR>मरुता कलिता द्रुमाः; GIT.-GOVIND. 1.14.:<BR>कलयसि करबालम्.<BR>2) cogitare. BHAR. 1.71.: {#DanyaH<BR>ko'pi na vikriyAN kalayati prApte nave yOvane#}.<BR>3) putare, reputare. BHAR. 2.37.: {#kalayati DAritron<BR>tfRasamAm#}. (Cf. चर्, चल्, gr. ϰέλομαι, ϰέλλω, lat.<BR>cello - excello, praecello - celsus; lith. kielù levo, elevo.)<BR>c. आ<BR>1) agitare, concutere. MAH. 1.2853.: {#mArutAkalitAs<BR>tatra drumAH#}; BHAR. 1.50.: केशान् आकलयन्.<BR>2) scire. GITA-G. III.7.7.: {#Kinnam asUyayA hfdayan<BR>tavA ''kalayAmi#}. (Gr. ὀϰέλλω.)<BR>c. प्र (productâ vocali radicali) id. MAH. 1.7178.: {#prakAlayann<BR>eva sa pArTivOGAn#}; 2.1952.: {#prakAlayed diSaH<BR>sarvAH pratodene'va SAraTiH#}. (Lat. procella.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=067-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कल|कलं|कलः<BR>कल (r. कल् s. अ)<BR>1) lenis, mollis, placidus, de voce.<BR>RAGH. 8.58.: कलम् अन्यभृतासु भाषितम् (निहितम्);<BR>1.41.: सारसैः कलनिह्रदैः. N. 9.25.; {#vAzpakalayA<BR>vAcA#}.<BR>2) leniter, placide sonans. RAGH. 16.12.:<BR>कलनूपुराणाम्…अभिसारिकाणाम्.<BR>3) m. sermo lenis,<BR>placidus. BR. 3.21.<BR>4) n. semen virile. MED.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=068-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कलकल|कलकलः<BR>कलकल m. (कल + कल) sonus lenis, placidus, praesertim<BR>cuculorum Indicorum. BHAR. 1.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=068-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

