कलधौत|कलधौतं<BR>कलधौत n.<BR>1) argentum.<BR>2) aurum. AM.: रूप्यहेमयोः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=068-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

