कल्य|कल्यं|कल्यः<BR>कल्य (r. कल् s. य)<BR>1) praeparatus.<BR>2) sanus.<BR>3) n. diluculum,<BR>ortus lucis, tempus matutinum v. sq. (V. कल्याण<BR>et cf. gr. ϰαλός<BR>e ϰαλλόσ - ϰαλλίων, ϰάλλιστος, ϰαλλι-, ϰάλλος - per assimilationem e ϰαλϳος sicut ἄλλος<BR>ex ἀλϳος, v. अन्य.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=069-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

