कामग<BR>कामग (e praec. et ग iens) qui secundum voluntatem vel<BR>desiderium it, i. e. qui quo vult potest ire. N. 18.23. IN. 2.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=070-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामगम<BR>कामगम (e काम et गम iens) i. q. praec. H. 3.5. SU. 2.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=070-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामतस्<BR>कामतस् Adv. (e काम s. तस्) ad voluntatem, secundum<BR>desiderium. H. 2.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=070-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामदुह्<BR>कामदुह् f. (nomin. -धुक् v. gr. 81^a). e काम et दुह् mulgens,<BR>a r. दुह्) quae mulgenti omnia optata praebet<BR>vacca. BH. 3.10. 10.28. N. 2.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=070-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामम्<BR>कामम् Adv. (accus. a काम)<BR>1) libenter. H. 2.34. N. 20.20.<BR>2) bene, facile, wohl. RAGH. 2.43. 4.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=070-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामरूप|कामरूपः<BR>कामरूप (e काम desiderium et रूप forma) I. TATP. optata<BR>forma. II. BAH.<BR>1) qui optatam quamcunque formam<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-a" target="_blank">Page071-a+ 37</a>]<BR>potest assumere. BH. 3.39. 43.; cf. कामरूपिन्.<BR>2) optatam<BR>i. e. pulchram formam habens. SU. 3.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=070-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामरूपिन्<BR>कामरूपिन् (a praec. s. इन्) Adj. qui optatam quamcunque<BR>formam potest assumere. H. 2.22. SU. 1.20. 34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामा<BR>कामा f. (r. कम् s. आ) voluntas. SA. 5.10.: कामया cum<BR>voluntate, libenter.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामिता<BR>कामिता f. (a sq. s. ता)<BR>1) desiderium, cupido, libido. HIT. 28.7.<BR>2) amor, benevolentia. RAGH. 9.57.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कामिन्<BR>कामिन् (r. कम् s. इन्)<BR>1) amans, cupiens, volens. BH. 2.70.<BR>2) m. amasins. Lass. 60.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

