कायस्थ|कायस्थः<BR>कायस्थ (e praec. et स्थ) classis hominum hujus nominis et<BR>vir hujus classis. Wils. «The Cayeth or writer cast,<BR>proceeding from a Cshettriya father and Sûdra mother».<BR>HIT. 49.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

