कारव|कारवः<BR>कारव m. (e. का et रव sonus) cornix (Lat. corvus, fortasse<BR>etiam gr. ϰόϱαξ, mutato v in k v. gr. comp. 19.; etiam<BR>ϰοϱώνη et cornix quodam modo cum कारव cohaerere<BR>videntur.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कारा<BR>कारा f. (ut videtur, a r. कृ in formâ caus. s. आ) carcer.<BR>(Lith. kaliu captivus sum, in carcere sum; kaliny-s captivus,<BR>kalinế carcer; v. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कारागार|कारागारं<BR>कारागार m. (e praec. et आगार domus) id. (Lat. carcer,<BR>quod etiam e repetita voce कारा explicari potest.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=071-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

