काश्<BR>काश् 1. et 4. A.<BR>1) lucere, splendere. RAGH. 10.87.<BR>2) apparere,<BR>videri. M. 43.: {#nE'va BUmir naca diSaH…<BR>cakASire#} (sic legendum pro प्रकाशिरे).<BR>c. निस् expellere, ausleuchten. Lass. 9.14.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. RAM. III.55.21.: {#udyAnAni prakASante<BR>mamA 'nyaTA#}. — Caus. (प्रकाशयामि) collustrare, illustrare;<BR>manifestare. A. 1.2. BH. 5.16. HIT. 30.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

काश्मीर|काश्मीरं|काश्मीरः<BR>काश्मीर nomen regionis. HIT. 46.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

काष्ठ|काष्ठं<BR>काष्ठ n. lignum. SA. 5.1. 2. HIT. 49.11. (Cambro-brit.<BR>coed, bret. coat; e syllaba काष् gr. ξυ vocis ξύ-λον<BR>litteris transpotis et â attenuato in v explicari possit.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

काष्ठा<BR>काष्ठा f. minuta pars temporis, v. कला. DEV. 11.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कास्<BR>कास् 1. A. (दीप्तौ शब्दकुत्सायाम् K. कुशब्दे V.)<BR>1) lucere,<BR>splendere (v. चकास्, काश् et cf. goth. haiza<BR>fax; Benary huc refert Κάσ-τωϱ).<BR>2) tussire. (Lith. kòs-tu<BR>tussio, kós-ế-ti tussire, slav. kasʽjljati; germ. vet.<BR>huosto tussis, v. Pott. I. p. 278.; scot. casad id., cambro-brit.<BR>pâs.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कास|कासः<BR>कास m. (r. कास् s. अ) tussis. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कासर|कासरः<BR>कासर m. bos bubulus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कासार|कासारं|कासारः<BR>कासार m. stagnum, lacus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कि<BR>1. कि 3. P. चिकेमि (ज्ञाने) scire. (Fortasse lat. scio praefixo<BR>s; hib. ci «see, behold», ci-thi «you see», citear<BR>«it seems, appears»; v. कित्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कि<BR>2. कि stirps interrogativa, v. किम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किंशारु|किंशारुः<BR>किंशारु m. (ut videtur, e किम् et शारु, quod simplex non<BR>invenitur, a r. शॄ laedere s. उ, v. gr. 671.) aristae spicarum.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किंशुक|किंशुकः<BR>किंशुक m. (KARM. ex interrog. किम् et शुक psittacus. gr. 671.)<BR>nomen arboris (Butea frondosa). N. 12.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किङ्कर|किंकर|किङ्करः<BR>किङ्कर m. (e किम् quid et कर faciens) servus, famulus. SA. 6.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किङ्किणि<BR>किङ्किणि f. cingulus cum parvis tintinnabulis, vel quodvis<BR>aliud ornamentum tinniens.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किङ्किणी|किंकिणी<BR>किङ्किणी f. i. q. praec.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किङ्किणीकिन्<BR>किङ्किणीकिन् (e praec. s. किन्) ornamento tinniente indutus.<BR>IN. 5.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किञ्चन|किंचन|किञ्चनः<BR>किञ्चन (Nom. कश्चन, काचन, किञ्चन, v. gr. 284.) aliquis,<BR>quispiam, ullus. SA. 2.21.; praesertim in costructione<BR>cum negativo न, e. c. SU. 4.3. 24. - Accus. neut. किञ्चन<BR>adverbialiter ponitur, praesertim in constructione cum न,<BR>ad exprimendum nullo modo, neutiquam, nequaquam.<BR>BR. 1.24. (Cum suffixo चन conferatur hun linguae<BR>goth., ubi ni hvas-hun idem valet ac sanscritum न कश्चन,<BR>v. gr. comp. 398.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किञ्चित्|किंचित्<BR>किञ्चित् (Nom. कश्चित्, काचित्, किञ्चित् v. gr. 284.)<BR>id. BR. 1.17. SU. 1.25. HIT. 21.5. - यः कश्चित् id. HIT. 11.5.:<BR>सुवर्णकङ्कनं यस्मै कस्मैचिद् दातुम् इच्छामिकिञ्चित्<BR>Adv. paululum. SA. 4.26. DR. 9.24. (Particula<BR>enclitica चित् quac in dialecto Vêdicâ etiam cun Substantivis<BR>conjungitur - e. c. वयश्चित् aves a वि - est<BR>neutrum stirpis चि, quod ortum est e कि, unde formis<BR>Vêdicis माकिस्, नकिस् respondent Zend. 𐬨𐬁𐬗𐬌𐬱<BR>mâ-ćis, 𐬥𐬀𐬈𐬗𐬌𐬱 naê-ćis, v. gr. comp. 328.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किञ्चिलिक|किंचिलिकः|किञ्चिलिकः<BR>किञ्चिलिक m. v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=072-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किञ्चुलुक|किञ्चुलुकः<BR>किञ्चुलुक m. (fortasse e किम् et चुलुक pro चलुक, a r.<BR>चल् se movere) vermis. AM. Scribitur etiam किञ्चिलिक.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किञ्जल|किंजल|किंजलः|किञ्जलः<BR>किञ्जल m. (e किम् et जल a r. जल् tegere s. अ) fibra loti,<BR>v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किञ्जल्क|किंजल्क|किञ्जल्कं|किंजल्कः|किञ्जल्कः<BR>किञ्जल्क m. (ut videtur, a praecedente, s. क, ita ut किञ्चल्क<BR>mutilatum sit e किञ्चलक) RAGH. 15.52.: {#himaklizwakiYjalkam<BR>paNkajam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किट्<BR>किट् 1. P. (गतौ K.) ire. (Cf. कट्, ex quo किट् ortum<BR>esse censeo attenuato अ in इ, sicut इट् q. v. ex अट्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किटि|किटिः<BR>किटि m. (r. किट् s. इ) aper. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किट्ट|किट्टं<BR>किट्ट n. sordes. AM.: = मल.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किण|किणः<BR>किण m. cicatrix. RAGH. 18.47.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कित्<BR>1. कित् 3. P. चिकेत्मि (cf. कि unde कित् ortum esse videtur<BR>adjecto त्, v. gr. comp. 109^b).)<BR>1) videre,<BR>cernere, percipere, animadvertere. RIGV. apud Rosen.<BR>p. 81.3.: यथा नो मित्रो वरुणो यथा रुद्रश् चिकेतति<BR>«ut nos Mitras, Varunas, et Rudras animadvertat» (चिकेतति<BR>pro चिकेत्ति, adjecto charactere 1^*mae classis, ita<BR>ut चिकिति pro radice haberi posset); p. 100.7.: {#tava<BR>vajraS cikite bAhvor hitaH#} «telum conspicitur tuis<BR>in manibus positum» (praeter. redupl. hic sicut saepe in<BR>dialecto Vêdicâ praesentis loco fungitur; posset tamen<BR>etiam चिकिते pro praes. cognatae radicis कि haberi);<BR>p. 106.3.: तवेऽद् इदम् अभितश् चेकिते वसु «tua<BR>haec ubique conspicitur opulentia» (चेकिते pro चिकिते,<BR>quod supra); 140.5.: चिकेतद् अस्मै «animum<BR>advertat huic» (चिकेतद् pro चिकेद् (चिकेत्) sicut<BR>supra चिकेतति pro चिकेत्ति).<BR>2) scire, nosse. RIGV.<BR>p. 137.4.: य ईञ् चिकेत गुहा भवन्तम् «qui eum novit<BR>in specu versantem»; p. 144.4.: {#cikitvAn agnim<BR>pade parame tasTivAMsam#} «cognoscens Agnim loco summo<BR>insistentem». (In utroque tamen loco significationem<BR>cernere, percipere praetulerim; grammatici<BR>vero hanc radicem explicant per ज्ञाने K. मतौ V.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कित्<BR>2. कित् 1. P. (रोगापनयने K. संशयेच्छावासारोग्येषु V.)<BR>sanare; dubitare; desiderare; habitare; valere. In<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-b" target="_blank">Page073-b+ 37</a>]<BR>dialecto Vêdicâ कित् cl. 1. item significat cernere, animadvertere.<BR>RIGV. p. 3.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कितव|कितवः<BR>कितव m. lusor, aleator. N. 17.37.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किन्तु|किंतु<BR>किन्तु (किम् + तु) sed, autem, vero. HIT. 10.11. 86.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किन्नर|किंनर|किन्नरः<BR>किन्नर (KARM. e किम् quid, et नर vir, v. gr. 671.) nomen<BR>ordinis Geniorum, qui Kuvêri sunt famuli et coelestes<BR>cantores et fidicines.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किन्नु|किंनु<BR>किन्नु (किम् + नु)<BR>1) an, num. N. 10.10. 12.98.<BR>2) quanto<BR>minus, nedum. BH. 1.35.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किम्<BR>1. किम् (Nom. कस्, का, किम्, gr. 273.) quis; - Nota locutionem<BR>cum gen. personae et instr. rei, ad exprimendum,<BR>quid prodest? e. c. N. 12.90.: {#ko nu me jIvitenA<BR>'rTas tam fte purazarzaBam#}; RAGH. 2.53.: {#kin rAjyena<BR>tadviparItavftteH#}; nonnunquam part. fut. pass. radicis कृ<BR>additur, e. c. Lass. 12.20.: {#kim bahunA mama BAzitena<BR>kartavyam#}. In hujusmodi locutionibus part. pass. praet.<BR>gerundii loco fungitur, e. c. DR. 7.4. H. 4.2. - Antecedente<BR>quopiam vocabulo interrogativo aliquis; BH. 2.21.: {#kaTaM<BR>sa…kaN GAtayati hanti kam#}; cum sequente अपि<BR>aliquis, quispiam. HIT. 4.7.; cum antecedente relativo et<BR>sequente अपि quisque, quicunque. N. 26.9. (Lith. kas<BR>accurate convenit cum nomin. masc. कस्; goth. hva-s<BR>quis? = कस्, hvô quae? = का, hva-ta quid? = obsoleto<BR>कत्, zendico 𐬐𐬀𐬝 kaṭ; lat. quis, quid, a Th. कि<BR>quo, quod (= कत्), qui, quorum, quos, a Th. क; de<BR>fem. et neut. pl. quae pro quâ = goth. hvô v. gr. comp. 387. 394.;<BR>ad Th. कि etiam pertinet lat. hi-c, ci-s, ci-tra,<BR>l. c. 394. 395. et goth. HI, unde hi-mma, hi-na, hi-ta, hidrê,<BR>angl. he, hi-s, hi-m, l. c. 397.; gr. ΠΟ; jon. ΚΟ<BR>(πό-τεϱον, ϰό-τεϱον, πῶς, ϰῶς etc.); slav. ky-ĭ, ka-ja, ko-e,<BR>gr. comp. 388.; hib. cia, scot. co, cambro-brit. pa quid?)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किम्<BR>2. किम् Adv.<BR>1) cur. BR. 3.2.<BR>2) an, num. HIT. 39.4.:<BR>अस्मिन् निर्जने वने कदाचित् किम् व्याधा सञ्चरन्ति;<BR>v. किन्नु, किम्वा.<BR>3) utrum ob. HIT. 53.18.<BR>4) Cum sequente पुनर् (किम् पुनर्) quanto magis vel<BR>quanto minus. BH. 9.33. A. 5.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किमर्थम्<BR>किमर्थम् Adv. (TATP. e. किम्, tanquam interrogativi stirpe<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">Page074-a+ 37</a>]<BR>cum vi genitivi, et अर्थम् v. अर्थ) cur, quam ob rem.<BR>H. 4.28.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=073-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किमु<BR>किमु v. उ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किमुत<BR>किमुत Adv. (किम् + उत) nedum, ne dicam. RAGH. 2.62.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किम्पचान|किंपचान|किम्पचानः<BR>किम्पचान (e किम् et पचान coquens a r. पच् s. partic.<BR>praes. ATM. आन pro मान) miser. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किम्पुरुष|किंपुरुष|किम्पुरुषः<BR>किम्पुरुष m. (e किम् et पुरुष vir) i. q. किन्नर. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किम्वदन्ती<BR>किम्वदन्ती f. (e किम् et वदन्ती part. praes. fem. radicis<BR>वद् dicere) rumor, fama. HIT. 39.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

