कियत्|कियन्त्<BR>कियत् (Nom. कियान्, कियती, कियत्, a stirpe interr.<BR>कि s. अत् e वत् abjecto व्, mutato इ stirpis कि in<BR>इय् ex euphon. lege 51., v. इयत्) quantus, quot. HIT. 56.16.<BR>PAT. 4. — कियत् Adv. aliquantulum, paululum.<BR>HIT. 86.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किर|किरः<BR>किर m. (r. कॄ s. अ) aper.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किरण|किरणः<BR>किरण n. (r. कॄ s. अन) radius luminis. RAGH. 5.74.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

किरात|किरातः<BR>किरात m. Kirâtus, homo ferus, silvas vel montes habitans<BR>et venatu vivens.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=074-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

