कूट|कूटः<BR>कूट m. (r. कूट् s. अ)<BR>1) vertex, cacumen. N. 12.8.<BR>2) acervus,<BR>v. कूटशस्.<BR>3) fraus. MAH. 1.2476.: {#na kUwamAnEr<BR>vaRijaH paRyam vikrIRate tadA#}; v. कूटबन्ध.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=078-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

