कृकवाकु|कृकवाकुः<BR>कृकवाकु m. (e कृक et वाकु a rad. वच् s. उ)<BR>1) gallus.<BR>AM.<BR>2) pavo. (Cum prima hujus comp. parte convenit<BR>hib. cearc gallina, v. कृकण).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=080-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृच्छ्र|कृच्छ्रं|कृछ्र<BR>कृच्छ्र (ut mihi videtur, e कृत् vel कृत abjecto अ et zra e<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=081-a" target="_blank">Page081-a+ 37</a>]<BR>श्रम abjectâ syllabâ finali)<BR>1) difficilis, molestus, aerumnosus.<BR>2) n. difficultas, onus, molestia, miseria. H. 1.15.<BR>BR. 3.11. N. 15.16. 24.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=080-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृज्<BR>कृज् 1. A. (भर्जने K.) assare, torrere. (Hib. sgreigim «I<BR>fry».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=081-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृत्<BR>1. कृत् 6. P. कृन्तामि (gr. 335.) findere, dissecare. DR. 8.27.:<BR>चकर्त निशितैर् भल्लैर् धनूंषिच शिरांसिच;<BR>RAM. III.74.3.: द्रुमः परशुना कृत्तः. (कृत् correptum<BR>est e कर्त् - v. «Vocalismus» p. 168. et cf. कर्त् - cui respondet<BR>lith. kertù caedo, infinit. kirs-ti; gr. ϰείϱω, ϰάϱσις,<BR>abjecto t, quâ in re convenit cum slav. korjû scindo;<BR>lat. curtus, cul-ter, v. कर्त्री; hib. ceartaighim «I prune,<BR>trim, cut», cuirc «a knife».)<BR>c. उत् i. q. simpl. H. 2.13.: एषाम् उत्कृत्य मांसानि.<BR>c. नि id. DR. 5.24.: पपात शाखीऽव निकृत्तमूलः.<BR>c. निस् abscindere. DR. 8.21. ATM.: {#Bujam mUle KaNgena<BR>nirakfntata#}.<BR>c. वि id. N. 10.17.: कथम् वासो विकर्तेयम् secundum<BR>1^mam classem.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=081-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृत्<BR>2. कृत् (r. कृ s. त्, gr. 643.) faciens, in fine compp. BH. 3.5.<BR>A. 4.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=081-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृत|कृतं<BR>कृत (part. pass. a r. कृ s. त<BR>1) factus.<BR>2) Subst. n. factum,<BR>facinus. Loc, कृते et instr. कृतेन tanquam praepositiones<BR>significant propter, c. genit. aut in compositione<BR>cum nomine recto. N. 4.3. 9.19. SA. 5.94. - V. कृतम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=081-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

