कृमि|कृमिः<BR>कृमि m. (fortasse a r. कृष्) insectum, vermis. RAGH. 16.20.:<BR>तिरस्क्रियन्ते कृमितन्तुज्ञालैः…गवाक्षाः (Schol.<BR>Calc. कृमि explicat per ऊर्णनाभ); BHAR. 1.63.: कृमिकुलशतावृततनुः…श्वा.<BR>(कृमि correptum est e कर्मि,<BR>v. ऋ. Lith. kirminis, kirmếlế, russ. червь ćervj, mutato<BR>m in v; hib. cruimh, cambro-brit. pryv; goth.<BR>vaurms, Th. vaurmi, e hvaurmi, v. gr. comp. 388.; lat.<BR>vermi-s e quermi-s; fortasse gr. ἕλμινς e ἕϱμινς, cf. lith.<BR>kirminis.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=082-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

