कृषिन्<BR>कृषिन् m. (r. कृष् s. इन्) arator. SU. 2.24.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृष्ण|कृष्णं|कृष्णः<BR>कृष्ण<BR>1) niger, violaceus.<BR>2) m. nom. propr. Krischnus,<BR>deus Wischnus humanâ formâ indutus. Dual. कृष्णौ<BR>Krischnus et Arjunus. (Russ. черный ćernyĭ niger<BR>ejectâ sibilante.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृष्णवर्त्मन्<BR>कृष्णवर्त्मन् m. (nigram viam habens, (BAH. e praec.<BR>et वर्त्मन् via) ignis.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृष्णसर्प<BR>कृष्णसर्प m. (e कृष्ण et सर्प) serpens niger. HIT. 67.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृष्णसार|कृष्णसारः<BR>कृष्णसार (BAH. e कृष्ण et सार q. v.<BR>1) niger. N. 24.16.<BR>2) m. dorcas, antilope niger. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृष्णा<BR>कृष्णा f. nomen Pândavorum uxoris.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कृष्णाय्<BR>कृष्णाय् (Denom. a कृष्ण, gr. 585.) nigrare. HIT. 22.74.:<BR>अङ्गारः शीतः कृष्णायते करम्. (Russ. черню ćernjû<BR>nigro).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कॄ<BR>1. कॄ 6. P. किरामि (gr. 334.) conjicere, spargere, perfundere,<BR>obruere, implere. GITA-GOV. 4.14.: {#kirati<BR>sajalakaRajAlam#}; DR. 8.6.: {#SaktitomaranArAcEH…<BR>kIryamARaH#}. (Gr. ϰεϱάω, ϰεϱάννυμι, ϰίϱνημι, quorum<BR>ultimum formâ cum कृणामि cl. 9. convenit, cf. पॄ, quod<BR>ex कॄ mutatâ gutturali in labialem ortum esse videtur.)<BR>c. अनु implere. MAH. 1.4340.: {#vaRigBiScA' nvakIryanta<BR>nagarARi#}. - अनुकीर्ण impletus. DR. 6.2. 8.48. A. 7.2.<BR>c. अभि implere. R. Schl. II.14.53.: अभ्यकीर्यत शोकेन.<BR>c. अव<BR>1) i. q. simpl. A. 3.32.: अस्त्रपूगेत…भूतम् अवाकिरम्. अवकीर्ण<BR>impletus, plenus. MAH. 1.7840.<BR>2) deserere, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-b" target="_blank">Page083-b+ 37</a>]<BR>relinquere. MAH. 1.3057.: {#avakIryaca mAM yAtA<BR>parAtmajam ivA 'satI#}.<BR>3) Pass. deserere, se dispandere,<BR>dilatare. R. Schl. I.38.14.: समन्ताद् अवकीर्यत<BR>(omisso augmento) {#samantatastu tAn devIm aByaziYcata<BR>pAvakaH#}.<BR>c. अव preaf. सम् i. q. simpl. A. 3.25.: {#tam…SaravarzeRa<BR>samavAkiram#}.<BR>c. आ implere. आकीर्ण impletus, plenus. N. 12.2. 113.<BR>A. 6.7. (Cf. lat. acervus.)<BR>c. आ praef. अप vacuefacere, ex inanire; MAH. 1.2851.:<BR>ना ऽपुष्पः पादपः कश्चित् षटपदैर् ना ऽप्य् अपाकीर्णः.<BR>c. आ preaf. सम् implere. समाकीर्ण. N. 12.38.<BR>c. उत्<BR>1) superfundere. UR. 37.5.: {#utkIrRA iva vAsayazwizu<BR>niSA nidrAlasA varhiRaH#}.<BR>2) perforare?<BR>RAGH. 4.59.: मत्तेभरदनोत्कीर्ण; v. sq.<BR>c. उत् praef. सम् id. RAGH. 1.4.: मणौ वज्रसमुत्कीर्णे<BR>(Schol. Calc. = हीरेण च्छिद्रिते.)<BR>c. परि<BR>1) circumfundere, undique implere. RAGH. ed. Calc. 8.35.:<BR>भ्रमरैः…परिकीर्णा (Schol. {#paritaH sarvataH<BR>kIrRA vyAptA#}).<BR>2) committere, tradere. RAGH. 18.32.:<BR>महीम् महेच्छः परिकीर्य सूनौ.<BR>c. प्र se dissipare, se disspergere. RAM. I.9.20.: {#sarvataH<BR>prakiranti sma lalamAnA varANganAH; - prakIrRa#} expansus,<BR>elatus. A. 6.2.: फेनवत्यः प्रकीर्णाश्च…ऊर्मयः;<BR>10.63.: प्रकीर्णकेशी. (Cf. lat. prôcêrus, quod etiam ad<BR>कृष् trahi potest, unde प्रकृष्ट longus.)<BR>c. वि spargere, expandere. HIT. 9.: तण्डुलकणान् विकीर्य;<BR>MAN. 11.196.: विकिरेत् यवसं गवाम्; A. 9.18.:<BR>विकीर्णैर् इव पर्वतैः. - श्वासान् विकरितुम् suspiria<BR>ducere. GITA-GOV. 5.16.<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) confundere, miscere. MAH. 1.3479.: सङ्कीर्णाचारधर्म;<BR>2) implere. IN. 1.28.: अप्सरोगणसङ्कीर्ण; SU. 2.24.:<BR>अस्थिकङ्कालसङ्कीर्ण.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कॄ<BR>2. कॄ 9. P.: कृणामि (= ϰίϱνημι, v. कॄ cl. 6., हिंसायाम् K.<BR>हिंसे V.) offendere, laedere, ferire, vexare, occidere.<BR>(Cf. चिरि, चीर्ण, चूर्ण्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=083-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कॄ<BR>3. कॄ 10. A.: कारये (विज्ञाने V.) noscere. (Gr. ϰϱίνω, lat.<BR>cerno, quae formâ cum कृणामि cl. 9. cohaerent, v.<BR>gr. comp. 109^a). 5.496.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कॄत्<BR>कॄत् 10. P. कीर्तयामि (ut mihi videtur, Denom. a कीर्ति<BR>gloria, quodipsum a कॄ, quocum fortasse lat. CEL vocis<BR>celeber cohaeret, mutato r in l)<BR>1) dicere, eloqui,<BR>enuntiare, memorare. MAN. 3.36.: {#sarvaM SfRuta tam<BR>viprAH samyak kIrtayato mama#}; 10.123.: {#viprasevE'va<BR>SUdrasya viSizwaN karma kIrtyate#}.<BR>2) laudare, celebrare.<BR>N. 20.36.: {#yeca tvAm manuzyA loke kIrtayizyanty<BR>atandritAH#}; BH. 9.14.: सततङ् कीर्तयन्तो माम्.<BR>c. उत्, अनु, परि, प्र, सम् + प्र, सम् id. RAGH. 10.33.:<BR>महिमानम्…उत्कीर्त्य तव; R. Schl. I.14.22.: {#avajYAya…mAnuzAn<BR>nA'nvakIrtayat#}; MAN. 2.122.: {#svan<BR>nAma parikIrtayet#}; M. 56. परिकीर्तित celebratus;<BR>MAN. 3.27.: ब्राह्मो धर्मः प्रकीर्तितः; BH. 18.4.: {#tyAgo<BR>hi…triviDaH samprakIrtitaH#}; N. 5.10.: {#saNkIrtyamAnezu<BR>rAjYAn nAmasu#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कॢप्<BR>1. कॢप् 1. A., secundam grammaticos etiam P. (ut videtur,<BR>a r. कृ adjecto प्, sicut saepe in formis caus. — gr. 519. sq.<BR>- mutato ऋ in ऌ, vel, in formis gunatis, अर् in<BR>अल्; plerumque enim haec radix कल्प् sonat, unde<BR>Praes. कल्पामि, कल्पे, v. कृप्) fieri, praesertim participem<BR>fieri alcjs rei, vel causam fieri alcjs rei, esse alicui<BR>rei, converti in alqd, afferre alqd, c. dat. rei, plerumque<BR>substantivorum abstructorum. BH. 2.15.: {#so'mftatvAya<BR>kalpate#} is immortalitatis particeps fit; RAGH. 18.32.:<BR>अजन्मने ऽकल्पत liberationis a nativitate particeps factus<BR>est. - कॢप्त factus, constitutus. MAN. 3.69.: {#paYca<BR>kxptA mahAyajYAH#}. (Huc traxerim nostrum helfe, goth.<BR>hilpa, praet. et radix halp, quod accuratissime cum कल्प्<BR>convenit, mutatâ initiali tenui in aspiratam, ex generali<BR>lege, et servatâ tenui finali, sicut in slêpa dormio =<BR>स्वप्, v. gr. comp. 89.; lith. gélbmi juvo, v. कॢप् cl. 10.)<BR>c. उप i. q. simpl. MAN. 3.202.: {#vAry api SradDayA dattam<BR>akzayAyo 'pakalpate#} (Schol. अक्षयसुखहेतुः सम्पद्यते).<BR>- उपकॢप्त factus, praeparatus, apportatus (v. कॢप्<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-b" target="_blank">Page084-b+ 37</a>]<BR>cl. 10. praef. उप). MAN. 3.208.: {#AsanezU 'pakxptezu…<BR>viprAMs tAn upaveSayet#} (Schol. उपकॢप्तेषु explicat<BR>per विन्यस्तेषु i. e. collocatis); 8.333.: {#yas tv etAny<BR>upakxptAni dravyARi stenayet#} (Schol. {#upaBogArTam<BR>kftasaMskArARi#}).<BR>c. वि haesitare, dubitare. HIT. 53.10.: आदिष्टो न विकल्पेत.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

कॢप्<BR>2. कॢप् 10. P. कल्पयामि.<BR>1) facere, efficere, creare.<BR>RAGH. 8.46.: {#mama BAgyaviplavAd aSaniH kalpita<BR>eza veDasA#}; R. Schl. I.35.1.: {#pOtrIm izwim<BR>akalpayat#}; RAGH. 1.94.: {#kalpayAmAsa vanyAm<BR>evA 'sya saMviDAm#} (Schol. Calc. = सम्पादयामास).<BR>2) dare, impertire. RAM. I.53.10.: {#BAgAn na<BR>kalpayaTa me surAH#}; MAN. 11.231.: {#kalpayitvA 'sya<BR>vfttim#}; MAH. Ex. 58.: आसनङ् कल्पयामास.<BR>c. उप praeparare, apportare. RAM. I.11.58.: {#yajYe yad<BR>upakalpitam#}; III.65.17.: शय्या त्वदर्थम् उपकल्पिता;<BR>N. 23.11.: {#tasya prakzAlanArTAya kumBAs tatro<BR>'pa kalpitAH#}.<BR>c. परि<BR>1) facere, parare. RAGH. 4.6.: परिकल्पितसान्निध्या…सरस्वती;<BR>11.23.: {#AsasAda munir Atmanas<BR>tataH SizyavargaparikalpitArhaRam…tapovanam#};<BR>MAN. 9.152.: सर्वम् वा रिक्थज्ञातन् तु दशधा परिकल्प्यच<BR>(Schol. दशधा कृत्वा).<BR>2) constituere, definire.<BR>UP. 35.: {#tasyA'pi…tayA niSi saNketakan dvitIyasmin<BR>prahare paryakalpyata#}.<BR>c. प्र<BR>1) facere. दण्डम् प्रकल्पितुम् punire, castigare.<BR>MAN. 8.324.<BR>2) dare, impertire. MAN. 11.22.: {#vfttin<BR>DarmyAm prakalpayet#}, v. simpl. sgf. 3.<BR>c. सम् cogitare. BHAR. 3.63.: {#atItam api na smarann<BR>apica BAvyasaNkalpayan#}. (Schol. {#Bavitavyan na<BR>saNkalpayan#}.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केका<BR>केका f. pavonum clamor. RAGH. 1.39.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केकिन्<BR>केकिन् m. (a praec. s. इन्) pavo. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केत्<BR>केत् 10. P. advocare, invitare; consilium dare (proprie<BR>facere ut aliquis sciat, Caus. radicis कित् scire).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केत<BR>केत m. (r. कित् s. अ)<BR>1) domus, habitatio.<BR>2) in dial.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">Page085-a+ 36</a>]<BR>Vêdicâ mens. Ros. L. 14. {#divyo ganDarvo ketapUH ketan<BR>naH punAtu#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=084-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केतक|केतकः<BR>केतक m. केतकी f. (r. कित् s. अक) planta quaedam,<BR>Pandanus odoratissimus. RAGH. 13.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केतन|केतनं<BR>केतन n. (r. कित् s. अन)<BR>1) signum, insigne. MAH. 1.8138.<BR>2) vexillum.<BR>3) habitatio. R. Schl. I.75.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केतु|केतुः<BR>केतु m. (r. कित् s. उ) vexillum. N. 12.38.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केप्<BR>केप् 1. A. (गत्याम् K. गत्याञ् चाले V.) ire, se movere,<BR>vacillare. (Cf. कम्प्, गेप्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केयूर|केयूरं|केयूरः<BR>केयूर n. armilla. RAGH. 6.68.; m. BHAR. 2.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केल्<BR>केल् 1. P. (गतौ K. चालगत्योः V.) ire, se movere, vacillare;<BR>cf. चल्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केलि|केलिः<BR>केलि m. f. (r. किल् s. इ) lusus, praesertim amatorius. HIT. 50.1.<BR>(Hib. cal «a joke», v. किल्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केव्<BR>केव् 1. A. (सेवने K. सेवे V.) colere, venerari (Cf. सेव्,<BR>quod ex केव् ortum esse potest, quum gutturales facile<BR>in sibilantes transenant.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केवर्त|केवर्तः|केवर्त्त|केवर्त्तः<BR>केवर्त m. (e के, locat. vocis क aqua, et वर्त iens) piscator,<BR>v. कैवर्त.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केवल|केवलं|केवलः<BR>केवल<BR>1) omnis, universus, totus. BH. 5.11. A. 9.7. DR. 4.17.<BR>2) unus, solus. RAGH. 2.63. (Goth. hail sanus ?)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केवलम्<BR>केवलम् Adv. (a praec. signo accus. म्) solum. HIT. 4.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केश|केशः<BR>केश m. (ut equidem puto, e locat. के in capite et श corrupto<BR>e शय, quod etiam in aliis hujusmodi compositis<BR>invenitur, e. c. जलेशय piscis; केश est igitur quod in<BR>capite jacet, sicut शिरोरुह quod in capite crescit,<BR>v. गिरिश) coma, caesaries. (Lat. caesaries formâ<BR>magis cum केशर convenit, quocum etiam nostrum<BR>Haar, anglo-sax. haer, contulerim, ita ut media syllaba<BR>vocis केशर ejecta sit, sicut कुमार apud Graecos sonat<BR>ϰόϱος, ϰοῦϱος. Cum priore compositi केश parte i. e.<BR>cum क caput conferri potest lat. ca vocis ca-pillus, quasi<BR>capitis pilus, nec non syllaba co, ϰο vocum co-ma,<BR>ϰόμη.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केशर|केशरं|केशरः<BR>केशर m. (a praec. s. र)<BR>1) juba leonis. Lass. 62.20.<BR>2) i. q.<BR>केसर (v. केश).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

केशरिन्<BR>केशरिन् (a praec. s. इन्)<BR>1) jubatus, de leone. MAH. 1.8286.:<BR>सिंहाः केशरिणः.<BR>2) m. leo. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=085-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

