क्लैव्य|क्लैव्यं<BR>क्लैव्य n. (a क्लीव s. य) debilitas, debilitatio, demissio animi,<BR>mollitia. BH. 2.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=090-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

क्व<BR>क्व ubi? SA. 6.9.; quo? Lass. 24.11.: क्व गच्छसि. Notentur<BR>locutiones veluti {#kvaca te kzatriyabalaN kvaca brahmabalam<BR>mahat#} ubi tua cschatriyica potentia? ubi brahmanica<BR>potentia magna? i. e. quantum interest inter illam<BR>et hanc. R. Schl. 56.4. - Exempla, ubi res vel persona<BR>superior in priore loco posita est, sunt; RAGH. 1.2.: {#kva<BR>sUryapraBavo vaMSaH kvacA 'lpavizayA matiH#}; MAH. 1.3065.:<BR>{#kva maharziH sacE'vA ''gryaH sA 'psarAH kvaca menakA<BR>. - kvA'pi#} alicubi. N. 16.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=090-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

क्वचित्<BR>क्वचित् (a praec. s. चित्) alicubi. N. 15.15. - Repetitum,<BR>ubique. IN. 3.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=090-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

क्वण्<BR>क्वण् 1. P. sonare. HIT. 58.21.: {#qiRqimo hastipakAhataH<BR>kvaRan; - kvaRita#} sonans, susurrans. UR. 68.1.:<BR>पद्मम् अन्तःक्वणितषट्पदम्. (Cf. कण्, कुण्,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=091-a" target="_blank">Page091-a+ 36</a>]<BR>चण्, स्वन्, ratione habitâ, gutturales facile in sibilantes<BR>degenerare; lat. cano, goth. hana gallus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=090-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

