खलु<BR>खलु<BR>1) sane, profecto, ad orationis vim augendam ponitur,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=097-b" target="_blank">Page097-b+ 36</a>]<BR>praesertim post voces negativas vel interrogativas. SAK. 5.15. 16.:<BR>{#Bo rAjan ASramamfgaH Kalv ayam . na Kalu<BR>na Kalu vARaH sannipAtyo 'yam asmin#} ja nicht! ja<BR>nicht!; RAGH. 9.28.: {#na Kalu tAvat aSezam apohitum<BR>ravir alam viralam kftavAn himam#}; Lass. 1.3.:<BR>प्रारभ्यते न खलु विघ्नभयेन नीचैः; N. 16.22.:<BR>कदा नु खलु दुःखस्य पारं यास्यति वै शुभा wann<BR>doch?; SAK. 23.15.: किङ् खलु; 44.2.infr.: क्व खलु;<BR>59.14.: कथम्…खलु.<BR>2) enim, praesertim antecedente<BR>न. SAK. 26.5.: {#mandOtsuKyo 'smi nagarAgamanam prati<BR>…na Kalu Sakto 'smi SakuntalAdarSanavyApArAd AtmAnan<BR>nivartayitum#}; RAGH. 3.51.: {#gfhARa Sastram…<BR>na Kalv anirjitya raGuN kftI BavAn#}.<BR>3) {#Kalv<BR>api#} sed etiam, antecedente न केवलम्. RAGH. 18.48.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=097-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

खलुज्<BR>खलुज् m. (N. खलुक्, ut videtur, e ख et लुज्, a r. लुज् laedere,<BR>occidere) obscuritas, caigo. (Cf. lat. caligo.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=097-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

