खुज्<BR>खुज् 1. P. (स्तेयकरणे K. स्तेये V.) furari. (Fortasse lith.<BR>wagiù furor, ita ut mutilatum sit e kwagiù, abjectâ gutturali<BR>et relicto w euphonico, sicut e. c. in lat. vermis e<BR>quermis et goth. vaurms e hvaurms = कृमि q. v. Res<BR>si ita se habet, vocalis a verbi wagiù formis gunatis radicis<BR>खुज् respondet, e. c. Caus. खोजयामि, abjecto उ<BR>radicali. Posset tamen wa etiam litteris transpositis ex<BR>au explicari.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=098-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

