खै<BR>खै 1. P. (स्थैर्ये खननहिंसयोः K. V. खेदने K.) firmum<BR>esse, fodere, laedere, occidere; dolore, moestitiâ affici,<BR>defatigari. Cf. क्षै, खन्, ग्लै, जै.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=098-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

