गम्भीर|गंभीर|गम्भीरं|गम्भीरः<BR>गम्भीर profundus, transl. ad sonum N. 12.57. 21.4. RAGH. 1.36.<BR>(V. गभीर et cf. lith. gillybế, gelmế, gylế altitudo,<BR>profunditas, gillus profundus, liquidis m et l inter se<BR>mutatis, sicut in lat. fla-re = scr. ध्मा, gr. comp. 20.;<BR>slav. glûbok profundus, glûbina profunditas.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=102-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

