गर्ह्<BR>गर्ह् 1. 10. P. A. vituperare, maledicere, conviciari. MAN. 11.229.:<BR>दुष्कृतङ् कर्म गर्हति; H. 4.6.: {#nE 'nAN<BR>garhitum arhasi#}; RAM. III.59.23.: {#kasmAd ajAnantaN<BR>garhase#}; BR. 1.33.: नृशंसो गर्हितो बुद्धैः; HIT. 109.13.:<BR>विषमां हि दशाम् प्राप्य दैवङ् गर्हयते नरः.<BR>(Haec radix e ग्रह् sumere orta esse videtur, transposito<BR>ra in ar; quod ad significationem attinet, respicias<BR>lat. reprehendo. E. गर्ह् mutato र् in ल् ortum est गल्ह्<BR>q. v.)<BR>c. परि id. RAM. III.75.43.: तातन् न परिगर्हेऽहम्.<BR>c. वि id. R. Schl. II.17.10.: स्वात्मा ऽप्य् एनम् विगर्हते;<BR>MAN. 11.232.: कर्म विगर्हितम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गर्हा<BR>गर्हा f. (r. गर्ह् s. आ) vituperatio, reprehensio, objurgatio.<BR>MAH. 1.6056.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गल्<BR>गल् 1. P. 10. A. (श्रावे) defluere, delabi, decidere, excidere.<BR>RAGH. 19.22.: गलिताश्रुविन्दु; 16.58.: गलिताङ्गराग;<BR>BHAR. 1.89.: गलत्कुष्ठाभिभूत; HIT. 10.22.:<BR>गलितनखदन्त; RAGH. 7.10.: {#galantI kasyAScid<BR>AsId rasanA#}. - गलितवयस् elapsam juventutem<BR>habens, senex, decrepitus. RAGH. 3.70. (Primitiva<BR>hujus radicis significatio fluere esse videtur, quam ob<BR>rem germ. vet. QUALL scaturire, - quillu, qual, quullumês<BR>- huc traxerim, unde quella fons; cf. जल aqua.)<BR>c. आ praef. सम् id. MAH. 1.1409.: समागलितपादपः.<BR>c. निस् id. RAGH. 5.17.: {#nirgalitAmbugarBaM SaradmeGan nA<BR>'rdati cAtako 'pi#}.<BR>c. वि id. ĆAUR. 28.: विगलदश्रुजलाकुलाक्षी; UR. 62.10.;<BR>RAGH. 9.67.: रतिविगलितबन्धः केशपाशः; GITA-GOV. I.3.31.:<BR>विगलितलज्जित.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गल|गलः<BR>गल m. collum. H. 2.4. (Fortasse a r. गॄ, e गर्, devorare,<BR>mutato र् in ल्, v. Wils. et cf. गल्ल, cui formâ respondere<BR>vldetur lat. collum, mutatâ mediâ in tenuem; germ.<BR>Hals, cujus initialis aspirata nititur lat. collum, gr. comp. 87.;<BR>cf. etiam lat. gula et nostrum Kehle.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गलहस्त|गलहस्तः<BR>गलहस्त m. (e गल et हस्त manus) actio collum torquendi. [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-b" target="_blank">Page103-b+ 36</a>]<BR>UP. 66.: अनिच्छन् गलहस्तेन ताभिर् निर्वासितस् ततः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गल्भ्<BR>गल्भ् 1. A. (आधार्ष्ट्ये K. धृष्टत्वे V.) fortem, audacem, strenuum<BR>esse. (Hib. galbha «rigour, hardness».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गल्ल|गल्लः<BR>गल्ल m. gena. HEM., v. गल.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गल्ह्<BR>गल्ह् 1. A. i. q. गर्ह् unde ortum est mutato र् in ल्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गवय|गवयः<BR>गवय m. (ut videtur, a गो s. अय) bovis species «the Gayal».<BR>DR. 4.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गवाक्ष|गवाक्षः<BR>गवाक्ष m. (bovis oculus, e TATP. गो et अक्ष) fenestra<BR>rotunda. RAGH. 7.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=103-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

