गान्धर्व|गांधर्व|गान्धर्व्वं|गान्धर्व्वः<BR>गान्धर्व (a गन्धर्व s. अ)<BR>1) Adj. gandharvicus. IN. 3.10.<BR>2) n. ars, scientia gandharvica. A. 4.58.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=104-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

