गिरि|गिरिः<BR>गिरि m. mons. H. 2.30. (गिरि ortum est e गरि, mutato अ<BR>in इ, per vim assimilationis इ finalis, sicut गुरु, q. v., e<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=105-a" target="_blank">Page105-a+ 36</a>]<BR>गरु; cf. zend. 𐬔𐬀𐬌𐬭𐬌 gairi, quod ex 𐬔𐬀𐬭𐬌 gari,<BR>unde gen. 𐬔𐬀𐬭𐬋𐬌𐬱 garôis, abl. 𐬔𐬀𐬭𐬋𐬌𐬝 garôiṭ,<BR>v. gr. comp. 41. 180.; slav. gora; fortasse etiam gr.<BR>ὄϱος e γόϱος.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=104-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

