गिरिश|गिरिशः<BR>गिरिश m. (in monte dormiens, vel jacens, e गिरि et श<BR>pro शय, a r. शी, v. Wils. et cf. केश. Posset tamen गिरिश<BR>etiam e गिरीश q. v. explicari, correpto ई) cognomen<BR>dei Sivi. RAGH. 2.41.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=105-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

