गुण्ठ्|गुंठ्<BR>गुण्ठ् 10. P. (scribitur गुठ्, gr. 110^a).) tegere. N. 10.6.<BR>DR. 9.13.; cf. गुड्, गुण्ड्, गुह् et boruss. vet. pokuntu<BR>custodio, protego, kuns-t custodire; fortasse lat.<BR>cus-tos e cut-tos vel cud-tos (gr. comp. 99.); v. {#guRq,<BR>guD, guh#}.<BR>c. अव id. MAN. 4.49.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=105-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

