गुध्<BR>2. गुध् 4. P. (परिवेष्टने K. वेष्टे V.) tegere, cf. {#guRW, guRq,<BR>guh, Cad#}; gr. ϰεύϑω, nostrum Haut, germ. vet.<BR>hût, Th. hûti, anglo-sax. hyde, hyd; lat. cutis, nisi pertinet<BR>ad कृत्ति, litterâ t melius convenit cum कुण्ठ् q. v.;<BR>germ. vet. cozo lacerna, umbi-chuzî amictus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=106-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

