गुल्म|गुल्मं|गुल्मः<BR>गुल्म m. frutex. H. 1.12. N. 13.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=106-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गुह्<BR>गुह् 1. P. A. (haec radix in formis, quae Gunam postulant,<BR>vocalem उ producit, e. c. गूहति, गूहते, जुगूह, pro<BR>गोहति etc.) tegere, abscondere. MAN. 7.105.: {#gUhet<BR>kUrma ivA 'NgAni#}. Part. pass. गूढ, gr. 102^a). IN. 5.12.:<BR>गूढगुल्फधर, N. 22.15.: गूढ occultus. (गुह् ortum est<BR>ex idem valente गुध्, relictâ solâ aspiratione litterae ध्,<BR>v. gr. comp. 23. Cum गुध् cognatum est गुण्ठ् et gr.<BR>ϰεύϑω, mutatâ mediâ in aspiratam; de ϑ pro ध् v. gr.<BR>comp. 16. Huc etiam trahi possit gr. δύω, lat. en-duo,<BR>mutatâ gutturali mediâ in lingualem, sicut in Δημήτηϱ<BR>pro Γημήηϱ, δῆμος pro γῆμος, v. जन; διδάσϰω pro<BR>γιγάσϰω, v. ज्ञा.<BR>c. उप amplecti. RAGH. 18.46.: तम्…उपजुगूह लक्ष्मीः;<BR>R. Schl. I.26.9.: अयोध्याम् उपगूहते सरःप्रवृत्ता सरयूः;<BR>RAGH. 6.13.: कराभ्याम् उपगूढनालम्…भ्रमयाञ्चकार;<BR>SA. 5.70.<BR>c. उप praef. सम् id. ĆAUR. 6.: अङ्गैर् अहं समुपगुह्य.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-a" target="_blank">Page107-a+ 35</a>]<BR>c. नि i. q. simpl. R. Schl. II.9.6.: {#kin na smarasi kEkeyi<BR>smarantI vA nigUhase#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=106-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गुह|गुहः<BR>गुह m. (r. गुह् s. अ) cognomen Kârtikêyi. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गुहा<BR>गुहा f. (r. गुह् s. आ) caverna, spelunca.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

