गृध्<BR>गृध् 4. P. desiderare, appetere. Yajurv. ap. Carey gr.<BR>p. 309.: मा गृधः कस्यचिद् धनम्; गृद्ध desideratus.<BR>MAH. 1.2642. (गृध् e गर्ध्, v. ऋ; huc trahimus<BR>germ. vet. gir, kir cupido, nostrum Gier, servatâ primitivâ<BR>mediâ, gr. comp. 92., et abjecto ध् finali; fortasse<BR>etiam angl. greedy ad hanc radicem pertinet; goth. grêdags<BR>famelicus, gaurs moestus; hib. greadaim «I burn»,<BR>greadhnach «joyful, glad», gradh m. «love, charity, Adj.<BR>dear, affectionate», graidheog «a beloved female», graidheoir<BR>«a lover», gradhuighim amo; lith. godùs avidus,<BR>ejecto r; v. Ruhig s. v. gierig; gedù lugeo, moereo;<BR>slav. glad fames, cf. कांक्ष् desiderare, unde nostrum<BR>Hunger; sl. schelajû cupio; v. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृध्नु|गृध्नुः<BR>गृध्नु (r. गृध् s. नु) avidus, desiderio incensus. (Goth.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">Page107-b+ 37</a>]<BR>gairns, Th. gairna, cupidus, quod suffixum na exhibet<BR>pro नु; gairnja desidero; lith. godùs avidus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृध्र|गृध्रः<BR>गृध्र (r. गृध् s. र)<BR>1) i. q. praec.<BR>2) m. vultur. DR. 8.31.<BR>(Germ. vet. gîr id., nostrum Geier.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृष्टि|गृष्टिः<BR>गृष्टि f. vacca, quae semel vitulum peperit. RAGH. 2.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृह्<BR>गृह् 10. A. i. q. ग्रह्, unde ortum est correpto र in ऋ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृह|गृहं<BR>गृह m. (r. ग्रह् s. अ)<BR>1) domus. SU. 1.32.<BR>2) plur. uxor.<BR>AM.; cf. दार. (गृह e ग्रह (v. ऋ), quo fortasse nititur<BR>nostrum Kirche, germ. vet. kiricha, island. kyrkia, anglo-sax.<BR>ciric, inserto i, pro circ; v. Graff III.481.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृहमेधिन्<BR>गृहमेधिन् m. (e गृह et मेधिन् intelligens) pater familias.<BR>DR. 5.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृहस्थ|गृहस्थः<BR>गृहस्थ m. (e गृह et स्थ stans) pater familias.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृहिन्<BR>गृहिन् m. (a गृह s. इन्) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृहिणी<BR>गृहिणी f. (a praec. signo fem. ई)<BR>1) hera, mater familias.<BR>HIT. 110.22.<BR>2) uxor. RAGH. 2.24. 8.66.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृहीत|गृहीतं<BR>गृहीत v. ग्रह्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गृहीतास्त्र<BR>गृहीतास्त्र Adj. (BAH. e praec. et अस्त्र telum) capta arma<BR>habens, qui arma cepit, accepit. IN. 3.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गॄ<BR>1. गॄ 6. P. गिरामि, et, mutato र् in ल्, गिलामि, gr. 334.<BR>(proprie गर् - v. ऋ - unde गिरामि, attenuato अ in<BR>इ, et mutato र् in ल्: गिलामि; गिरामि cum praet. redupl.<BR>जगर s. जगार eandem rationem habet ac praesent.<BR>goth. ut lisa cum praet. ut las, gr. comp. 109^a).1.; part.<BR>pass. गीर्ण, v. gr. 609.) deglutire. (Lith. gérrù bibo,<BR>praet. gếrau, girtoju perpoto; lat. glu-tio, gula, v. गल,<BR>gurgulio per reduplic. pro gurgurio, voro, ut videtur, e<BR>guoro, v. कृमि; slav. gr-lo guttur, russ. жòра schòra<BR>homo edax, abdomini natus; cf. Pott. p. 227.)<BR>c. नि id. MAH. 1.8239.: {#tasya pUva Siro grastam pucCam<BR>asya nigIryate#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गॄ<BR>2. गॄ 9. P. गृणामि (gr. 334.) sonare, mussare. BH. 11.21.:<BR>केचिद् भीताः प्राञ्जलयो गृणन्ति; RAGH. 10.64.:<BR>ब्रह्मर्षिभिः परम् ब्रह्म गृणद्भिर् उपतस्थिरे. In dial.<BR>vêd. laudare, celebrare. RIGV. Ros. 21.2.: {#gfRanti vipra<BR>te DiyaH#} «canunt, sapiens! tua facinora». Schol. {#tvadIyAni<BR>karmARi kaTayAnte#}. (V. गिर् et cf. hib. goirim<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-a" target="_blank">Page108-a+ 37</a>]<BR>(*) clamo; gr. γηϱύω, γλῶσσα, zacon. γϱοῦσσα, v.<BR>«Vocalismus» p. 173. Huc etiam germ. vet. QUAR gemere,<BR>quir, quar, quâr; boruss. vet. gerbu dico, loquor,<BR>trahi possent, adjecto b; ita lat. verbum e guerbum, sicut<BR>vivo e guivo = जीव्; etiam nostrum Wor-t, goth.<BR>vaur-ds abjectâ gutturali ad r. गर् reduci possint. Cum<BR>formâ गिलामि e गलामि conferatur anglo-sax. gale<BR>cano, nostrum gal in Nachtigal, germ. vet. nahti-gala<BR>luscinia; lat. gallus, a canendo dictus, sicut goth. hana,<BR>nostrum Hahn convenit cum lat. cano, et lith. gaidys id.<BR>cum giédmi cano. Sed liquida l vocum laudatarum etiam<BR>a द् radicis गद् deduci posset, sicut lith. gaidys gallus<BR>apud Lettos sonat gailis. Ita etiam scr. गॄ, i. e. गर्, cum<BR>गद् cohaerere videtur. Lat. gallus etiam ad गर्ज् referri<BR>potest. In dialecto vêd. etiam जॄ cl. 1. A. pro गॄ 9. P. invenitur,<BR>quum gutturales facile in palatales transeant; v. RIGV. Ros. p. 2.)<BR>c. अभि in dial. vêd. affari, alloqui, laudare, celebrare.<BR>RIGV. Ros. p. 14.4.: एहि स्तोमां (**) {#aBisvarA 'BigfRIhy<BR>Aruva#} «Veni, hymnos comproba, affare, alloquere»;<BR>95.14.: सा नः स्तोमां अभिगृणीहि «Tu nostras<BR>preces comproba».<BR>c. उत् effari, enuntiare. RAGH. 14.53.: {#mahIpateH SAsanam<BR>ujjagAra#}.<BR>(*) goirim nititur formâ primitivâ garâmi mutato a in<BR>o et inserto i ex vi attractionis i sequentis, v. librum meum<BR>„Die Celtischen Sprachen” p. 11.<BR>(**) De scriptione stômâṅ pro stômân v. Ros. p. IV.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=107-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गेप्<BR>गेप् 1. A. (गतिचालयोः K. गत्याञ् चाले V.) ire, se movere.<BR>(Cf. गा, unde गेप् ortum esse videtur adjecto<BR>प्, sicut in formis caus., et anomale mutato आ in ए.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गेय|गेयं|गेयः<BR>गेय n. (r. गै canere, s. य, v. gr. 626.) cantus. IN. 5.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गेव्<BR>गेव् 1. A. (सेवने) venerari, colere. (Cf. केव्, ग्लेव् et<BR>सेव्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गेष्<BR>गेष् 1. A. (अन्वेषायाम् K. अन्वेषे V.) quaerere. (Cf.<BR>गवेष्, unde fortasse गेष् ejecto अव्, nisi गेष् e गो,<BR>correpto ओ in अ, et इष् desiderare.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गेह|गेहं<BR>गेह n. domus, habitatio. N. 17.16. BH. 6.41. (Cf. गृह,<BR>quod ipsum e गर्ह (v. ऋ), unde गेह ejecto र् et mutato<BR>अ in ए ortum esse videtur; respicias formas prâcritas<BR>ut गेह्णदु pro गृह्णातु, et v. Höfer p. 35.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गेहिन्<BR>गेहिन् m. (a गेह s. इन्) i. q. गृहिन्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गेहिनी<BR>गेहिनी f. (a praec. signo fem. ई) uxor. RAGH. 8.72.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गै<BR>गै 1. P. A. canere. IN. 2.28.: गाथा गायन्ति; N. 15.15.; SU. 1.32.:<BR>पीयताङ् गीयताञ्च, v. gr. 501.; गीत n. cantus.<BR>IN. 3.6. (Cf. कै; fortasse lith. źáidziu «ich spiele<BR>scherzend oder auf Saitenspielen», praet. źaidau, adjecto<BR>d, v. gr. comp. 109^b).<BR>1); de ź pro g v. s. v. गण्ड;<BR>de giedmi cano v. गद्.)<BR>c. अधि decantare, recitare. MAN. 1.59.: {#etad Di matto<BR>'Dijage#}.<BR>c. अनु cantum alicujus sequi. GITA-GOV. 1.8.<BR>c. अभि i. q. simpl. RAM. I.4.77.: रामायणम् अभ्यगायताम्.<BR>c. उत् id. RAGH. 2.12.: {#SuSrAva kuYjezu yaSaH svam<BR>uccEr udgIyamAnam#}.<BR>c. उप id. RAGH. 10.22.: {#saptasAmopagItan tvAm…<BR>AcAKyuH#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गैरिक|गैरिकं<BR>गैरिक n. (a गिरि s. क vel इक) aurum. RAGH. 5.72.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गो<BR>गो (nom. गौस्, fortasse a r. गा)<BR>1) m. f. bos masc. et fem.,<BR>taurus, vacca.<BR>2) f. terra. RAGH. 1.26.; locus, spatium,<BR>sedes. SA. 3.6.<BR>3) m. coelum.<BR>4) m. luminis radius. R. Schl. I.7.18.:<BR>तेजोमयैर् गोभिर् इवो ऽदितो ऽर्कः.<BR>5) f. oculus.<BR>6) f. oratio, sermo. RAGH. 5.12.: {#raGor<BR>udArAm api gAn niSamya#}. (Cum गो bos, vacca, cf.<BR>gr. ΓΑ τοῦ ΓΑ-ΛΑΚΤ, quod primitive lac vaccinum<BR>significaverit, et cujus pars posterior convenit cum lat.<BR>LACT et, nisi fallor, cum scr. दुग्ध pro दुक्त, mutato dʽ<BR>in l; βοῦς, mutatâ gutturali in labialem; lat. bos, bovis,<BR>gr. comp. 123.; germ. vet. chuo, Th. et genit. chuoi,<BR>quod adjecto i propius accedit ad गव्य, unde explicari<BR>possit, ita ut अ finale abjectum et chuoi per metathesin e<BR>chowi ortum sit; angl. cow, nostrum Kuh; lett. gohw<BR>(= gôw) vacca; lith. werʃzin-ga vacca praegnans, cujus<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">Page109-a+ 36</a>]<BR>pars prior accus. est vocis werʃzis vitulus, cf. वृष taurus;<BR>slav. govjado pecus bubulum. Cum गो terra cf.<BR>gr. γαῖα, γῆ et goth. gavi, Th. gauja, e gavja, regio (nostrum<BR>Gau), quod formâ accuratissime cum derivato<BR>गव्य q. v. convenit, ad cujus femininum gr. γαῖα traxerim,<BR>ita ut hoc ortum sit e γαϜια ejecto Ϝ.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=108-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गोकुल|गोकुलं<BR>गोकुल n. (e गो et कुल familia, genus) boum grex. R. Schl. I.9.61.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गोचर|गोचरः<BR>गोचर m. (e गो et चर iens) quod sensibus percipitur, ut<BR>sonus, forma etc. BH. 13.5.: वाणगोचर teli jactus, quae<BR>sagittâ attingi potest distantia. DR. 8.28.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गोत्र|गोत्रं|गोत्रः<BR>गोत्र n. (e गो et त्र servans, tuens, a त्रा vel त्रै s. अ, cf. तनुत्र)<BR>1) familia. HIT. 8.3.<BR>2) nomen, appellatio. RAGH. 19.24.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गोत्रभिद्<BR>गोत्रभिद् m. (e praec. et भिद् findens) cognomen Indri.<BR>RAGH. 6.73.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गोदा<BR>गोदा f. (e गो et द dans in fem.) Gôdâvarî flumen. RAGH. 13.35.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गोदावरी<BR>गोदावरी f. (e praec. et वरी; fem. τοῦ वर) id. RAGH. 13.33.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गोधा<BR>गोधा f. (r. गुध् s. अ in fem.) tegmen scorteum, quod sagittarii<BR>in brachio laevo gerunt, ne arcûs nervo laedatur.<BR>R. Schl. I.24.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

