गोपाय्<BR>गोपाय् (Denominativum a praec. s. य्, v. gr. 585.) custodire.<BR>N. 18.8. 22.25. (*)<BR>(*) Forsterus gôpây radicibus primitivis adscribit; Wilkinsius,<BR>in libro suo, The Radicals etc. perperam deducit<BR>gôpâyâmi a gup cl. 4. quod gôpâmi, gôpasi etc. formare<BR>debet.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

