गोष्पद|गोष्पदं<BR>गोष्पद n. (e गो et पद, adjectâ sibilante, quam ex nominativi<BR>signo explicaverim, ita ut गौस् correptum sit in<BR>गोस्, mutato स् in ष्, propter antecedens ओ, v. gr. 79.)<BR>vaccae vestigium. MAH. 1.1444.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गौर|गौरं|गौरः<BR>गौर (fem. -रा et -री, fortasse a गो s. र) flavus. RAGH. 2.35.:<BR>गौरम् वृषम्; Lass. 65.6.: कनकगौर. (Huc traxerim<BR>lat. gil-vus cum l pro r, ejecto u diphthongi âu, et<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=110-a" target="_blank">Page110-a+ 36</a>]<BR>attenuato â in i; lith. geltônas gilvus, gielế icterus; russ.<BR>жилшый schiltyĭ, nostrum gelb; de nostro Gold v.<BR>ज्वलितः lat. aurum fortasse e gaurum mutilatum est,<BR>sicut amo e camo, ars e cars.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=109-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

गौरी<BR>गौरी f. (a गौर signo fem.)<BR>1) puella octo annos nata. AM.;<BR>etiam quaevis puella adhuc libera a menstruis.<BR>2) cognomen<BR>Pârvatiae. RAGH. 2.26. (Fortasse angl. girl, quasi<BR>गौरिला.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=110-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

