ग्लह्<BR>ग्लह् 1. A. i. q. ग्रह्, unde ortum est mutato r in l. (Hib.<BR>glacaim «I accept, receive, take, seize, feel, apprehend».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=112-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

