ग्लानि|ग्लानिः<BR>ग्लानि f. (a r. ग्लै s. नि pro ति, gr. 645.)<BR>1) fatigatio, lassitudo,<BR>languor. SA. 5.27. BH. 4.7.<BR>2) tristitia. BHAR. 1.45.:<BR>मुदञ्च ग्लानिञ्च कथयति पथिषु.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=112-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ग्लास्नु|ग्लास्नुः<BR>ग्लास्नु (r. ग्लै s. स्नु, fem. स्नु) fessus, defessus, lassus, fatigatus.<BR>AM. (Cf. lat. lassus, quod fortasse e glassus, sicut<BR>natus e gnatus; glassus vero per assimilationem ortum<BR>esse potest e glasnus, quod sanscrite ग्लस्नस् sonaret.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=112-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

