ग्लेव्<BR>ग्लेव् 1. A. (सेवने) colere, venerari; cf. {#gev, kev,<BR>Kev, sev#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ग्लेष्<BR>ग्लेष् 1. A. i. q. गेष् et गवेष् q. v.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ग्लै<BR>ग्लै 1. P. (part. pass. ग्लान, gr. 611.)<BR>1) fatigare, defatigare.<BR>2) contristare, dolore afficere. Pass. ग्लाये.<BR>SA. 3.23.: सावित्र्या ग्लायमानायास् तिष्ठन्त्याश्च दिवानिशम्.<BR>— Caus. ग्लापयामि et ग्लपयामि (gr. 519. 520.)<BR>facere ut alqs defatigetur, contristetur. RAGH. 16.38.:<BR>निदाघग्लपिताम् इवो ऽर्वीम्. (V. ग्लानि, ग्लास्नु<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-b" target="_blank">Page113-b+ 9</a>]<BR>et cf. lat. lâbor quod a fatigatione nominatum esse<BR>potest et formâ cum Caus. ग्लापयामि convenit, mutatâ<BR>tenui in mediam et abjectâ initiali gutturali, sicut in lassus,<BR>si hoc cum ग्लास्नु q. v. cohaeret.)<BR>c. परि i. q. simpl. परिग्लान languore confectus, exhaustus.<BR>N. 11.25.: श्रान्तस्य ते क्षुधार्तस्य परिग्लानस्य.<BR>c. परि praef. अभि id. MAH. 1.4489.: क्षुच्छ्रमाभिपरिग्लान.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ग्लौ<BR>ग्लौ m. luna.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घंष्<BR>घंष् 1. A. (क्षरे, scribitur घष्) stillare, effundere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घंस्<BR>घंस् 1. A. (क्षरणे, scribitur घस्, gr. 110^a).) id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घग्घ्<BR>घग्घ् 1. P. (हसने) ridere; cf. idem valentes formas {#gagG,<BR>kaK, kakK, KakK, kakk#} et lat. cachinnari,<BR>gr. ϰαχάζω, ϰαγχάζω, goth. hlaha, v. खक्ख्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घट्<BR>घट् 1. A. (चेष्टायाम् K. चेष्टे V.)<BR>1) ire, pervenire. Lass. 18.8.:<BR>{#yadi mama haste pustakI'yaN Gawati (Gawate?)<BR>tadA 'han tAm priyAY jIvApayAmi#}; c. ablat. exire.<BR>Lass. 36.7.: तेन हस्ताद् घटितो रथो दर्शितः.<BR>2) conjungere,<BR>conglutinare. UR. 49.9.infr.: {#vajralepaGawitam<BR>iva me hastayugalan na samarTA 'ham apanetum#}.<BR>3) facere, conficere. ĆAUR. 22.: स्नेहैकपात्रघटिताम् अवनीशपुत्रीम्<BR>(Schol. editionis Serampur. घटिताम् explicat<BR>per निर्मिताम्).<BR>c. उत् 10. P. (उद्घाटयामि)<BR>1) aperire. BHAR. 1.62.:<BR>निरयनगरद्वारम् उद्घाटयन्ती; MAH. 1.4504.: {#udGAwanIyAny<BR>etAni kuRqAni#}; UP. 78.: {#sadasy udGAwitA<BR>tatra maYjuzA#}.<BR>2) erigere, levare, sublevare (v.<BR>उद्घाटिन् et apud Wils. उद्घाटन, उद्घाटित. उद्घाटिन्<BR>fortasse non ab उद्घट् sed a substantivo उद्घाट<BR>elevatio descendit). HIT. 109.11.: कार्यम् उद्घाटितम्.<BR>c. वि 1. A. dissolvi, perire. HIT. 109.11.: {#kAryam udGAwitaN<BR>kvA 'pi maDye viGawate yataH#} (Ed. Ser. कार्यं<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1b" target="_blank">Page113-1b+ 24</a>]<BR>सुघटितङ् क्वा ऽपि दैवयोगाद् विनश्यति). MR. 66.4.infr.:<BR>चारुदत्तस्य विभवे विघटिते.<BR>c. सम् excitare. RAM. III.55.26.: {#BerImfdANgavIRAnAN<BR>koRasaNGawitaH…SabdaH#}; v. घट्ट् praef. वि.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

