घटना<BR>घटना f. (r. घट् s. अन in fem.) caterva elephantorum<BR>bellicorum. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घट्ट्<BR>घट्ट् 1. A. 10. P. (चलने K. चाले V.) movere, commovere,<BR>वीणाम् विघट्टितुम् lyram pulsare. MR. 20.3.<BR>Cf. घट्.<BR>c. वि<BR>1) movere, commovere. BHAR. 3.36.: वायुविघट्टिताभ्रपटली.<BR>2) aperire. MAH. 2.1674.: {#dvAram…<BR>viGawwayan karAByAm#}.<BR>c. सम् terere, conterere, fricare. RAGH. 6.73.: {#saNGawwayann<BR>aNgadam aNgadena#} (Schol. घर्षयन्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घट्टन|घट्टनं<BR>घट्टन n. (r. घट्ट् s. अन) tactio, ictus. RAGH. 11.71.:<BR>सुप्तसर्प इव दण्डघट्टनाद् रोषितोऽस्मि (Schol.<BR>संयोगात्); v. घाट.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

