घण्ट्|घंट्<BR>घण्ट् 10. P. (भाषार्थे K. द्युतौ V.; scribitur घट्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>loqui, splendere; v. घण्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=113-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

