घातय्<BR>घातय् forma caus. r. हन्, gr. 524. 4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=114-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

