घास|घासः<BR>घास m. (r. घस् s. अ) gramen. AM. (Germ. vet. wisa pratum,<BR>nostrum Wiese, v. कृमि et Graff. I.1977.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=114-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

