घुर्<BR>1. घुर् 6. P. (भीमार्तिशब्दे K. ध्वनौ भीमार्थे V.) prae timore,<BR>terrore clamare. (Goth. gaurs tristis, gaurida<BR>tristitia; v. घोर.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=114-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

