घृण्ण्<BR>घृण्ण् 1. A. घृण्णे (ग्रहणे; scribitur घृण्; gr. 110^a).) capere,<BR>prehendere; cf. ग्रह्, गृह्णामि.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घृत|घृतः<BR>घृत n. (r. घृ s. त) butyrum liquefactum. BHAR. 1.65. 3.97.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घृताची<BR>घृताची f. (e घृत et अची a r. अञ्च् s. अ, in fem.) n. pr.<BR>Apsarasis. IN. 2.29.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घृष्<BR>घृष् 1. P. fricare, terere, conterere. ĆAUR. 12.: कनककुण्डलघृष्टगण्ड;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">Page115-b+ 37</a>]<BR>MR. 140.9.infr.: घृष्यन्ते वैदूर्याः;<BR>7.infr.: घृष्यते चन्दनरसः. (Huc referri posset lat.<BR>verro pro guerro, nisi pertinet ad कृष्; v. hanc radicem<BR>et vocem घृष्टि, cui verres respondet.)<BR>c. उत् id. RAGH. 17.28.: चूडामणिभिर् उद्घृष्टपादपीठ.<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) i. q. simpl. सङ्घृष्यत् contritus (v. gr. 597.).<BR>MAH. 1.1134.: {#saNGfzyantaH parasparam nyapatan…parvatAgrAn<BR>mahAdrumAH#}.<BR>2) certare, aemulari. RAGH. 19.36.:<BR>प्रयोक्तृभिः सञ्जघर्ष सह (Schol. सङ्घर्षः पराभिभवेषा).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घृष्टि|घृष्टिः<BR>घृष्टि (r. घृष् s. ति) Fem.<BR>1) frictio, tritus.<BR>2) aemulatio,<BR>certatio. Masc. porcus, sus. (Lat. verres e guerres pro<BR>guerses, sicut vivo pro guivo = जीव्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घोटक|घोटकः<BR>घोटक m. equus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घोणा<BR>घोणा f. (ut videtur, a r. घ्रा s. अना, ejecto र् et mutato आ<BR>in ओ, sicut in सोढुम्, षोडश, v. gr. 468. 40. et cf.<BR>prâcr. घाण pro scr. घ्राण) nasus. DR. 7.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घोणिन्<BR>घोणिन् (a praec. s. इन्) porcus, sus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घोर|घोरं|घोरः<BR>घोर (r. घुर् s. अ) terribilis, terrificus, atrox. IN. 5.62. H. 1.17.<BR>BR. 1.3. (Goth. gaurs, Th. gaura tristis, nisi pertinet<BR>ad गृध्; hib. gorg «fierce, cruel».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घोरदर्शन|घोरदर्शनः<BR>घोरदर्शन (BAH. e praec. et दर्शन n. visus, conspectus)<BR>terribilem speciem habens, terribilis visu. H. 2.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घोष|घोषं|घोषः<BR>घोष m. (r. घुष् s. अ)<BR>1) proclamatio, pronuntiatio. MAH. 1.5333.:<BR>सुखपुण्याहघोष.<BR>2) sonus, strepitus. N. 2.11. 19.25. 21.2.<BR>DR. 6.7.<BR>3) pastoralis sedes. N. 17.49.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घोषणा<BR>घोषणा f. (r. घुष् s. अन in fem.) proclamatio. AM.; RAGH. 12.72.:<BR>जयघोषण.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घ्न<BR>घ्न (f. घ्नी, r. हन् s. अ, v. gr. 645.) occidens, in fine compp.<BR>N. 12.18. 13.28.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घ्रा<BR>घ्रा 1. P. जिघ्रामि (proprie cl. 3. correpto आ in अ, et in<BR>syllabâ redupl. attenuato अ in इ, ob duas sequentes consonantes,<BR>sicut in तिष्ठामि pro तस्थामि, a r. स्था) odorari.<BR>RAM. I.12.42.: धूमगन्धङ् जिघ्रति; HIT.: {#jiGrann<BR>api BujaNgamo hanti#}. (Pottius ingeniose confert lat.<BR>fra-gra-re, ita ut fra sit syllaba reduplicativa pro ghra;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-a" target="_blank">Page116-a+ 8</a>]<BR>hib. gros «a snout»; nisi hoc pertinet ad ग्रस्; fortasse<BR>nostrum riechen, cujus radix est ruch, germ. vet. riuhu,<BR>rouh, ruhumês, litteris transpositis ortum est e HRU, attenuato<BR>â in u; huc etiam traxerim lith. kwếpju oleo,<BR>kwápas odor, quae conveniunt cum formâ caus. घ्रापयामि,<BR>cum k pro g et w pro r. Pottius apte confert gr. ἄϱω-μα,<BR>ita ut ad आघ्रा pertineat, ejectâ gutturali, sicut in<BR>ϱ̔ίς, ϱ̔ῑν-ός, quod cum घ्राण convenit.)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-b" target="_blank">Page116-b+ 7</a>]<BR>c. अव<BR>1) id. MAN. 3.218.: अवजिघ्रेच्च तान् पिण्डान्.<BR>2) osculari. R. Schl. II.20.21.: अवघ्रातश्च मूर्धनि.<BR>c. आ id. H. 2.8.: आघ्राय मानुषङ् गन्धम्.<BR>c. आ praef. उप osculari. IN. 2.21.: मूर्द्ध्निचै ऽनम् उपाघ्राय.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=115-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

घ्राण|घ्राणं<BR>घ्राण n. (r. घ्रा s. अन)<BR>1) odoratus, odoratio.<BR>2) nasus. H. 2.12.<BR>(Gr. ϱ̔ῑν, abjectâ gutturali, attenuato â in î.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ङु<BR>ङु 1. A. (ध्वनौ) sonare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

च्<BR>च् Haec littera orta est e क्, et in comparandis linguis cognatis<BR>non aliter accipienda est, ac si क् in ejus loco<BR>inveniretur; v. gr. comp. 14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

च|चः<BR>च Partic. enclit. (a stirpe interr. क, mutato क् in च्, v. gr.<BR>comp. 398.)<BR>1) et, que, saepissime; repetitum et - et, tum<BR>- quum. N. 24.50. 26.5.<BR>2) enim. N. 10.14.<BR>3) si. DR. 9.10.<BR>4) tamen. N. 21.32.<BR>5) vero, autem. N. 23.28.<BR>HIT. 43.10.<BR>6) expletive sive ad vim orationis augendam.<BR>H. 1.26. BR. 3.20. 22. — Cum sequente अपि<BR>1) et etiam.<BR>H. 2.24.<BR>2) vero, autem. DR. 8.52. BR. 2.26. — Cum<BR>sequente एव<BR>1) et etiam. BR. 2.26.; repetitum et-et,<BR>tum-quum. BR. 2.25.<BR>2) vero. H. 4.33. (Lat. que, gr.<BR>ϰε, τε (gr. comp. 401.); goth. uh, h, e. c. quêthunuh dixeruntque,<BR>hvazuh quisque, nih neque (Grimm III.23.);<BR>slav. же sche, gr. comp. 402.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्<BR>चक् 1. P. A. terrere. चकित territus, timens. BHAR. 3.10.:<BR>मरणोपायचकित; RAGH. 10.74.: पौलस्त्यचकितेश्वर<BR>(secundum K. दीप्तौ lucere); v. चक्क्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चकक्<BR>चकक् 10. P. (व्यसने K. आर्तौ V.) dolore afficere, vexare;<BR>v. चक्, चिक्क्, चुक्क्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चकास्<BR>चकास् 2. P. (दीप्तौ) splendere; v. कास्, unde reduplicatione<BR>oritur चकास्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चकोर|चकोरः<BR>चकोर m. (ut videtur, a r. कुर् sonare, cum syllabâ redupl.<BR>s. अ, sic etiam Lass.; cf. कुरर) perdix rufa. Lass. 52.20.<BR>(Lith. kurrapkà perdix.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्र|चक्रं|चक्रः<BR>चक्र m. (ut videtur, forma redupl. a r. क्रम् se movere, abjecto<BR>म्; secundum v. a r. कृ)<BR>1) rota. A. 9.8.<BR>2) orbis,<BR>circulus. Lass. 63.8.<BR>3) discus, telum missile circulare.<BR>IN. 1.5.<BR>4) regio, provincia.<BR>5) exercitus. (Ut videtur,<BR>gr. ϰύϰλος pro ϰύϰϱος, attenuato α in v.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्रधर|चक्रधरः<BR>चक्रधर m. (e praec. et धर tenens) cognomen Vischnûs.<BR>RAGH. 16.55.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्रपाणि|चक्रपाणिः<BR>चक्रपाणि m. (e चक्र et पाणि manus) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्रवर्तिन्|चक्रवर्त्तिन्<BR>चक्रवर्तिन् m. (e चक्र et वर्तिन्) rex supremus, terrae<BR>dominus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्रवाक|चक्रवाकः<BR>चक्रवाक m. (e चक्र et वाक sermo) anseris genus. Wils.<BR>«the ruddy goose or Brahmani goose, Anas casarea».<BR>N. 12.113.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्रवाल|चक्रवालं|चक्रवालः<BR>चक्रवाल m. (e चक्र et वाल, a r. वल् circumdare) horizon.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्रिन्<BR>चक्रिन् m. (a चक्र s. इन्) disco praeditus. BH. 11.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्ष्<BR>चक्ष् 2. A. (v. gr. 362.) dicere, loqui, narrare, indicare.<BR>(Hanc radicem equidem ad कास् splendere reduxerim,<BR>ejecto अ, sicut जक्ष् e घस् explicavimus. Quod ad<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-a" target="_blank">Page117-a+ 37</a>]<BR>significationem attinet, respiciatur, graecum ϕημί origine<BR>idem esse ac sanscritum भामि splendeo.)<BR>c. आ id. H. 4.28.: आचक्ष्व मान् तत् सर्वम्; N. 11.31.:<BR>सर्वम् एतत्…आचचक्षे ऽस्य; 16.39.: आचष्टे दमयन्त्याः;<BR>DR. 2.5.: आचक्ष्व बन्धूंश्च पतिङ् कुलञ्च.<BR>c. आ praef. प्रति repudiare. MAN. Schol. 4.250. ubi निर्णुदेत्<BR>explicatur per प्रत्याचक्षीत.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् i. q. आचक्ष्. DR. 4.5.: {#tAM samAcakzva<BR>yadi syAc CEvya mAnuzI#}.<BR>c. परि nominare. MAN. 2.171.: {#vedapradAnAd AcAryam<BR>pitaram paricakzate#}; BH. 17.13. 17.<BR>c. प्र<BR>1) dicere, profiteri, declarare. RAGH. 8.85.: {#svajanASru…dahati<BR>pretam iti pracakzate#}.<BR>2) nominare.<BR>MAN. 2.17.: तन् देवनिर्मितन् देशम् ब्रह्मावर्तम् प्रचक्षते.<BR>c. वि dicere. YAJURV. Carey 904.: ये नस् तद् विचचक्षिरे.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=116-2b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्षुष्मत्|चक्षुष्मन्त्<BR>चक्षुष्मत् (a चक्षुस् s. मत्, v. euph. r. 101^a).) oculos i. e.<BR>oculorum usum habens, videns. SA. 7.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्षुष्मत्ता<BR>चक्षुष्मत्ता f. (a praec. s. ता) Abstractum praecedentis, visus,<BR>videndi facultas. RAGH. 4.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्षुष्य|चक्षुष्यं|चक्षुष्यः<BR>चक्षुष्य (a चक्षुस् s. य) speciosus, pulcher, amoenus. (Hib.<BR>cais «agreeable, pleasant» v. चक्षुस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चक्षुस्<BR>चक्षुस् n. (r. चक्ष् s. उस्) oculus. IN. 4.1. N. 5.8. (Hib.<BR>cais oculus, abjectâ penultimâ gutturali radicis चक्ष्, quâ<BR>in re cum anomalis formis ut चष्टे dicit convenit, gr. 362.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चङ्कुर|चंकुर|चङ्कुरं|चंकुरः|चङ्कुरः<BR>चङ्कुर m. n. (ut mihi videtur, a forma intensiva r. चर् i. e.<BR>a चञ्चुर्, servatâ primitivâ radicis gutturali). (Cf. currus<BR>et v. चर्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चञ्च्|चंच्<BR>चञ्च् 1. P. vacillare, tremere. Lass. 4.20.: चञ्चच्चिताग्नितडित;<BR>GITA-GOV. 4.8.: रोदिति चञ्चति. (Cf. चर्<BR>et चल्, quorum Intensiva sonant चञ्चुर्, चञ्चल्, unde<BR>चञ्च् explicaverim abjecto उर् vel अल्; hib. ceangtha<BR>«they go, travel», ceangastair «walking, pacing»; fortasse<BR>lat. cunctari, a lento progressu dictum.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चञ्चत्क|चंचत्क<BR>चञ्चत्क (a चञ्चत् part. praes. radicis चञ्च् s. क) se movens,<BR>tremens.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

