चञ्चलत्व<BR>चञ्चलत्व n. (a praec. s. त्व) mobilitas. BH. 6.33.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चञ्चु|चंचु|चञ्चुः<BR>चञ्चु f. (ut mihi videtur, a चञ्चम्, Intens. radicis चम्<BR>edere, abjecto म्) rostrum. ĆAUR. 8. (Hib. caoinse<BR>«the face».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=117-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

