चतुःशाला<BR>चतुःशाला f. (e चतुर् et शाला) locus quadratus quatuor<BR>domibus inclusus. AM., v. चत्वर.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चतुर्<BR>1. चतुर् (in casibus fortibus चत्वार्, unde चतुर् ejecto<BR>आ; fem. चतसृ, gr. 255.) quatuor. (Cum nom.<BR>masc. चत्वारस् conferatur gr. πέσσαϱες, τέτταϱες,<BR>per assimilationem e τέτϜαϱες, sicut prâcr. चत्तारो e<BR>चत्वारो; aeol. πίσυϱες, mutatâ gutturali in labialem,<BR>quâ in re cum goth. fidvôr et cambro-brit. pedwar masc.,<BR>pédair fem. convenit; lat. quatuor, lith. keturi, slav.<BR>четыϱїе ćetyrje; hib. ceathair masc., ceteora fem. =<BR>चतस्रस्; v. gr. comp. 312., Pictet p. 145.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चतुर्<BR>2. चतुर् Adv. (pro चतुर्स्, unde per metathesin zend.<BR> 𐬗𐬀𐬚𐬭𐬎𐬱 ćathrus) quater. (Lat. quater.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चतुर|चतुरः<BR>चतुर<BR>1) aptus, idoneus; dexter, versutus, callidus. Lass. 20.17.<BR>RAGH. 9.47. 68. 18.14. UR. 48.11.<BR>2) pulcher.<BR>RAGH. 8.94.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चतुर्थ|चतुर्थः<BR>चतुर्थ (a चतुर् s. थ pro थम vel तम, v. gr. comp. 321.)<BR>quartus. (Lith. ketwirtas, slav. четвеϱтый ćetvertyĭ,<BR>fem. четвеϱтaѧ ćetverta-ja, gr. τέτ(Ϝ)αϱτος,<BR>lat. qua(tu)rtus, goth. fidvôrda, nisi fidurda, nostrum<BR>vierter.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

