चतुष्टय|चतुष्टयं<BR>चतुष्टय n. (a चतुर् s. तय, gr. 652. s. तय) quaternio,<BR>τετϱάς. HIT. 4.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चत्वर|चत्वरं<BR>चत्वर n. (ut mihi videtur, a चतुर् vel potius pleniore et<BR>primitivâ formâ चत्वार्, correpto आ, suff. अ) aulea.<BR>MR. 11.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

