चत्वारिंशत्<BR>चत्वारिंशत् (e चत्वारि nom. acc. neut. τοῦ चतुर् et<BR>शत्, quod ex दशत् a दशन् decem mutilatum esse censeo,<BR>insertâ nasali, v. gr. min. 229. not. 3.) quadraginta.<BR>(Lat. quadraginta pro quadra(de)cinta, gr. τεσσαϱά(δε)ϰοντα;<BR>v. gr. comp. 320. not.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

