चन्<BR>1. चन् 1. P. (हिंसायाम् K. हिंसे V.) laedere, ferire, occidere.<BR>(Cf. चण्, हन्; fortasse goth. han-dus<BR>manus, nostrum Hand huc pertinet.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्<BR>2. चन् 1. P. (शब्दे) sonare. (Cf. चण्, कण्, क्वन्, स्वन्,<BR>lat. cano, goth. hana gallus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन<BR>चन (ut mihi videtur, e stirpe interrogativa क, adjecto<BR>न). Particula enclitica, quae vocibus interrogativis adjuncta<BR>sensum interrogativum in indefinitum convertit.<BR>(Goth. hun, v. gr. comp. 398.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्|चंद्<BR>चन्द् 1. P. (आह्लादने दीप्तौ K. ह्लादे दीप्तौ V.; scribunt<BR>चद्, gr. 110^a).) exhilarare, lucere; v. चन्द, चन्द्.<BR>(Cf. कन् splendere et voces cum hac radice comparatas,<BR>quorum candeo, candela melius ad चन्द् referuntur;<BR>ad कन् autem reduxerim goth. skeina luceo, rad.<BR>SKIN, attenuato अ in i et praefixo s, sicut e. c. in stauta<BR>verbero, nostrum stosse = तुद्, tundo; cum चन्द् vel,<BR>quod ad idem redit, cum कन्, conferatur etiam bret.<BR>sked splendor; v. Pict. p. 43.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द|चंद|चंदः|चन्दः<BR>चन्द m. (r. चन्द् s. अ) luna. (V. tritiorem formam चन्द्र<BR>et cf. hib. cann «full moon» per assimilationem e cand,<BR>quod etiam e चन्द्र abjecto र् ortum esse potest.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=118-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्दन|चंदन|चंदनं|चन्दनं|चंदनः|चन्दनः<BR>चन्दन m. n. (r. चन्द् s. अन) santalum. IN. 5.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्र|चंद्र|चन्द्रं|चन्द्रः<BR>चन्द्र m. (r. चन्द् s. र) luna. SU. 2.25.; v. चन्द.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्रकान्त|चंद्रकांत|चन्द्रकान्तं|चन्द्रकान्तः<BR>चन्द्रकान्त (e praec. et कान्त splendens, a r. कम्)<BR>1) sicut<BR>luna splendens. BHAR. 1.20.<BR>2) m. gemma quaedam<BR>fabulosa, quae radiis lunae congelatis nasci creditur.<BR>Lass. 92.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्रचूड|चंद्रचूड|चन्द्रचूडः<BR>चन्द्रचूड m. (lunam in vertice gerens, BAH. e चन्द्र<BR>et चूडा vertex) cognomen Sivi. BHAR. 1.97.; v. चन्द्रशेखर.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्रमस्|चंद्रमस्<BR>चन्द्रमस् m. (e चन्द्र et मस् luna, quod simplex non invenitur<BR>et ex मास् correptum esse videtur) luna. N. 17.6.<BR>Lass. 60.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्रमौलि|चंद्रमौलि|चन्द्रमौलिः<BR>चन्द्रमौलि m. (BAH. e चन्द्र et मौलि q. v.) cognomen<BR>Sivi. RAGH. 6.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्रशाला|चंद्रशाला<BR>चन्द्रशाला f. (e चन्द्र et शाला) conclave in superiore domûs<BR>parte. RAGH. 13.43.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्रशेखर|चंद्रशेखर|चन्द्रशेखरः<BR>चन्द्रशेखर (BAH. e चन्द्र et शेखर) cognomen Sivi. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चन्द्रिका|चंद्रिका<BR>चन्द्रिका f. (a चन्द्र s. इक in fem.) lunae lumen. RAGH. 19.39.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चप्<BR>1. चप् 1. P. (सान्त्वने K. सान्त्वे V.) consolari, blandiri.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चप्<BR>2. चप् 1. P. se movere, vacillare; v. चपल et cf. {#cup,<BR>kamp#}; hib. tap «quick, swift», tapadh «haste, activity»;<BR>v. Pict. p. 41.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चप्<BR>3. चप् 10. P. चपयामि (कल्के) conterere. (Cum voce<BR>कल्क, quâ radix चप् a grammaticis explicatur, conferatur<BR>lat. calcare; v. चल्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चपल|चपलं|चपलः<BR>चपल (r. चप् s. अल)<BR>1) tremens, vacillans. M. 42. RAGH. 11.8.<BR>2) celer, citus, alacer. SAK. 56.3.infr.<BR>3) vagus,<BR>mobilis, levis, inconstans. HIT. 24.1. Cf. चम्प् et<BR>कम्प्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चपलता<BR>चपलता f. (a praec. s. ता) levitas, mobilitas animi. HIT. 49.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चम्<BR>चम् 1. 5. P. चमामि, चम्नोमि, part. pass. चान्त (अदने<BR>K. भक्षे V.) edere, vesci; v. चाम्य. (Cf. {#jam, Jam,<BR>jim#}; hib. toimhil «eatings» - v. Pictet p. 41. - toimhlim<BR>«I eat, waste, spend, consume».)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">Page119-b+ 36</a>]<BR>c. आ productâ vocali radicali in tempp. spec.<BR>1) os aquâ<BR>eluere. MAN. 2.51.: अश्नीयाद् आचम्य; 5.144.: {#AcAmed<BR>eva BuktvA#}; v. आचमनीय.<BR>2) se lavare, purificare<BR>in universum. MAN. 2.222. 3.217.: आचम्य; 5.143.:<BR>आचान्तः शुचिताम् इयात्. — Caus. आचामयामि;<BR>MAN. 5.142.: {#spfSanti vindavaH pAdO ya AcAmayataH<BR>parAn#} (Schol. {#anyezAm AcamanArTaY jalan<BR>dadato ye vindavo pAdO spfSanti#}.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चमर|चमरं|चमरः<BR>चमर (r. चम्?) bos grunniens. Wils.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चमस|चमसं|चमसः<BR>चमस m. (r. चम् s. अस) patera sacrificalis. R. Schl. I.32.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चमू<BR>चमू f. (ut videtur, a r. चम् s. ऊ)<BR>1) exercitus. RAGH. 4.30.<BR>2) pars exercitûs. MAH. 1.292.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चम्प्|चंप्<BR>चम्प् 1. P. ire, se movere; v. चपल et cf. चम्ब्, कम्प्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चम्पक|चंपक|चम्पकं|चंपकः|चम्पकः<BR>चम्पक m. arbor quaedam gilvis, fragrantibus floribus,<BR>Michelia Ćampaka. ĆAUR. 1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चम्ब्|चंब्<BR>चम्ब् 1. P. (गत्याम्) ire; cf. खम्ब्, गम्ब्, घम्ब्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चय्<BR>चय् 1. A. (गतौ) ire. (Cf. शै, श्यै, nec non चर्, cum semivocales<BR>facile inter se mutentur; gr. ϰίω, ϰινέω,<BR>lat. cieo, cio, citus; hib. cai «a way, a road»; lith. kòja<BR>pes, kettur-kójis quadrupes.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चय|चयः<BR>चय m. (r. चि colligere, s. अ) cumulus, multitudo. (Cambro-brit.<BR>cai collectio; hib. sceo «plenty, abundance».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चयन|चयनं<BR>चयन n. (r. चि colligere, s. अन) strues lignorum, rogus.<BR>DR. 2.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्<BR>1. चर् 1. P.<BR>1) ire, incedere, ambulare. N. 24.34.: {#ayaY<BR>carati loke 'smin BUtasAkzI sadAgatiH#}; 33.34.;<BR>SA. 5.74.b.: मृगाणाञ् चरताम् वने; IN. 1.23.: {#svargam<BR>prAptAS caranti sma devEH saha#}; ATM. ut videtur metri<BR>causâ, SA. 5.74.: नक्तञ्चराश् चरन्ते ते.<BR>2) permeare,<BR>peragrare. N. 19.32.: {#pracCannA hi mahAtmAnaS caranti<BR>pfTivIm imAm#}; 24.23.: {#dUtAS caranti pfTivIN<BR>kftsnAm#}; SU. 4.24.<BR>3) facere, agere, committere. BR. 2.31.:<BR>धर्मश्च चरितो मया; N. 24.31.: {#yaTA nA 'sat<BR>kftaN kiYcin manasA 'pi carAmy aham#}; BH. 3.36.:<BR>पापञ् चरति; मृगयाञ् चरितुम् venari. DR. 6.9. [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=120-a" target="_blank">Page120-a+ 37</a>]<BR>चरित n. actio, factum vitae ratio. N. 6.8. 23.2. 5. Intens.<BR>चञ्चुर्, चञ्चूर्य् (v. gr. 570.). MAH. 1.7910.: {#yAnES<BR>caYcUryante#} vehiculis invehuntur, ils vont en voiture,<BR>cf. चङ्कुर currus et चल्. (Lat. curro, currus, attenuato<BR>a in u, sicut in Intensivo चञ्चुर् et चङ्कुर currus;<BR>fortasse etiam pro-perus huc pertinet, mutatâ gutturali<BR>in labialem; hib. cara «a leg or haunch», carachadh<BR>«moving», carachd «motion, movement»; gr.<BR>ϰύϱω, ϰυϱέω; goth. fara proficiscor, nostrum fahre,<BR>mutatâ gutturali in labialem, sicut in fidvôr = चत्वारस्<BR>et fimf = पञ्चन्; germ. vet. hor-sc celer, anglo-sax.<BR>et angl. hor-s, hor-se equus; lith. kieláuju proficiscor,<BR>mutato r in l, sicut in scrto चल्, kiélias via,<BR>kielónế iter.)<BR>c. अति P. A. transgredi, peccare. N. 19.; c. acc. pers.<BR>quam peccando offendimus. DR. 5.21.: {#nA 'ticare kaTaYcit<BR>patIn mahArhAn manasA 'pi jAtu#}.<BR>c. अनु percurrere. RAM. I.46.20.: लोकान् अनुचरन्तु;<BR>III.64.50.: ते कीर्तिर् लोकान् अनुचरिष्यति. Caus.<BR>MAN. 9.266.: देशान् चारैः…अनुचारयेत्.<BR>c. अनु praef. सम् ambulare, migrare. MAH. 1.3606.: {#pfTivyAm<BR>anusaYcaranti#}.<BR>c. अभि<BR>1) adire, visitare, frequentare. R. Schl. 34.10.:<BR>मागधी…पूर्वाभिचरिता.<BR>2) offendere. MAN. 5.165.:<BR>पतिं या ना ऽभिचरति मनोवाग्देहसंयता (Schol. व्यभिचरति).<BR>c. अभि praef. वि id. sgnf. 2. MAH. 1.3234.: {#abrAhmaRaN<BR>kartum icCanti rOdrAs te mAM yaTA vyaBicaranti nityam#}.<BR>c. आ<BR>1) adire, frequentare. N. 15.19.: {#SvApadAcarite nityam<BR>vane#}.<BR>2) facere, agere, peragere, committere. N. 4.7.;<BR>विप्रियं ह्य् आचरन् मर्त्यो देवानाम्; UR. 7.15. 86.8.infr.<BR>BR. 2.4.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् id. sgnf. 2. MAN. 10.111.: {#iman DarmaM<BR>samAcaret#}; H. 2.29. BH. 3.9. 19.<BR>c. उत्<BR>1) provenire, praesertim de sono. RAGH. 9.73.: {#uccacAra<BR>ninado 'mBasi#}; 11.73.: राम इत्य् अयं शब्द<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=120-b" target="_blank">Page120-b+ 36</a>]<BR>उच्चरितः.<BR>2) alvum evacuare. MAN. 4.49.: उच्चरेत्<BR>(Schol. मूत्रपुरीषोत्सर्गङ् कुर्यात्).<BR>c. उत् praef. वि offendere, laedere, praesertim adulterio.<BR>MAH. 1.4732.: व्युच्चरन्त्याः पतिन् नार्याः; 4733.: {#BAryAN<BR>taTA vyuccarataH#}; ATM. 4720.: {#tAsAm vyuccAramARAnAm<BR>…patIn#}; v. चर् praef. अभि, व्यभि.<BR>c. उप ministrare, servire, curare. RAM. I.9.71.: {#svayam<BR>upacacArE 'nam#}; N. 21.30.: {#sa mocayitvA tAn aSvAn<BR>upacaryaca SAstrataH#}; SAK. 43.11.: यत्नाद् उपचर्यताम्;<BR>c. instr. rei RAGH. 14.17.: {#sugrIvaviBIzaRAdIn<BR>upAcarat kftrimasamviDABiH#}; MAH. 1.769.: {#na<BR>yuktam BavatA 'ham anfteno 'pacaritum#}. (*)<BR>c. निस् egredi. BH. 6.26.: निश्चरति मनः.<BR>c. परि circumgredi. N. 10.17.; reverentiae causâ. RAM. III.47.6.:<BR>लक्ष्मणश्चा ऽपि रामस्य पादौ परिचरन् वने.<BR>c. प्र<BR>1) progredi, proficisci, ambulare, migrare. RAM. I.2.42.:<BR>रामायणकथा लोकेषु प्रचरिष्यति.<BR>2) facere,<BR>agere, peragere. MAN. 10.100.: कर्मभिः प्रचरितैः.<BR>c. वि ambulare, migrare, peragrare. IN. 5.50.: {#zaRqavad<BR>vicarizyasi#}; H. 2.31. 4.32.; SU. 4.24.: {#AdityacaritA~<BR>llokAn vicarizyasi#}; MAN. 9.20.<BR>c. सम् id. Lass. 74.4.infr.: इतस्ततः सञ्चरत्; Caus.<BR>सञ्चारयामि commovere. RAGH. 6.8.: सञ्चारिते…धूपे.<BR>(*) Notatu dignissimus est supra laudatus locus propter<BR>passivam Infinitivi vim sine ullo verbo auxiliari, quo vulgo<BR>passiva forma, quae Infinitivo deest, suppletur, in sententiis<BR>ut jêtuṅ śakyatê.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=119-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्<BR>2. चर् 10. P.: comperire, certiorem fieri, erfahren. R. Schl. I.9.13.:<BR>चारयित्वा तु तम् ऋषिम् आश्रमाद् अभिनिर्गतम्.<BR>(Huc trahi posset lat. peritus, com-perio,<BR>ex-perior, mutatâ gutturali in labialem, nisi perio compositum<BR>est ex per et eo.)<BR>c. वि secum volvere, perpendere, cogitare, deliberare,<BR>considerare, dubitare, haesitare. N. 5.15.: {#sA viniScitya<BR>bahuDA vicAryaca punaH punaH#}; 19.35.: {#evam vicArya<BR>bahuSas#}; SA. 5.107.: मा विचारय non haesita. [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">Page121-a+ 36</a>]<BR>विचारित n. dubitatio, haesitatio. SA. 3.13.; v. अविचारितम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=120-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर|चरः<BR>चर (r. चर् s. अ)<BR>1) iens, mobilis, agens, in fine compp.<BR>et in initio compp. DVANDV. चराचर n. (चर + अचर)<BR>mobile et immobile. BH. 9.10. 10.39.<BR>2) m. explorator.<BR>HIT. 92.22.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चरण|चरणं|चरणः<BR>चरण n. (r. चर् s. अन, v. gr. 94^a).)<BR>1) actio, effectio, perfunctio.<BR>N. 12.77.<BR>2) pes. A. 9.8. (Huc traxerim gr.<BR>et lat. πέϱνα, perna, mutatâ gutturali in labialem; goth.<BR>fairzna calx, insertâ sibilante, nisi z pertinet ad suffixum,<BR>cf. scr. suff. स्नु; nostrum Ferse; lith. kul-nis calx, mutato<BR>r in l, v. चल्; gr. πτέϱνα, adjecto τ, sicut in πτόλις<BR>pro πόλις = पुरी; de lat. calx v. चल्; hib. cairine<BR>crura; etiam lat. crus radice cum चरण cohaerere videtur,<BR>ejecto a radicali.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चरम|चरमः<BR>चरम (ut videtur, a r. चर्)<BR>1) ultimus. चरमम् Adv. ultimo.<BR>MAH. 1.3628.<BR>2) m. occidens, occasus. (Hib. iar «the<BR>end, every thing last, the west», abjectâ litterâ initiali,<BR>v. Pict. P. 45.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चरित|चरितं<BR>चरित v. 1. चर्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चरित्र|चरित्रं<BR>चरित्र n. (r. चर् s. त्र, inserto इ) agendi ratio. Lass. 26.18. 27.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चरु|चरुः<BR>चरु m. (ut videtur, a चर्व् edere) cibus, praesertim sacrificalis,<BR>e lacte et butyro paratus. RAGH. 10.52. पयश्चरु<BR>(Schol. पयसा दुग्धेन पक्तम् चरुम् अन्नम्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्च्<BR>1. चर्च् 1. 10. P. A. (परिभाषणतर्जनयोः K. उक्तौ भर्त्से इतौ<BR>V.; videtur esse forma redupl. pro चर्चर्, v. चञ्च्)<BR>reprehendere, minari, dicere, ire; cf. जर्च्, गर्ज्, तर्ज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्च्<BR>2. चर्च् 10. P. A. (अध्ययने K.) legere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्चा|चर्च्चा<BR>चर्चा f. (r. चर्च् s. आ)<BR>1) consideratio, cogitatio. HIT. 49.19. 125.20.<BR>(v. 2. चर् praef. वि).<BR>2) unctio. AM.; v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्चित|चर्च्चितं<BR>चर्चित (a चर्चा s. इत, nisi part. pass. a r. चर्च् s. त) unctus,<BR>pollutus. DEV. 11.28.: असुरासृग्वसापङ्कचर्चित; Lass. 26.7.:<BR>रुधिरचर्चितसर्वाङ्गी.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्ब्<BR>चर्ब् 1. P. (गतौ) ire; cf. चर्, खर्ब्, गर्ब्, घर्ब्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्मकार|चर्मकारः|चर्म्मकार|चर्म्मकारः<BR>चर्मकार m. (e चर्मन् et कार faciens) sutor. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्मन्|चर्म्मन्<BR>चर्मन् n. (r. चर् s. मन्)<BR>1) cutis. HIT. 82.10.: द्वीपिचर्मपरिच्छन्न.<BR>2) corium. HIT. 125.14.: चर्मबन्ध.<BR>3) scutum. DR. 8.19. (Lat. corium radicali syllabâ accurate<BR>cum ćar-man convenit; fortasse cal-ceus, mutato<BR>r in l (v. चर्मकार sutor); hib. croi-cionn «a skin,<BR>hide» per metathesin e coir-cionn ortum esse videtur;<BR>gr. ΠΕΛΜΑΤ solea, calceus, etiam suffixo cum चर्मन्<BR>cohaeret, mutatâ nasali in tenuem ejusdem organi, siout<BR>e. c. in ὈΝΟΜΑΤ = नामन्, nomen etc.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्या|चर्य्या<BR>चर्या (r. चर् s. या)<BR>1) actio eundi, ambulandi, migrandi.<BR>R. Schl. I.19.19.: रथ्यचर्या vectio, vectura.<BR>2) perfunctio,<BR>effectio, exsecutio. R. Schl. I.9.40.: व्रतचर्या.<BR>3) servitium, munus, officium. l. c. 40.6.: अश्वचर्या.<BR>4) agendi ratio. BHAR. 2.59.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्व्<BR>चर्व् 1. P. mandere, manducare. DEV. 7.10.: {#nikzipya vaktre<BR>daSanES carvati#}. (Hib. carbad «the jaw»; carbal<BR>«the palate of the mouth»; creimim «I gnaw», creim<BR>«corrosion, exesion, arrosion, mordication», mutato v<BR>in m, v. gr. comp. 124. Pict. p. 58. sq.; lith. kramtau<BR>mando; conferatur etiam russ. жева́шь schevátj mandere,<BR>ratione habitâ, litteram ж cum g cognatam esse<BR>atque saepe cum scr. ज् convenire. Fortasse क्रव्य caro<BR>ad hanc radicem, quae e कर्व् orta est, pertinet.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चर्वण|चर्वणं|चर्व्वण|चर्व्वणं<BR>चर्वण n. (r. चर्व् s. अन) actio mandendi.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चल्<BR>1. चल् 1. P.<BR>1) se movere, vacillare. N. 5.9.: {#dfzwir mahAtmanAY<BR>cacAla#}.<BR>2) ire, abire, decedere, recedere.<BR>HIT. 26.9.: {#calaty ekena pAdena tizWaty ekena<BR>budDimAn#}; BH. 6.21. 37.: चलति तत्त्वतः; MAN. 7.15.:<BR>स्वधर्मान् न चलन्ति; HIT. 9.8.: व्याकुलश् चलितः;<BR>Lass. 42.19.: स्वागारम् विहाय यावच् चलति; ATM.<BR>30.15.: धावते चलते तथा. — Caus. चालयामि commovere.<BR>R. III.76.47.: {#na hy ahan te tu vacanEH…<BR>tvayA cAlayituM Sakyo vAtEr iva mahIDaraH#}. (Cf.<BR>केल्, क्वेल्, खल्, चर्, unde चल्, mutato र् in ल् ortum<BR>esse censeo. E. cognatis linguis huc, sive, quod ad<BR>idem redit, ad चर् traxerim gr. ϰέλω, ϰέλλω, ὀ-ϰέλλω,<BR>quae sensu ad formam caus. pertinent; ϰέλης; lat. celer,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=122-a" target="_blank">Page122-a+ 37</a>]<BR>pro-cello, ex-cello, prae-cello; calco, calc-s, fortasse<BR>sunt formae reduplicativae, sicut चञ्च्, q. v.; etiam<BR>calcar, quod ad eundum stimulat, huc sive ad चर् pertinet,<BR>ita ut reduplicatione ortum sit e calcal vel carcar;<BR>lith. kieláuju proficiscor jam sub r. चर् laudavimus; respiciatur<BR>etiam kielos surgo, v. चल् praef. उत् et gr.<BR>comp. 476., kielu levo, expergefacio; hib. caill «a path».<BR>Mutatâ gutturali in labialem, sicut in goth. fara = चरामि,<BR>huc trahi posset nostrum falle, germ. vet. vallu,<BR>praet. vi(v)al = चचाल; v. चल् praef. प्र; nec non<BR>πάλλω, πέλω, lat. pello; cf. Pott. s. r. कॄ p. 227.; de vacillo<BR>v. चल् praef. वि.)<BR>c. उत् surgere. RAGH. 2.6.: {#sTitaH sTitAm uccalitaH<BR>prayAtAn nizeduzIm AsanabanDaDIraH…CAye 'va<BR>tAm BUpatir anvagacCat#}; 12.27.: {#kAnanaM sA cakArA<BR>'NgarAgeRa puzpoccalitazawpadam#}.<BR>c. प्र<BR>1) ire, progredi, proficisci, abire. HIT. 46.14.: {#kASmIram<BR>pracalitaH#}; 60.70.: पशून् हन्तुम् प्रचलितः.<BR>2) cadere. RAM. I.18.23.: {#vyaTitamanAH pracacAlacA<BR>''sanAt#}.<BR>c. वि<BR>1) dimovere. N. 14.7.: {#na Sakto 'smi padAd vicalitum<BR>padam#}; A. 9.6.<BR>2) se movere, vacillare. {#vicalan<BR>praTamotpAte hayAnAm#}. — Caus. RAM. I.16.27.:<BR>विचालयेयुः शैलेन्द्रान्; MAN. 7.14.: {#tan Darman na<BR>vicAlayet#}. — Caus. Pass. BR. 2.13.: {#vicAlyamAnA<BR>vE prArTyamAnA durAtmaBiH#}; BH. 6.22.: दुःखेन विचाल्यते.<BR>(Lat. vacillo huc melius quadrat quam ad कक्<BR>ire, q. v.; esset igitur va-cillo vocalibus transpositis ortum<BR>e vicallo; syllaba va etiam ad praep. अव referri<BR>(अवचल्) vel e syllabâ redupl. explicari posset, ita ut<BR>vacillo pro vacallo mutilatum sit e quacallo.)<BR>c. वि praef. प्र dimovere. BHAR. 2.81.: {#nyAyyAt paTaH<BR>pravicalanti padan na DIrAH#}.<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) ire, Caus. movere. SAK. 57.7.: {#saYcAlayAmi<BR>nalinIdalatAlavfntam#}.<BR>2) surgere. R. I.66.47.: {#saYcacAlA<BR>''sanAt tUrRam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=121-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चल्<BR>2. चल् 6. P. (विलसने K. विलासे V.) ludere, jocari, nugari, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=122-b" target="_blank">Page122-b+ 37</a>]<BR>to dally, praesertim de mulieribus cum marito ludentibus<BR>et jocantibus. K.: चलति भर्त्रा नारी. (Cf. {#cull,<BR>kil, keli#}, hib. cal «a joke», cail «desire, longing,<BR>appetite».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=122-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चल्<BR>3. चल् 10. P. (भृत्याम् K. भृतौ V.) sustentare, nutrire.<BR>(Hib. cail «protection, keeping».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=122-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

