चारुसर्वाङ्गदर्शन<BR>चारुसर्वाङ्गदर्शन (BAH. e चारु et comp. TATP. significans,<BR>omnium membrorum visus, e सर्व omnis, अङ्ग<BR>membrum et दर्शन visus) pulchram omnium membrorum<BR>speciem habens. N. 12.26.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=123-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

