चिराय्<BR>चिराय् (Denominat. a चिर s. य्, v. gr. 585.) tardare, cunctari.<BR>H. 4.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चिराय<BR>चिराय Adv. (Dat. a चिर) diu. HIT. 51.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चिरि|चिरिः<BR>चिरि 5. P. चिरिणोमि (हिंसे V.) offendere, ferire, laedere,<BR>occidere; cf. ऋ, ऋणोमि, चीर्ण, कॄ, जॄ, जिरि.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चिरेण<BR>चिरेण Adv. (Instr. a चिर) post longum tempus, sero, tarde.<BR>RAGH. 5.64.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चिल्<BR>चिल् 6. P. (वसने K. वासे V.) vestire. (V. चेल et cf.<BR>hib. ceilim «I conceal, hide, cover», caille «a veil or<BR>cowl»; lat. celare, fortasse etiam velum, velare, quae e<BR>quelum, quelare explicaverim, sicut vermis e quermis, v.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">Page125-b+ 36</a>]<BR>कृमि; germ. vet. hilu celo, a rad. HAL, quod nititur<BR>formâ gunatâ चेल्, abjecto i; helm galea, heliu velo, heli<BR>velamentum; goth. hulja occulo; lat. oc-culo.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चिल्ल्<BR>चिल्ल् 1. P. (शौथेल्ये K. शैथिल्ये हावकृतौ V.)<BR>1) relaxari,<BR>solvi, mitigari. K.: चिल्लति साधुर् दयया.<BR>2) i. q. 2. चल् et चुल्ल्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चिवुक|चिवुकं|चिवुकः<BR>चिवुक n. mentum. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चिह्न|चिह्नं<BR>चिह्न n.<BR>1) nota, signum, macula. IN. 2.25. N. 17.7.<BR>2) vexillum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीक्<BR>चीक् 1. et 10. P. (अमर्षणे K. मर्शे V.) tolerare, patientem<BR>esse; tangere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीत्कार|चीत्कारः<BR>चीत्कार m. (e चीत्, quod vocabulum a sono factum, et<BR>कार faciens) clamor, ruditus, rugitus. HIT. 49.21. de<BR>asino; v. sq. et cf. चुक्कार.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीत्कारवत्|चीत्कारवन्त्<BR>चीत्कारवत् (a praec. s. वत्) clamore praeditus. MALATI-MADH. 1.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीन|चीनं|चीनः<BR>चीन m.<BR>1) capreae genus.<BR>2) vexillum; cf. चिह्न.<BR>3) nomen<BR>terrae, Sina.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीभ्<BR>चीभ् 1. A. (कत्थने K. कत्थे V.) laudare, extollere, gloriari,<BR>se jactare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीब्<BR>चीब् 1. A. (आदानसम्वरणयोः K.) sumere, capere, tegere.<BR>(Cf. चीव्; hib. cib manus; cambro-brit. cipiaw<BR>sumere.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीय्<BR>चीय् 1. P. A. (सम्वृत्यादानयोः) tegere, sumere, capere;<BR>cf. चि tegere et 1. चीव्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीर|चीरं<BR>चीर n. (ut videtur, a r. चि tegere s. र, vel a चिल् q. v.,<BR>mutato ल् in र्)<BR>1) vestis.<BR>2) cortex.<BR>3) vestis e cortice.<BR>M. 5. R. Schl. II.11.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीर्ण|चीर्णं|चीर्ण्ण<BR>चीर्ण scissus, divisus, trop. impletus, solutus, de votis (a r.<BR>चॄ descendere videtur, non tamen haec syllaba a grammaticis<BR>inter radices recepta est). RAM. I.18.5.; SA. 6.12. 41.<BR>(lege चीर्णानि, चीर्णं. - Cf. चिरि, चूर्ण, कॄ, जॄ.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीव्<BR>1. चीव् 1. A. (ग्रहसम्वृत्योः) sumere, capere, tegere; cf.<BR>चि, चीय्, चीब्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीव्<BR>2. चीव् 10. P. (भाषार्थे K. दीप्तौ V.) loqui, lucere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चीवर|चीवरं<BR>चीवर n. vestis pannosa. RAGH. 11.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=125-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुक्क्<BR>चुक्क् 10. P. (व्यसने K. आर्तौ V.; e चक्क् attenuato अ<BR>in उ) i. q. चक्क् et चिक्क्, quae tres radices<BR>eandem inter se habent rationem, quam gothicae formae,<BR>ut band ligavi, bundum ligavimus, binda ligo.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुक्कार|चुक्कारः<BR>चुक्कार m. (e चुक् et कार faciens, v. चीत्कार) leonis rugitus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुचुक|चुचुकं|चुचुकः<BR>चुचुक m. n. (e चूष् bibere?) papilla. (Hib. cioch mamma.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुट्<BR>1. चुट् 1. P. (अल्पीभावे K. तुच्छने V.) parvum, debilem<BR>esse; cf. चुट्ट्, चुण्ट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुट्<BR>2. चुट् 6. 10. P. चुटामि, चोटयामि. i. q. चट्, unde चुट् attenuato<BR>अ in उ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुट्ट्<BR>चुट्ट् 10. P. चुट्टयामि. i. q. 1. चुट्; cf. चुण्ट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुड्ड्<BR>चुड्ड् 1. P. (हावकरणे K.) i. q. 2. चल्, चिल्ल् et चुल्ल्;<BR>respiciatur, lingualem ड् fere ut र् pronunciari, र्<BR>autem facile in ल् converti.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुण्<BR>चुण् 6. P. (छेदे K. छिदि V.; mutilatum esse videtur e चुण्ट्<BR>vel चुण्ड्) findere. (Hib. guinim «I wound, prick,<BR>sting», guinneach «sharp-pointed», gun-ta «wounded».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुण्ट्|चुंट्<BR>1. चुण्ट् 1. P. चुण्टामि (e चुट् insertâ nasali; scribitur<BR>चुट्, v. gr. 110^a).) i. q. 1. चुट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुण्ट्|चुंट्<BR>2. चुण्ट् 10. P. चुण्टयामि. i. q. चट् et 2. चुट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुण्ड्|चुंड्<BR>1. चुण्ड् 1. P. (अल्पीभावे K. तौछ्ये V.; scribitur चुड्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>i. q. 1. चुट् et 1. चुण्ट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुण्ड्|चुंड्<BR>2. चुण्ड् 1. 10. P. (छेदने K. छिदि V., scribitur चुड्, v. gr. 110^a).)<BR>i. q. चट्, 2. चुट् et 2. चुण्ट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुत्<BR>चुत् 1. P. (आसेचने K. क्षरे V.) stillare, fundere, effundere.<BR>(Cf. च्युत्, goth. GUT - giuta, gaut, gutum - pro quo<BR>e generali consonantium permutandarum lege HUTH<BR>exspectaveris, gr. comp. 87.; gr. ΧΥ, χεύω, χύ-σις,<BR>abjectâ litterâ finali et mutatâ tenui in aspiratam.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुद्<BR>चुद् 10. P.<BR>1) mittere, impellere, incitare, stimulare. IN. 5.2.:<BR>शरैर् मन्मथचोदितैः; H. 4.4.: {#coditE 'zA hy<BR>anaNgena#}; SU. 3.9.: पितामहम् अचोदयन्; DR. 8.1.:<BR>विपरिधावत इति स्म…चोदयामास तान् नृपान्;<BR>MAH. 1.1916.: ततस् त्वा ऽहम् अचूचुदम्; A. 9.30. ATM.<BR>R. I.11.51.: चोदयस्व नृपर्षभान्.<BR>2) instituere,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-b" target="_blank">Page126-b+ 36</a>]<BR>imperare, praecipere. MAN. 2.165.: व्रतैश्च विधिचोदितैः.<BR>(Huc trahi posset lat. cûdo et, mutatâ gutt. in labialem,<BR>re-pudio; gr. σπεύδω, praefixo σ.)<BR>c. अभि<BR>1) i. q. simpl. R. I.34.6.: राज्ञाभिचोदितः; 15.45.:<BR>अब्रवीत् प्रसृतम् वाक्यं राज्ञा यद् अभिचोदितम्.<BR>2) interrogare, percunctari de alquâ re, c. acc. rei.<BR>MAH. 1.2913.: {#fziH kaScid ihA ''gamya mama janmA<BR>'Byacodayat#}.<BR>c. परि i. q. simpl. MAN. 3.233.: गुणैश्च परिचोदयेत्.<BR>c. प्र<BR>1) i. q. simpl. IN. 5.3.: मन्मथेन प्रचोदिता; DR. 8.6.:<BR>नाराचैर् वीरबाहुप्रचोदितैः; A. 8.2.<BR>2) pronunciare,<BR>proclamare. MAN. 3.228.: गुणान् सर्वान् प्रचोदयन्<BR>(Schol. कथयन्).<BR>c. प्र praef. अभि id. MAH. 1.575.: दैवेना ऽभिप्रचोदितः.<BR>c. प्र praef. सम् id. A. 7.7.: हयास् ते सम्प्रचोदिताः.<BR>c. सम् id. SA. 2.6.: पित्रा सञ्चोदिता.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुन्द्<BR>चुन्द् 1. P. A. (निशाने K., scribitur चुद्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>acuere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुप्<BR>चुप् 1. P. se movere (explicatur per मन्दायाङ् गतौ K.<BR>शनैर् गतौ V.; i. e. lente ire). MAH. 3.10648. 10649.:<BR>{#kiM svit svapnaN na nimizati kiM svij jAtan na<BR>copati . kasya svid Dfdayan nA 'sti kiM svid vegena<BR>vardDate .. matsyaH supto na nimizaty aRqaY jAtan<BR>na copati . aSmano hfdayan nA 'sti nadI vegena<BR>vardDate..#}. (Cf. चप् se movere, vacillare, unde चुप्, attenuato<BR>अ in उ; conferatur etiam कुप् irasci, quod a<BR>motione animi dictum esse censeo; huc trahi posset<BR>lith. kópu scando, nostrum hüpfen, angl. to hop.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुम्ब्|चुंब्<BR>चुम्ब् 1. 10. P. (scribitur चुब्, gr. 110^a).) osculari. HIT. 27.20.:<BR>चुम्बति पतिन् निर्दयम् आलिङ्ग्य.<BR>(Goth. kukja osculor, servatâ initiali tenui contra regulam,<BR>gr. comp. 87. et mutatâ finali labiali in gutturalem,<BR>positâ tenui pro mediâ, e generali lege, gr. comp. 87.;<BR>hib. pogaim osculor, mutatâ gutturali in labialem et vice<BR>versâ; etiam lith. bućioju id. transpositum esse videtur, e<BR>ćubioju; lett. sz-kûpstit osculari.)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">Page127-a+ 37</a>]<BR>c. परि id. ĆAUR. 14.: मुक्ताकलापपरिचुम्बितचूचुकाग्रा;<BR>cf. l. c. sl. 17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=126-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुम्बिन्|चुंबिन्<BR>चुम्बिन् (r. चुम्ब् s. इन्) osculans, in fine compp. ĆAUR. 17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुर्<BR>1. चुर् 4. A.: चूर्ये (*) (दाहे) urere. (Lith. kurrù calefacio<BR>cubiculum, per assimil. e kurju, v. gr. comp. 501.,<BR>praet. kuriau; sukurrù ugniṅ ignem accendo; goth. hauri<BR>et gr. ΚΑΥ, ϰαύ-σω, ϰαῦ-μα, abjecto r finali, nituntur<BR>formâ Vriddhi auctâ कौर्.<BR>(*) Radix ćur in tempp. special. vocalem suam producit,<BR>in analogiâ cum Passivis radicum in ir vel ur desinentium<BR>(gr. 495.). Wils. et Forsterus hanc rad. scribunt ćûr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुर्<BR>2. चुर् 1. 10. P. चोरामि, चोरयामि furari. MAN. 8.331.:<BR>यस् त्व् अग्निञ् चोरयेद् गृहात्. (Vide चौर et<BR>cf. lat. fûr, gr. ϕώϱ, mutatâ gutturali in labialem et tenui<BR>in aspiratam; gr. ω nititur formâ Vriddhi auctâ<BR>चौर्, abjecto उ; hib. COIR «false, deceitfull» in initio<BR>compp.; coire «trespass, offence», coireach «criminal, a<BR>malefactor», cuireat «the knave at cards», cuireadach<BR>«knavish».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुल्<BR>चुल् 10. P. (निमज्जने) submergere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुलुम्प्|चुलुंप्<BR>चुलुम्प् 1. P. (लोपे) findere, rumpere, abscindere; cf.<BR>लुप्, लुम्पामि, लुम्पे, unde चुलुम्प् quodam reduplicationis<BR>modo ortum esse videtur.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चुल्ल्<BR>चुल्ल् 1. P. (हावकरने K. हावकृतौ V.) i. q. 2. चल्, unde<BR>चुल्ल् attenuato अ in उ, et reduplicato ल्. K.: {#cullati<BR>priyeRa nArI#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चूचुक|चूचुकं<BR>चूचुक m. n. (etiam चुचुक, forma reduplicata, ut videtur, a<BR>चूष् bibere, sicut gr. ϑηλή, τίτϑη, τιτϑός, nec non<BR>nostrum Zitze, cum धे bibere (cf. ϑῆσϑαι) cohaerent,<BR>et lat. papilla tanquam forma redupl. ad पातुम्, po-tum,<BR>reduci posset) papilla. UR. 84.1. ĆAUR. 14. (Hib. cioch<BR>mamma, fortasse etiam coicht «children» huc pertinet.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चूडा<BR>चूडा f.<BR>1) vertex, culmen, cacumen, praesertim capitis vertex.<BR>RAGH. 17.28. HIT. 55.19.<BR>2) cincinnus singulus<BR>in vertice. RAGH. 18.50.<BR>3) crista.<BR>4) caput. Wils.<BR>(Cf. कूट et hib. cuit caput.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चूण्<BR>चूण् 10. P. (सङ्कोचे) curvare, inflectere; cf. कूण्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चूत|चूतः<BR>चूत m. arbor, Mangifera Indica. RAGH. 7.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चूर्ण्<BR>चूर्ण् 10. P. (पेषणे K. पेषे V., ut videtur Denom. a चूर्ण<BR>q. v.) frangere, conterere. DEV. 3.35.: {#tAn (BUDarAn)<BR>prahitAMs tena cUrRayantI SarotkarEH#}; 9.12.: {#muzwipAtena<BR>devI taccA 'py acUrRayat (SUlam)#}; A. 8.2.:<BR>तद् (अश्मवर्षम्) अचूर्णयम् वेगवद्भिः शरैः; 3.: {#cUrRyamAne'Smavarze<BR>tu#}. (Cf. चीर्ण, चिरि, 2. {#kF, SF, jF,<BR>jUr#}; hib. coirneach «a part», crinim «I knaw, bite».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चूर्ण|चूर्णं|चूर्णः|चूर्ण्ण<BR>चूर्ण m. (ut videtur, part. pass. ab obsoletâ rad. चॄ, unde<BR>supra चीर्ण deduximus; forma चूर्ण convenit cum formâ,<BR>quam ॠ vulgo post labiales assumit; e. c. पूर्ण a पॄ) pulvis.<BR>A. 8.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चूष्<BR>चूष् 1. P. sugere, चोष्य sugendus. MAH. 2.316.: {#lehyaY<BR>cozyaYca peyaYca#}. (Fortasse चूष् e चुक्ष्, ejecto क्, mutilatum<BR>est, cf. चुचुक, चूचुक; चुक्ष् autem e quadam<BR>simpliciore radice in gutturalem vel palatalem desinente<BR>deducendum esset, sicut धिक्ष् accendere a दह्, भक्ष्<BR>edere a भग्, vel भज्, cf. ϕάγω et भुज्; res si ita se<BR>habet, cum चूष्, e चुक्, et चुचुक papilla contulerim<BR>lat. sugo et succus, mutatâ initiali gutturali in sibilantem,<BR>nostrum saugen, gr. ὑγϱός.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चृत्<BR>1. चृत् 6. P. (हिंसायाम् K. हिंसे ग्रन्थे V.) offendere, laedere,<BR>occidere; cf. कृत्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चृत्<BR>2. चृत् 1. 10. P. (सन्दीपने) collustrare, illustrare, celebrare.<BR>c. वि id. RIGV. p. 137.4.: वि ये चृतन्ति (अग्निम्) «qui<BR>Agnim hymnis canunt».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेट|चेटः<BR>चेट m. (r. चिट् mittere, nisi चिष्ट्, ejecto ष्, s. अ) servus,<BR>famulus. HEM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेटक|चेटकः<BR>चेटक m. (r. चिट्, nisi चेष्ट्, s. अक) id. HIT. 65.16. BH. 1.91.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेटिका<BR>चेटिका f. (Fem. praecedentis, v. gr. 645. s. इक) ancilla.<BR>UP. 49.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेटी<BR>चेटी f. (a चेट signo fem. ई) id. UP. 38.41.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेत्<BR>चेत् Conj. (ut equidem puto, e च et इत् q. v.) si, postponitur.<BR>BR. 2.17. N. 17.29. R. Schl. II.8.34. - Cum antecedente<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-a" target="_blank">Page128-a+ 37</a>]<BR>यदि<BR>1) si quidem. R. Schl. II.8.34.b.: {#yadi ced<BR>Barato DarmAt pitryaM rAjyam avApsyati#}.<BR>2) etsi,<BR>etiamsi. MAH. 1.4203.: {#yady asti ced DanaM sarvam<BR>vfTABogA Bavantu tAH#}. (Gr. ϰαί.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=127-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेतना<BR>चेतना (r. चित् s. अना) animus sui compos, Besinnung,<BR>Bewuʃstsein. UR. 76.14. RAGH. 17.1. BH. 13.6. — In<BR>fine compp. possess. N. 2.3. 7.14. 9.20. 10.19. 13.60.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेतस्<BR>चेतस् n. (r. चित् s. अस्) mens, animus. IN. 2.32. RAGH. 14.60.<BR>N. 9.33. 21.8. — In fine compp. possess. BH. 4.23. 5.26. 8.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेदि|चेदिः<BR>चेदि m. nomen regionis. N. 12.132.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेल्<BR>चेल् 1. P. (गतौ K. चालगत्योः V.) se movere, ire; scribitur<BR>etiam चेल्ल्; cf. चल्, praet. redupl. pl. चेलिम.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेल|चेलं<BR>चेल m. n. (r. चिल् s. अ) vestis. BH. 6.11.; Schol. {#celam<BR>vastram#}. (Lat. velum, v. sq. et rad. चिल्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेली<BR>चेली f. (a praec. signo fem. ई) id. (Hib. caille fem. «a<BR>veil or cowl», v. r. चिल्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेष्ट्<BR>चेष्ट् 1. A. (चेष्टायाम् K. ईहे V.)<BR>1) se movere. MAN. 1.52.<BR>यदा स देवो जागर्ति तदे ऽदञ् चेष्टते जगत्; R. Schl. I.2.14.:<BR>{#taM SoRitaparItANgaY cezwamAnam mahItale<BR>dfzwvA#}; M. 22.: {#gaNgAyAn na hi Saknomi vfhattvAc<BR>cezwitum#}.<BR>2) ire, adire, frequentare. RAGH. 6.51.: {#rurucezwita<BR>BUmizu#}.<BR>3) niti, tendere, operam dare. RAM. III.47.51.:<BR>{#daSA kftAntopahate 'yam AvilA kim<BR>atra Sakyam puruzeRa cezwitum#}; c. acc. rei. BH. 3.33.:<BR>सदृशञ् चेष्टते स्वस्याः प्रकृतेर् ज्ञानवान् अपि. चेष्टित<BR>n. nisus, opera, factum. N. 23.18. RAGH. 4.68. — Part.<BR>praes. PAR. R. Schl. I.34.25. — Caus. commovere,<BR>agitare. MAN. 12.15.: भूतानि सततञ् चेष्टयति.<BR>(Cf. इष् ire, desiderare, अन्विष् quaerere, इष्ट desideratus,<BR>unde चेष्ट् praefixo च ortum esse videtur; lat.<BR>QUAES, quaero, quaesivi; cambro-brit. cais contentio,<BR>labor.)<BR>c. अति ultra modum se movere, ultra modum niti, operam<BR>dare. HIT. 36.21.: {#vfttyarTan nA 'ticezweta sA hi<BR>DAtrE 'va nirmitA#}.<BR>c. वि<BR>1) niti, operam dare, agere. MAN. 8.334.: येन येन<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">Page128-b+ 37</a>]<BR>…अङ्गेन स्तेनो नृषु विचेष्टते. - विचेष्टित n. nisus,<BR>contentio, actio. N. 23.3. RAM. III.65.12.<BR>2) reniti,<BR>obniti, reluctari. DR. 9.13. part. praes. PAR.: {#tata enam<BR>vicezwantam baDvA#}.<BR>3) ultro citroque se movere, se<BR>volutare. RAM. III.62.19.: {#SatruGnaBaratAv uBO DarAyAM<BR>sma vyacezwetAm BagnaSfNgAv ivA 'rzaBO#}; III.51.23.:<BR>ता वाष्पेणच सम्वीताः…व्यचेष्टन्त निरानन्दाः.<BR>c. सम् niti, operam dare, agere. N. 23.3.: {#saYcezwamAnasya<BR>lakzayantI vicezwitam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेष्टा<BR>चेष्टा f. (r. चेष्ट् s. आ) nisus, actio. HIT. 110.22. RAGH. 6.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चेष्टित|चेष्टितं<BR>चेष्टित v. चेष्ट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चैतन्य|चैतन्यं|चैतन्यः<BR>चैतन्य n. (a चेतन s. य) anima. RAGH. 5.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चैत्य|चैत्यं|चैत्यः<BR>चैत्य (ut videtur, a चिता vel चिति s. य)<BR>1) n. locus sacrificii.<BR>2) n. monumentum sepulcrale. Lass. 17.<BR>3) m.<BR>arbor sacra, ficus religiosa, in vici vicinitate. H. 1.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चैत्र|चैत्रं|चैत्रः<BR>चैत्र m. (a चित्र vel चित्रा s. अ) mensis Ćaitrus, Martius-Aprilis.<BR>BHAR. 1.35.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चैत्ररथ|चैत्ररथं<BR>चैत्ररथ m. (a चित्ररथ Gandharvus, qui Kuvêri horti custos<BR>est, s. अ) Kuvêri hortus. RAGH. 5.60.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चोदना<BR>चोदना f. (r. चुद् impellere, s. अन in fem.) impulsus, incitatio.<BR>BH. 18.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चोर|चोरः<BR>चोर m. (r. चुर् s. अ) fur, v. चौर.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=128-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

