छ|छं|छः<BR>छ Haec littera, ubi in initio vocabulorum invenitur, e स्क्<BR>vel स्ख् orta esse videtur, atque hoc loco in cognatis linguis<BR>fere semper sibilanti cum gutturali conjunctae respondet.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छग|छगः<BR>छग m. caper, capra. HEM. v. छाग. (Fortasse nostrum<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1b" target="_blank">Page129-1b+ 24</a>]<BR>Bock, anglo-sax. bucca, germ. vet. boch, poch, pog huc<BR>pertinent, - v. Graff. III.30. - mutatâ initiali gutturali in<BR>labialem et abjectâ sibilante, quam ex छ् = sk exspectaveris;<BR>lat. caper, Th. capru, quod cum छगल vel छागल<BR>contulerim, in secundâ syllabâ gutturalem in labialem et<BR>mediam in tenuem convertit; etiam hircus ad छगल<BR>trahi possit, ita ut litteris transpositis e hicrus ortum<BR>sit.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छगल|छगलं|छगलः<BR>छगल m. (a praec. s. ल) caper. (Lat. caper, Th. capru,<BR>capro, v. छग.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छगला<BR>छगला f. (Fem. praec.) capra. (Lat. capra, v. छग.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छगली<BR>छगली f. (a छग signo fem. ई) capra. (Hib. gabhar, gen.<BR>gabhair, v. छग.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छटा<BR>छटा f. lux, splendor. Lass. 67.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छत्र|छत्त्रं|छत्त्रः|छत्रं|छत्रः<BR>छत्र n. (pro छत्र, r. छद् s. त्र) umbella. RAGH. 3.16. V.<BR>छद्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छद्<BR>1. छद् 1. P. A. (Part. pass. छन्न, gr. 607.) tegere. N. 17.6.:<BR>छन्नो ऽभ्रेणे ऽव चन्द्रमाः. (Cf. स्कु tegere; hib.<BR>scailim «I shade, shelter» = छदामि, mutato d in l;<BR>scailein «a fan, umbrella» v. छत्र; scail «a shadow»,<BR>scaileachd «darkness», scath «shadow, shade, protection,<BR>a veil, covering», mutato d radicis in th, nisi th ad<BR>suffixum derivationis pertinet, abjecto d radicali, sicut<BR>in scr. छाया umbra q. v.; gr. σϰιά, σϰο-τός; etiam in<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=130-a" target="_blank">Page130-a+ 36</a>]<BR>goth. sca-dus umbra syllaba du ad derivationis suffixum<BR>trahenda esse videtur; lith. skyda scutum, skidélế parvum<BR>scutum; nostrum Schil-d e scil-d, mutato d in l;<BR>goth. skal-ja tegula; germ. med. schal cutis, cortex, putamen,<BR>nostrum Schale; lat. squâ-ma, abjectâ radicis<BR>consonante finali, sicut saepissime, v. छद्मन्; spolium,<BR>mutatâ gutturali in labialem, et d in l.)<BR>c. परि i. q. simpl. HIT. 81.10.: द्वीपिचर्मपरिच्छन्न.<BR>c. प्र id. प्रच्छन्न occultus. N. 19.32.; HIT. 9.14.<BR>c. प्रति id. RAM. I.9.5.: मुनिवेशप्रतिच्छन्न.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=129-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छद्<BR>2. छद् 10. P. A. छादयामि tegere. DEV. 7.17.: {#SaravarzEH…<BR>CAdayAmAsa#}; GAT. 6.: छादिते दिनकरस्य भावने.<BR>c. आ<BR>1) id. DEV. 10.10.: {#tataH SaraSatEr devIm ACAdayata<BR>so'suraH#}.<BR>2) abscondere. HIT. 22.1.: {#tatsamIpe<BR>AtmAnam ACAdya sTitaH#}.<BR>c. प्र id. R. Schl. II.8.36.: {#pracCAdyamAnaM rAmeRa BAratan<BR>trAtum arhasi#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=130-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छद्<BR>3. छद् 10. P. छदयामि (ऊर्जने (*)) educare, nutrire liberos.<BR>K.: छदयति पुत्रङ् घृतेन पिता.<BR>(*) Sic legimus pro ujjanê apud Wilkins., quod ex<BR>ûrjjanê corruptum esse censeo; ûrjana autem hoc loco<BR>ad Caus. ûrjayâmi facio ut alqs fortis fiat, pertinet.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=130-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छद|छदः<BR>छद m. (r. छद् s. अ)<BR>1) folium. A. 4.50.<BR>2) ala. N. 9.12.<BR>(Hib. sgiath ala.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=130-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छदिस्<BR>छदिस् n. (r. छद् s. इस्) tectum domûs. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=130-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छद्मन्<BR>छद्मन् n. (r. छद् s. मन्) occultatio, alienae formae assumptio.<BR>RAGH. 12.2.; v. sq. (Cf. nostrum Schir-m,<BR>germ. vet. scer-m, Th. scer-ma scutum, mutato d in r;<BR>v. छद्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=130-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

