छल|छलं|छलः<BR>छल n. (ut mihi videtur, a छद् tegere, abscondere, mutato<BR>द् in ल्, suff. अ) alienae formae assumptio, dissimulatio;<BR>dolum, fraus. HIT. 4.2. RAGH. 6.54. 16.28. HIT. 4.2.<BR>RAGH. 7.27.; v. छद्मन्, छद्मिन्. (Cf. lat. scelus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=130-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

