छुरी<BR>छुरी f. (r. छुर् s. अ in fem.) id. (Cf. germ. vet. scâri forfex,<BR>et v. छुर्; etiam lat. for - compositi for-fex ad rad.<BR>छुर् vel ad cognatam खुर् vel ad कृत्, e कर्त्, trahi<BR>possit, mutatâ gutturali in lab.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=132-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

छृद्<BR>1. छृद् 7. P. A. छृणद्मि, छृन्दे (देवनद्युतिवमनेषु) ludere,<BR>splendere, vomere, v. sq. et छर्द्. (Cum छृन्द्, quod<BR>ortum est e स्कर्न्द् vel स्क्रन्द्, conferri possit lat. splendeo,<BR>mutatâ gutturali in labialem et r in l; lith. spindźiu<BR>splendeo, spindulys splendor, solis lumen; skais-tus,<BR>skais-tas clarus, splendidus; huc etiam trahi posset nostrum<BR>Glanz, germ. med. glanz splendidus, glenze splendeo,<BR>abjectâ sibilante; etiam glize splendeo, praet. gleiz,<BR>nostrum gleiʃze, Gleiʃsner.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=132-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

