जङ्घाल|जंघाल|जङ्घालः<BR>जङ्घाल m. (ut videtur, forma redupl. a rad. गा vel गम् s.<BR>ल pro र) viator agilis, velox; v. जङ्घा.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जज्<BR>जज् 1. P. (युद्धे K. युधि V.) pugnare, v. sq. (Fortasse hib.<BR>fighim «I fight», nostrum fechte, germ. vet. vihtu, lat.<BR>pugno, mutatâ gutturali in lab., v. जञ्ज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जज्ञिवस्<BR>जज्ञिवस् Part. praet. redupl. radicum जन् et ज्ञा.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जञ्ज्|जंज्<BR>जञ्ज् 1. P. (a जज् insertâ nasali, scribitur जज्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>pugnare. (Lith. źincźiju «ich streite mich, drohe»;<BR>v. जज्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जट्<BR>जट् 1. P. (संहतौ) coacervare, cf. झट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जटा<BR>जटा f. (r. जट् s. आ) coma implicata, involuta (*). SU. 1.8.<BR>(*) Wils.: The hair matted as worn by the god Siwa,<BR>and by ascetics; the long hairs occasionally clotted together,<BR>and brought over the head, so as to project like a<BR>horn from the forehead, at other times allowed to fall<BR>carelessly over the back and shoulders.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जटायु|जटायुः<BR>जटायु et जटायुस् m. (e जट accumulatus et आयु vel आयुस्<BR>vita) n. pr. vulturis fabulosi, Aruni, solis aurigae,<BR>filii, quem Râvanus occidit. R. Schl. I.1.51.: {#gfDraM hatvA<BR>jawAyuzam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जटिल|जटिलः<BR>जटिल (a जटा s. इल) implicatam comam habens.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जटुल|जटुलः<BR>जटुल m. (r. जट् s. उल) macula, nota in corpore. AM.: =<BR>पिप्लु.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जठर|जठरं|जठरः<BR>जठर m. venter. H. 2.3. (Goth. qvithrs, Th. qvithra in<BR>comp. lausqvithrs inanem ventrem habens, quithus uterus;<BR>fortasse lat. venter e guenter, insertâ nasali.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जड|जडं|जडः<BR>जड<BR>1) frigidus.<BR>2) hebetatus, obtusus, conturbatus, mente<BR>captus, stolidus, stupidus. UR. 7.9. RAGH. 8.74. BHAR. 3.59.<BR>(Cf. hib. fiod f. frigus, fuar frigidus, quae, si huc<BR>pertinent, gutturalem in labialem converterunt.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जत्रु<BR>जत्रु n. os collare, clavicula. R. Schl. I.1.12.: गूडजत्रु.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जन्<BR>1. जन् 3. P. जजन्मि gignere, generare. Participia जनित<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=134-a" target="_blank">Page134-a+ 37</a>]<BR>et जात usu ita distingui videntur, ut illud passivam, hoc,<BR>ubi non ad जन् cl. 4. pertinet, activam significationem<BR>habeat, sicut शक् - posse format शकित cum sensu pass.<BR>et शक्त potens, capax; e. c. MAH. 1.3036.: {#BAryAyAY janitam<BR>putram AdarSezv iva cA ''nanam . hlAdate janitA<BR>prekzya svargam prApye 'va puRyakft; prajAtA#} quae<BR>peperit. MAH. 1.3046. (Gr. ΓΕΝ, γίγνομαι; lat. GEN,<BR>gigno, genui, (g)nascor, gnatus; hib. genim «I beget,<BR>generate»; lith. gemù nascor, gaminu gigno, gim-minế<BR>genus, cujus suffixum convenit c. scr. मान, gr. μενος;<BR>gen-tis cognatus; goth. KIN germinare, keina, kain, kinum;<BR>kuni, Th. kunja, genus; nostrum keime, Kin-d i. e.<BR>genitus; v. जन, जनी.)<BR>c. अधि id. RAGH. 18.23.: {#ISvareRa tena kziter viSvasaho<BR>'DijajYe#}.<BR>c. प्र parere. प्रजाता quae peperit. MAH. 1.3046.: {#prajAtA<BR>'ham…imaN kumAram#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=133-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जन्<BR>2. जन् 4. A. जाये (v. gr. 332.)<BR>1) nasci. HIT. 4.19.: {#mfto<BR>ko vA na jAyate#}; c. loc. matris et ablat. patris:<BR>MAN. 10.64.: शूद्रायाम् ब्राह्मणाज् जातः; MAH. 1.371.:<BR>शकुन्तलायान् दुष्मन्ताद् भरतश्चा ऽपि जज्ञिवान्.<BR>2) oriri. RAM. I.35.15.: सप्त स्रोतांसि जज्ञिरे; 48.5.:<BR>यष्टुम् मतिर् अजायत; III.55.19.: शब्दो जायते तुमुलः.<BR>3) fieri. NALOD. 1.42.: {#AyatayA vIkzya dfSA taM<BR>smarAturA 'jayata#}; MAH. 1.6625.: क्षुधार्त्ता जज्ञिरे जनाः. Caus.<BR>जनयामि, Praet. mltf. अजीजनम् (gr. 526.) facere<BR>ut aliquis nascatur, oriatur, gignere, procreare, parere,<BR>c. loc. feminae ex quâ aliquis liberum gignit. N. 5.47.:<BR>{#janayAmAsaca nalo damayantyAm…indrasenaM sutaYcA<BR>'pi indrasenAYca kanyakAm#}; A. 6.13.: {#sa tu SabdaH…pratiSabdam<BR>ajIjanat#}; R. I.15.83.: {#kOSalyA<BR>'janayad rAmam#}.<BR>c. अनु postea nasci. MAN. 9.134.: यदि पुत्रो ऽनुजायते.<BR>c. अभि nasci, oriri. BH. 2.62.: कामात् क्रोधो ऽभिजायते;<BR>16.5.: सम्पदन् दैवीम् अभिजातो ऽसि ad divinam<BR>sortem natus es.<BR>c. उप id. HIT. 8.3.: अस्मिन् न निर्गुणङ् गोत्रे अपत्यम् उपजायते;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=134-b" target="_blank">Page134-b+ 37</a>]<BR>BH. 2.62.: सङ्गस् तेषू ऽपजायते propensio<BR>erga eas (res sensuales) oritur; 14.2.: {#sarge 'pi<BR>no 'pajAyante#}.<BR>c. प्र id. MAH. 1.4660.: {#iha tasmAt prajAhetoH prajAyante<BR>narottamAH#}. De प्रजाता quae peperit v. जन् cl. 3.<BR>c. वि active parere. R. Schl. I.27.8.: यक्षी पुत्रम् व्यजायत.<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) nasci. R. I.57.20.: तस्माद् मरीचिः सञ्जज्ञे;<BR>40.49.: अष्टौ सञ्जज्ञिरे पुत्राः.<BR>2) oriri. H. 1.14.: {#pARquputrARAm<BR>mUrCe 'va samajAyata#}; SA. 5.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=134-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जन|जनः<BR>जन m. (r. जन् s. अ)<BR>1) vir, homo, persona, praesertim in<BR>plur. DR. 3.5. BR. 2.12. N. 13.35. 49. 14.14. — Sing.<BR>praecedente pronomine demonstrativo interdum pronominis<BR>1^mae personae utriusque generis loco fungitur; e. c.<BR>UR. 24.6.: तस्मिन् जने mihi (regi); 28.2.infr.: {#paravaSo<BR>'yaY janaH#} ego (Urvasia); 19.: अयञ् जनः ego<BR>(rex); RAGH. 8.80.<BR>2) Collect. homines, die Leute. N. 10.10. 13.50.;<BR>SA. 7.5.; in fine compp. turba. N. 17.24.:<BR>बन्धुजनः; RAGH. 14.13. 60.: श्वश्रूजन. (Hib. duine<BR>«man either male or female»; gr. δῆμος vocis जन fortasse<BR>Fem. जना mulier exstitit, cui responderet goth.<BR>qvinô, Th. qvinôn, mulier, adjecto n, v. gr. comp. 142.;<BR>slav. жена schenà.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=134-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनक|जनकः<BR>जनक (r. जन् s. अक) Adj. generans. Lass. 83.14. Subst.<BR>m.<BR>1) genitor, pater.<BR>2) n. pr. regis Mithilae. RAGH. 11.38.<BR>(Nostrum König, germ. vet. cuning, chuning rex; v.<BR>जनी mulier, angl. queen; fortasse vocis जनक exstitit<BR>Fem. जनका vel जनकी, cum quo conveniret gr. ΓΥΝΑΙΚ<BR>quod e ΓΥΝΑΚΙ, regresso ι finali in antecedentem<BR>syllabam, explicaverim; lith. źmogùs homo e<BR>źamogus correptum esse videtur, mutato radicis n in m, sicut<BR>in gamù; v. जन्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=134-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जननी<BR>जननी f. (r. जन् s. अन in fem.) genitrix. IN. 5.40. (Lith.<BR>źmonà mulier, quod e źamonà correptum esse puto, nititur<BR>formâ जनना, v. जन् et जम्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=134-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनपद|जनपदः<BR>जनपद n. (e जन et पद n. locus) regio, terra, rus. N. 12.132. 26.33.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=134-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनान्तिकम्|जनांतिकम्<BR>जनान्तिकम् Adv. (e जन et अन्तिक propinquitas in accus.)<BR>in linguâ scenicâ, ad personam aliquam secreto loquens.<BR>UR. 31.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनार्दन|जनार्दनः|जनार्द्दन|जनार्द्दनः<BR>जनार्दन m. (hominum vexator, e जन et आर्दन vexator)<BR>cognomen Krischni.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनि|जनिः<BR>जनि v. जनी.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनितृ<BR>जनितृ m. (r. जन् s. तृ) genitor, pater. (Lat. genitor, gr.<BR>γενέτωϱ, γενετήϱ; hib. genteoir «a begetter, sower,<BR>planter».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनित्री<BR>जनित्री f. (Fem. praecedentis) genitrix, mater. N. 16.34.<BR>(Lat. genitrî-x, gr. γενέτειϱα, v. gr. comp. 119.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनी<BR>जनी correptum जनि f. (a जन vir signo fem. ई, correptum<BR>इ) mulier; cf. जानि. (Hib. gean «a woman»;<BR>goth. qvêns, Th. qvêni uxor, qveins, Th. qveini id., angl.<BR>queen; de goth. qvinô et slav. жена schena v. जन.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जनिमन्<BR>जनिमन् n. (r. जन् s. मन्, inserto इ) nativitas, natales, ortus.<BR>AM.; v. जन्मन्. (Hib. geineamhuin «birth, conception».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जन्तु|जंतु|जंतुः|जन्तुः<BR>जन्तु m. (r. जन् s. तु) animal, animans, creatura. RAGH. 8.86.<BR>BHAR. 2.9. 3.45. BH. 5.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जन्मन्<BR>जन्मन् n. (r. जन् s. मन्) nativitas, natales, origo. N. 1.29.<BR>BH. 4.5. (Formâ respondet lat. ger-men, quod jam<BR>Vossius a geno deduxit, mutato n in r, sicut in ger-mânus,<BR>cf. जायमान; hib. geanamhuin «engendering».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जन्य|जन्यं|जन्यः<BR>1. जन्य m. (fortasse a जनी s. य; Schol. ad RAGH. ed. Calc. 6.30.<BR>जन्यान् explicat per: जनीम् वधूम् वहन्ति)<BR>nymphagogus, Brautführer, v. जन्या; secundum AM.<BR>sponsi amicus: जन्याः स्निग्धा वरस्य ये. MAH. 1.7203.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जन्य|जन्यं|जन्यः<BR>2. जन्य n. (fortasse a हन् occidere, mutatâ gutturali in palat.,<BR>sicut in syllabâ redupl. τοῦ जघान) proelium. RAGH. 4.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जन्या<BR>जन्या f. (Fem. τοῦ जन्य m.) paranympha, Brautführerin.<BR>RAGH. 6.30. (in ed. Calc. legitur जन्या).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जप्<BR>जप् 1. P. submissâ voce dicere, praesertim preces. R. Schl. I.2.10.:<BR>जप्त्वा जप्यञ्च वाग्यतः; IN. 1.20.: {#jajApa<BR>japyam#}; R. Schl. I.25.3.: जेपतुः परमञ् जपम्; Lass. 18.6.:<BR>एकम् मन्त्रञ् जपित्वा; GITA-GOV. 4.16.: हरिर् इति जपति सकामम्;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">Page135-b+ 36</a>]<BR>cf. जल्प्, unde fortasse<BR>जप् ejectâ liquidâ.<BR>c. उप<BR>1) submissâ voce loqui. RAM. Schl. I.9.38.: {#SrotramUleco<BR>'pajepuH#}.<BR>2) sibi conciliare. MAN. 7.197.: {#upajapyAn<BR>upajapet#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जप|जपः<BR>जप m. (r. जप् s. अ) submissâ voce dictae preces. R. Schl. I.25.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जभ्<BR>1. जभ् 1. P. (यमने K. जभने V.) refraenare, cohibere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जभ्<BR>2. जभ् 1. A. (गात्रविनामे K. जृम्भे V.) oscitare; cf. 2. {#jamB,<BR>jfmB#}. (Lith. is-si-źoju os aperio, źó-tis rima, fissura,<BR>źếpsa patet, źopsnu os apertum habeo, źoplys os<BR>apertum.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जम्<BR>1. जम् 1. P. (अदने K. भक्षे V.) edere. (Cf. {#cam, Jam,<BR>jim#}; hib. diamann «food, sustenance», v. जमन;<BR>gion «the mouth»; germ. vet. gouma, kouma coena,<BR>prandium, convivium, pastus; gaumo palatum, faux,<BR>guttur. gaumian, gaumôn, epulari.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जम्<BR>2. जम् Indecl. uxor in comp. जम्पती uxor et conjux. (जम्<BR>e जन् ortum esse videtur, e vi euphon. sequentis labialis;<BR>cf. hib. gamh «a woman», gr.<BR>γαμέω, ἄγαμος, γαμέτις.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जमदग्नि|जमदग्निः<BR>जमदग्नि nom. pr. (BAH. e जमत् edens et अग्नि ignis)<BR>Sanctus quidam, Paraśurâmi pater. MAH. 1.2611.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जमन|जमनं<BR>जमन n. (r. जम् s. अन)<BR>1) actio edendi.<BR>2) cibus. (Hib.<BR>diamann «food, sustenance».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जम्बाल|जंबाल|जंबालः|जम्बालः<BR>जम्बाल m. n. lutum, argilla. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जम्बु|जंबु|जम्बुः<BR>जम्बु f. nomen arboris (Wils.: The rose apple - Eugenia<BR>Jambu). N. 12.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=135-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

