जल|जलं|जलः<BR>जल (ut videtur, partim a r. जल्, partim a गल् fluere, s.<BR>अ) Adj.<BR>1) frigidus.<BR>2) mente captus, turbatus, stupidus,<BR>stultus, cf. जड. - Subst. n.<BR>1) frigus.<BR>2) (a r. गल्<BR>fluere?) aqua, saepissime. (Cf. lat. gelu, goth. kalds frigidus;<BR>lith. szála gelascit, su-szalú frigore necor, szaltas<BR>frigidus; russ. холодный cholodnyĭ id.; hib. gil<BR>aqua.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=136-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

