जष्<BR>जष् 1. P. (हिंसायाम् K. वधे V.) laedere, occidere. (Cf.<BR>जस्, झष्, जूष्, झूष्, कष्, खष्, चष्; hib. gus<BR>mors.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जस्<BR>1. जस् 4. P. (मोक्षणे K. मोक्षे V.) dimittere, liberare. K.:<BR>जस्यति वत्सङ् गोपः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जस्<BR>2. जस् 10. P. जासयामि (हिंसायाम् K. वधे अनादरे V.)<BR>laedere, occidere, spernere. (V. उज्जासन, जसुरि,<BR>et cf. जष् etc.; goth. fra-qvistja, us-qvistja deleo, vasto,<BR>fra-qvistna perdor; fortasse lat. vasto e guasto.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

