जागृ<BR>जागृ 2. P. (forma redupl., quae Intensivorum speciem prae<BR>se fert; v. gr. 108.) vigilare. H. 1.51.; BH. 2.69.: {#yA<BR>niSA sarvaBUtAnAn tasyAY jAgArti samyamI . yasyAY<BR>jAgrati BUtAni sA niSA paSyato muneH#}; c.<BR>loc. vel accus. rei cujus causâ alqs vigilat vel a quâ sibi<BR>cavet, quam custodit. RAGH. 8.23.: {#Satruzuce 'ndriyezuca<BR>…jAgratO#}; ĆAUR. 35.: {#naKapadaM stanamaRqale yad dattam…jAgarti<BR>rakzati vilokayati#}. — Caus. expergefacere.<BR>HIT. 50.4.: कथं स्वामिनन् न जागरयसि.<BR>(Gr. (γ)εγείϱω; lat. vigil, vigilo, e guigil, guigilo? mutato<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">Page137-b+ 36</a>]<BR>r in l et abjectâ initiali gutturali, sicut in vivo pro guivo<BR>= जीवामि; sic etiam germ. vet. wachar vigil e quachar<BR>vel huachar explicandum esse censeo; wachal id., mutato<BR>r in l, sicut in lat. vigil; abjectâ finali radicis syllabâ:<BR>wachêm vigilo, goth. waka; fortasse etiam hib. mosgalaim<BR>vigilo huc pertinet, ita ut in mos-galaim dissolvendum<BR>sit; nescio tamen, unde deduci possit syllaba mos.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जाड्य|जाड्यं<BR>जाड्य n. (a जड s. य)<BR>1) frigus.<BR>2) stultitia. BHAR. 2.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जात|जातं<BR>जात (Part. pass. r. जन् s. त)<BR>1) natus.<BR>2) n. species, genus,<BR>classis, tribus. RAGH. 5.1. 11.71. (Huc trahimus<BR>nostrum Kin-d, ratione habitâ, scr. जात mutilatum esse<BR>e जन्त; lith. gentis cognatus, attenuato a in i.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जातपुत्र<BR>जातपुत्र (BAH. e praec. et पुत्र filius) natos filios habens,<BR>in fem. quae filios peperit. BR. 2.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जातमन्मथ<BR>जातमन्मथ (BAH. e जात et मन्मथ m. amor) natum amorem<BR>habens, amore captus, amans, c. loc. rei. IN. 4.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जातरूप|जातरूपं<BR>जातरूप n. (natam formam, pulchritudinem habens.<BR>BAH. e जात et रूप) aurum. R. Schl. I.38.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जातवेदस्<BR>जातवेदस् m. (natos Vêdos habens, qui Vêdos genuit,<BR>e जात et वेदस् Collect. Vêdi)<BR>1) cognomen dei Agnis.<BR>(*)<BR>2) ignis. MAH. 1.883. RAGH. 12.104. 15.72.<BR>(*) Wils.: One legend makes the Vêdas to have issued<BR>from the mouth of Agni.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जातस्नेह<BR>जातस्नेह (BAH. e जात et स्नेह amor, desiderium) natum<BR>amorem, desiderium habens, desiderio captus, desiderans<BR>c. loc. BR. 1.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जाति|जातिः<BR>जाति f. (r. जन् s. ति cf. जात<BR>1) nativitas, natales, origo.<BR>R. Schl. I.59.18.<BR>2) familia, stirps, genus, species, tribus,<BR>classis. N. 13.25. 55. DR. 4.16. SU. 2.8. (Lat. gens<BR>e gen-ti-s, servatâ nasali, quam scr. जाति, e जन्ति, expulit;<BR>lith. pri-gentis f. natura.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जातीय|जातीयः<BR>जातीय (a praec. s. ईय) gentilicius. R. Schl. II.15.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जातु<BR>जातु (fortasse a stirpe interr. क, mutatâ tenui gutt. in mediam<BR>palat.; cf. चित्) Adv. unquam, praecipue in constructione<BR>cum न occurrit, ad exprimendum nunquam.<BR>H. 2.20. 4.44.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=137-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जात्य|जात्यः<BR>जात्य (a जाति s. य) generosus, nobilis, excellens, praestans.<BR>RAGH. 17.4. R. Schl. II.9.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जानपद|जानपदः<BR>जानपद m. (a जनपद s. अ) rusticus. N. 26.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जानि<BR>जानि f. (ut mihi videtur, a जन vir, productâ vocali अ, sicut<BR>in नारी a नर, adjecto signo fem. ई, quod correptum<BR>est in इ) uxor. RAGH. 15.61. PAN. V.4.134. (Hoc<BR>vocabulum accuratius quam जनि cum goth. qvêns, Th.<BR>qvêni, uxor convenit, quum goth. ê praeter ô respondeat<BR>scrto आ; v. gr. comp. 69.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जानु<BR>जानु n. genu. N. 19.21. जानु दातुम् genu imponere<BR>alicui. DR. 9.5.: तस्य जानु ददौ. (Lat. genu, gr. γόνυ,<BR>goth. kniu, Th. kniva, nostrum Knie; fortasse etiam hib.<BR>glun, insertâ liquidâ; slav. коΛѣно koljeno, lith.<BR>kiélis.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जापय्<BR>जापय् Caus. radicis जि, gr. 521.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जामातृ<BR>जामातृ m. (ut mihi videtur, e जा pro जाया et मातृ mater,<BR>qui uxoris matrem tanquam matrem suam habet)<BR>gener. (Lat. gener, nisi directe venit a rad. GEN,<BR>ita ut genitorem significet, separari possit in ge-ner =<BR>जानर uxoris (i. e. filiae) vir, correpto आ in ĕ; etiam<BR>gr. γά-μβϱος ad जानर reduxerim, mutatâ dentali nasali<BR>in labialem, quam ab rem δ euphonicum, quod in<BR>ἀνδϱίς etc. videmus, transierit in μ; cf. μεσημβϱία.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जामि|जामिः<BR>जामि f.<BR>1) soror.<BR>2) casta mulier. AM. cf. जम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जाया<BR>जाया f. (r. जन् s. य in fem.) uxor. RAGH. 2.1. 7.68.; v. जामातृ.<BR>(Cf. lat. Gâja, v. «Vocalismus» p. 207.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जाम्बूनद|जांबूनद|जांबूनदं|जाम्बूनदं<BR>जाम्बूनद n. aurum. (Wils.: E जम्बुनदी (*) a river flowing<BR>from mount Sumêru, the Indian Pactolus, and<BR>अ aff.) DR. 7.7. A. 2.5. Ejus originis mythus exponitur<BR>RAM. I.31.49.<BR>(*) Potius jambûnadî, scribitur enim quoque jambû<BR>pro jambu.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जायु|जायुः<BR>जायु m. medicamentum. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जार|जारः<BR>जार m. (fortasse e जा pro जाया, v. जामातृ, et र a r. रम्,<BR>abjecto म्) adulter, amasius adulterinus. (Goth. hôrs,<BR>Th. hôra moechor, nostrum Hure.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जाल|जालं|जालः<BR>जाल n. (r. जल् tegere)<BR>1) rete. HIT. 9.14.; transl. turba,<BR>multitudo, copia. A. 10.29. RAGH. 9.27. 10.62.<BR>2) fenestra.<BR>RAGH. 6.43.<BR>3) flos non aperta.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जालक|जालकं|जालकः<BR>जालक n. (a praec. s. क) id. RAGH. 9.43. 68. Lass. 63.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जाल्म|जाल्मः<BR>जाल्म m. (ut videtur, a r. जल् s. म)<BR>1) crudelis, severus,<BR>ferox, durus.<BR>2) homo vilis, abjectus, nebulo. MR. 251.13.<BR>(Hib. galmha «hardness, hardihood, rigour, valour».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जाह्नवी<BR>जाह्नवी f. (a जह्नु s. अ in fem.) cognomen Gangae, v.<BR>जह्नुतनया.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जाह्नवीय<BR>जाह्नवीय (a praec. s. ईय) ad Gangem pertinens. RAGH. 10.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जि|जिः<BR>जि 1. P. जयामि, praet. redupl. जिगय, जिगाय, gr. 443.)<BR>1) vincere, expugnare. BH. 2.6.: {#nacE 'tad vidmaH kataran<BR>no garIyo yad vA jayema yadi vA no jayeyuH#};<BR>11.34.: जेतासि रणे सपत्नान्; N. 7.5.: {#akzadyUte nalaY<BR>jetA BavAn#}; SU. 2.9.: सर्वाम् महीञ् जेतुम्.<BR>2) ludendo auferre ab alquo, eludere aliquem aliquid, c.<BR>acc. pers. et rei; Pass. c. nom. pers. et accus. rei. N. 3.5.:<BR>जित्वा राज्यन् नलन् नृपम्; 12.83.: {#jito rAjyam<BR>vasUnica#}; cf. Stenzler. ad Kumâra Sambh. p. 111.<BR>Caus. जापयामि (v. gr. 521.) vincere jubere. SAK. 29.4.infr., PASS.:<BR>न मे हस्तः प्रसरति वाङ्मात्रेण जाप्यसे.<BR>- Desid. जिगीषामि; BH. 10.38.: {#nItir asmi<BR>jigIzatAm#}. (Fortasse lith. galu possum, galybế potestas,<BR>ap-galu, per-galu supero, vinco, pergalế victoria,<BR>quorum l a य् τοῦ जयामि deduci potest - v. gr. comp. 20.<BR>- sicut in nostro Leber = यकृत् jecur, ἧπαϱ, et<BR>prâcr. लट्टी = scr. यष्टि (Lass. gr. prâcr. 195.), et sicut<BR>r pro य् invenitur in hib. treigim relinquo = त्यजामि;<BR>hib. gar «profit, advantage, gain, good».)<BR>c. अव recuperare. MAH. 1.7765.: अवजित्यच तद् धनम्.<BR>c. नि i. q. simpl. SU. 2.7.: {#tAv indralokan nijitya<BR>yakzarakzogaRAMs tataH#}.<BR>c. निस् id. RAM. I.50.28.: कामक्रोधाव् अनिर्जित्य; N. 12.47.:<BR>निर्जितारिगण; 13.58.: द्यूते स निर्जितः; victoriâ [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=139-a" target="_blank">Page139-a+ 37</a>]<BR>acquirere. MAH. 1.152.: {#yadA 'SrOzam drOpadIM raNgamaDye<BR>lakzyam BittvA nirjitAm arjunena#}.<BR>c. निस् praef. वि id. MAN. 11.205.: विवादे विनिर्जित्य.<BR>c. परा id. DEV. 2.2.: {#asurEr mahAvIryEr devasEnyam<BR>parAjitam#}; N. 26.19.: {#ekapARena vIreRa nalena sa<BR>parAjita#}. Praet. multf. ATM. MAH. 1.6378.: {#droRaH parAjEzwa<BR>mAM sa saKivigrahe (parAjezwa?)#}.<BR>c. वि P. A. id. SU. 2.8.: सर्वा म्लेच्छजातीर् विजिग्यतुः;<BR>MAH. 1.2268.: दक्षिणां सहदेवस् तु विजिग्ये; RAGH. 12.104.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=138-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जिगीष्<BR>जिगीष् Desid. r. जि, v. gr. 544.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=139-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जिगीषु<BR>जिगीषु (a praec. s. उ, gr. 645.) vincendi cupidus. RAM. I.36.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=139-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

