जिम्<BR>जिम् 1. P. (अदने K. भक्षे V.) edere; cf. जम्, चम् et v.<BR>जेमन.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=139-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

