जिष्णु|जिष्णुः<BR>जिष्णु (fem. -ष्णु, r. जि s. स्नु; v. gr. 645. s. स्नु)<BR>1) Adj. vincens,<BR>victoriosus. RAGH. 4.85. 10.18.<BR>2) cognomen Arjuni.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=139-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

