जीव्<BR>जीव् 1. P. A. vivere. N. 11.17.: जीवत्व् असुखजीविकाम्;<BR>H. 1.39.: स जीवेत सुखं लोके. — न जीवितुम्<BR>mori. SA. 5.99.: {#purA mAtuH pitur vA 'pi yadi<BR>paSyAmi vipriyam . na jIvizye#}. — Caus. facere ut<BR>alqs reviviscat, vitam recipiat. MAH. 1.1994.: {#vfkzam<BR>jIvayAmAsa#}; 1995.: पार्थिवञ् जीवयिष्यति. (*) — [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=140-a" target="_blank">Page140-a+ 33</a>]<BR>Desid. जिजीविषामि. BH. 2.6.: {#yAn eva hatvA na jijIvizAmas<BR>te 'vasTitAH pramuKe#}. (Lith. gywénu vivo,<BR>gywas vivus, slav. живᴕ schivû vivo; goth. qvivs vivus,<BR>germ. vet. queh, anglo-sax. cvic vivus, mutato v in<BR>gutturalem, sicut in lat. vic-si, vic-tum, gr. comp. 19.;<BR>nostrum queck in Quecksilber, er-quicke recreo; lat. vivo<BR>e guivo, abjectâ gutturali, servato v euphonico, cui respondet<BR>β τοῦ βίος, βιόω, cf. ज्या nervus arcûs, cum<BR>quo convenit βιός; ζάω correptum esse videtur e ζιϜάω<BR>tanquam Denominativum, cui responderet scr. जीवयामि<BR>a जीव vita.)<BR>c. अनु vivendo sequi alqm. SA. 5.94.: जीवन्ताव् अनुजीवामि;<BR>RAGH. 19.15.: अन्वजीवद् अमरालकेश्वरौ<BR>(Ed. Calc. अत्यजीवद्; quod Schol. explicat per {#atikramya<BR>jIvitavAn tato 'py utkfzwajIvita AsIt#}.)<BR>c. उप<BR>1) obsequi, obedire c. acc. pers. MAN. 9.105.: {#SezAs<BR>tam upajIveyuH#}; MAH. 2.1625.: {#bAnDavAs tvo<BR>'pajIvantu sahasrAkzam ivA 'marAH#}. Pass. RAM. III.76.58.:<BR>सुजीवं नित्यशस् तेन यः परैर् उपजीव्यते.<BR>2) c.<BR>acc. rei exsequi, perficere, observare. MAN. 10.74.: {#te<BR>samyag upajIveyuH zaw karmARi#}.<BR>3) c. ablat. dependere<BR>ab alquo. RAM. III.76.58.: {#tena tu durjIvaM yaH parAd<BR>upajIvati#}.<BR>c. उप praef. प्रति reviviscere, vitam recipere. Mr. 122.3.infr.:<BR>प्रत्युपजीविता ऽस्मि.<BR>c. वि id. MAH. 1.2002.: {#dvijapraBAvAd rAjendra vyajIvat<BR>sa vanaspatiH#}.<BR>c. सम् i. q. simpl. N. 26.25.: सञ्जीव शरदां शतम्; DR. 9.4.:<BR>पुनः सञ्जीवमानस्य. — Caus. facere ut alqs reviviscat,<BR>in vitam revocare. RAGH. 12.74.: सीताम्…समजीवयत्.<BR>- Desid. formae causalis MAH. 1.2012.:<BR>सञ्जिजीवयिषु in vitam revocandi cupidus.<BR>(*) In recentioribus libris invenitur forma caus. anomala<BR>jîvâpayâmi (Lass. XVIII.6.9. 14.16.), cujus analogiam<BR>sequuntur Prâcritae formae ut môâbêhi (UR. XX.12.), quod<BR>sanscrite sonaret môćâpaya; cf. Lass. Institut. linguae<BR>Prâcr. p. 360.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=139-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जीव|जीवः<BR>जीव (r. जीव् s. अ)<BR>1) Adj. vivus. DR. 7.20.<BR>2) Subst. m.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=140-b" target="_blank">Page140-b+ 36</a>]<BR>vita. (Lith. gywas vivus; goth. qvivs, Th. qviva, lat. vivus;<BR>gr. βί(Ϝ)ος; hib. beo «living, alive».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=140-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

