जृभ्<BR>जृभ् 1. A. जर्भे hiare, aperire, expandere, os diducere, oscitare;<BR>v. sq. et cf. जभ्, जम्भ्. (Germ. vet. CHLUP<BR>findere, chliupu findo, attenuato अ τοῦ जर्भ् in u; germ.<BR>med. KLUB hiare, separari; transfindere; nostrum klaffe,<BR>Kluft; huc etiam traxerim goth. graba fodio, nostrum<BR>grabe, gr. γϱάϕω; hib. grabhaim «I carve, grave, insculp»,<BR>grafaim «I write, inscribe, scrape, grub», grafan<BR>«a grubbing-ax».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=141-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जृम्भ्|जृंभ्<BR>जृम्भ् 1. A. (scribitur जृभ्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>1) id. H. 2.6.: जृम्भमाण;<BR>PAR. BHAR. 3.4.: {#tfzRe jfmBasi pApakarmanirate<BR>nA 'dyA 'pi santuzyasi#}.<BR>2) laxare arcum. R. Schl. I.75.17.:<BR>तदा तु जृम्भितं शैवन् धनुर्…हूङ्कारेण;<BR>19.: जृम्भितन् तद् धनुर् दृष्ट्वा. V. जृभ्, जृम्भण.<BR>c. उत् hiare, aperire, se expandere. Lass. 69.5.: {#vasantaH<BR>santato 'jfmBetAnaNgaSfNgAraH#}.<BR>c. उत् praef. सम् conari, contendere. BHAR. 2.6.: {#vyAlam<BR>bAlamfRAlatantuBir asO rodDum ujjfmBate#}.<BR>c. वि hiare, se expandere; diffundi, dispergi. UR. {#rajanyAm<BR>vijfmBate madanavADA#}; RAGH. 3.19.: {#suKaSravA<BR>maNgalatUryanisvanAH…vyajfmBanta#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=141-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

