जेह्<BR>जेह् 1. A. (यत्ने. Fortasse forma redupl. a r. हि, abjecto इ)<BR>operam dare, niti.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=141-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

