ज्वर्<BR>ज्वर् 1. P. (रोगे) aegrotare, febrire. ĆAUR. 6.: दीर्घविरहज्वरिताङ्गयष्टि;<BR>ubi Schol. ज्वरित per पीडित explicat.<BR>(V. जूर्ति, ज्वर et cf. जॄ, जूर्, lat. ae-ger, v. जॄ;<BR>hib. gurt «pain, trouble, fierceness», v. जूर्ति; fortasse<BR>huc pertinet nostrum schwer, germ. vet. swâr et swâri<BR>gravis, germ. med. swâr, swœre gravis, molestus, tristis,<BR>aeger animi, mutatâ gutturali in sibilantem, vel abjectâ<BR>gutturali et deinde praefixo s euphonico, sicut nostrum<BR>schwätze, germ. med. swaze garrio cum वद् dicere cohaerere<BR>videtur; cf. germ. vet. var-wâzu maledico. Huc<BR>etiam referri possit nostrum Qual, quälen, mutato r<BR>in l.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ज्वर|ज्वरः<BR>ज्वर m. (a praec. s. अ) aegritudo, transl. molestia, difficultas,<BR>labor, dolor. BR. 1.15. N. 20.39. BH. 3.30. RAGH. 8.83.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ज्वल्<BR>ज्वल् 1. P. flammare, flagrare. IN. 1.6.: ज्वलितास्य; H. 4.48.:<BR>रोषज्वलन्. — Caus. accendere. SA. 5.78.:<BR>ततो ऽग्निम् आनयित्वे ऽह ज्वालयिष्यामि पावकम्.<BR>(Hib. guallaim «I blacken, burn», gual «coal, coals,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-b" target="_blank">Page144-b+ 32</a>]<BR>fire»; huc etiam nunc traxerim nostrum Kohle, germ.<BR>vet. colo, angl. coal, quae supra minus apte cum अङ्गार<BR>comparata sunt; fortasse lith. swelù amburo, ustulo, mutatâ<BR>gutturali in sibilantem; germ. vet. wallu ferveo,<BR>aestuo, bullio, walm fervor (aestatis), wâli tepor, abjectâ<BR>initiali gutturali, sicut in warm, v. घर्म; fortasse<BR>etiam lat. bullio huc pertinet, mutato v in b, sicut in bis<BR>= द्विस्.)<BR>c. प्र P. A. id. IN. 5.26.: प्रजज्वलमानेषु अग्निषु; N. 23.13.:<BR>अथ प्रज्वलितस् तत्र सहसा हव्यवाहनः; DR. 6.28.:<BR>क्रोधः प्रजज्वाल. - प्रज्वलित flammans. A. 13.38.<BR>Caus. accendere. HIT.: दीपम् प्रज्वाल्य.<BR>c. वि praef. अभि id. BH. 11.28.: वक्त्राण्य् अभिविज्वलन्ति.<BR>c. सम् Caus. accendere. SA. 6.25.: अग्निन् तत्र सञ्ज्वाल्य.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ज्वल|ज्वलः<BR>ज्वल (r. ज्वल् s. अ) flagrans. H. 2.7. BHAR. 1.95.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ज्वलन|ज्वलनः<BR>ज्वलन (r. ज्वल् s. अन)<BR>1) Adj. flammans, flagrans. A. 10.43.<BR>2) Subst. n. flamma. BH. 11.29.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ज्वलानन<BR>ज्वलानन (BAH. e praec. et आनन n. vultus) flagrantem<BR>vultum habens. H. 2.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ज्वलित|ज्वलितः<BR>ज्वलित (r. ज्वल s. त)<BR>1) flagrans, flammans, v. ज्वल्.<BR>2) n. splendor. RAGH. 8.83. (Aut huc aut ad गौर flavus<BR>trahi posset nostrum Gold, ita ut aut a flavo colore aut<BR>a splendore dictum sit, servatâ initiali mediâ (gr. comp. 92.),<BR>quae in voce Kohle secundum generalem legem<BR>in tenuem se convertit; v. कनक a कन् splendere.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ज्वलितास्य<BR>ज्वलितास्य (BAH. e praec. et आस्य vultus) flagrantem<BR>vultum habens. IN. 1.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ज्वाल|ज्वालः<BR>ज्वाल m. (r. ज्वल् s. अ) flamma. AM.; v. sq. (Hib. gual m.<BR>«coal, coals, fire»; v. ज्वल्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=144-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

