झला<BR>झला f.<BR>1) lux solis, lux splendida, splendor.<BR>2) filia. MED.<BR>(Cf. ज्वल्, hib. gal m. «heat», galla f. «fairness,<BR>brightness, beauty», gallad «a lass, a young girl»; sic<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=145-b" target="_blank">Page145-b+ 17</a>]<BR>scr. युवन् a splendore dictum esse videtur, ita ut e द्युवन्<BR>mutilatum sit, cf. द्युवन् sol a दिव् splendere.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=145-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

