तस्<BR>तस् 1. et 10. P. (अलङ्कारे K. अलङ्कृतौ V.; scribitur तस्,<BR>gr. 110^a).) ornare; v. अवतंस. (Boruss. vet. teisint<BR>honorare, teisi honor.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=146-3a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तक्<BR>तक् 1. P. (सहनहासयोः K. सहने हासे V.) sustinere,<BR>perferre; ridere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=146-3a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तक्ष्<BR>तक्ष् 1. et 5. P.<BR>1) frangere, dissecare, findere. MAH. 3.1585.:<BR>शरैस् ततक्षाते परस्परम्; 4.1883.: {#anyonyan<BR>tatakzur izuBiH#}.<BR>2) in dial. Vêd. facere, fabricari.<BR>RIGV. 32.2.: त्वष्टा ऽस्मै वज्रं स्वर्यन् ततक्ष<BR>«Tvashtris ei telum laude dignum paravit»; 20.2.;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=146-3b" target="_blank">Page146-3b+ 11</a>]<BR>52.7.; 61.6.; 111.1. (Lith. taszau dolo, ascio;<BR>russ. tesatj dolare; polon. ćieśla faber lignarius, v. sq.;<BR>lat. tig-num, cf. Pott. I.270.; boruss. vet. tikint facere,<BR>tikinnimai facimus, teikusna creatio, creatura; gr.<BR>ΤΕΚ, τίϰτω, τέϰνον, τεύχω.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=146-3a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तक्षन्<BR>तक्षन् m. (r. तक्ष् s. अन्) faber lignarius, v. तक्ष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=146-3b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तङ्क्|तंक्<BR>1. तङ्क् 1. A. (गतौ K. scribitur तक्, gr. 110^a).) ire. (V.<BR>टिक् et cf. hib. teicheamh «a going, passage», tochamhlaim<BR>«I march», tochar «a causeway, pavement»,<BR>toichim «going, departing»; lith. tekù curro, tákas semita,<BR>tekûnas cursor; slav. tekû curro.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=146-3b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तङ्क्|तंक्<BR>2. तङ्क् 1. P. (कृच्छ्रजीवने K. दौष्ठ्ये V.; scribitur तक्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>in miseriâ vivere; v. आतङ्क.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तङ्ग्|तंग्<BR>तङ्ग् 1. P. (स्खलने K. कम्पे गते V.; scribitur तग्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>vacillare, ire. (V. टिक् et cf. hib. tagaidh<BR>«come ye on, advance», tigim «I come, go, consent».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तञ्च्|तंच्<BR>1. तञ्च् 1. P. (गतौ K. इतौ V.) ire.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तञ्च्|तंच्<BR>2. तञ्च् 7. P. तनच्मि (सङ्कुचि) curvare, inflectere; v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तञ्ज्|तंज्<BR>तञ्ज् 7. P. तनज्मि (सङ्कोचे) id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तट्<BR>1. तट् 1. P. (उच्छ्राये K. उच्छ्रये V.) surgere; extollere,<BR>sublevare. (Fortasse lith. tếsiu levo, erigo, mutato<BR>t in s.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तट्<BR>2. तट् 10. P. ताटयामि (आहतौ) percutere, ferire; cf.<BR>तड्, तुड्, तुद्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तट|तटं|तटः<BR>तट m. n. (r. तट् surgere s. अ)<BR>1) ripa. HIT. 126.9.<BR>2) montis planities. UR. 41.5.<BR>3) clunis. IN. 2.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तटिनी<BR>तटिनी f. (a praec. s. इन् in fem.) fluvius.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तड्<BR>तड् 10. P. pulsare, ferire, percutere, tundere. MAN. 4.164.:<BR>शिष्ट्यर्थन् ताडयेत् तु तौ; 8.299.: {#tAqyAH syU<BR>rajvA#}; MAH. 1.2368. 5302.: तम् पदा ऽताडयत्; DR. 9.3.:<BR>शिरो गृहीत्वा राजानन् ताडयामास; A. 3.21.: {#atAqayaM<BR>SareRA 'Ta tad BUtam#}; 27.: {#tAnicA 'sya SarIrARi<BR>SarEr aham atAqayam#}. (V. {#taRq, tuq, tuRq,<BR>tud#} et cf. hib. tathaim «I kill, destroy», tathog «a<BR>clash, a slap».)<BR>c. वि i. q. simpl. MAH. 1.8273.: देवान् व्यताडयेतां शरैः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तडाग|तडागं|तडागः<BR>तडाग n. piscina, lacus. N. 12.8.; 13.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तडित्<BR>तडित् f. (r. तड् s. इत्) fulmen.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तडित्वत्|तडित्वन्त्<BR>तडित्वत् (a praec. s. वत्) fulmine praeditus. UR. 9.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तण्ड्|तंड्<BR>तण्ड् 1. A. (scribitur तड्, gr. 110^a).) i. q. तड्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तण्डुल|तंडुल|तंडुलः|तण्डुलः<BR>तण्डुल m. (r. तण्ड् s. उल) frumenti granum, praecipue<BR>oryzae. HIT. 14.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्<BR>1. तत् (Them. त, Nom. m. स, सो, सः, f. सा, n. तत्, v.<BR>gr. 267.) is, hic, ille; repetitum, hic et ille. SA. 6.20.:<BR>तांस् तान् विगणयन्न् अर्थान्. — Ad respondendum<BR>ad repetitum relativum (यो यः quicunque) etiam demonstrativum<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-b" target="_blank">Page147-b+ 37</a>]<BR>repetitur, e. c. N. 5.12.: {#yaM yaM hi dadfSe tezAn<BR>tan tam mene nalan nfpam#}; BH. 3.21.: {#yad yad Acarati<BR>SrezWas tat tad eve 'taro janaH#}. — Interdum ad<BR>orationis vim augendam in constructione cum aliis pronominibus<BR>ponitur, tam tertiae quam secundae vel primae<BR>personae; e. c. {#sA 'haN kamalagarBABam apaSyantI<BR>hfdi priyam . na vindAmi#}. Interdum ad personam<BR>non separatim expressam, sed verbi terminatione indicatam<BR>refertur; e. c. N. 12.85.: {#sA vanAni girIMScE<BR>'va…vicarAmi#}. De adverbiali hujus pronominis usu v.<BR>p. 39. s. v. इदम्. — Interdum तत् in initio compositorum,<BR>quae cum alio antecedente vocabulo conjuncta sunt,<BR>redundat; e. c. Lass. 32.12.: भर्तृतद्गतमानसा = भर्तृगतमानसा,<BR>nam तत् h. l., ut recte observat Lassenius,<BR>nil aliud valet, quam भर्तृ; v. तत्पर. (Lith. tas hic,<BR>tá haec; goth. THA (Them. articuli masc. et neut.),<BR>Nom. masc. sa = स, fem. sô = सा; gr. ΤΟ, ΤᾹ, ὁ, ̔ᾱ, τό;<BR>slav. ΤΟ, ΤᾹ, nom. t̕ hic, ta haec, to hoc; lat.<BR>is-te, is-ta, is-tud, tam, tum, tunc. Hib. so hic = स.<BR>Sé is, er; si ea, sie, et ti is, is qui ad स्य, त्य pertinere<BR>videntur; v. त्यत् et gramm. comp. §§. 343. sq. 353. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्<BR>2. तत् (Acc. neut. praec.)<BR>1) ideo. N. 17.43.<BR>2) in recentioribus<BR>scriptis sicut nostrum so ad particulam conditionalem<BR>respondet. Lass. 43.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत|ततं|ततः<BR>तत v. तन्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ततस्<BR>ततस् Adv. (a stirpe त, gr. 267., s. तस्)<BR>1) inde, ab hoc<BR>tempore. N. 20.34., sequente पश्चात् postea, H. 4.16.<BR>Hinc frequentissime tum, deinde. H. 4.26. N. 1.20.<BR>2) in<BR>constructione cum comparativo ablativi तस्मात् substantive<BR>positi locum tenet. H. 1.37. BR. 1.8. 18.<BR>3) cum vi<BR>accusat. illuc. BR. 1.20. — Post इतस् q. v. vel accusativi<BR>vel locativi vim habet, illuc, illic. N. 10.4. DR. 8.25.<BR>4) repetitum, iterum iterumque. N. 11.19.<BR>5) in<BR>apodosi respondet ad यदि. Lass. 45.2. 77.14. (Gr.<BR>τόϑεν, slav. ot-tûdû; v. gr. comp. §. 421.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्क्षणात्<BR>तत्क्षणात् Adv. (e तत् et ablat. क्षणात्) eodem momento,<BR>statim. N. 23.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=147-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्त्व|तत्त्वं<BR>तत्त्व vel तत्व n. cf. gr. 633. (a pronom. neut. तत् id,<BR>hoc, illud, s. त्व)<BR>1) veritas. DR. 2.5. N. 16.38. BH. 3.28.<BR>2) natura, vera natura. N. 19.2. 28. A. 4.37. BH. 18.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्त्वतस्<BR>तत्त्वतस् Adv. (a praec. s. तस्) secundum veritatem, veram<BR>naturam; accurate, penitus. BH. 4.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्पर|तत्परः<BR>तत्पर (hunc, hanc, hoc, hos etc. tanquam praecipuum<BR>habens. BAH. e तत् et पर n., v. gr. §. 666.)<BR>plane addictus, plane deditus, in fine compp. ubi तत् redundat,<BR>e. c. N. 16.26.: ध्यानतत्पर = ध्यानपर meditationi<BR>addictus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्परता<BR>तत्परता f. (a praec. s. ता) Abstractum praec. HIT. 128.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्र<BR>तत्र (a stirpe pronominali त s. त्र)<BR>1) ibi, hic, illic. IN. 1.6.<BR>— Pro locat. तस्मिन्. BR. 1.22. (तत्र वासे i. e. {#tasmin<BR>vAse#} in hac habitatione, cf. एकत्र). {#tatra<BR>tatra#} hic et illic, ubique. IN. 2.31. SU. 1.33. N. 17.36.<BR>2) illuc, in illum locum. H. 2.16. BR. 2.3. (Cf. goth.<BR>thathrô inde, v. gr. comp. §. 420.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्रत्य|तत्रत्यः<BR>तत्रत्य (a praec. s. त्य) qui illic est, dortig. HIT. 88.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्रभवत्|तत्रभवन्त्<BR>तत्रभवत् m. (e तत्र illic et भवत्) in linguâ scenicâ excellens,<BR>praeclarus, dominus, de persona absente, (ita<BR>अत्रभवत् de personâ praesente «der Vortreffliche<BR>hier»). UR. 15.12.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्रभवती<BR>तत्रभवती Fem. praec. UR. 15.11.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तत्व|तत्वं<BR>तत्व v. तत्त्व.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तथा<BR>तथा (e stirpe pronom. त, s. था) sic, ita. DR. 4.1.; tam.<BR>H. 3.3. A. 7.13. — Particula assentiendi ita, vero, sane.<BR>H. 4.59. SU. 3.22. Repetitum respondet ad यथा यथा<BR>(quomodocunque). N. 8.14. — तथा ऽपि nihilominus,<BR>tamen. HIT. 11.5. 15.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तथ्य|तथ्यं<BR>तथ्य (a praec. s. य) Adj. verus. Subst. n. verum. N. 5.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तद्<BR>तद् v. तत्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तदनन्तर<BR>तदनन्तर (TATP. e तत् et अनन्तर intervalli expers, proximus)<BR>ejus proximus. N. 22.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तदा<BR>तदा Adv. (a stirpe pronom. त s. दा) illo tempore, tunc.<BR>H. 1.15. — Respondet ad यदा quando. BH. 2.52. 4.7.<BR>DR. 5.18. — Saepe redundat, ubi in narrationibus eventus<BR>tempus definit, quod jam aliis temporis adverbiis sufficienter<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-b" target="_blank">Page148-b+ 37</a>]<BR>indicatum est. H. 1.30. N. 20.3. — In apodosi<BR>post यदि valet nostrum s o. Lass. 7.13.: {#yady ezA mama<BR>BAryA Bavati tadA jIvAmi#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तदानीम्<BR>तदानीम् (v. gr. 652. s. दानीम् et cf. इदानीम्) tunc.<BR>DR. 6.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तदीय<BR>तदीय (a तत् s. ईय, v. gr. 288.)<BR>1) qui ejus, hujus, illius,<BR>eorum, earum est. RAGH. 2.28.<BR>2) i. q. primitivum तत्,<BR>e. c. RAGH. 1.81.: सुतान् तदीयां सुरभेः कृत्वा प्रतिनिधिम्<BR>«filiam hanc»; P. 2.: {#tadIyam asti nO<BR>Danam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

