तनु|तनुः<BR>तनु (r. तन् s. उ)<BR>1) Adj. (fem. तनु, तनू, तन्वी) tenuis.<BR>DR. 7.7.<BR>2) Subst. f. n. corpus. DR. 6.20. IN. 1.33. (Gr.<BR>τανυ in initio compp.; lat. tenuis, adjecto i, v. गुरु; germ.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=149-a" target="_blank">Page149-a+ 37</a>]<BR>vet. dunni — Them. dunnja — nostrum dünn; hib.<BR>tana; russ. tonkiĭ; v. 1. तन्. Cum तनु corpus cf. slav.<BR>тѣΛо tjelo.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=148-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

