तन्त्र्|तंत्र्<BR>तन्त्र् 10. A. (scribitur तत्र्, gr. 110^a). sed videtur esse Denom.<BR>a तन्त्र, quod a तन् extendere) sustentare, praesertim<BR>familiam. SAK. 91.13.: {#prajAH prajAH svA iva<BR>tantrayitvA#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=149-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

