तर्ज्<BR>तर्ज् 1. P.<BR>1) minari. RAM. II.70.25.: तर्जद्भिर् इव वानरैः.<BR>2) reprehendere, conviciari. BHATT. 14.80.:<BR>तन् ततर्ज. — Cl. 10. P. A.<BR>1) minari c. acc. pers. et<BR>instr. rei RAGH. 4.28.: {#ahitAn anilodDUtEs tarjayann<BR>iva ketuBiH#}; 12.41.: {#aNkuSAkArayA 'NgulyA<BR>tAv atarjayat#}; MAH. 4.567.: {#iti bruvARA vAkyAni<BR>sA mAn nityam atarjayat#}.<BR>2) reprehendere, conviciari.<BR>RAM. II.58.24. परुषैर् वाक्यैस् तेन तर्जिता.<BR>(Fortasse huc pertinet germ. vet. TRUG, DRUK, triugu,<BR>driuku fallo.)<BR>c. अभि 10. A. i. q. simpl. MAH. 3.11716.: {#aBitarjayamAnASca<BR>ruvantaSca mahAravAn#}.<BR>c. सम् id. RAGH. 15.19.: इति सन्तर्ज्य शत्रुघ्नम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=151-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

