तिरस्कृ<BR>तिरस्कृ (r. कृ q. v. praef. तिरस्)<BR>1) obtegere. RAGH. 16.20.:<BR>तिरस्क्रियन्ते कृमितन्तुजालैः…गवाक्षाः; R. Schl. II.12.89.:<BR>{#kAlarAtrir me nUnam BAryArUpatiraskftA<BR>tvam rAjaputri#}.<BR>2) superare. RAGH. 3.8.: {#tadIyam<BR>AnIlamuKaM stanadvayam . tiraScakAra…sujAtayoH<BR>paNkajakoSayoH Sriyam#}; HIT. 81.8.: स तिरस्क्रियते ऽरिभिः.<BR>3) conviciari, contumeliam dicere. HIT. 13.11.: {#taM<BR>sarve tiraskurvanti#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=153-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

