तीव्<BR>तीव् 1. P. (स्थौल्ये) magnum, crassum, corpulentum, turgidum<BR>esse.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तीव्र|तीव्रं|तीव्रः<BR>तीव्र (r. तीव् s. र) magnus, violentus, vehemens, acer. N. 11.13.;<BR>24.8.: तीव्रशोक; M. 3.: तीव्रन् तपः; SU. 2.7.:<BR>तीव्रविक्रम; Lass. 58.17.: क्रोधतीव्रेण वह्निना.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तु<BR>1. तु 2. P. तौमि et तवीमि (PAN. VII.3.95.) crescere.<BR>RIGV. 94.2.: यस्मै त्वम् आयजसे…स तूताव<BR>«cui tu sacra perficis, is crescit». (Cambro-brit. tyv-u<BR>crescere; pers. توان tuvân potestas, توانم tuvânem possum;<BR>zend. tav posse, v. gr. comp. §. 538.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तु<BR>2. तु (fortasse a stirpe demonstrat. त, attenuato अ in उ, sicut<BR>in interrog. कु e क)<BR>1) vero, autem. IN. 3.5. 4.7.<BR>BR. 1.17. 3.18. N. 23.9.<BR>2) et, etiam. N. 25.14. BR. 3.22.<BR>A. 3.23. DR. 5.17.<BR>3) post pron. interrog. किम् valet<BR>nostrum doch. BR. 1.7. 35. 13.17.<BR>4) in apodosi post<BR>चेत् valet nostrum so. BR. 2.17.: {#taY ced ahan na<BR>ditseyam…pramaTyE 'nAM hareyus tu#}. — Enunciationem<BR>nunquam incipit.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुङ्ग|तुंग|तुङ्गः<BR>तुङ्ग (r. तुञ्ज् s. अ)<BR>1) Adj. altus. RAGH. 6.3.<BR>2) Subst. m.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">Page154-b+ 36</a>]<BR>arbor quaedam, Rottleria tinctoria. (Cf. lat. turgeo,<BR>liquidis n et r inter se mutatis, tu-mulus, tu-mor, tumeo;<BR>gr. τύ-λος; lith. tunkù pinguesco; russ. tućnyĭ pinguis,<BR>cf. Benfey II.235. I.591.; hib. tonngo «a billowy<BR>sea», tonnghail, tonnta «waved», tonnaim «I undulate,<BR>dip in water», nisi haec pertinent ad तरङ्ग fluctus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुच्छ|तुच्छं|तुच्छः<BR>तुच्छ inanis, vacuus. AM. (Lith. tuszćias id.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुज्<BR>तुज् 1. P. (in dial. vêd. 6. P. A.)<BR>1) ferire, vulnerare, occidere.<BR>RIGV. 61.6.: वृत्रस्य मर्म तुजन् वज्रेण तुजता.<BR>2) tremere. RIGV. 61.14.: {#asya BiyA dyAvAca<BR>BUmA tujete#}.<BR>3) festinare, properare. RIGV. 3.5. 61.12.:<BR>तूतुजान properans.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुञ्ज्<BR>1. तुञ्ज् 1. P. (हिंसाबलवेष्टनप्राणनेषु K. प्राणे बले V.;<BR>scribitur तुज्, gr. 110^a).) offendere, laedere, ferire,<BR>occidere; robustum esse; vestire; vivere (V. तुङ्ग).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुञ्ज्<BR>2. तुञ्ज् 10. P. (भाषट्टार्थे; scribitur तुज् gr. 110^a).) loqui;<BR>superare, occidere, ferire.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुट्<BR>तुट् 6. P. (कलहकर्मणि K. कलहे V.) rixari, altercari,<BR>contendere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुड्<BR>तुड् 1. 6. P. frangere, rumpere, lacerare, findere; occidere.<BR>Cf. तुण्ड्, तुद्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुड्ड्<BR>तुड्ड् 1. P. (अनादरे) contemnere, spernere. Cf. तूड्, तोड्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुण्<BR>तुण् 6. P. (कौटिल्ये K. जैह्म्ये V.) curvum, inflexum esse.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुण्ड्|तुंड्<BR>तुण्ड् 1. A. (scribitur तुड्, gr. 110^a).) id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुण्ड|तुंड|तुंडं|तुण्डं<BR>तुण्ड m. rostrum. M. 1.1474.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुत्थ्<BR>तुत्थ् 10. P. (स्तृतौ K.) sternere, obtegere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुद्<BR>तुद् 6. P. A. tundere, ferire, pungere. BHATT. 14.81.: {#tutoda<BR>gadayA 'rim#}; 15.4.: अतौत्सुः शूलैः; DR. 8.52.:<BR>अश्वांस् तुदन्तौ; MAH. 3.335.: प्रतोदेन तुद्यमान; 2.2530.:<BR>तुदसि मर्माणि वाक्शरैः. — Part. pass. तुन्न<BR>R. Schl. II.14.23.: तुन्न इव तीक्ष्णेन प्रतोदेनः. (Lat.<BR>TUD, tundo; goth. STAUT, stauta; nostrum stoʃse,<BR>praefixo s; fortasse e सन्तुद्.)<BR>c. आ i. q. simpl. MAH. 1.195.: धनुःकोट्यातुद्य वीरम्.<BR>c. वि id. MAH. 1.3559.: वाक्कण्टकैर् वितुदन् मानुषान्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=154-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुन्द्<BR>तुन्द् 1. P. (चेष्टायाम् K.; scribitur तुद्, gr. 110^a).) se movere,<BR>ire; operam dare, anniti. K.: तुन्दति सुखाय.<BR>Cf. त्रन्द्.<BR>c. नि discedere? RIGV. 58.1.: सहोजा अमृतो नितुन्दते<BR>«robore genitus immortalis discedit».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुन्द|तुंद|तुंदं|तुन्दं<BR>तुन्द n. venter. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुप्<BR>तुप् 1. 6. P. pulsare, ferire, occidere. (Cf. {#tump, tuP,<BR>tumP, tumb, tuB, trup, trump, truP, trumP#}; gr.<BR>ΤΥΠ, τύπτω).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुफ्<BR>तुफ् 6. P. id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुभ्<BR>तुभ् 1. A. 4. et 9. P. तोभे, तुभ्यामि, तुभ्नामि. id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुमुल|तुमुलं|तुमुलः<BR>तुमुल Adj.<BR>1) turbatus, perturbatus, confusus. A. 6.22.<BR>RAGH. 5.49. (Schol. = सङ्कुल.)<BR>2) tumultuosus. BH. 1.13. 19.<BR>A. 2.2. (Cf. lat. tumultus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुम्प्|तुंप्<BR>तुम्प् 1. P. et 10. P. (तुम्प् 10. scribitur तुप्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>i. q. तुप्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुम्फ्<BR>तुम्फ् 6. P. id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुम्ब्|तुंब्<BR>तुम्ब् 1. et 10. P. (अर्दने K. अर्दे V.; scribitur तुब्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>vexare. Cf. तुप्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुम्बुरु|तुंबुरु|तुंबुरुः|तुम्बुरुः<BR>तुम्बुरु m. nom. pr. Gandharvi. IN. 2.28.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुर्<BR>तुर् 3. P. तुतोर्मि properare (v. त्वर्, unde तुर् ejecto अ.<BR>Cf. द्रु).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुरग|तुरगः<BR>तुरग m. (celeriter iens e तुर, quod seorsim non invenitur,<BR>et ग) equus. RAGH. 1.42.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुरङ्गम|तुरंगम|तुरंगमः|तुरङ्गमः<BR>तुरङ्गम m. (e तुर in acc. et गम) id. A. 7.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुरासाह्<BR>तुरासाह् m. (Nom. तुराषाट्, e तुरा i. q. त्वरा et साह् perferens<BR>a r. सह्) cognomen Indri. RAGH. 15.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुरीय|तुरीयं|तुरीयः<BR>तुरीय (a चतुर्, abjectâ syllabâ initiali, s. ईय pro तीय, cf.<BR>द्वितीय, तृतीय) quartus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुर्य|तुर्य्य|तुर्य्यः<BR>तुर्य (e praec. ejecto ई) id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुर्व्<BR>तुर्व् 1. P. तूर्वामि (हिंसायाम् K. हिंसे V.) ferire, laedere,<BR>occidere; cf. थुर्व्, दुर्व्, धुर्व्, जूंर्व्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुल्<BR>तुल् 1. et 10. P. tollere, sublevare. RAM. I.54.15.: {#Danus<BR>tolayizyAmi pARinA#}. — Part. pass. तुलित<BR>sublevatus. RAGH. 4.80.: पौलस्त्यतुलितस्या ऽद्रेः; 12.89.:<BR>तुलितकैलाश. (Cf. दुल्, lat. tollo, tuli; gr.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">Page155-b+ 36</a>]<BR>πλάω, τελάμων, τάλαντον (v. तुला); goth. thula tolero;<BR>nostrum dulde; lith. turrù habeo, ap-turru adipiscor.)<BR>c. आ id. RAM. I.48.42.: न शेकुर् आतोलयितुम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुलय्<BR>तुलय् (Denom. a तुला) ponderare. MAH. 3.10583.: {#utkftya<BR>svayam mAMsan tulayAmAsa kapotena samam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुला<BR>तुला f. (r. तुल् s. अ in fem.)<BR>1) libra. HIT. 133.1.<BR>2) similitudo.<BR>RAGH. 5.68.; cum instr. ibd. 8.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुल्य|तुल्यः<BR>तुल्य (a praec. s. य) aequalis, similis, c. instr. N. 4.6. DR. 6.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुष्<BR>तुष् 4. P. gaudere, contentum esse. MAH. 3.1109.: {#tuzya<BR>mA kruDaH#}; 2.149.: तुतोष पूजाम् प्राप्य; A. 4.49.: {#nityan<BR>tuzwASca te rAjan prARinaH suraveSmani#}. C. instr.<BR>MAN. 12.37.: येन तुष्यतिचा ऽऽत्मा ऽस्य. C. gen. MAH. 1. 3017:<BR>{#karmasAkzI kzetrajYo yasya tuzyati, na tu tuzyati<BR>yasyE 'za puruzasya#}. C. loc. HIT. 40.7.: {#yasyAm BartA na<BR>tuzyati#}. C. acc. MAH. 1.4198.: न तुतोष पतिन् तदा.<BR>— Caus. exhilarare. N. 1.7.: तं स भीमः…तोषयामास…सत्कारेण;<BR>MAH. 3.9943.: तन् तोषय तपसा. (Cf.<BR>तूष्; lith. tếsziju recreo, reficio.)<BR>c. परि i. q. simpl. R. Schl. II.2.33.: उत्सवेषु परितुष्यति.<BR>— Caus. SA. 3.21.: भर्तारम् पर्यतोषयत्.<BR>c. सम् id. BH. 3.17.: आत्मनि सन्तुष्टः; 12.14. 19. — Caus.<BR>MAH. 3.13685.: गुरुं सन्तोषयेत; HIT. 25.16.: {#BojanaviSezEr<BR>vAyasan santozya#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुष|तुषः<BR>तुष m. folliculus, gluma oryzae etc. DR. 6.21. (cf. त्वच्<BR>tegere, त्वच् cutis, cortex.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुषार|तुषारः<BR>तुषार m. pruina, nix, gelu. RAGH. 9.68. 14.84.; R. Schl. I.49.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुष्टि|तुष्टिः<BR>तुष्टि f. (r. तुष् s. ति) gaudium, satisfactio. IN. 5.13. SA. 1.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुस्<BR>तुस् 1. P. (शब्दे K. ध्वाने V.) sonare. (Fortasse lat. tus-sis<BR>ex tus-tis.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुस्त|तुस्तं<BR>तुस्त n. pulvis. (Cf. angl. et anglo-sax. dust.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुह्<BR>तुह् 1. P. (अर्दने) vexare. Cf. 2. दुह्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुहिन|तुहिनं<BR>तुहिन n. pruina, nix, gelu. AM. (Hib. deigh «ice».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=155-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

तुहिनाद्रि|तुहिनाद्रिः<BR>तुहिनाद्रि m. (Schneeberg e praec. et अद्रि) i. q. हिमालय.<BR>RAGH. 8.53.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=156-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

