त्रङ्क्|त्रंक्<BR>त्रङ्क् 1. A. (गतौ; scribitur त्रक्, gr. 110^a).) ire; cf. {#taNk,<BR>tik, tOk, trOk, traNK, triNK, traNg#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=159-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

