त्रन्द्|त्रंद्<BR>त्रन्द् 1. P. (scribitur त्रद्, gr. 110^a).) i. q. तुन्द्, quod e<BR>त्रन्द् ortum esse videtur ejecto र् et attenuato अ in उ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=159-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

त्रप्<BR>त्रप् 1. A. pudere, praesertim c. praef. अप. (Fortasse primitive<BR>convertere, converti; cf. gr. τϱέπω, ἐντϱέπω<BR>pudore afficio; lith. trópiju ico; slav. trepet tremor; lat.<BR>trepido.)<BR>c. अप i. q. simpl. MAH. 3.110.: {#yenA 'patrapate sADur asADus<BR>tena tuzyati#}; 5.262.: {#krUreRa nA 'patrapase kaTaM<BR>Sakre 'ha karmaRA#}. (Cf. gr. ἀποτϱέπω.)<BR>c. अप praef. वि id. MAH. 2.1433.: {#viBIzakABir bahvIBir<BR>BIzayan sarvapArTivAn na vyapatrapase kasmAt#};<BR>R. Schl. II.37.10.: सा व्यपत्रपमाने ऽव. — PAR.<BR>ibd. II.57.28.: {#adye 'mam anayaN kftvA vyapatrapasi<BR>rAGava#}; c. gen. MAH. 1.4585.: व्यपत्रपन् मनुष्याणाम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=159-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

