त्रयोदशन्<BR>त्रयोदशन् (Comp. anom. pro त्रिदशन्; e त्रयस्, Nom. pl.<BR>m. τοῦ त्रि, et दशन्, v. gr. 254.) tredecim. (Lat. tredecim,<BR>lith. trylika e trydika, v. gr. comp. 319. annot.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=159-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

