दङ्घ्|दंघ्<BR>दङ्घ् 1. P. (scribitur दघ्, gr. 110^a).) id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=162-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दण्ड्|दंड्<BR>दण्ड् 10. P. (ut videtur, Denom. a दण्ड, quod fortasse ipsum<BR>a दम् s. ड, nisi a तड्, mutato त् in ड्; cf.<BR>Lass.) percutere, punire. N. 13.69. RAGH. 1.25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=162-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दण्ड|दंड|दंडं|दंडः|दण्डः<BR>दण्ड m. (v. praec.)<BR>1) baculus, sceptrum; poena. N. 4.10.<BR>DR. 6.20.<BR>2) plantae caulis. RAGH. 16.46.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=162-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

