दयालु|दयालुः<BR>दयालु m. f. n. (a praec. s. आलु) misericors, ad misericordiam<BR>propensus. HIT. 77.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=164-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

