दर्शन|दर्शनं<BR>दर्शन n. (r. दृश् s. अन)<BR>1) visus, conspectus; aspectus,<BR>species. A. 2.11. H. 2.5. N. 17.14.<BR>2) respectus, ratio.<BR>RAGH. 8.71.<BR>3) consilium, propositum, institutum. R. Schl. I.58.18.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=164-b" target="_blank">Page164-b+ 37</a>]<BR>— A formâ caus.<BR>1) monstratio. Lass. 87.3.<BR>2) speculum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=164-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

