दामन्<BR>दामन् n. (fortasse a r. दम् s. अन्, nisi a 2. दा vel दो s.<BR>मन्) funis; taenia, infula. UR. 5.9. H. 3.13. (Cf. gr.<BR>δέω, δια-δή-μα; hib. damhnadh «a band or tye».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=167-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

