दाय|दायः<BR>दाय n. (r. दा s. य) donum; portio. R. Schl. I.29.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=167-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दायाद|दायादः<BR>दायाद m. (e praec. et आद sumens, accipiens)<BR>1) filius.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=167-b" target="_blank">Page167-b+ 37</a>]<BR>MAH. 1.871.<BR>2) oriundus ab aliquo, proles, prognatus.<BR>R. Schl. I.60.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=167-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

