दिन|दिनं|दिनः<BR>दिन m. n. (a Lassenio apte e दिवन ejectâ syllabâ व explicatur,<BR>v. दिवन्) dies. RAM. I.28.8. GHAT. 21.<BR>(Lith. diếna f. dies, slav. denj m. id.; cf. lat. peren-dinus,<BR>peren-dinatio, quorum pars prior ad पर pertinet. Cum<BR>Pottio (II. 148.) huc trahimus goth. sin-teins, Them.<BR>sinteina quotidianus; sin = सम्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=168-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

