दूर|दूरं<BR>दूर (ut videtur, a r. दू vel दु s. र) longinquus, distans, remotus.<BR>H. 4.38. — Neutr. c. gen. SA. 5.38. 45.: {#dUram<BR>paTo gatan tvayA#}. — दूरात् longe. HIT. 37.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=173-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

