दूरपार<BR>दूरपार m. (ulteriorem ripam remotam habens, i. e.<BR>latus, BAH. e praec. et पार ulterior ripa) cognomen<BR>Gangis fluminis. H. 1.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=173-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

