दृ<BR>दृ 6. A. praef. आ respicere, curare, colere, aestimare. R. Schl. I.75.10.:<BR>अनादृत्य तु तद्वाक्यम्. — Pass. HIT. 4.9.:<BR>द्वितीया ऽऽद्रियते सदा; MAN. 2.234.: {#sarve tasya<BR>''dftA DarmA yasyE 'te traya AdftAH . anAdftAs tu<BR>yasyE 'te sarvAs tasyA 'PalAH kriyAH#}. — आदृत etiam<BR>sensu activo respiciens, curans, curam habens. MAN. 11.225.:<BR>सर्वेष्व् एव व्रतेष्व् एवम् प्रायश्चित्तार्थम् आदृतः<BR>(Schol. यत्नवान् प्रायश्चित्तार्थम् अनुतिष्ठेत्); MAN. 7.150.:<BR>तस्मात् तत्रा ऽऽदृतो भवेत् (Schol. {#tadapasAraRe<BR>yatnavAn syAt#}). Cf. दृश्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=173-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दृंह्<BR>दृंह् 1. (scribitur दृह्, gr. 110^a).) In dial. Vêd. PAR. firmare,<BR>firmum reddere. YAJ.-V.: {#pfTivIn dfMha; — pfTivIm<BR>upareRA 'dfNGIH#}. — ATM. firmum esse. YAJ.-V.<BR>दृंहस्व (Schol. दृढीभव); दृंहन्तान् दुर्या (domicilia)<BR>पृथिव्याम्. (V. Westerg. et cf. दृह्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=174-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दृढ|दृढं|दृढः<BR>दृढ v. दृह् (gr. 102.a.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=174-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दृढविक्रम<BR>दृढविक्रम (BAH. e praec. et विक्रम fortitudo) magnam<BR>fortitudinem habens. SU. 1.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=174-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दृढव्रत<BR>दृढव्रत (BAH. e दृढ et व्रत votum) firma vota habens. SU. 1.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=174-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दृति|दृतिः<BR>दृति m. (r. दॄ s. ति) corium. MAN. 2.99.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=174-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

दृप्<BR>1. दृप् 4. P.<BR>1) gaudere. BHATT. 14.106. praef. {#atiH vijigye<BR>tAM senAm…atidadarpaca#}.<BR>2) superbire.<BR>MAH. 1.162.: वरदानाद् दृप्ताः. — Caus. superbum<BR>reddere. HIT. 103.7.: कं श्रीर् न दर्पयति. (Cf. तृप्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=174-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

