दृषद्<BR>दृषद् f. lapis, saxum; v. दृशद्. RAGH. 4.74.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=175-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

