धु|धुः<BR>धु 5. P. A. agitare, commovere, concutere. H. 2.6.: {#Dunvan<BR>rUkzAn SiroruhAn#}; MAH. 2.2704.: गदान् धुन्वानः.<BR>Pass. धूये et Intens. दोधूय् tam a धु quam a धू derivari<BR>possunt; v. gr. 495. (V. धू et cf. gr. ϑύω, ϑύνω, ϑύελλα; ϑαύ-μα,<BR>a motione animi; hib. doineann «inclement<BR>weather, a tempest», doineannach, doineannta<BR>«stormy, tempestuous»; nisi in his vocabulis do est particula<BR>privativa.)<BR>c. वि i. q. simpl. R. Schl. II.23.4.: अग्रहस्तम् विधुन्वन्;<BR>MAH. 1.7035.: विधुन्वन्तो ऽजिनानि.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=184-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धुक्ष्<BR>धुक्ष् 1. A. (ut mihi videtur, a r. दह्, attenuato अ in उ, v.<BR>धिक्ष्) i. q. धिक्ष्.<BR>c. सम् ardere, flagrare. BHATT. 14.109.: {#sanduDukze tayoH<BR>kopaH#}. Caus. accendere. BHATT. 2.28.: शराग्निः सन्धुक्ष्यताम्;<BR>MAH. 1.5628.: अग्निस्तोकम् इवा ऽऽत्मानं<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=184-b" target="_blank">Page184-b+ 37</a>]<BR>यः सन्धुक्षयति नरः. Recreare. MAH. 1.2344.: {#kfSAn<BR>sanDukzayanti#}; GITA-GOV. 3.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=184-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धुर्<BR>धुर् f. (Nom. धूर्, धूः, gr. 73^a)., a r. धृ, i. e. धर्, attenuato<BR>अ in उ, v. कृ, unde करोमि, कुर्मस्)<BR>1) temo. DR. 8.18.;<BR>transl. frons, primus locus. RAGH. 1.91. 2.2.<BR>2) onus. RAGH. 1.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=184-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

