धृतराष्ट्र|धृतराष्ट्रः<BR>धृतराष्ट्र m. (BAH. e धृत et राष्ट्र) n. pr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धृति|धृतिः<BR>धृति f. (r. धृ s. ति) constantia. N. 6.10. BH. 18.33. 34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धृष्<BR>1. धृष् 5. P.<BR>1) audere. MAH. 1.35. 73.: {#na tvAn DfzRumaH<BR>prazwum#}. Part. pass. धृष्ट audax. BHAR. 3.48. R. Schl. II.96.43.<BR>2)<BR>sustinere, resistere. MAH. 6.453.:<BR>वयं हि शक्तिसम्पन्ना अकाले त्वाम् अधृष्णुम. (V.<BR>2. धृष् et cf. gr. ϑάϱσος, ϑαϱσέω, ϑϱάσος, ϑϱασύς;<BR>lith. drasùs audax, drystu audeo, praet. drysau; goth.<BR>ga-DARS audere, ga-dars audeo, audet, ga-daursum<BR>audemus (praet. cum signif. praes.); germ. vet. TARR,<BR>DARR per assimil. e TARS, DARS, ge-tars-t audes, v.<BR>Graff. 5.441.; hib. dasachd «fierceness, boldness», dasidh<BR>«furious, mischievous», donaighim «I dare, defy,<BR>adventure».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धृष्<BR>2. धृष् 1. et 10. P. laedere, violare, opprimere, superare.<BR>N. 3.15.: तेजसा तस्य धर्षिताः; R. Schl. I.24.13.:<BR>न सुप्तन् धर्षयिष्यन्ति नैरृताः; I.25.11.: {#tapasyantam<BR>iha sTARum…aDarzayad durmeDAH#}; MAH. 1.3454.:<BR>जरा त्वाम् अचिराद् धर्षयिष्यति; 1.1677.: न हि तं<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">Page186-b+ 36</a>]<BR>राजशार्दूलम् अधर्षयन्. — धर्षयितुं स्त्रियम् feminam<BR>violare, stuprare. R. Schl. I.49.6.: ऋषिपत्नीन् धर्षयित्वा;<BR>N. 10.14.: {#nacE 'zA tejasA SakyA kEScid Darzayitum<BR>paTi#}.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. R. Schl. I.97.9. 34.27. A. 5.3. N. 11.36.<BR>c. वि id. MAH. 1.1421.: {#rajAMsi mukuwAny ezAm utTitAni<BR>vyaDarzayan#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धॄ<BR>धॄ 9. P. धृणामि senescere. Cf. जॄ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धे<BR>धे 1. P. bibere. MAN. 4.59.: न वारयेद् गान् धयन्तीम्;<BR>MAH. 3.10452.: धास्यति किम्; 10453.: {#mAm ayan<BR>DAsyati#}; NALOD. 2.11.: मधु नानाविधम् अधयत्.<BR>(Cf. दधि; slav. dojû mulgeo; lith. dế-lế sanguisuga;<BR>goth. daddja lacto, mammam praebeo; gr.<BR>ϑῆσαι, ϑῆσϑαι, ϑηλή, ϑῆλυς, τίτϑη, ϑοίνη; germ. vet. tuta,<BR>tutta mamma (nostrum Zitze), cujus syllaba reduplicativa<BR>respondet sanscrito द in praet. redupl. दधौ (a धा,<BR>v. gr. min. 353.), attenuato अ in u; hib. daif f. «drink»<BR>fortasse forma redupl. cum f pro ध् sicut e. c. in lat. fumus<BR>= धूम, v. gr. comp. 11.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धेनु|धेनुः<BR>धेनु f. (r. धे s. नु) vacca lactaria.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धैर्य|धैर्यं|धैर्य्य|धैर्य्यं<BR>धैर्य n. (a धीर firmus, s. य) firmitas, constantia. IN. 5.55.<BR>SU. 3.24. N. 3.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धोर्<BR>धोर् 1. P. (गतिचातुर्ये) ire, currere; habilem, dexterum<BR>esse. (Cf. तुर्, तूर्, त्वर्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धौत|धौतं<BR>धौत v. धाव्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

धौम्य|धौम्यः<BR>धौम्य m. (a धूम s. य) n. pr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ध्मा<BR>ध्मा 1. (in tempp. special. धम्) flare, inflare, sufflare,<BR>flando excitare ignem. BH. 1.12.: शङ्खन् दध्मौ; SA. 5.77.:<BR>वायुना धम्यमानः…अग्निः; MAH. 2.2483.:<BR>धमेच् छान्तम् पावकम्. TROP. ध्मात inflatus. (Lat.<BR>flare, cum f pro ध् sicut in fumus = धूम mutatis liquidis<BR>m, l; v. gr. comp. 20.; germ. vet. dun-s-t, tun-s-t procella,<BR>cum s euphon., v. gr. comp. 95.; blâjan, blâhan,<BR>blâsan flare; gr. σμώ-νη, σμώ-ς, σμ pro ϑμ, sicut<BR>e. c. in πέπεισ-μαι pro -ϑμαι cf. Pott. I.187.)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=187-a" target="_blank">Page187-a+ 37</a>]<BR>c. आ id. HIT. 68.9.: दर्पाध्मात.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् id. MAH. 2.1925.: शङ्खान् समादध्मुः.<BR>c. उप id. MAH. 3.11706.: शङ्खम् उपाध्मासीत्; MAN. 4.53.:<BR>ना ऽग्निम् मुखेनो ऽपधमेत्.<BR>c. प्र id. A. 6.12.: शङ्खम् उपादाय…प्राधमन् तम्; BH. 1.14.:<BR>दिव्यौ शङ्खौ प्रदध्मतुः.<BR>c. वि difflare, dispellere, discutere. A. 3.28.: (ubi cum ed.<BR>Calc. व्यधमम् pro न्यधमम् legendum) {#SarIrARi ekIBUtAni…tAny<BR>aham vyaDamam punaH#}; 7.24.: {#tAn<BR>(vARAn) vyaDamaM SarEH#}; 8.10.: {#tato 'ham agniM vyaDamaM<BR>salilAstreRa#}; MAH. 1.5462.: {#vyaDamad anIkAni<BR>kzaRAt#}; R. Schl. II.80.8.: {#apare vIraRastambAn…vyaDamanti<BR>sma durgARi sTalAnica#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=186-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ध्माङ्क्ष्|ध्मांक्ष्<BR>ध्माङ्क्ष् 1. P. (घोरवासिते K. काङ्घे घोररुते V.; scribitur<BR>ध्माक्ष्, v. gr. 110^a).) i. q. द्राङ्क्ष्. V. {#DrANkz,<BR>drANkz, DvANkz#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=187-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ध्या<BR>ध्या v. ध्यै.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=187-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ध्यान|ध्यानं<BR>ध्यान n. (r. ध्यै s. अन) contemplatio, meditatio. BH. 12.12.<BR>N. 2.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=187-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ध्यै<BR>ध्यै 1. P. interdum A., etiam ध्या 2. meditari, cogitare. R. Schl. I.1.71.:<BR>ध्यायन्तीन् ददर्श; 9.43.: {#DyAyamAnaYca<BR>tan dfzwvA#}; N. 12.100.: ध्यात्वा चिरम्. Cum acc. rei.<BR>MAN. 9.21.: ध्यायत्य् अनिष्टञ् चेतसा; BH. 2.62. 12.6.:<BR>ध्यायन् विषयान्; MAH. 3.13209.: {#Sivena DyAhi<BR>saputrabAnDavam#}. (Gr. ϑέα, ϑεάομαι; respiciatur sanscritum<BR>विद् scire in latinâ, बुध् scire in zendicâ linguâ<BR>significare videre; respiciatur etiam εἴδω, οἶδα;<BR>cf. Pott. I.231.)<BR>c. अप et समप devovere, exsecrari; mala precari alicui.<BR>MAH. 3. 13652-56.: {#tAm avekzya tataH krudDaH samapaDyAyata<BR>dvijaH, apaDyAtAca vipreRa nyapatad DaraRItale#}.<BR>c. अभि i. q. simpl. MAN. 1.8. MAH. 3.11238.<BR>c. अव spernere. R. Schl. I.25.12.: अवध्यात (cf. {#avaDIr,<BR>avaman#}.<BR>c. उप i. q. simpl. MAH. 1.3848.: सो ऽपध्याता भगवता.<BR>c. नि id. BHATT. 14.65.: तन् निदध्यौ.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=187-b" target="_blank">Page187-b+ 34</a>]<BR>c. नि praef. अभि id. R. Schl. I.28.7.<BR>c. प्र id. N. 19.3.: प्रदध्यौच महामनाः; MAH. 1.1783.:<BR>प्रदध्यौ राजानम् प्रति. Putare, credere, habere. MAH. 1.7013.:<BR>{#dfzwvA tu tAn…BasmAvftAn iva havyavAhAn<BR>kfzRaH pradaDyO#}.<BR>c. प्र praef. सम् i. q. simpl. MAH. 3.1411.<BR>c. सम् id. M. 2.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=187-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ध्रज्<BR>ध्रज् 1. P. (गतौ) ire. Cf. धृज्, ध्रञ्ज्, ध्रिज्, ध्वज्, ध्वञ्ज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=187-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

