नाग|नागं|नागः<BR>नाग m. (a नग mons. s. अ)<BR>1) serpens (Wils.: A serpent<BR>in general, or especially the Spectacle snake, or Cobra<BR>Capella (Coluber Naga).) SU. 2.8. BH. 10.29.<BR>2) elephantus.<BR>N. 13.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नागरिक<BR>नागरिक m. (a नगर s. इक) oppidanus, civis. UR. 82.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नाट्य|नाट्यं<BR>नाट्य n. (a नट s. य) repraesentatio, actio scenica. UR. 4.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नाडी<BR>नाडी f.<BR>1) caulis.<BR>2) fistula.<BR>3) vena.<BR>4) intestinum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नाथ्<BR>नाथ् 1. P.<BR>1) rogare, petere. NAIṢ. 3.25.: {#nATanti ke<BR>nAma na lokanATam#} (Schol. याचन्ते).<BR>2) ATM. appetere,<BR>optare, c. gen. rei. PAN. II.3.55.: मधुनो नाथते;<BR>BHATT. 8.120.: धृत्या नाथस्व.<BR>3) aegrotum esse. YAJURV.<BR>(v. Westerg.): अवतान् (अवतात्) मा नाथतात्.<BR>4) dominari, imperare; v. नाथ. (Cf. नाध्. Huc<BR>vel ad नाध् traxerim germ. vet. nôt «necessitas, tribulatio,<BR>angor»; anglo-sax. nead, neod; goth. nauthjan cogere,<BR>naudi-band necessitatis vinculum.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नाथ|नाथः<BR>नाथ m. (r. नाथ् s. अ nisi anom. a r. नी s. थ, v. नीथ)<BR>dominus, tutor.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नाथवत्|नाथवन्त्<BR>नाथवत् (a praec. s. वत्) domino, tutore praeditus. DR. 6.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

