नाभि|नाभिः<BR>नाभि f.<BR>1) modiolus rotae.<BR>2) umbilicus. MEGH. 29.; 80.<BR>3) moschus. (Germ. vet. naba f. modiolus rotae, nabalo<BR>m. umbilicus; gr. ὀμϕαλός litteris transpositis e νοϕαλος,<BR>mutato ν in μ propter sequentem labialem, nisi ex ο-ναϕαλος,<BR>ejecto α, praefixo ο, sicut in ὄνυξ, ὀϕϱύς, ὀδούς, ὄνομα;<BR>ita lat. umbilicus e nubilicus vel u-nabilicus, sicut<BR>unguis ex u-naguis, v. नख.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नाम<BR>नाम (accus. τοῦ नामन्)<BR>1) Adv. nomine. H. 2.1. SU. 1.2.<BR>N. 1.1. 18.5. DR. 7.9. 12.<BR>2) particula interrog. N. 11.4.;<BR>12.19.: ननु नाम; SAK. 51.2.infr. et HIT. 75.2.:<BR>को नाम; N. 24.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=193-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

