नार|नारं|नारः<BR>नार n. (fortasse a r. स्ना abjecto s sicut in lat. natare) aqua.<BR>(Gr. νηϱός madidus; neogr. νηϱόν aqua; lith. naras urinator,<BR>nardau demergor, submergor.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=194-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

