निज्<BR>निज् 3. P. A. (शोचे K. पोषे शुद्धौ V.) purificare, lavare;<BR>nutrire. (V. निञ्ज् et cf. hib. nighim «I wash»,<BR>nighte «washed» = निक्त; lat. ninguis, nix e nig-s, nivis<BR>e niguis, ninguo, ningo; graec. νίζω, νίψω, νίπτω, ΧΕΡ-ΝΙΒ,<BR>mutatâ gutturali in labialem.)<BR>c. निस् lavare, abluere, purificare, lustrare. MAN. 5.127.:<BR>अद्भिर् निर्णिक्तम्; RAGH. 17.22.: तोयनिर्णिक्तपाणयः;<BR>MAN. 11.189.: एनस्विभिर् अनिर्णिक्तैः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निज|निजं<BR>निज (r. जन् praef. नि s. अ, v. gr. 645.)<BR>1) innatus. RAGH. 3.15.<BR>2) indigena. HIT. 21.1.<BR>3) proprius; in recentioribus<BR>scriptis pronominum possessivorum vice fungitur;<BR>meus, tuus, suus, noster etc. UP. 3. et 87.: निजम् suum;<BR>RAGH. 18.27.: निजे in suo.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निञ्ज्|निंज्<BR>निञ्ज् 2. A. (scribitur निज्, gr. 110^a).) i. q. निज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नितम्ब|नितंब|नितंबः|नितम्बः<BR>नितम्ब m. (r. तम्ब् praef. नि s. अ; fortasse नि in hoc<BR>comp. ortum est e न, attenuato अ in इ, ita ut नितम्ब<BR>proprie significet non se movens; cf. नग mons et v.<BR>निखिल)<BR>1) collis. N. 12.110.<BR>2) nates, clunes. IN. 5.10.<BR>RAGH. 4.52. 6.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नितम्बिनी|नितंबिनी<BR>नितम्बिनी f. (a praec. s. इन् in fem.) pulchris clunibus<BR>praedita femina, ϰαλλίπυγος. RITU-S. 1.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नितराम्<BR>नितराम् Adv. (a नि s. तराम् acc. fem. suff. comp. तर, v.<BR>gr. 652. suff. तम, तर) semper, in perpetuum. MR. 267.5.<BR>ĆAUR. 42. RAGH. 1.95. Lass. 58.20. — Cf. नित्य.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नितान्त|नितांत|नितान्तं<BR>नितान्त v. तम् praef. नि.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नित्य|नित्यं|नित्यः<BR>नित्य (a praepos. नि s. त्य, v. gr. 652. et cf. नितराम्)<BR>sempiternus. — Acc. नित्यम् Adv. semper. IN. 3.10. 5.61.<BR>H. 4.10. BR. 3.6. SU. 1.31., v. gr. 652.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नित्यत्व|नित्यत्वं<BR>नित्यत्व n. (a नित्य s. त्व) aeternitas, perennitas, constantia,<BR>perseverantia. BH. 13.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नित्यदा<BR>नित्यदा (a नित्य s. दा) semper.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

नित्यशस्<BR>नित्यशस् (a नित्य s. शस्) semper. N. 26.14. 16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निद्<BR>निद् 1. P. A. (कुत्सायाम् K. सन्निधौ कुत्सने V.)<BR>1) i. q.<BR>निन्द्.<BR>2) propinquum, prope esse. (V. निन्द् et<BR>cf. gr. ὄνειδος, praef. ο goth. ga-naitja contumeliâ afficio;<BR>germ. vet. nîd invidia.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=195-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निदर्शन|निदर्शनं<BR>निदर्शन n. (a Caus. r. दृश् s. अन) exemplum. RAGH. 8.45.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निदाघ|निदाघः<BR>निदाघ m. (r. दह् praef. नि s. अ, mutato ह् in घ् vel servato<BR>primitivo घ्; cf. hib. daghaim uro)<BR>1) aestus, calor.<BR>RAGH. 10.5.<BR>2) aestas. RAGH. 10.84. RITU-S. 1.1. et 65.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निदान|निदानं<BR>निदान n. (r. दा vel दो s. न vel अन) causa principalis.<BR>RAGH. 3.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निदेश|निदेशः<BR>निदेश m. (r. दिश् s. अ) jussus, praeceptum, imperium,<BR>auctoritas. M. 19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निद्रा<BR>निद्रा f. (a r. द्रै dormire, praef. नि, mutato ऐ in आ) somnus.<BR>H. 1.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निधन|निधनं<BR>निधन m. (r. हन्, cujus forma primitiva est धन् = gr.<BR>ΘΑΝ, s. अ; v. gr. 104.) mors, exitium. BR. 2.2. N. 2.17.<BR>BH. 3.35. (Hib. nidh, nith «manslaughter, homicide, a<BR>battle»; v. r. हन्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निधान|निधानं<BR>निधान n. (r. धा praef. नि deponere, s. अन) thesaurus,<BR>gaza. BH. 9.18. 11.38.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निधि|निधिः<BR>निधि m. (r. धा praef. नि s. इ, nisi potius sine suffixo, attenuato<BR>आ in इ) receptaculum, thesaurus, gaza. A. 6.6.<BR>N. 24.37.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निनाद|निनादः<BR>निनाद m. (r. नद् praef. नि s. अ) sonus, stridor, strepitus.<BR>RAGH. 11.15. RITU-S. 1.25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निन्द्|निंद्<BR>निन्द् 1. P. interdum A. (scribitur निद्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>1) reprehendere,<BR>vituperare. RAM. II.76.92.: {#nindAmy<BR>ahaN karma kftam pitus tat#}; MAN. 8.19.: {#nindArho<BR>yatra nindyate#}; MAH. 3.15229.: {#anindyan nindate yo<BR>hi#}.<BR>2) spernere. BH. 2.36.: निन्दन्तस् तव सामर्थ्यम्.<BR>— अनिन्दित non spretus. N. 12.120. IN. 4.15. (V.<BR>निद्.)<BR>c. प्रति reprehendere, vituperare. DR. 5.18.: {#svabudDim<BR>pratininditAsi#}.<BR>c. वि id. MAH. 3.13700.: विनिन्दन् स्वम् आत्मानम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निन्दा|निंदा<BR>निन्दा f. (r. निन्द् s. आ) vituperium. BH. 12.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निन्व्<BR>निन्व् 1. P. (सेके; scribitur निव्, gr. 110^a).) irrigare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निपात|निपातः<BR>निपात m. (r. पत् s. अ)<BR>1) actio decidendi, delabendi. A. 8.6.<BR>2) impetus. RAGH. 2.60.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निपातन|निपातनं<BR>निपातन n. (a Caus. r. पत् praef. नि s. अन) actio caedendi,<BR>occidendi. RAGH. 9.49.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निपातिन्<BR>निपातिन् (r. पत् praef. नि s. इन्)<BR>1) decidens. UR. 87.8.<BR>RAGH. 9.40.<BR>2) (a Caus.) cadere faciens, caedens, occidens.<BR>RAGH. 11.21. N. 12.93.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निपुण|निपुणः<BR>निपुण (r. पुण् praef. नि s. अ) aptus, idoneus, habilis, peritus,<BR>doctus; v. नैपुण, नैपुण्य.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निबन्ध|निबंध|निबन्धं|निबंधः|निबन्धः<BR>निबन्ध m. (r. बन्ध् s. अ) actio ligandi, constringendi.<BR>BH. 16.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निबन्धन|निबंधन|निबंधनं|निबन्धनं<BR>निबन्धन n. (r. बन्ध् praef. नि s. अन) causa. RAGH. 8.51.<BR>UP. 11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

निभ|निभः<BR>निभ (r. भा splendere, praef. नि s. अ) similis, in fine compp.<BR>H. 3.9. V. सन्निभ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

