निमित्त|निमित्तं<BR>निमित्त n. (fortasse e निमित reduplicato त्, a r. मा vel<BR>मि praef. नि s. त)<BR>1) causa. Accus. adverb. (निमित्तम्)<BR>praepositionis loco fungitur, ad exprimendum causâ,<BR>propter (gr. 691.). N. 9.34.<BR>2) signum. N. 23.5. 8. BH. 1.31.<BR>N. 13.20. 16.26.<BR>3) vestigium. HIT. 24.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

