नियुद्ध|नियुद्धं<BR>नियुद्ध n. (r. युध् praef. नि s. त) singulare certamen. Lass. 48.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=196-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

