नील|नीलं|नीलः<BR>नील (r. नील् s. अ, nisi potius नील् Denom. a नील, hoc<BR>autem a निश् nox suff. ल, abjecto श् et producto इ; cf.<BR>lat. niger, Them. nigru, quod e nic-ru explicari potest,<BR>mutatâ tenui in mediam; v. Benfey. II.57.) niger, caeruleus,<BR>violaceus; lividus. H. 1.37. 4.29. N. 16.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=201-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

