पठ्<BR>पठ् 1. P. interdum A. recitare, legere. R. Schl. I.1.94.: {#yaH<BR>paWed rAmacaritam#}; MAH. 3.8172.: {#gAyatrIm paWate<BR>yaH#}; 8173.: सावित्रीम् पठन्; SA. 1.31.: {#SrutaM hi DarmaSAstrezu<BR>paWyamAnan#} (sic legendum pro पट्यमानं) द्विजातिभिः;<BR>MAH. 1.1438.: {#etad icCAmy ahaM Srotum<BR>purARe yadi paWyate#}. — Caus. facere ut aliquis loquatur,<BR>loqui docere aliquem. HIT. 8.2.: {#na Sukavat pAWyate<BR>vakaH#}. Facere ut aliquis legat, ad legendum exhortari,<BR>instruere: पिता वैरी येन बालो न पाठ्यते.<BR>(Cf. 2. पट्, कथ्.)<BR>c. अति celebrare, nominare. MAH. 3.12813.<BR>c. परि id. MAH. 1.2020.<BR>c. सम् i. q. simpl. MAN. 4.98.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=204-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

