पताकिनी<BR>पताकिनी f. (a पताका s. इन् in fem.) exercitus. RAGH. 4.82.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पति|पतिः<BR>पति m. (ut videtur, a r. पा regere, correpto आ, s. ति)<BR>1) dominus. N. 1.2.<BR>2) conjux, maritus. BR. 2.12.<BR>(Lith. pati-s dominus in comp. wiếsz-patis «Landesherr,<BR>ein grofser Herr» = Vêd. विश्पति; pat-s pro pati-s,<BR>conjux, maritus; slav. gos-podj; russ. gospodin dominus;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-b" target="_blank">Page206-b+ 37</a>]<BR>goth. FADI, nom. faths dominus, dux, in fine compp.<BR>ut hunda-faths, bruth-faths; gr. πόσις e πότις; lat. potis.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पतित्व|पतित्वं<BR>पतित्व n. (a praec. s. त्व) Abstractum praecedentis, conjugium<BR>feminae cum conjuge. N. 3.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पत्तन|पत्तनं<BR>पत्तन n. (r. पद् s. तन) urbs. HIT. 63.16. (Sensu et radice<BR>convenit lat. oppidum, ob-pidum; v. पद्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पत्ति|पत्तिः<BR>पत्ति m. (r. पद् ire s. ति) pedes. HIT. 95.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पत्नी<BR>पत्नी f. (a पति abjecto इ s. नी, cf. formas velut इन्द्राणी,<BR>v. gr. min. 218.) uxor. N. 12.174. (Cf. gr. πότνια, lith.<BR>pati uxor.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पत्र|पत्त्रं|पत्रं<BR>पत्र n. (etiam पत्त्र, r. पत् s. त्र)<BR>1) ala.<BR>2) folium.<BR>3) (r.<BR>पद्) currus. RAGH. 15.48. (Gr. πέταλον, πτίλον.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पत्रिन्<BR>पत्रिन् m. (a praec. s. इन्)<BR>1) avis. RAGH. 11.29.<BR>2) sagitta.<BR>RAGH. 3.53.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

