पथ|पथः<BR>पथ m. (r. पथ् s. अ) via, regio, in fine compp. IN. 1.31.<BR>(V. पथिन् et cf. gr. πάτος; germ. vet. pad, fad, phat,<BR>pfat, Them. padi etc. via, semita; anglo-sax. padh,<BR>paedh; hib. fath «a district, a field, a green, a lawn»,<BR>fatha «a plain». V. पथिन्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=206-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

