पद्मलोचन<BR>पद्मलोचन (BAH. e पद्म lotus et लोचन oculus) loto similes<BR>oculos habens. IN. 2.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=208-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पद्मा<BR>पद्मा f. (fem. τοῦ पद्म) cognomen deae Lakṣmiae. HIT. 57.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=208-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पद्मिनी<BR>पद्मिनी f. (a पद्म s. इन् in fem.) nymphaearum multitudo,<BR>lacus nymphaeis abundans. N. 13.10. 16.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=208-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पन्<BR>पन् P. A. (पनायामि, पनाये, PAN. III.1.28.; refertur ad<BR>1^mam classem, quanquam analogiam classis 10^mae sequitur,<BR>producto अ initiali characteris अय; in dialecto<BR>Vêd. tamen haec productio omittitur) laudare, celebrare.<BR>RIGV. 20.6. not.: तत् पनयद् वचो वः «illud comprobavit<BR>sermonem vestrum»; 87.3.: {#svayam mahitvam<BR>panayanta DUtayaH#} «ipsi potentiam suam declarant<BR>quassatores».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=208-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पन्थ्<BR>पन्थ् 10. P. (scribitur पथ्, gr. 110^a).) ire. V. {#paT, panTan,<BR>paTin#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=208-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पन्न|पन्नं|पन्नः<BR>पन्न v. 1. पद् (gr. 607.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पन्नग|पन्नगः<BR>पन्नग m. (pedibus non iens e पद् pes, न non, et ग<BR>iens, v. euph. r. 58.) serpens (cf. उरग).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पम्ब्<BR>पम्ब् 1. P. (गतौ) ire, se movere. (V. कम्प् et cf. {#parb,<BR>bamb, barb, mamb, marb, namb, narb, Kamb,<BR>Karb, gamb, garb, Gamb, Garb, camb, carb, tamb,<BR>tarb#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पय्<BR>पय् 1. P. A. (गतौ) ire.<BR>c. वि sternere. (in dial. Vêd. nisi विपयामि cohaeret<BR>cum rad. वप्, attenuato अ in इ). RIGV. (v. Westerg.)<BR>विपयन्ति वर्हिः. (Schol. स्तृणन्ति.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पय|पयः<BR>पय Suffixum, v. कतिपय.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पयस्<BR>पयस् n. (r. पी bibere s. अस्)<BR>1) aqua. MEGH. 23. 25. 41.<BR>2) lac.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पयोद|पयोदः<BR>पयोद m. (e praec. et द dans) nubes. MEGH. 7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पयोधर|पयोधरः<BR>पयोधर m. (e पयस् et धर tenens)<BR>1) nubes. AM.<BR>2) mamma,<BR>IN. 2.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पयोधि|पयोधिः<BR>पयोधि m. (e पयस् et धि tenens, a r. धा) mare. Lass. p. 77.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पयोमुच्<BR>पयोमुच् m. (e पयस् et मुच् dimittens) nubes. UR. 78.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पयोष्णी<BR>पयोष्णी f. (ut videtur, e पयस् et स्न se baignant in fem.,<BR>ar. स्ना s. अ) nomen fluminis. N. 9.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पर|परं|परः<BR>पर (ut videtur, ex अपर abjecto अ initiali)<BR>1) alius. H. 4.3.<BR>2) remotior, ulterior, posterior. DR. 2.8. (v. परम्).<BR>3) eximius, praecipuus, altus, altissimus, summus. H. 4.22.<BR>N. 21.20. BH. 5.16. — In construct. cum ablat.<BR>Comparativi vim habet. M. 50. BH. 3.42. De पर n. eximium,<BR>praecipuum in fine compositorum v. gr. 666.<BR>N. 2.2. 3.12. 78.80. BH. 18.52.<BR>4) hostis. IN. 5.59. N. 12.30.<BR>DR. 6.29. (Cum accus. परम् convenit lat. peren<BR>in vocibus peren-die, peren-dinus, peren-dinatio;<BR>huc etiam cum Pottio, II.230., traxerim par aequalis,<BR>quasi alter; germ. vet. fer procul (v. पार et पारदेश्य);<BR>angl. far; goth. fairra id., fortasse per assimil. e fairna<BR>quod ab Adv. परम् deduci posset, mutato m in n, adjecto<BR>a sicut in acc. pronom. (ut thana = तम्, τόν); fairnjis,<BR>Them. fairnja vetus; nostrum fern; germ. vet. furiro<BR>prior, furist primus; lat. prior ejectâ vocali mediâ; primus<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">Page209-b+ 37</a>]<BR>= परम q. v.; gr. πϱίν, dor. πϱάν.) Huc etiam<BR>trahi posset slav. praep. insep. пϱе pre trans, e. c. preidû<BR>transibo, pre-voditi traducere. V. {#pAra, puras, pUrva,<BR>pra#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परतस्<BR>परतस् Adv. (a पर s. तस्) ultra. BH. 3.42.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परत्र|परत्रं<BR>परत्र (a पर s. त्र) alibi, praesertim in illo, futuro mundo,<BR>opp. τῷ इह (cf. अमुत्र). HIT. 32.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परन्तप|परंतप|परन्तपः<BR>परन्तप Adj. vel Subst. m. (e पर hostis in Acc. v. gr. 645.<BR>suff. अ, et तप qui urit, vexat) qui hostem urit, hostium<BR>vexator. H. 3.6. BH. 4.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परपुष्ट|परपुष्टः<BR>परपुष्ट m. (ab alio nutritus, e पर et पुष्ट a r. पुष्) i. q.<BR>कोकिल i. e. cuculus indicus. Fem. परपुष्टा. UR. 63.5.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परभृत|परभृतः<BR>परभृत m. (e पर et भृत sustentatus) id. Fem. -भृता. UR. 63.8.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परम्<BR>परम् Adv. (acc. neut. vocis पर)<BR>1) ultra, ulterius, post,<BR>deinde. Lass. 13.1. Antecedente अतस् ad tempus vel<BR>locum relato. BH. 12.8.; N. 9.23.; antecedente अस्मात्<BR>MEGH. 98. — परम् मुहूर्तात् post temporis momentum,<BR>statim. UR. 39.12.<BR>2) sed, verum. Lass. 40.10.; 43.7.;<BR>परन्तु id. Lass. 41.17. 44.8. (V. अपर et cf.<BR>nostrum aber.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परम|परमः<BR>परम (a पर s. म) eximius, altissimus, summus. IN. 5.23.<BR>BH. 13.31. In fine compositi BAH. (v. gr. 666.). BH. 16.11.<BR>(Cf. lith. pirma-s primus; lat. primus, v. पर; goth.<BR>fruma, Them. fruman, prior, primus; frumôza prior,<BR>frumists primus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परमर्षि|परमर्षिः<BR>परमर्षि m. (KARM. e praec. et ऋषि) summus Rischis. IN. 2.10.<BR>SU. 3.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परमार्थ|परमार्थः<BR>परमार्थ m. (e परम et अर्थ) veritas. SAK. 41.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परमार्थतस्<BR>परमार्थतस् Adv. (a praec. s. तस्) re verâ. UR. 37.24. (v.<BR>not. LX.); 72.15. Penitus, accurate. SAK. 47.4.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परमिक<BR>परमिक (a परम s. इक omissâ Vriddhi) i. q. परम. IN. 5.59.<BR>BR. 1.16. 25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परमेष्ठिन्<BR>परमेष्ठिन् m. (e Loc. परमे in altissimo et स्थिन्, qui est,<BR>mutato स् in ष् ad analogiam r. 80., v. etiam euph. r.<BR>101^a).) nomen dei Brahmae.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=209-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परम्पर|परंपर|परम्परः<BR>परम्पर (e पर alius in Acc. et पर) successivus, ab alio ad<BR>alium progrediens.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परम्परा|परंपरा<BR>परम्परा f. (Abstractum praecedentis) successio, progressio<BR>ab alio ad alium, e. c. a patre ad filium. BH. 4.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परलोक|परलोकं|परलोकः<BR>परलोक m. (e पर et लोक) alius, futurus mundus, coelum.<BR>HIT. 73.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परवत्|परवन्त्<BR>परवत् (-वान्, -वती, -वत्, a पर s. वत्) alius potestati<BR>obnoxius. SAK. 36.2. 43.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परवत्ता<BR>परवत्ता f. (a praec. s. ता) Abstractum praec. UR. 91.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परशु|परशुः<BR>परशु m. securis, ascia. SA. 4.18. (Gr. πέλεϰυς.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परस्तात्<BR>परस्तात् Adv. (a पर ulterior, s. स्तात्) ultra, cum abl.<BR>BH. 8.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परस्पर|परस्परं<BR>परस्पर (e परस् - nom. sing. masc. hac in compositione<BR>Fem. et Neut. vice etiam fungente, servato स् ante प्<BR>secundum r. 79. - et पर, quod hac in compositione in<BR>obliquis sing. casibus solnm usurpatur) i. q. अन्योन्य<BR>q. v. H. 4.36. SU. 4.15. N. 13.14. BH. 3.11. 10.9. M. 35.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परा<BR>परा (fortasse a पर alius sicut दक्षिणा a दक्षिण) Praep.<BR>insep. retro. (Cf. gr. παϱά; lith. par (praep. insep.) retro,<BR>e. c. par-wadinu revoco, par-eimi redeo; hib. frea-,<BR>far- e. c. freagaraim «I answer», far-bhuille «a backblow»,<BR>v. Pictet p. 89. Fortasse etiam lat. re-, osset.<BR>ra- huc pertinent, abjectâ syllabâ initiali. E goth. linguâ<BR>fair- huc retulerim, attenuato a in i, praefixo a, v.<BR>gr. comp. 82.; germ. vet. far, fir; nostrum ver, v.<BR>Grimm III.256.4. c.; etiam faur pro e परा ortum esse<BR>potest, abjecto आ finali, attenuato a medio in u; germ.<BR>vet. furi; nostrum für; island. vet. fyri, attenuato आ in<BR>i; v. परि.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराक्रम|पराक्रमः<BR>पराक्रम m. (r. क्रम् ire praef. परा s. अ) vis, robur, fortitudo.<BR>H. 2.36.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराक्रान्त|पराक्रांत<BR>पराक्रान्त v. क्रम् praef. परा.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराग|परागः<BR>पराग m. (e परा et ग iens) pulvis. RAGH. 4.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराङ्मुख|पराङ्मुखः<BR>पराङ्मुख (BAH. e पराक् - secundum r. 59. pro पराच् aversus,<BR>mutato क् in ङ् secundum r. 58. - et मुख os, vultus)<BR>aversum os habens. IN. 2.4. N. 8.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराच्<BR>पराच् Adj. (r. अञ्च् praef. परा, v. gr. 196.) aversus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराजय|पराजयः<BR>पराजय m. (r. जि praef. परा s. अ)<BR>1) clades, strages.<BR>2) separatio. N. 13.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराजित|पराजितः<BR>पराजित v. जि praef. परा.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराधीन|पराधीनः<BR>पराधीन Adj. (TATP. e. पर alius et अधीन q. v.) alii subjectus,<BR>alius potestati obnoxius. BR. 1.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराभाव|पराभावः<BR>पराभाव m. (r. भू praef. परा s. अ) clades, destructio. A. 10.45.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परायण|परायणं<BR>परायण (e पर et अयन itio) in fine compositorum BAH. aequat<BR>vocem पर (v. gr. 666.); e. c. शोकपरायण moerorem<BR>tanquam praecipuum habens, moerori deditus, in<BR>moerore defixus. N. 12.83. 23.1. BH. 5.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परार्ध्य<BR>परार्ध्य vel परार्ड्य (a परार्ध - पर + अर्ध - praecipuum dimidium,<BR>s. य) eximius, excellens. H. 1.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परावर<BR>परावर n. (DVANDV. ex पर remotus et अवर posterior) remotum<BR>et posterius, i. e., ut equidem puto, praeteritum<BR>et futurum. SA. 6.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परासु|परासुः<BR>परासु (BAH. ex पर remotus et असु q. v.) remotos vitales<BR>spiritus habens, mortuus. N. 11.38.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पराह्न<BR>पराह्न n. (ex पर et अह्न pro अहन् dies) pomeridianum<BR>tempus, posterior diei pars (cf. पूर्वाह्न). A. 4.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परि<BR>परि Praep. insep. circum; in comp. cum adjectivis valde, v.<BR>परिलघु, परिशुष्क. (Gr. πεϱί; hib. faoi «about, around»<BR>ejecto r; germ. vet. furi, island. fyri, nostrum für huc<BR>referri possent, nisi इ finale in linguis germanicis ubique<BR>evanuisset, quam ob rem vocalem i hujus praepositionis<BR>ab â formae परा deduxerim, quod primum in a breve,<BR>deinde, quod saepissime accidit, in i se attenuaverit. De<BR>lat. et lith. per v. पार.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परिक्लान्त|परिक्लांत<BR>परिक्लान्त v. क्लम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परिक्लेष्टृ<BR>परिक्लेष्टृ m. (r. क्लिश् vexare praef. परि s. तृ) vexator.<BR>DR. 9.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परिखा<BR>परिखा f. (r. खन् fodere praef. परि, abjecto अन्, suff.<BR>अ in fem.) fossa quae urbem cingit.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परिग्रह|परिग्रहः<BR>परिग्रह m. (r. ग्रह् praef. परि s. अ)<BR>1) amplexus. Lass. 85.2.infr.<BR>2) comitatus, familia. BH. 6.10. in comp. c.<BR>अ.<BR>3) uxor. UR. 70.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परिघ|परिघः<BR>परिघ m. (r. हन् ferire, praef. परि, ह् mutato in घ्, cf.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=211-a" target="_blank">Page211-a+ 37</a>]<BR>gr. 367., abjecto अन् ante suffixum अ)<BR>1) clava.<BR>2) pessulus.<BR>SAK. 38.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=210-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

