पर्वत|पर्वतः|पर्व्वत|पर्व्वतः<BR>पर्वत m. (ut videtur, a r. पर्व् suff. अत vel त inserto अ)<BR>mons. UR. 70.15. (Serb. brdo id.; fortasse goth. fairguni<BR>mons huc pertinent, mutato v in gutturalem, v.<BR>gr. comp. 19.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=212-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पर्वन्|पर्व्वन्<BR>पर्वन् n. (r. पर्व् s. अन्) Wilsonus explicat:<BR>1) a knot, a<BR>joint in a cane or body etc.<BR>2) a name given to certain<BR>days in the lunar month, as the full and change of the<BR>moon and the 6th, 8th and 10th of each half month.<BR>3) Particular periods of the year, as the equinox, solstice<BR>etc.<BR>4) the moment of the sun's entering a new sign.<BR>5) a festival, a holiday.<BR>6) Opportunity, occasion. MED.<BR>7) a chapter, a book, the division of a work. OR. D.<BR>8) a<BR>moment, an instant SABD. CH. SA. 1.25. UR. 70.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पर्ष्<BR>पर्ष् 1. P. A. (स्नेहने K. स्नेहे V.) amare. RIGV. 86.7.: {#yasya<BR>prayAMsi#} (Ros. «cibos») पर्षथ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पल्<BR>1. पल् 1. P. (गतौ, ut mihi videtur, e पद् mutato द् in<BR>ल्, v. Delii Radd. Prâcr. p. 3.) ire. (V. पद्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पल्<BR>2. पल् 10. पलयामि (रक्षणे K. रक्षे V.) servare, tueri; v.<BR>पाल्, पा.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पल|पलं|पलः<BR>पल<BR>1) n. caro. AM.<BR>2) m. stramen. (Hib. feol, feoil caro;<BR>anglo-sax. flesc, flœsc, flee; germ. vet. fleisk id.; lat.<BR>palea; gall. paille.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पलल|पललं|पललः<BR>पलल n.<BR>1) id.<BR>2) limus, lutum. (Hib. poll mire, dirt; gr.<BR>πηλός.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पलाय्<BR>पलाय् (pro पराय् a r. अय् i. e. इ cl. 1. praef. परा, mutato<BR>र् in ल्. PAN. VIII.2.19.) fugere. DR. 5.6.: पलायमान;<BR>8.36.: पलायन्तञ् जयद्रथम्; 8.59.: पलायसे.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पलायन|पलायनं<BR>पलायन n. (r. अय् i. e. इ cl. 1. praef. पला pro परा s. अन)<BR>fuga. DR. 8.32. 58.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पलाश|पलाशं|पलाशः<BR>पलाश n.<BR>1) folium.<BR>2) nomen arboris rubros ferentis<BR>flores (Butea frondosa).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पलित|पलितं|पलितः<BR>पलित Adj. canis capillis praeditus. Subst. n. pl. पलितानि<BR>cani capilli. MAH. 1.3467. HIT. 28.7. (Cf. lat. pallidus;<BR>gr. πολιός; slav. plaw flavus; lith. balta-s albus,<BR>palwa-s flavus; germ. vet. falo flavus, Them. falawa,<BR>gen. falawe-s.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पल्युल्<BR>पल्युल्, पल्यूल् 10. P. (लूनिपूत्याम् K. लूनिपूत्योः<BR>V.; ut mihi videtur, e परि + लू, mutato<BR>र् in ल्, transposito लू in ऊल्) findere, abscindere,<BR>evellere; purificare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=213-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

