पारक्य|पारक्यं<BR>पारक्य (a परक, quod ipsum a पर alius, alienus, hostis,<BR>suff. य) hostilis, inimicus. HIT. 109.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पारग|पारगः<BR>पारग (e पार et ग iens) ad ripam ulteriorem iens, transiens,<BR>translat. perlegens. N. 12.81. 13.44.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पारद|पारदः<BR>पारद m. argentum vivum. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पारदेश्य|पारदेश्यः<BR>पारदेश्य m. (a परदेश alia regio s. य) peregrinator, peregrinus.<BR>(Cf. priorem partem lat. per-egrinus, v. पार.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पारावत|पारावतः<BR>पारावत m. columba. UR. 37.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पारिषद|पारिषदः<BR>पारिषद m. (a परिषद् coetus s. अ) unus e coetu, e multitudine.<BR>N. 18.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पारुष्य|पारुष्यं|पारुष्यः<BR>पारुष्य n. (a परुष s. य)<BR>1) asperitas, severitas. HIT. 102.22.<BR>2) sermo contumeliosus. BH. 16.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पार्थ|पार्थः<BR>पार्थ m. (a पृथा s. अ) a Prithâ oriundus, Prithâ natus,<BR>cognomen Pândavorum, praecipue Arjuni.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पार्थिव|पार्थिवं|पार्थिवः<BR>पार्थिव (a पृथिवी terra s. अ)<BR>1) Adj. (fem. ई) terrenus,<BR>terrester. SA. 6.18.<BR>2) m. princeps, rex. H. 4.39.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पार्वतीय|पार्व्वतीय<BR>पार्वतीय (a पर्वत mons s. ईय) montanus. DR. 8.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पार्श्व|पार्श्वं|पार्श्वः<BR>पार्श्व m. n. latus. SU. 3.26. N. 19.16. (Fortasse gr. πλευϱά,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-a" target="_blank">Page216-a+ 37</a>]<BR>πλευρόν quasi पार्श्वर, ejecto आ et श्, mutato र् in λ<BR>L. Diefenbach apte huc trahit lith. pussế dimidium, per<BR>assimil. e pursế.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=215-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पार्श्वतस्<BR>पार्श्वतस् Adv. (a praec. s. तस्) ad latus, a latere. SU. 3.25. 27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पार्ष्णि|पार्ष्णिः<BR>पार्ष्णि m. f. calx. (Goth. fairzna pro firzna - v. gr. comp. 82.<BR>- attenuato आ in i; et germ. vet. fersna nituntur formâ<BR>पार्ष्णा; ita gr. πτέϱνα adjecto τ; cf. पृष्ठ dorsum,<BR>tergum.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पाल्<BR>पाल् 10. P. interdum A. (रक्षणे K. रक्षे V.)<BR>1) servare, tueri.<BR>R. Schl. I.45.29.: पालया ऽस्मान्; MAH. 1.8414.:<BR>ऋषीन् अस्मान् बालकान् पालयस्व.<BR>2) regere.<BR>R. Schl. I.5.11.: ताम् पुरीम् पालयामास; DEV. 1.11. 12.<BR>(V. पा unde पाल्, quod etiam pro Caus. radicis<BR>पा habetur, adjecto ल्; cf. hib. fal «guarding, tending<BR>cattle», falaim «I hedge, inclose»; v. पाल.)<BR>c. अनु i. q. simpl. sens. 1. MAN. 1.27. R. Schl. I.1.24.:<BR>प्रतिज्ञाम्; II.34.43.: निदेशम्.<BR>c. अभि id. MAH. 3.8472.<BR>c. परि<BR>1) i. q. simpl. BR. 2.28. N. 5.44.<BR>2) exspectare.<BR>R. Schl. II.70.13.: मुहूर्तम् परिपाल्यताम्.<BR>c. प्रति<BR>1) i. q. simpl. MAH. 1.3521. 4080.<BR>2) exspectare.<BR>UR. 37.14.: एनम् अवलोकमार्गे परिपालयामि; SAK. 8.13.:<BR>यावद् एताः…प्रतिपालयामि. Intrans. MAH. 3.8793.:<BR>यावद् आगमनम् मह्यन् तावत् त्वम् प्रतिपालय.<BR>c. सम् servare. MAH. 3.15249.: प्रतिज्ञाम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पाल|पालः<BR>पाल m. (r. पाल् s. अ) servator, custos, dominus, rex, in<BR>fine compp. N. 2.8. 21.17. BH. 11.26. IN. 1.1. (Hib.<BR>fal «a king, privileged person».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पालन|पालनं<BR>पालन n. (r. पाल् s. अन) servatio, tuitio. HIT. 96.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पावक|पावकः<BR>पावक m. (r. पू purificare s. अक) ignis. (Conferantur,<BR>quod ad syllabam radicalem attinet, gr. πῦϱ, germ. vet.<BR>fiur. Goth. fôn, Them. fôna ignis formâ convenit cum<BR>पवन et पावन, quae ejecto व् coalescerent in पान,<BR>quod gothice sonaret fôna. Fortasse lat. focus e pocus,<BR>foveo e poveo sicut fluo e pluo = प्लवामि a r. प्लु.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पावन|पावनं|पावनः<BR>पावन (r. पू s, अन)<BR>1) n. purificatio, lustramen. BH. 18.5.<BR>2) Adj. (fem. ई) purus. RAGH. 15.101.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पाश|पाशः<BR>पाश m. (r. पश् ligare s. अ) funis. SA. 5.16. (V. r. 1. पश्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पाशव<BR>पाशव (a पशु s. अ, v. gr. 650.) pecuinus. N. 23.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पाशुपत|पाशुपतः<BR>पाशुपत m. (a पशुपति - animalium dominus, nomen Sivi suff.<BR>अ) sagitta miraculosa Sivi. A. 3.51.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पाषाण|पाषाणः<BR>पाषाण m. lapis. HIT. 57.4.: निकषपाषाण «lapis Lydius».<BR>(Cf. r. βάσανος.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पि<BR>1. पि 6. P. पियामि (गतौ) ire. In dial. Vêd. opimare, fecundum<BR>reddere, augere; fecundum fieri, augeri. (V.<BR>Westerg. et cf. प्यै, पीन.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=216-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

