पित्सत्|पित्सन्त्<BR>पित्सत् m. (volare volens, part. praes. praec.; nom.<BR>पित्सन्) avis. AM. (Cf. psittacus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=217-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पिधान|पिधानं<BR>पिधान n. (r. धा praef. पि pro अपि s. अन) tegumentum.<BR>(Cambro-brit. fedon «a skreen».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=217-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

