पिनाक|पिनाकं|पिनाकः<BR>पिनाक m. n.<BR>1) Sivi arcus. A. 3.5.<BR>2) tridens. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=217-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पिनाकिन्<BR>पिनाकिन् m. (a praec. s. इन्) nomen dei Sivi.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=217-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पिन्व्<BR>पिन्व् 1. P. (scribitur पिव्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>1) effundere. RIGV. 64.6.:<BR>पिन्वन्त्य् अपो मरुतः; 34.4.: {#triH pfkzo<BR>asme akzare 'va (akzarA iva) pinvatam#} «ter cibum<BR>nobis, aquarum instar, effundite (Asvini!)».<BR>2) conspergere,<BR>irrigare. RIGV. 64.5.: भूमिम् पिन्वन्ति पयसा.<BR>3) implere. RIGV. (v. Westerg.) पिन्वतम् अपितः<BR>(Schol. जलरहिता नदीः) पिन्वतन् धियः. ATM.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=217-b" target="_blank">Page217-b+ 37</a>]<BR>impleri, turgere. RIGV. 8.7.: {#yaH kukziH…samudra iva<BR>pinvate#}. (Fortasse पिन्व् reduplicatione ortum est e<BR>1. पा bibere - cf. पिवामि - ita ut sensu caus. primitive<BR>significet bibere facere; cf. मिन्व्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=217-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पिपासा<BR>पिपासा f. (a पिपास् DESID. rad. पा bibere suff. आ) bibendi<BR>desiderium, sitis. H. 1.4. SU. 1.8. (Fortasse gr.<BR>δίψα e βίψα pro πίψα.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=217-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

