पुङ्गव|पुंगव|पुङ्गवः<BR>पुङ्गव m. (e पुम् et गव bos, in compositis solum usurpato,<BR>a गो suff. अ; vid. गवराज apud Wils.)<BR>1) taurus.<BR>2) in fine compositorum optimus, princeps (cf. ऋषभ).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

