पुण्ड्|पुंड्<BR>पुण्ड् 1. P. (मर्दे; scribitur पुड्, gr. 110^a).) conterere. Cf.<BR>2. पुट्, पुंस्, मुण्ट्, मुट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्डरीक|पुंडरीक|पुंडरीकं|पुण्डरीकं|पुण्डरीकः<BR>पुण्डरीक n. alba lotus; v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्डरीकोदरप्रभ<BR>पुण्डरीकोदरप्रभ (BAH. e {#puRqarIkodara - puRqarIka +<BR>udara#} albae loti venter - et प्रभा splendor) albae loti<BR>ventris splendorem habens. H. 1.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्य|पुण्यं<BR>पुण्य (r. पुण् s. य)<BR>1) Adj. purus, justus, bonus, pulcher.<BR>N. 12.37. IN. 2.1. 9.23. BH. 7.9.<BR>2) n. Subst. virtus. N. 15.17.<BR>Lass. 34.7. IN. 2.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्यकर्तृ<BR>पुण्यकर्तृ m. (e praec. et कर्तृ) qui virtutem exercet, justus,<BR>probus, sanctus. IN. 2.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्यकर्मन्|पुण्यकर्म्मन्<BR>पुण्यकर्मन् (BAH. ex पुण्य et कर्मन् factum) bona, justa<BR>facta habens i. e. agens. IN. 1.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्यकृत्<BR>पुण्यकृत् (ex पुण्य et कृत् q. v. faciens) i. q. पुण्यकर्तृ.<BR>BH. 6.41.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्यगन्ध|पुण्यगंध|पुण्यगन्धः<BR>पुण्यगन्ध (BAH. ex पुण्य et गन्ध odor) suavem odorem<BR>habens, bene olens. IN. 2.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्यगन्धिन्<BR>पुण्यगन्धिन् (a पुण्यगन्ध suavis odor suff. इन्) suavi<BR>ordore praeditus. IN. 2.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्यवत्|पुण्यवन्त्<BR>पुण्यवत् (a पुण्य s. वत्)<BR>1) virtute praeditus, bonus,<BR>justus, probus.<BR>2) felix, fortunatus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुण्याह|पुण्याहं<BR>पुण्याह n. (e पुण्य et अह dies, v. gr. 681.) dies festus<BR>(Wilson: A holy day).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुत्र|पुत्त्रः|पुत्रः<BR>पुत्र m. filius. In Plur. et ubi in initio comp. pluralem habet<BR>sensum,<BR>1) filii,<BR>2) liberi, tam masculini quam feminini.<BR>BR. 1.19. Scribitur etiam पुत्त्र. (Armor. paotr puer;<BR>pers. pusr filius, puer; lat. puer; v. पुत्री.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुत्रक|पुत्त्रकः|पुत्रकः<BR>पुत्रक m. (a praec. s. क) filius. Lass. 2.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुत्रदार<BR>पुत्रदार n. (DVANDV. e पुत्र et दार, v. gr. 660.) liberi et<BR>uxor. BR. 1.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुत्रपौत्रिन्<BR>पुत्रपौत्रिन् (ex comp. DVANDV. पुत्रपौत्र suff. इन्) filios<BR>et filiorum filios habens vel liberos et liberorum liberos<BR>habens. SA. 5.57.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुत्रिका<BR>पुत्रिका (Fem. τοῦ पुत्रक, mutato penultimo अ in इ)<BR>filia. N. 16.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुत्रिन्<BR>पुत्रिन् (a पुत्र s. इन्) liberos habens. N. 24.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुत्री<BR>पुत्री f. (a पुत्र signo fem. ई) filia. SA. 1.29. (Hib. piuthar<BR>«a sister».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुत्रीय|पुत्त्रीयं<BR>पुत्रीय (a पुत्र s. ईय) ad filium, ad filios, ad liberos spectans.<BR>RAGH. 10.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुथ्<BR>पुथ् 4. P. praesertim 10. P. पुथ्यामि, पोथयामि conterere.<BR>DR. 8.22.: {#gajaH…patann avAkSiro BUmO hastyArohAn<BR>apoTayat#}; MAH. 4.643.: {#tasya poTayAmi padA<BR>SiraH#}; 3.11106.: महावृक्षान् पोथयन्; 5.5021.: {#poTayAmAsa<BR>tAn sarvAn#}; 3.545.: सर्वान् सर्पान् अपोथयत्.<BR>(Cf. पुन्थ्, पुण्ड्, 2. {#puw, maT, manT, muw,<BR>muRw, kunT#}, lat. quatio, concutio, mutatâ labiali in gutturalem,<BR>sicut e. c. in quinque = पञ्च; v. कुन्थ्.)<BR>c. वि id. DEV. 2.57.: {#vipoTitA nipAtena gadayA Buvi<BR>Serate#}; MAH. 4.1105.: अश्वान् अस्य व्यपोथयत्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुनर्<BR>पुनर् Adv.<BR>1) iterum, denuo, rursus. N. 8.8. 15.16. Saepe<BR>repetitur. N. 7.16.<BR>2) retro. पुनर् एष्यति redibit. DR. 6.16.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">Page220-a+ 37</a>]<BR>3) adhuc. DR. 9.4.<BR>4) autem, vero. UR. 47.9. 58.8.<BR>- किम् पुनर् v. किम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=219-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुनरुक्त|पुनरुक्तं<BR>पुनरुक्त (e पुनर् et उक्त dictus)<BR>1) repetitus, v. sq.<BR>2) superfluus,<BR>supervacuus. UR. 39.10. 89.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुनर्जन्मन्<BR>पुनर्जन्मन् (e पुनर् et जन्मन्)<BR>1) KARM. n. regeneratio,<BR>nova nativitas. BH. 8.15.<BR>2) BAH. m. (repetitam, alteram<BR>nativitatem habens) Brâhmanus, v. {#dvija,<BR>dvijAti#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुनर्लाभ<BR>पुनर्लाभ m. (ex पुनर् et लाभ adeptio) recuperatio. N. 16.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुन्थ्<BR>पुन्थ् 1. P. (हिंसायां सङ्क्लेशे K. कुन्थे V.; scribitur पुथ्,<BR>gr. 110^a).) vexare, occidere. V. पुथ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुन्नाग|पुंनाग|पुन्नागः<BR>पुन्नाग m. nomen arboris (Wils. Rottleria tinctoria).<BR>N. 12.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुमांस्<BR>पुमांस् v. पुंस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुर्<BR>1. पुर् 6. P. (अग्रगमने K. अग्रगत्याम् V.) praecedere, ire.<BR>Cf. पर.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुर्<BR>2. पुर् f. (Nom. पूर्, पूः) urbs. RAGH. 16.23. v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुर|पुरं|पुरः<BR>पुर n. (ut videtur, a rad. पॄ vel पूर् implere, v. Lass.) urbs.<BR>V. पुरी.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरःसर|पुरःसरः<BR>पुरःसर m. (e पुरस् q. v. et सर a rad. सृ suff. अ) antecedens,<BR>dux.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरतस्<BR>पुरतस् Adv. (a पुरस् abjecto स् suff. तस्) coram. Vaivarta-Pur. Stenzl. 2.70.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरन्दर|पुरंदर|पुरन्दरं|पुरंदरः|पुरन्दरः<BR>पुरन्दर m. (urbem findens, urbium destructor, e<BR>पुर in Acc. et दर a rad. दॄ suff. अ, v. gr. 645.) nomen<BR>Indri. IN. 3.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरस्<BR>पुरस् Praep.<BR>1) ante, in initio compp.; v. धा, पुरःसर, पुरोगम<BR>etc.<BR>2) coram, c. gen. MEGH. 3. (Cf. पर, goth.<BR>faur ante pro fur, v. gr. comp. 82.; germ. vet. fora,<BR>for, nostrum vor; fortasse lat. coram e poram, palam e<BR>param; boruss. vet. pirs-dan ante, coram.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरस्कृ<BR>पुरस्कृ (e पुरस् et कृ facere) primo loco ponere. SU. 3.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरस्तात्<BR>पुरस्तात् (a पुरस् s. स्तात्, v. gr. 652.) coram, c. gen. A. 4.10.<BR>Absol. in fronte. BH. 11.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरा<BR>पुरा Adv.<BR>1) antea, olim. H. 1.30. 4.10. N. 10.8.<BR>2) priusquam, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">Page220-b+ 37</a>]<BR>antequam. DR. 6.20. 21.; cum ablat. A. 4.20. SA. 5.99.<BR>(Cf. पुरस् et v. पर.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुराण|पुराणं|पुराणः<BR>पुराण (a पुरा)<BR>1) Adj. (fem. आ et ई) antiquus, priscus.<BR>M. 56. BH. 2.20. 15.4.<BR>2) n. nomen carminum mythologicorum,<BR>octodecim numero.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरातन|पुरातनः<BR>पुरातन Adj. (fem. ई, a पुरा suff. तन) antiquus, pristinus.<BR>SU. 1.1. N. 24.49. BH. 4.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरी<BR>पुरी f. (a पुर n. urbs, signo fem. ई) urbs. IN. 1.42. N. 13.47.<BR>(Gr. πόλις, fortasse lat. urbs, litteris transpositis.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरीष|पुरीषं<BR>पुरीष n. faeces, excrementum. HIT. 85.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरु|पुरुः<BR>पुरु<BR>1) Adj. m. f. n. (r. पॄ i. e. पर् implere s. उ) multus.<BR>AM.<BR>2) m. nom. pr. regis. (Cf. पुल्, पुल, पूर्, पूर्ण;<BR>gr. πολύς, goth. filu, germ. vet. filu, filo, vilo, nostrum<BR>viel, lat. plus quasi पुरीयस्, plurimus e plusimus; fortasse<BR>hib. mor «great, big, bulky, many, noble», moradh<BR>«augmentation» mutatâ labiali mutâ in nasalem ejusdem<BR>organi; ita lat. mul-tus; v. पूर्, पूर्ण.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरुष|पुरुषः<BR>पुरुष m.<BR>1) vir, mas, homo. IN. 4.2. H. 2.30. BR. 1.8.<BR>2) famulus, minister. N. 13.65. 18.5. 11.18. SA. 5.15.<BR>3) anima, animus, spiritus. BH. 8.10. 22. 13.19. etc. 15.16. etc.<BR>4) nomen arboris. SA. 6.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरोगम|पुरोगमः<BR>पुरोगम m. (ex पुरस् et गम iens) praeiens, dux. N. 12.123.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरोडाश|पुरोडाशः<BR>पुरोडाश m. butyrum purificatum sacrificum. DR. 6.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरोधस्<BR>पुरोधस् m. (ex पुरस् ante et धस् a धा ponere suff. अस्)<BR>sacerdos. BH. 10.24. cf. पुरोहित.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुरोहित|पुरोहितः<BR>पुरोहित m. (antepositus ex पुरस् et हित) id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुर्व्<BR>पुर्व् 1. P. (पूरणे K. पूर्तौ V.) implere. Cf. पर्व्, पूर्, पॄ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुल्<BR>1. पुल् 1. et 6. P. पोलामि, पुलामि (महत्वे) magnum<BR>esse vel fieri. (ल् pro र्, cf. पुरु.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुल्<BR>2. पुल् 10. P. (सङ्घाते K. उच्छ्रितौ V.) coacervare; eminere,<BR>altum, magnum esse; v. 1. पुल्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुल|पुलः<BR>पुल (r. पुल् s. अ)<BR>1) Adj. magnus, amplus.<BR>2) Subst. m.<BR>erectio pilorum. (Cf. lat. pilum, v. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पुलक|पुलकं|पुलकः<BR>पुलक m. (r. पुल् s. अक) erectio pilorum. (Cf. lith. plauka-s<BR>coma, quod etiam a प्लु volare derivari potest.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=220-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

