पू<BR>पू 9. P. A. et 1. A. पुनामि, पुने (gr. 385.), पवे. Purificare,<BR>lustrare. R. Schl. prooem. 3.: {#punAti Buvanam puRyA<BR>rAmAyaRamahAnadI#}; MAH. 3.6030.; MAN. 11.248.: भ्रूणहणम्…पुनन्ति;<BR>MAH. 3.7081.: कुलम् पुनीते; BHATT. 6.61.:<BR>पवसे हविः; 1. P. BH. 10.31.: {#pavanaH pavatAm<BR>asmi#}. — Pass. MAN. 2.62.: {#hfdgABiH (adBiH) pUyate<BR>vipraH pUta#} lustratus. BH. 4.10. 9.10. Caus. facere ut<BR>alqs lustretur, lustrare. MAH. 5.414.: पावयिष्यामि वज्रिणम्.<BR>(Cf. lat. pû-rus, pu-tare; lith. pûs-tas desertus,<BR>vastus (e put-tas? v. gr. comp. 102.), pus-tau acuo,<BR>v. तिज्, तेजस्; germ. vet. bar purus, nudus, inanis<BR>fortasse a Caus. पावयामि mutato v in r sicut in birumês<BR>sumus = भवामस्, gr. comp. 20. V. पावक, पवित्र.)<BR>c. परि i. q. simpl. MAN. 8.330. 331.<BR>c. वि id. MAH. 2.1150.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=221-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

