पृ<BR>2. पृ 6. A. प्रिये (व्यायामे) laborare, operam dare, occupatum<BR>esse.<BR>c. आ praef. वि id. व्यापृत occupatus. MAH. 2.2126.: {#mA<BR>vyApftaH parakAryezu BUH#}; 1.7281.: वैवस्वतो व्यापृतः सत्रहेतोः;<BR>4.597.: व्यापृतो गोषु; R. Schl. II.39.14.: {#vyApftam<BR>vittasaYcaye#}. — Caus. occupare, occupatum tenere.<BR>RAGH. 2.38.: {#vanadvipAnAn trAsArTam asminn<BR>aham vanakukzO vyApAritaH SUlaBftA#}; 7.54.: {#sa dakziRan<BR>tURamuKena vAmam vyApArayan hastam#}; 6.19.:<BR>एकम् व्यापारयामास करङ् किरीटे. (Cf. पॄ, पूर् implere;<BR>पृत occupatus proprie oneratus, chargé.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=222-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृ<BR>3. पृ 10. P. पारयामि (पूरणे K. पालने पूर्तौ V.) implere;<BR>nutrire, sustentare. Cf. पॄ, पूर्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=222-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृच्<BR>1. पृच् 7. P. पृणच्मि.<BR>1) miscere, conjungere. RAGH. 213.:<BR>पृक्तस् तुषारैः पवनः; BHATT. 6.39.: अपृणग् धनुषा शरम्.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-a" target="_blank">Page223-a+ 35</a>]<BR>— De आपृच्, उपपृच्, प्रपृच् in dial. Vêd.<BR>v. Westerg. (Cf. पृज्, पृञ्ज्, वृच्; Graffius - III.769. - apte<BR>huc refert gr. πλέϰω, ut videtur e πέϱϰω cum λ<BR>pro ϱ qnod in πόϱϰης, πόϱϰος servatum est; lat. plico,<BR>plecto; germ. vet. FLAHT, flihtu, flaht, fluhtumês.)<BR>c. सम् conjungere. सम्पृक्त conjunctus. MAN. 9.322. 12.14. 19.;<BR>R. Schl. II.65.8. RAGH. 1.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=222-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृच्<BR>2. पृच् 1. et 10. P. 2. A. i. q. पृच् cl. 7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

