पृथिवीपति|पृथिवीपतिः<BR>पृथिवीपति m. (terrae dominator e praec. et पति<BR>dominus, dominator) rex.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृथिवीक्षित्<BR>पृथिवीक्षित् m. (e पृथिवी et क्षित् q. v.) terrae dominator,<BR>rex. N. 5.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृथु|पृथुः<BR>पृथु (fem. पृथु et पृथ्वी, compar. प्रथीयस्, superl. प्रथिष्ठ,<BR>r. प्रथ् s. उ) latus, amplus, magnus. N. 19.13. IN. 5.5. 27.<BR>(Gr. πλατύς; lith. platùs id.; anglo-sax. brâd; goth.<BR>braid-s; nostrum breit; hib. farsaing «wide, ample» mutato<BR>थ् in s, farsneachd «width», farsnighim «I widen»;<BR>lat. latus e platus?)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृथुल|पृथुलं<BR>पृथुल (a praec. s. ल) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृथुलोचन<BR>पृथुलोचन Adj. (BAH. ex पृथु et लोचन oculus) magnos<BR>oculos habens. IN. 5.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृथुश्रोणी<BR>पृथुश्रोणी f. (e पृथु et श्रोणी lumbus, femur, clunis) lata,<BR>turgida femora habens. IN. 5.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृथ्वी<BR>पृथ्वी f. (magna, lata, fem. a पृथु) terra, cf. मही; usitatius<BR>est पृथिवी, quod e पृथ्वी inserto इ ortum esse<BR>censeo. (*) (Cambro-brit. prîz «mould or earth».)<BR>(*) Wilsonus deducit पृथ्वी a पृथु nomine regis, प्रथिवी<BR>vero a rad. प्रथ् celebrem esse.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृष्<BR>पृष् 1. P. (सेके) inspergere, adspergere, irrigare. Cf. वृष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृषत्|पृषन्त्<BR>पृषत् (Part. praes. rad. पृष्) inspergens, adspergens, irrigans.<BR>— Subst.<BR>1) n. gutta. AM.<BR>2) m. (nom. पृषन्)<BR>nomen animalis, Wils. «the porcine deer». AM. Fem.<BR>पृषती. RAGH. 8.58.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृषत|पृषतः<BR>पृषत m. (r. पृष् s. अत)<BR>1) gutta. RAGH. 3.3.<BR>2) nomen<BR>animalis (v. praec.). DR. 4.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृष्ट<BR>पृष्ट v. प्रछ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृष्ठ|पृष्ठं<BR>पृष्ठ n. (fortasse e praep. प्र et स्थ stans, nisi, quod sensui<BR>magis congruit, e परा correpto अरा in ऋ, et स्थ, v. उपस्थ)<BR>dorsum, tergum. H. 1.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पृष्ठतस्<BR>पृष्ठतस् Adv. (a praec. s. तस्) a tergo. SU. 3.26. 27. BH. 11.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पॄ<BR>पॄ 3. et 9. P. पिपर्मि, पृणामि (v. gr. 385.)<BR>1) implere.<BR>RIGV. V. (v. Westerg.): यः समुद्रान् पिपर्ति. Part.<BR>pass. पूर्ण (gr. 607.) impletus, plenus. MAH. 3.16625.:<BR>पूणे वर्षे. Etiam पूर्त. PAN. VIII.2.57.<BR>2) satiare. RIGV.<BR>(v. Westerg.): पिपृतन् नो भरीमभिः (= भरिमभिः).<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=224-a" target="_blank">Page224-a+ 36</a>]<BR>3) largiri. RIGV. 33.21.: पृणीत भेपजम्.<BR>4) servare,<BR>tutari, custodire. RIGV. V. (v. Westerg.): ता अंहसः पिपृहि.<BR>5) trajicere, traducere. ibd.: पारं नः…पर्षन्; v.<BR>अतिपॄ, तिरःपॄ. (V. पृ, पूर्, पूल्, पृण्, पूण् et cf. gr.<BR>πίμπλημι cum पिपर्मि; cum part. pass. पूर्ण impletus,<BR>plenus cf. lith. pilna-s, lat. plenus, goth. fulls, Them.<BR>fulla per assimil. e fulna; cum formâ पूर्त cf. hib. pailt<BR>«abundant, plentiful, copious», lith. pri-pilta-s plenus.)<BR>c. अति trajicere, traducere. RIGV. 97.8.: {#sa naH sinDum<BR>iva nAvayA 'tiparzA#} (= अतिपर्ष, imper. praet. mtf.);<BR>99.1.: स नः पर्षद् अति दुःखानि.<BR>c. अभि implere. अभिपूर्ण impletus, plenus. DR. 4.19.<BR>c. तिरस् trajicere, traducere. RIGV. V. (v. Westerg.): {#durgA<BR>pipftan tiro naH#}.<BR>c. परि परिपूर्ण impletus, plenus. N. 13.64.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=223-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

