पेटक|पेटकं|पेटकः<BR>पेटक m. n. (r. पिट् s. अक) id. UR. 86.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=224-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पेण्<BR>पेण् 1. P. (पेषगतिश्लेषेषु) conterere, ire, amplecti.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=224-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पेल्<BR>पेल् 1. P. (गतौ K. चाले गतौ V., proprie पिल् q. v.) ire,<BR>se movere, vacillare. (Cf. चल् e कल्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=224-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

