पोत|पोतः<BR>1. पोत m. (fem. पोती, fortasse a r. पुष् abjecto ष्, nisi<BR>potius पोत pro पात, a r. पा nutrire, ita ut आ attenuatum<BR>sit in ऊ, unde ओ adjecto gunae incremento; v. पोत्र<BR>et cf. Pott. I.193.) pullus, catulus. H. 2.18. (Cf. lith.<BR>pauta-s ovum; gr. πῶ-λος; lat. pullus, pûsus; goth. fula<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=224-b" target="_blank">Page224-b+ 36</a>]<BR>pullus, Them. fulan; germ. vet. folo m., fuli n.; v. r.<BR>पाल्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=224-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

