प्यै<BR>प्यै 1. A. (वृद्धौ) pinguescere, crescere. Part. pass. पीन<BR>pinguis, corpulentus, crassus, turgidus. N. 5.6. Etiam<BR>प्यान. PAN. VI.1.28. (V. पीवर et cf. gr. πῑαϱός, πῖας, πῑων, πῑμελή;<BR>lat. pinguis; island. vet. feit-r pinguis;<BR>anglo-sax. faett; germ. vet. feizt; nostrum feist, fett; v.<BR>Graff. III.738.)<BR>c. आ<BR>1) pinguescere, crescere. RIGV. 91.16.: आप्यायस्व.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=225-a" target="_blank">Page225-a+ 37</a>]<BR>— आप्यान pinguis, turgidus. BHATT. 5.16. 9.2.<BR>2) augere, corroborare. MAH. 5.508.: {#apyAyaDvan tapasA<BR>tejasA mAm#}. — Caus.<BR>1) pinguefacere, augere,<BR>amplificare. MAH. 3.13542.: {#tejasA tava tejo vizRur<BR>ApyAyizyati#}; R. Schl. I.28.30.: {#tapoyogabalenE<BR>'nam ApyAyayitum arhasi#}.<BR>2) exhilarare, oblectare.<BR>MEGH. 45.: आप्याययेस् तम् मयूरम्. V. आप्यायित.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् id. BHATT. 14.62.: मन्युर् अस्य समापिप्ये.<BR>— Caus. MAH. 3.8725.: {#sa samApyAyito vizRunA<BR>balavAn samapadyata#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=224-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

