प्रभिन्नकरट<BR>प्रभिन्नकरट Adj. (BAH. ex praec. et करट elephanti gena)<BR>fissas genas habens, dicitur de elephantis, quibus ardoris<BR>coëundi tempore succus मद dictus ex temporibus effluit.<BR>SU. 2.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=229-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रभु|प्रभुः<BR>प्रभु m. (a r. भू praef. प्र et correpto ऊ, v. not. ad gr. 49.)<BR>dominus, excelsus, augustus. H. 1.25. SU. 1.19. 2.6. BH. 5.14.<BR>— Cum infin. qui par, idoneus est alicui rei efficiendae.<BR>RAGH. 2.62. (Fortasse goth. frauja dominus e<BR>frabuja; germ. vet. frô dominus, frowa domina; nostrum<BR>Frau.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=229-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रभुत्व|प्रभुत्वं<BR>प्रभुत्व n. (a praec. s. त्व) imperium. RAGH. 18.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=229-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रभृति|प्रभृतिः<BR>प्रभृति Adv. (Acc. neut. τοῦ प्रभृति f. a r. भृ praef. प्र s.<BR>ति) in posterum, c. antecedente ablat. vel formâ in तस्<BR>vel compositi membro ablativi vice fungente; e. c. {#bAlyAt<BR>praBfti#} ab infantiâ in posterum, inde ab infantiâ,<BR>ततःप्रभृति abhinc in posterum, inde ab hoc tempore.<BR>N. 2.1. यतःप्रभृति ex quo - tempore. SA. 4.27. जन्मप्रभृति<BR>inde a natalibus. RAM. अद्यप्रभृति inde ab hodierno<BR>die. SA. 2.23. In fine compositorum DVANDV. declinationem<BR>plur. assumit; e. c. विश्वावसुप्रभृतयो गन्धर्वाः<BR>Visvâvasus et posteri (ceteri) Gandharvi. IN. 2.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=229-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रमदा<BR>प्रमदा f. (r. मद् praef. प्र s. अ in fem.) femina. SU. 3.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=229-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रमदावन|प्रमदावनं<BR>प्रमदावन n. (ex praec. et वन sylva) nemus voluptarium<BR>regium. N. 1.25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=229-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रमाण|प्रमाणं<BR>प्रमाण n. (r. मा metiri praef. प्र s. अन, v. gr. min. 94^b).<BR>annot.)<BR>1) mensura, modus. RAGH. 18.37. 41.<BR>2) dijudicatio,<BR>arbitrium, auctoritas. BH. 3.21. 16.24. SA. 2.28.<BR>N. 4.31. 18.13. 19.32. 33. — Plur. masc. id. DR. 9.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=229-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रमाथ|प्रमाथः<BR>प्रमाथ m. (r. मथ् praef. प्र s. अ) actio commovendi, agitandi,<BR>perturbandi, vexandi, praecipue feminae raptus; [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=230-a" target="_blank">Page230-a+ 37</a>]<BR>ita Mahâbhârati quoddam episodium inscribitur द्रौपदीप्रमाथ<BR>Draupadiae raptus. DR. 5.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=229-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रमाथिन्<BR>प्रमाथिन् (a r. मथ् praef. प्र s. इन्) qui agitat, commovet,<BR>tremefacit. BH. 2.60. (Schol. {#pramATIni pramaTanaSIlAni<BR>kzoBakAni#}), 6.34. DR. 7.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=230-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

