प्रवण|प्रवणः<BR>प्रवण (e प्र et वण incertae originis, nisi प्रवण e प्रपन्न<BR>inclinatus, mutato प् in व् sicut in पिवामि pro पिपामि)<BR>1) declivis.<BR>2) propensus, deditus, addictus. P. 9.<BR>(Fortasse lat. prônus e provonus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=230-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

