प्रासाद|प्रासादः<BR>प्रासाद m. (r. सद् ire c. आ praef. प्र s. अ) palatium. H. 1.34.<BR>N. 13.49. 21.6. 22.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=232-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्राह्न<BR>प्राह्न m. (KARM. ex प्र et अह्न dies in fine compp.) dies antemeridianus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=232-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रिय|प्रियः<BR>प्रिय (r. प्री diligere s. अ) amatus, dilectus, carus, gratus.<BR>IN. 5.32. H. 2.34. BH. 5.20. 7.17. N. 18.16. SA. 5.95.<BR>— Subst. m.<BR>1) amasius. MEGH. 29. Lass. 25.13.<BR>2) maritus.<BR>AM. (Cambro-brit. priawd «a maried person, a<BR>spouse».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=232-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रियंवद|प्रियंवदः<BR>प्रियंवद vel प्रियम्वद (ex प्रिय in acc. et वद् dicens, v.<BR>gr. 645. s. अ) gratum dicens, dulciloquus, suaviloquus.<BR>IN. 4.11. SU. 1.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=232-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रियकाम<BR>प्रियकाम (BAH. ex प्रिय et काम desiderium, amor) grati<BR>desiderium habens, benevolus. BR. 2.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=232-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रियकार<BR>प्रियकार (ex प्रिय et कार faciens) gratum faciens. SU. 1.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=232-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रियातिथि<BR>प्रियातिथि (dilectos hospites habens, BAH. ex प्रिय<BR>et अतिथि) hospitalis. DR. 3.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=232-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रियाल|प्रियालः<BR>प्रियाल m. nomen arboris (Wils.: A tree, commonly Piyal,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-a" target="_blank">Page233-a+ 36</a>]<BR>Buchanalia latifolia, Roxburgh's catalogue, but<BR>the name is applied to different trees).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=232-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्री<BR>1. प्री 9. P. A. (तर्पणे K. कान्तौ तर्पणे V.) प्रीणामि, प्रीणे.<BR>1) exhilarare. MAH. 3.4007.: तन् मे प्रीणाति हृदयम्;<BR>BHAR. 2.58.: प्रीणाति यः सुचरितैः पितरं स पुत्रः. — प्रीत<BR>exhilaratus. IN. 4.15. SU. 1.20.<BR>2) amare.<BR>BH. 10.1.: यत् ते ऽहम् प्रीयमाणाय वक्ष्यामि हितकाम्यया<BR>(amato?). (Goth. frijô amo, frijônds amans,<BR>amicus, fria-thva fem. amor, quasi प्रियत्व, quod e प्रिय<BR>formari posset; faihu-freiks pecuniam amans, avarus;<BR>germ. vet. friunt amicus, fri-du m. fri-da f. pax, friudil,<BR>fri-del, fre-del amasius, quod cum lith. priế-telus<BR>amicus, russ. prijatelj ad comparat. प्रियतर traxerim,<BR>mutato r in l; frao, fraw, frô laetus; frawî laetitia; unde<BR>denomin. frawôn, frôôn laetari, frawjan exhilarare; gr.<BR>ϕίλος, ϕιλέω, ut videtur, litteris transpositis ΦΙΛ e<BR>ΦΛΙ cum λ pro ϱ; πϱαΰς, πϱᾶος; fortasse lat. pla-ceo,<BR>pla-co nituntur formâ gunatâ प्रे = prai, abjecto i; fortasse<BR>pius e prius = प्रिय; lae-tus e plae-tus explicari<BR>potest, sicut latus e platus, v. पृथु; fortasse filius, nisi<BR>est e fidius, primitive significat amatus, ita ut sit =<BR>प्रिय; de cambro-brit. prïawd v. प्रिय; de hib. frith v.<BR>प्रीति.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्री<BR>2. प्री 4. A. gaudere, laetari (proprie Pass. praec.) MAH. 1.1070.:<BR>प्रीयामहे भृशन् तात; 2173.: प्रीयताम् अयम्;<BR>4.275.: प्रीयेरंस् तेन वासेन; RAGH. 15.30.: {#paSyan<BR>yamunAm…pipriye#}. — Cum acc. R. Schl. I.52.11.:<BR>प्रीयेतान् तौ परस्परम् alter altero (प्रीयेताम् omisso<BR>augmento pro अप्रीयेताम्). Cum terminatione PAR.<BR>MAH. 3.15025.: प्रीयामो दर्शनेन वः. — Caus. {#prIRayAmi,<BR>prIRaye#} (v. gr. 523.) facere ut quis laetetur, exhilarare.<BR>MAH. 1.6414.: वनानि प्रीणयन्ति नः; 1.5047.:<BR>प्रीणयते चक्षुस् तस्य सः.<BR>c. सम् i. q. simpl. R. Schl. II.48.18.: {#ko nv anena…<BR>samprIyetA 'manojYena vAsena#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्री<BR>3. प्री 1. P. A. प्रयामि, प्रये i. q. प्री cl. 9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्री<BR>4. प्री 10. P. A. प्राययामि, प्रायये (proprie Caus. reg. pro<BR>anom. प्रीणयामि, v. 2. प्री) exhilarare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रीति|प्रीतिः<BR>प्रीति f. (r. प्री s. ति)<BR>1) gaudium, voluptas. IN. 1.37. 3.10.<BR>H. 2.31. SU. 4.8.<BR>2) amor, amicitia. HIT. 17.10. et 11. 22.19.<BR>(Hib. frith f. «service, attendance».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रु<BR>प्रु 1. A. (गतौ K. सर्पणे V.) ire. Cf. प्लु.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रुष्<BR>1. प्रुष् 1. P. (दाहे K. दहि V.; ut mihi videtur, e praep. प्र<BR>abjecto अ et उष्) urere, ardere. RIGV. 58.2.: प्रुषित<BR>flagrans. (Cf. प्लुष्, germ. vet. FRUS frigere, v.<BR>Graff. III.828., nostrum frieren, Frost.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रुष्<BR>2. प्रुष् 9. P. प्रुष्णामि (स्नेहनमोचनपूरणेषु K. {#sekapUrtyoH<BR>snehe#} V.) amare, dimittere, implere, conspergere,<BR>effundere. Cf. पृष्, पूर्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रेक्षणीय<BR>प्रेक्षणीय Adj. (Part. fut. pass. a r. ईक्ष् praef. प्र s. अनीय,<BR>v. euph. r. 94^a).) spectandus, spectatu dignus. IN. 5.13.<BR>in Comparativo.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

