प्रेष्य|प्रेष्यः<BR>प्रेष्य m. (mittendus ex प्रेषय् — Caus. rad. इष् praef. प्र s.<BR>य) servus, famulus, minister. IN. 5.20. N. 17.33. 21.30.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रेष्यता<BR>प्रेष्यता f. (a praec. s. ता) servitudo. N. 16.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रेष्यवधू<BR>प्रेष्यवधू f. (KARM. ex प्रेष्य et वधू femina) famula, serva.<BR>DR. 6.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रोत|प्रोतं<BR>प्रोत v. वे praef. प्र.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रोथ|प्रोथः<BR>प्रोथ m. n. nasus animalis, ut equi, apri. N. 19.13. A. 3.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्रौढ|प्रौढं<BR>प्रौढ v. वह् praef. प्र.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लक्ष्<BR>प्लक्ष् 1. P. A. (भक्षणे) edere. Cf. भक्ष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लक्ष|प्लक्षः<BR>प्लक्ष m. nomen arboris (Wils.:<BR>1) The waved leaf fig tree,<BR>ficus infectoria.<BR>2) Another tree, Hibiscus populneoides. [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">Page234-a+ 36</a>]<BR>3) The holy fig, Ficus religiosa).<BR>N. 12.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=233-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लव्<BR>प्लव् 1. A. (गतौ) ire. Cf. प्लु, unde प्लव् adjecto Gunae incremento.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लव|प्लवं|प्लवः<BR>प्लव m. (r. प्लु natare s. अ)<BR>1) saltus.<BR>2) natatio, natatus.<BR>3) navis. BR. 3.4. H. 1.14. BH. 4.36. (Gr. πλόος, πλόῖον;<BR>hib. falc «a flood» e flac, quod e flav? v. प्लु.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लवग|प्लवगः<BR>प्लवग m. (e प्लव saltus et ग iens)<BR>1) simia. RAGH. 12.70.<BR>2) rana. MED.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लवङ्ग|प्लवंग|प्लवंगः|प्लवङ्गः<BR>प्लवङ्ग m. (e प्लव in acc. et ग iens) simia. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लवङ्गम|प्लवंगम|प्लवंगमः|प्लवङ्गमः<BR>प्लवङ्गम (e प्लव in acc. et गम iens) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लविन्<BR>प्लविन् m. (r. प्लु s. इन्) avis.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लिह्<BR>प्लिह् 1. A. (गतौ K. गत्याम् V.) ire, se movere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लिहन्<BR>प्लिहन् m. (ut videtur, a r. प्लिह् s. अन्) lien. (Gr. σπλήν, σπλάγχνον<BR>praefixo σ, nisi प्लिहन् e स्प्लिहन्; lat. lien<BR>abjecto p.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्ली<BR>प्ली 9. P. प्लीणामि ire. Cf. प्लु, ली.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लु<BR>प्लु 1. A. interdum P.<BR>1) natare. MAH. 2.2196.: शिलाः प्लवन्ते…अम्भसि;<BR>A. 6.5.: तत्र रत्नसङ्घाः प्लवन्ति;<BR>R. Schl. II.69.9.: प्लवमानश्च ह्रदे. Intens. R. Schl. II.95.10.:<BR>{#poplUyamAnAn aparAn paSya tvaY jalamaDyagAn<BR>(puzpasaYcayAn)#}.<BR>2) navigare, navi proficisci. M. 36.:<BR>सागरम् पुप्लुवे तदा नौकया; MAH. 1.4207.: {#plavamAnaH<BR>yadfcCayA jagAma subahUn deSAn anDas teno<BR>'qupena ha#}.<BR>3) volare (in aëre navigare). MAH. 3.11767.:<BR>प्लवमाना विहायसा गन्धमादनम् आजग्मुः (यक्षाः);<BR>2.386.: {#saBA…guhyakEr uhyamAnA sA Ke…plavamAne<BR>'va dfSyate#}; v. प्लाविन् avis.<BR>3) transsilire. R. Schl. I.1.70.:<BR>शतयोजनविस्तीर्णम् पुप्लुवे लवणार्णवम्;<BR>MAH. 3.11227.: प्लवतः (transilientis); 16255.: {#pupluve<BR>'ham mahArRavaM SatayojanavistIrRam#}.<BR>4) flare. MAH. 3.11070.:<BR>प्लवमानो वायुः. — Caus. alluere, perfundere.<BR>R. Schl. I.42.19.: {#BaSmarASIkftAn etAn plAvayel<BR>lokapAvanI (gaNgA)#}; 44.43.: {#aTa gaNgAmBasA<BR>tatra plAvitAH sAgarAtmajAH#}; MAH. 3.12885.: {#jaladA<BR>GorAH…sarvataH plAvayanti…vasunDarAm#}. — ATM.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-b" target="_blank">Page234-b+ 37</a>]<BR>se lavare. R. Schl. I.44.56.: {#plAvayasva tvam AtmAnam…sado<BR>'cite salile#}. (Cf. प्रु; lat. PLU, pluit; fluo;<BR>mutatâ tenui in asp.; fortasse fundo e flundo adjecto<BR>d sicut in lith. plûs-tu e plûd-tu, et sicut t adjectum<BR>est in island. vet. FLUT; insertâ nasali sicut e. c. in<BR>tundo = तुदामि; luo e pluo? fortasse plu-ma a volando<BR>dictum sicut penna et nostrum Feder a पत्, q. v.; gr.<BR>πλέω e πλέϜω = प्लवामि, πλεύ-σομαι = प्लोष्ये;<BR>πλύ-νω; mutatâ tenui in aspir. vel mediam: ϕλύω, βλύω;<BR>abjecto π: λούω? russ. plyvu et plovu nato, navigo,<BR>fluo; lith. PLŪD, plus-tu, nato supra aquam, praet.<BR>plûdau; scot. plucas «a flux, ventris fluxio»; hib. plod «a<BR>fleet», plodaim «I float»; fortasse lua, scot. lu aqua, e<BR>plua, plu; scot. luaineas «motion, as of a stream»; cf.<BR>प्लवन; hib. luathaim «I hasten, I move», luan «a woman's<BR>breast», cf. पयोधर; island. vet. FLUT fluere, adjecto<BR>t, v. gr. comp. 109^b).; germ. vet. FLUZ id.; fortasse<BR>FLUG volare e FLUW, v. gr. comp. 19. et Graff. III.760.<BR>— Ad Caus. प्लावयामि pertinent: lith. pláuju<BR>eluo, abluo, praet. plówjau = अप्लावयम्; plauk-iu nato,<BR>cujus k e w ortum esse videtur sicut lat. fluc-si, fluc-tus<BR>e fluv-si, fluv-tus; cf. प्लुव् τοῦ पुप्लुवे; russ. plávaju nato;<BR>lat. plôro e plôvo sicut germ. vet. birumês sumus = भवामस्,<BR>v. gr. comp. 20.; fleo = प्लावयामि ejecto âv,<BR>eo = अयामि, -ês = अयसि, v. gr. comp. 109^a).6.;<BR>lavo, λούω e plavo, πλούω, nisi, quod minus mihi arridet,<BR>pertinent ad धाव्; germ. vet. flewiu lavo, flewitin<BR>lavarent, ar-flawêm eluo; v. Graff. III.740.; hib. falcaim<BR>«I bathe» e flacaim pro flavaim? mutato v in c, v. gr.<BR>comp. 19.)<BR>c. अभि perfundere, obruere. MAN. 4.41.: {#rajasA 'BiplutAn<BR>nArIm#} menstruis pollutam mulierem.<BR>c. अभि praef. सम् id. MAN. 4.42.: {#rajasA samaBiplutAm<BR>(nArIm)#}. TROP. MAH. 3.2016.: सर्वान् शोकः समभिपुप्लुवे.<BR>c. अव desilire. DR. 6.10.: रथाद् अवप्लुत्य.<BR>c. आ<BR>1) natare. A. 6.20.: आप्लवन्त गतैः सत्त्वैः मत्स्याः शतसहस्रशः.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=235-a" target="_blank">Page235-a+ 24</a>]<BR>2) submergere, lavare. MAH. 3.8514.:<BR>आप्लुत्य गात्राणि. Se submergere, se lavare. MAN. 11.202.:<BR>सचेलः…आप्लुत्य. — आप्लुत qui se submersit,<BR>se lavavit. IN. 1.20.: गङ्गायाम् आप्लुतः; 2.5.: {#anAplutEs<BR>tIrTezu#}. TROP. N. 18.12. 22.29.: व्यसनाप्लुत in<BR>calamitate submersus. — Cum acc. loci se immergere.<BR>MAN. 5.77.: सवासा जलम् आप्लुत्य. — Caus.<BR>1) facere<BR>ut alqs se lavet. MAH. 1.7334.: कृष्णाम् आप्लाव्य.<BR>2) humectare. MAN. 3.244.: अन्नाद्यम्…आप्लाव्य वारिणा.<BR>TROP. 11.97.<BR>3) transsilire (v. प्लु sens. 3.). R. Schl. I.16.24.:<BR>आप्लावेयुर् महार्णवान् (वानराः).<BR>c. आ praef. सम् irrigare. N. 4.13.: {#samAplutAByAn netrAByAM<BR>SokajenA 'Ta vAriRA#}.<BR>c. उत् subsilire. HIT. 27.13. 111.4. RITU-S. 1.18.<BR>c. उप perfundere, obruere; invadere, irruere. R. Schl. II.7.13.:<BR>उपप्लुतम् अघौघेन; MAN. 4.118.: {#cOrEr upaplute<BR>grAme#}; RAGH. 10.5.: देवाः पौलस्त्योपप्लुताः (Schol. रावणेनोपद्रुताः);<BR>14.64.<BR>c. परि circumfluere. MAH. 3.12884.: पृथिवी…सलिलौघपरिप्लुता;<BR>N. 24.7.: अश्रुपरिप्लुतः; 24.46.: शोकपरिप्लुतः.<BR>c. परि praef. अभि id. M. 9.<BR>c. वि<BR>1) circumagi. HIT. 79.10.: {#akarRaDArA jalaDO viplavete<BR>'ha nOr iva#}.<BR>2) confundi. MAH. 2.1429.: विप्लुताचा ऽस्य…बुद्धिः;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=235-b" target="_blank">Page235-b+ 24</a>]<BR>1430.: तस्य विप्लवते बुद्धिः.<BR>3) concumbere cum aliquâ, विप्लुत qui concubuit. MAN. 8.277.:<BR>ब्राह्मण्या गुप्तया सह विप्लुतौ (वैश्यपार्थिवौ);<BR>2.249.: अविप्लुतः. — Caus. divulgare, profanare<BR>arcanum. MAN. 11.198.: वेदम् विप्लाव्य (Schol. {#anaDyApyaM<BR>vedam aDyApya#}).<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) confluere. BH. 2.46.: उदपाने सर्वतः सम्प्लुतोदके.<BR>2) perfundere, obruere, implere. A. 2.12.: हर्षसम्प्लुतम्.<BR>— Caus. inundare. R. Schl. I.44.34.: {#gaNgA<BR>samplAvayAmAsa yajYavawam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=234-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लुष्<BR>1. प्लुष् 1. et 4. P. urere. RAM. II.79.20.: अग्निप्लुष्ट. V.<BR>प्रुष् et cf. प्लुस्.<BR>c. उत् comburere. RITU-S. (Lass.) 1.22.: वनदाहोत्प्लुष्टशस्पप्ररोहाः…वनान्ताः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=235-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लुष्<BR>2. प्लुष् 9. P.<BR>1) i. q. प्रष् cl. 9.<BR>2) urere. BHATT. 20.34.: {#pApam<BR>pluzRAtu vA 'nalaH#}; 20.37.: मा प्लुषाण वह्ने.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=235-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लुस्<BR>प्लुस् 4. P. (दाहविभागयोः K. दाहविभागे V.) urere, distribuere.<BR>V. प्लुष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=235-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्लेव्<BR>प्लेव् 1. A. (सेवने K. सेवे V.) servire, ministrare, colere,<BR>venerari. Cf. पेव्, मेव्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=235-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

प्सा<BR>प्सा 2. P. (भक्षणे) edere. BHATT. 15.6.: मांसम् अप्सासीत्.<BR>(Cf. भस्, unde in dialecto vêd. forma reduplicata<BR>बप्स्, v. Westerg.; germ. vet. spîsa cibus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=235-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

