फण्<BR>फण् 1. P. (गतौ) ire, se movere. — Caus.<BR>1) फणयामि<BR>facere ut alqs se moveat.<BR>2) फाणयामि pingue lactis<BR>auferre. K.: फाणयति दुग्धम् «he skims the milk».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=235-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

