फुल्ल्<BR>फुल्ल् 1. P. (ut videtur, Denom. a फुल्ल, v. 1. फल्) se expandere,<BR>de floribus; florescere. (Cf. gr. ϕύλλον =<BR>फुल्ल, v. 1. फल्; lat. folium; flôs, flôris e flôv-is, a flu per<BR>metath. e ful? sicut plôro = प्लावयामि a प्लु q. v.; anglo-sax.<BR>blôvan florere; germ. vet. bluôn, pluôn id.; blômo,<BR>Them. blô-mon; goth. blô-ma, Them. blô-man, flos,<BR>suff. man = मान, gr. μενος, part. praes. med.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=236-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

