बद्ध|बद्धं<BR>बद्ध v. बन्ध्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=236-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बध्<BR>1. बध् 1. A. (बन्धने K. निन्दे बन्धे V.) ligare, vituperare,<BR>spernere. V. बन्ध्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=236-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

