बधिर|बधिरः<BR>बधिर (ut videtur, a r. बन्ध् s. इर) surdus. AM. (Hib.<BR>bodhar, cambro-brit. byzar, armor. byzar id.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=236-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

