बन्ध्|बंध्<BR>1. बन्ध् 9. P. interdum A. (बध्नामि, बध्ने, v. gr. 387.) Pass.<BR>बध्ये (gr. 503.), part. बद्ध.<BR>1) ligare, alligare, religare.<BR>SA. 5.17.: यमस् तु तम्…बद्ध्वा; M. 47.: {#himavataH<BR>SfNge nAvam baDnIta#}; A. 5.13.: बबन्धचै ऽव मे<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-a" target="_blank">Page237-a+ 37</a>]<BR>मूर्द्ध्नि किरीटम्; R. Schl. II.74.29.: {#rajjum badDvA 'TavA<BR>kaRWe#}; MAH. 3.10727.: बन्धिष्ये सेतुना गङ्गाम्;<BR>BH. 4.14.: कर्मभिः स न बध्यते; M. 48.: {#sA (nOH)<BR>badDA tatra#}. Figere, defigere, e. c. animum, oculos. RAGH. 6.36.:<BR>तस्मिन्…बबन्ध सा न…भावम्; 3.4.: {#babanDa<BR>manaH#}; SAK. 43.7.: लक्षम् बद्ध्वा.<BR>2) capere, prehendere.<BR>HIT. 16.22.: {#baDyante nipuREr agADasalilAn<BR>matsyAH samudrAt#}.<BR>3) producere. RAGH. 12.69.:<BR>काले खलु समारब्धाः फलम् बध्नन्ति नीतयः (Schol.<BR>जनयन्ति). — Caus. ligandum curare. RAGH. 12.70.:<BR>स सेतुम् बन्धयामास प्लवगैः. (Cf. बुन्ध्, goth.<BR>BAND ligare, binda, band, bundum; fortasse anglo-sax.<BR>fas-t, faes-t; island. vet. fas-t; nostrum fes-t firmus,<BR>fixus = बद्ध; zend. baś-ta ligatus, v. gr. comp. 102.;<BR>gr. ΠΙΘ, mutatâ mediâ in tenuem sicut in ΠΑΘ =<BR>बध्, बाध्, attenuato a in i sicut in goth. binda; πεῖ-σ-μα, πείϑω;<BR>lat. fî-lum pro fid-lum, fû-nis pro fudnis,<BR>fid-es, fîd-o pro feido = πείϑω foed-us = foidus,<BR>regressâ aspiratione, v. gr. comp. 104., Ag. Benary «Römische<BR>Lautlehre p. 190»., cf. Pott. I.251.; lith. bandà<BR>pecus, a ligando dictum sicut पशु a पश्; slav. vjaζati<BR>ligare. V. बन्ध, बन्धन, बन्धु.)<BR>c. अनु<BR>1) ligare, alligare. R. Schl. I.72.8. DEV. 1.22.<BR>2) adhaerere. HIT. 24.20.: {#BaNge 'pi mfRAlAnAm anubaDnanti<BR>tantavaH#}.<BR>3) durare. N. 13.31.: {#nA 'nubaDnati<BR>kuSalam#}.<BR>c. आ illigare. R. Schl. II.96.31. MEGH. 9.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) ligare, adstringere. BH. 9.9. 14.7. N. 16.8.<BR>MAH. 4.982.<BR>c. परि id. TROP. R. Schl. II.58.11.: वाचा…वाष्पपरिबद्धया.<BR>c. प्रति id. TROP. RAGH. 1.79.: प्रतिबध्नाति हि श्रेयः पूज्यपूजाव्यतिक्रमः.<BR>c. सम् id. A. 8.7. — Caus. alligandum curare. R. Schl. I.62.24.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=236-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बन्ध्|बंध्<BR>2. बन्ध् 10. P. ligare. R. Schl. II.84.4.: {#banDayizyativA<BR>pASEr aTavA 'smAn baDizyati#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बन्ध|बंध|बंधः|बन्धः<BR>बन्ध m. (r. बन्ध् s. अ) nexus, vinculum. BH. 2.39. 18.30.<BR>RAGH. 6.81. (Cf. hib. bad «a bunch, bush, cluster, tuft,<BR>thiket»; armor. bód «touffe, buisson, trousseau».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बन्धकी|बंधकी<BR>बन्धकी f. (a बन्धक, quod a r. बन्ध् s. अक) femina impudica,<BR>adultera, meretrix. HIT. 86.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बन्धन|बंधन|बन्धनं<BR>बन्धन n. (r. बन्ध् s. अन)<BR>1) alligatio. M. 49.<BR>2) vinculum.<BR>RAGH. 3.30. 12.76. (Goth. bindan ligare; hib. badan<BR>«a tuft of trees, a tuft of hair».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बन्धु|बंधु|बंधुः|बन्धुः<BR>बन्धु m. (r. बन्ध् s. उ)<BR>1) affinis, cognatus. BR. 1.23. N. 16.18. 30.<BR>2) amicus. BH. 6.5. 9. (Cf. hib. badh «love,<BR>friendship».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बन्धुकाम<BR>बन्धुकाम (BAH. e बन्धु et काम amor, desiderium) erga<BR>propinquos amorem habens. BR. 1.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बन्धुर|बंधुर|बन्धुरं|बन्धुरः<BR>बन्धुर (r. बन्ध् s. उर) iniquus, undatus, undulatus. RAGH. 13.47.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बन्ध्य|बंध्य|बन्ध्यः<BR>बन्ध्य (r. बन्ध् s. य) sterilis. RAGH. 1.70. HIT. 4.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बभ्र्<BR>बभ्र् et वभ्र् 1. P. (गतौ K. गत्याम् V.; ut videtur, forma<BR>redupl.; cf. भ्रम्) ire, errare. HIT. 82.13.: {#vayam…anDA<BR>iva baBrAmaH#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बभ्रु|बभ्रुः<BR>बभ्रु<BR>1) (fem. उ et ऊ) flavus, rutilus. RAGH. 15.16. 19.25.<BR>2) m. ichneumon. Lass. 46.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बर्ब्|बर्ब्ब्<BR>बर्ब् 1. P. (गत्याम्) ire, se movere. V. पम्ब्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बर्बर|बर्बरः|बर्ब्बर<BR>बर्बर stultus, stupidus, baro. HIT. 50.8. (Cf. lat. baro.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बर्ह्<BR>1. बर्ह् vel वर्ह् 1. et 10. P. (वधे दीप्तौ) ferire, occidere,<BR>lucere. Cf. वृह्, बल्ह्.<BR>c. नि in dial. Vêd. prosternere. RIGV. 100.18.: {#dasyUn…<BR>hatvA pfTivyAM SarA nibarhIt#} «hostes feriendo humi<BR>tela prostravit».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बर्ह्<BR>2. बर्ह् vel वर्ह् 1. P. (स्मृतिहिंसादानवाक्षु) meminisse;<BR>ferire, laedere, occidere; dare; loqui. Cf. {#vfh,<BR>balh#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बर्ह्<BR>3. बर्ह् vel वर्ह् 1. A. (श्रेष्ठे) excellere. Cf. बल्ह्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल्<BR>1. बल् 1. P. (धान्यावरोधे K. धान्यावरोधे जीवने V.)<BR>opulentiam, fortunam alcjs impedire, perturbare;<BR>vivere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल्<BR>2. बल् 1. A. (दानवधनिरूपेषु) abscindere (दान a दो?);<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">Page238-a+ 36</a>]<BR>ferire, occidere; explorare, investigare. Cf. भल् 1. A.,<BR>बिल्, भिल्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=237-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल्<BR>3. बल् 10. P. बालयामि (भृतौ K.) sustentare, nutrire. K.:<BR>बालयति बालम् पिता. (Cf. भृ i. e. भर्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल्<BR>4. बल् 10. P. बलयामि (निरूपणे K. निरूपे V.) explorare,<BR>investigare. V. 2. बल्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल|बलं|बलः<BR>बल (r. बल् s. अ)<BR>1) n. vis, robur. IN. 4.8. H. 4.14.<BR>2) n. exercitus.<BR>N. 2.11. 17.22.<BR>3) m. nom. pr. Daityi, quem Indrus<BR>occidit. (Cf. lat. valor, validus, valeo, cum praep. de:<BR>debilis.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बलवत्|बलवन्त्<BR>बलवत् (a praec. s. वत्)<BR>1) Adj. vi, robore praeditus,<BR>robustus, fortis. H. 1.8. 42. 2.12.<BR>2) Adv. valde. A. 7.24.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बलाका<BR>बलाका v. वलाका.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बलाहक|बलाहकः<BR>बलाहक m. nom. pr. DR. 2.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बलि|बलिः<BR>1. बलि m. (r. बल् s. इ)<BR>1) nutrimentum, cibus. RAGH. 2.24.<BR>2) tributum. RAGH. 1.18.<BR>3) sacrificium.<BR>4) nom.<BR>pr. Daityi. A. 5.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बलि|बलिः<BR>2. बलि f. (r. बल् s. इ) ruga.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बलिन्<BR>बलिन् (a बल s. इन्) vi, robore praeditus, fortis, robustus.<BR>H. 4.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बलिभ|बलिभः<BR>बलिभ (a बलि s. भ) rugosus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बलिष्ठ|बलिष्ठः<BR>बलिष्ठ Superl. a बलवत् vel बलिन्. Etiam sensu Compar.<BR>(v. gr. min. 227.). RAGH. 17.59.: {#balizWaS cet<BR>parasmAt#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

