बलीयस्<BR>बलीयस् (Compar. a बलवत् vel बलिन्, v. gr. min. 227.)<BR>valde fortis. H. 4.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल्ह्<BR>1. बल्ह् vel वल्ह् 1. A. i. q. 2. बर्ह् et 3. बर्ह्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

