बहु<BR>बहु (fem. वी vel उ, scribitur etiam वहु, r. बंह् vel वंह्<BR>ejectâ nasali suff. उ) multus. SA. 1.11. — Adv. multum.<BR>N. 13.64. (Gr. βαϑύς, cf. lat. pro-fundus, v. बंह् et<BR>Benfey II.67.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

