बाल|बालं|बालः<BR>बाल m. (r. 3. बल् nutrire s. अ)<BR>1) puer, parvulus, infans.<BR>Collective, in Plur. vel initio compos. pueri, parvuli, infantes<BR>utriusque sexus. BR. 1.28. 3.7. N. 12.123. SA. 2.8.<BR>2) pilus.<BR>3) cauda. RAGH. 9.66. MEGH. 54. — Adj.<BR>infans, aetate parvus, juvenis, novus, novellus, recens.<BR>UR. 75.13.: बालम् इवे ऽन्दुम्; RAGH. 3.22.: बालचन्द्रमाः;<BR>SAK. 8.9.: बालविटपिभ्यः. (Lith. wála-s<BR>pilus caudae equi. V. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बालक|बालकं|बालकः<BR>बालक (a praec. s. क) puer, parvulus. N. 9.23. (Hib.<BR>ballach «a boy».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बालखिल्य|बालखिल्यः<BR>बालखिल्य m. Geniorum genus pollicis magnitudinem aequans<BR>(Wils.: A divine personage of the size of the thumb;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=239-a" target="_blank">Page239-a+ 36</a>]<BR>sixty thousand of whom were produced from the hair of<BR>Brahma's body). SU. 3.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=238-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

