बालभाव|बालभावः<BR>बालभाव m. (e बाल et भाव existentia, natura) infantia,<BR>pueritia, puerilis aetas. N. 13.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=239-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

