बाहु|बाहुः<BR>बाहु vel वाहु m. (si वाहु primitiva esset forma, deducendum<BR>esset a r. वह् vehere, ferre; forma बाहु autem<BR>sustentatur zendico 𐬠𐬁𐬰𐬎 bâzu, gr. βϱαχίων, lat. brachium)<BR>brachium. IN. 2.24. (Gr. πῆχυς, mutatâ mediâ<BR>in tenuem, βϱαχίων, lat. brachium insertâ liquidâ sicut<BR>in frango, ϱ̔ήγνυμι, goth. BRAK = भञ्ज्, nisi formae<BR>scrtae बाहु, भञ्ज् mutilatae sunt e ब्राहु, भ्रञ्ज्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=239-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

