भङ्ग|भंग|भंगः|भङ्गः<BR>भङ्ग m. (r. भञ्ज् s. अ)<BR>1) fractio, fractura. RAGH. 16.14.<BR>— पुष्पभङ्ग florum contritio. N. 25.7. (Schol. Nîl.<BR>पुष्पसम्मर्दः). TROP. repudiatio. RAGH. 13.78.<BR>2) fragmentum.<BR>UR. 69.4.<BR>3) unda, fluctus, v. sq. (Lith. bangà<BR>unda, fluctus; gr. ἀγή, v. भञ्ज्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=242-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

