भट्टार|भट्टारः<BR>भट्टार (forma Prâcr. a भर्तृ, in casibus fort. भर्तार्, suff.<BR>अ, mutato त् in ट् cui se assimilavit antecedens र्; v.<BR>भट्टिणी et cf. Lass. s. vv. भट्ट et भट्टारक) venerabilis,<BR>sanctus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=243-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

