भा<BR>भा 2. P. A.<BR>1) splendere, fulgere. N. 12.103.: {#ayam agamaH…ApIqEr<BR>bahuBir BAti#}; 13.52.: {#BAsi vidyud<BR>ivA 'Brezu#}; 17.8.<BR>2) apparere, videri. H. 1.10.: {#jaNGAvAto<BR>baBOcA 'sya SuciSukrAgame yaTA#}. (Cf. {#BAs,<BR>Bas, BAz#}; gr. ϕάω, ϕαίνω, ϕημί; ϕοῖβος, forma<BR>anomale redupl. sicut ϕέβομαι a भी, बिभेमि; lat.<BR>fâ-ri.)<BR>c. अति valde splendere. RAM. II.46.11.<BR>c. अभि splendere. GHAT. 10.<BR>c. आ<BR>1) id. R. Schl. I.15.19.<BR>2) videri, apparere. RAGH. 13.14.<BR>c. उत् apparere. MAN. 1.7.: स्वयम् उद्बभौ.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=244-b" target="_blank">Page244-b+ 37</a>]<BR>c. निस् elucere, exoriri. MAN. 5.113.: {#apAm agneSca saMyogAd<BR>DemaM rUpyaYca nirbaBO#}.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. MAH. 3.10054. — प्रभात n. ortus lucis,<BR>diluculum. Loc. प्रभाते diluculo, ad primam auroram.<BR>SA. 5.80.<BR>c. प्रति<BR>1) splendere. GHAT. 15.<BR>2) apparere, c. gen. R. Schl. I.55.17.:<BR>{#yAni devezucA 'strARi…pratiBAntu<BR>mama#}; c. acc. MAH. 3.10169.: {#tan tu kftsno Danurvedo<BR>pratyaBAt#}.<BR>3) videri. DR. 4.4. A. 4.39.<BR>c. प्रति praef. सम् videri. MAH. 1.8095.<BR>c. वि splendere. R. Schl. II.72.20. RAGH. 5.72.<BR>c. सम् praef. प्र apparere, videri. MAH. 3.10055.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=244-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

