भाम|भामः<BR>भाम m. (r. भा s. म)<BR>1) lumen, splendor.<BR>2) sol. MED.<BR>3) ira, furor. (Fortasse lat. furo, furor radice cum hoc<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=245-a" target="_blank">Page245-a+ 37</a>]<BR>vocabulo cohaerent, ita ut ad भा vel potius ad भस् vel<BR>भास् referenda sint.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=244-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

