भुज्<BR>1. भुज् 6. P. भुजामि, part. pass. भुग्न (gr. 607.) flectere,<BR>curvare. (Cf. भञ्ज्; goth. BUG id, biuga, baug,<BR>bugum, v. gr. comp. 489.; part. pass. bug-a-ns, them.<BR>bug-a-na = भुग्न; nostrum biege, bog, Bug; cum Caus.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=247-b" target="_blank">Page247-b+ 37</a>]<BR>e भोजयामि convenit goth. baugja, us-baugja verro,<BR>nostrum beuge, v. gr. comp. 109^a).6. Hib. bogaim «I<BR>move, put in motion, wag, shake, toss, stir», bogha<BR>«bow», boghaighim «I bend, arch, camerate», boghadoir<BR>«archer»; fortasse gr. ΦΥΓ, ϕεύγω, lat. FUG, fugio<BR>a vertendo dicta; fortasse πυγών e ϕυγών.)<BR>c. अव i. q. simpl. अवभुग्न inflexus. H. 1.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=247-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भुज्<BR>2. भुज् 7. P. A. भुनज्मि, भुञ्जे, part. pass. भुक्त.<BR>1) edere,<BR>vesci. SU. 1.5.: विना ऽन्योन्यन् न भुञ्जाते; BH. 2.5.:<BR>भोक्तुम् भैक्ष्यम्; 3.12.: {#tEr dattAn (BogAn)<BR>na pradAyE 'Byo yo BuNkte#}; R. Schl. I.13.17.: {#buBujire<BR>'nnAni#}; 18.: अन्नपानानि तत्रा ऽभुञ्जत; N. 13.68.:<BR>उच्छिष्टन् नै ऽव भुञ्जीयाम् (sic etiam in ed. Calc. pro<BR>भुञ्जीय).<BR>2) frui, gaudere, uti, possidere. N. 4.8.: {#virajAMsica<BR>vAsAMsi divyAS citrAH srajas taTA…BuNkzva#};<BR>MAH. 1.3901.: {#AsAdya SAntanus tAYca BuBuje<BR>kAmato vaSAm#}; RAGH. 8.7.: {#buBuje mahABujaH…medinIn<BR>navapARigrahaRAm vaDUm iva#}; 12.8.: {#tasya<BR>rAjyan nyAsam ivA 'Bunak#}; BH. 2.37.: {#hato vA prApsyase<BR>svargaY jitvA vA Bokzyase mahIm#}; R. Schl. I.46.14.:<BR>त्रैलोक्यविजयम् पुत्रं स ह भोक्ष्यसि. — Pass.<BR>absol. BR. 2.31.: भुक्तम्…मया. — Caus.<BR>1) cibare,<BR>cibos porrigere. MAN. 3.106.: {#na vE svayan aSnIyAd<BR>atiTiM yan na Bojayet#}; 113.: {#itarAn api<BR>…annam…Bojayet#}. Cum instr. rei. MAH. 3.1007.:<BR>भ्रातॄन्…अभोजयन्त मृष्टान्नैः सूदाः.<BR>2) fruendum, possidendum<BR>dare. BHATT. 8.83. — Desid.<BR>1) edere, velle,<BR>esurire. MAH. 1.887.: ना ऽहम् अन्नम् बुभुक्षे. — बुभुक्षित<BR>esuriens. MAN. 10.105.<BR>2) frui, possidere velle.<BR>MAH. 1.5667.: स राज्यम् बुभुक्षति. (Cf. भक्ष्, lat. fungor,<BR>fruor e frugor, inserto r, fruges, fructus, faux;<BR>island. vet. brûka uti; germ. vet. brûchan, prûchan id.)<BR>c. अधि frui, possidere. HIT. 130.: राज्यम्.<BR>c. अनु frui. MAN. 4.240.<BR>c. उप<BR>1) edere, vesci, bibere. R. Schl. II.30.16.: फलानि;<BR>RAGH. 1.67.: पयः.<BR>2) frui, gaudere, uti, possidere.<BR>MAH. 1.8343. HIT. 28.12. MAN. 12.8.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=248-a" target="_blank">Page248-a+ 37</a>]<BR>c. सम् Caus. cibare, c. instr. rei. MAH. 3.12672.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=247-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भुज्<BR>3. भुज् (r. 2. भुज्) edens, vescens, in fine compos. BH. 4.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=248-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भुज|भुजः<BR>भुज m. (r. 1. भुज् s. अ)<BR>1) brachium.<BR>2) manus. H. 1.2.<BR>3) elephanti proboscis. DR. 8.21. (Fortasse lat. pugnus<BR>pro fug-nus = part. pass. भुग्न.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=248-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भुजग|भुजगः<BR>भुजग m. (tortuose iens e भुज, quod hic flexum, incurvationem<BR>significat, e ग iens) serpens. N. 11.28. V.<BR>भुजङ्ग et cf. पतग, पतङ्ग.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=248-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भुजगी<BR>भुजगी f. (a praec. signo fem. ई) Fem. praec. HIT. 121.19.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=248-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भुजङ्ग|भुजंग|भुजंगः|भुजङ्गः<BR>भुजङ्ग m. i. q. भुजग (cf. पतङ्ग). UR. 91.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=248-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भुजमध्य<BR>भुजमध्य n. (e भुज brachium et मध्य medium) pectus.<BR>RAGH. 13.73.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=248-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भुजान्तर|भुजांतर|भुजान्तरं<BR>भुजान्तर n. (e भुज et अन्तर) id. UR. 70.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=248-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

