भ्राश्<BR>भ्राश् 1. et. 4. A. splendere, lucere. RIGV. 66.3.: {#citro<BR>yad aBrAd#} «versicolor quum splendet». (Cf. {#BrAj,<BR>BlAS#}.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

