भ्रुकुटि|भ्रुकुटिः<BR>भ्रुकुटि, भ्रुकुटी v. भृकुटि.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भ्रुव<BR>भ्रुव supercilium, in fine compositorum possessivorum (v. gr. 681.).<BR>N. 5.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भ्रू<BR>भ्रू f. supercilium. DR. 1.14. (Gr. ὀϕϱῡ́ς, praefixo ο; russ.<BR>brovj f. id.; germ. vet. brâwa f. Etiam hib. fabhar «the<BR>eye-brow, eye-lid, eye» nisi descendit a lat. palpebra,<BR>huc referri posset, ita ut fa significet oculum; v. पश्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भ्रूक्षेप|भ्रूक्षेपः<BR>भ्रूक्षेप m. (TATP. e praec. et क्षेप conjectio, jactus, a rad.<BR>क्षिप् s. अ) superciliorum jactus, oculorum lusus, nictatio.<BR>IN. 5.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

