भ्रूक्षेपालापमाधुर्य<BR>भ्रूक्षेपालापमाधुर्य (BAH. e praec. et माधुर्य dulcedo) oculorum<BR>loquelae dulcedinem habens. IN. 5.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

