भ्रूण|भ्रूणः<BR>भ्रूण m. (fortasse forma anomala a r. भृ) fetus utero matris<BR>inclusus, ἔμβϱυον.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भ्रेज्<BR>भ्रेज् 1. A. lucere, splendere, fulgere. Cf. भ्राज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

भ्रेष्<BR>भ्रेष् 1. A. (चले भये)<BR>1) ire, se movere, vacillare. BHATT. 14.87.:<BR>स बिभ्रेष (Schol. चलितः).<BR>2) timere; cf.<BR>भेष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

