मंह्<BR>1. मंह् 1. A. (वृद्धौ scribitur मह्, gr. 110^a).) crescere. (V.<BR>महत् magnus, महिमन् magnitudo et cf. {#mah, mAh,<BR>vfMh, vakz#}; goth. MAG posse, mag possum, mah-ta potui,<BR>mah-ts potestas, ma-iza major, mag-us puer, magath<BR>virgo, mikils magnus; slav. mogû possum; lith. macnus<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-1b" target="_blank">Page253-1b+ 8</a>]<BR>potens macìs, mácế potestas; gr.<BR>μέγας, μέγεϑος, μῆϰος, μαϰϱός; lat. mag-nus, mac-tus; fortasse<BR>etiam mâ-turus a crescendo dictum, sicut scr. वृद्ध senex<BR>a वृध् crescere; cf. Ag. Benary Römische Lautlehre<BR>p. 258.; hib. mochd «promotion, Adj. great», mead «encrease,<BR>bigness, bulk, size», v. महत्; meadhaighim «I<BR>encrease, enlarge»; moid «bulk, hight».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मंह्<BR>2. मंह् 10. P. (त्विषि) lucere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=253-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मंहिष्ठ<BR>मंहिष्ठ Superl. τοῦ महत् in dialecto Vêd. RIGV. 51.1. (Gr.<BR>μέγιστος; goth. maists maximus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मकर|मकरः<BR>मकर m. nomen piscis immani magnitudine (Wils.:<BR>1) A<BR>marine monster, confounded usually with the crocodile<BR>and shark, but properly a fabulous animal; as a fish it<BR>might be conjectured to be the horned shark or the unicorn<BR>fish, but it is often drawn, as in the pictured signs<BR>of the zodiac, with the head and fore legs of an antelope,<BR>and the body and tail of a fish; it is the emblem of the<BR>god of love.<BR>2) One of the signs of zodiac corresponding<BR>with capricorne and like the Greek representation of<BR>that sign being an animal in the fore parts, and ending<BR>in the tail of a fish.). DR. 7.19. A. 6.4. BH. 10.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मकरकेतु|मकरकेतुः<BR>मकरकेतु m. (BAH. e praec. et केतु vexillum) nomen Anangi,<BR>dei amoris. UR. 16.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मकरध्वज|मकरध्वजः<BR>मकरध्वज m. (BAH. e मकर et ध्वज vexillum) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मक्क्<BR>मक्क् 1. A. (गतौ) ire, se movere. Cf. मख्, मङ्क् etc.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मक्ष्<BR>मक्ष् 1. P. (सङ्घाते K. रोषे सङ्घाते V.) coacervare, irasci.<BR>Cf. म्रक्ष्, मृक्ष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मक्षिका<BR>मक्षिका f. (ut videtur, a r. मक्ष् s. इक in fem.) musca.<BR>(Lat. musca; germ. vet. mucca culex; russ. mucha; lith.<BR>mussế, per assim. e muksế; gr. μυῖα.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मख्<BR>मख् 1. P. (सर्पणे) ire, see movere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मख|मखः<BR>मख m. (cf. मह् colere, venerari) sacrificium. DR. 2.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मगध|मगधः<BR>मगध m. nomen regionis «South Behar». Wils.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मग्न|मग्नः<BR>मग्न v. मज्ज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मघ|मघः<BR>मघ m. (r. मह् colere, venerari, s. अ) beatitudo.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मघवन्<BR>मघवन् (a praec. quod etiam sacrificium significare videtur,<BR>s. वत्, v. मख)<BR>1) Adj. in dial. Vêd. sacrificans.<BR>Lass. 148.<BR>2) m. nomen dei Indri. N. 2.15. A. 11.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मघा<BR>मघा f. plur. (fem. τοῦ मघ) decimum astrum lunare<BR>(Wils.: The tenth lunar asterism, containing five stars<BR>figured by a house, apparently α, γ, ζ, η and ν Leonis).<BR>SU. 2.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मघोन्<BR>मघोन् v. मघवन्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मङ्क्|मंक्<BR>मङ्क् 1. A. (मण्डने गतौ K. भूषे गतौ V. scribitur मक्)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-b" target="_blank">Page254-b+ 37</a>]<BR>ornare; ire, se movere. Cf. makk, makh, maGkh, maGgh etc.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मङ्ख्<BR>मङ्ख् 1. P. (गतौ K. सर्पणे V.) ire, se movere. Cf. {#makk,<BR>maK, maNk#} etc.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मङ्ग्|मंग्<BR>मङ्ग् 1. P. (सर्पणे; scribitur मग्) ire, se movere. Cf.<BR>मकक्, मङ्क्, मङ्घ्, मख्, मङ्ख्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मङ्गल|मंगल|मङ्गलं|मङ्गलः<BR>मङ्गल (ut videtur, a r. मङ्ग् s. अल) I. Adj. salutaris, felix.<BR>SU. 2.4. II. Subst.<BR>1) n. fortuna, felicitas. N. 18.17.<BR>2) m. nomen plantae, Wils. «a bent grass (Panicum<BR>dactylon) with white blossoms». UR. 44.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मङ्घ्|मंघ्<BR>1. मङ्घ् 1. A. (कैतवे K. कैतवगतौ निन्दारम्भजवेषु V.;<BR>scribitur मघ्) ludere; ire, properare; vituperare;<BR>incipere. Cf. मङ्ग्, मङ्ख्, मख्, मक्क्, मर्घ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मङ्घ्|मंघ्<BR>2. मङ्घ् 1. P. (भूषे) ornare. Cf. मङ्क्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मच्<BR>मच् 1. A. (कल्कने K. कल्कने दम्भे शाढ्ये V.) decipere,<BR>fallere; gloriari.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मज्ज्<BR>मज्ज् 6. P. interdum A. (scribitur मस्ज्, gr. 110^b).) mergi,<BR>submergi, aquâ hauriri, c. loc. vel acc. N. 6.13.:<BR>कृच्छ्रे स नरके मज्जेद् अगाधे विपुले ह्रदे; R. Schl. I.1.89.:<BR>ना ऽप्सु मज्जन्ति जन्तवः; MAN. 4.81.: {#tamaH<BR>…majjati#}; MAH. 2.605.: यमुनाम्भस्य् अमज्जत; 2203.:<BR>मा मज्जीः शोकसागरे; M. 8.: {#BayOGAn mahato majjantam<BR>mAm…trAhi#}. — मग्न submersus. A. 6.4.: {#jale<BR>magnA ivA 'drayaH#}. — Caus. mergere, immergere. H. 2.10.:<BR>अष्टौ दंष्ट्रा देहेषु मज्जयिष्यामि. (मज्ज् per<BR>assimil. e मर्ज् ortum esse videtur; cf. मृज् i. e. {#marj,<BR>mArj, maYj, muj, muYj#}; lat. mergo; lith. merkiu macero,<BR>mazgóju lavo = Caus. मज्जयामि.)<BR>c. उत् emergi, emergere. MAH. 3.13163.: {#vApIn nyamajjan<BR>na punar udamajjat#}. — Caus. MAN. 8.115.<BR>c. नि submergi, submergere, aquâ hauriri. HIT. ed. Ser. 126.16.:<BR>कार्याब्धौ स निमज्जति; SA. 6.43.: {#nimajjamAnam…tamomaye<BR>hrade#}; MAH. 1.6747.: अम्भसि निमज्जेयम्;<BR>BHATT. 3.20.: शोके न्यमाङ्क्षीत्. — Trans.<BR>demergere. MAH. 1.4156.: मा निमज्जीः पितामहान्.<BR>— Caus. submergi jubere. MAN. 8.114.: {#apsucE 'nan<BR>nimajjayet#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=254-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मज्जन्<BR>मज्जन् m. (r. मज्ज् s. अन्) medulla. (Germ. vet. marag,<BR>anglo-sax. mearg, merg id., v. sq. et r. मज्ज् e मर्ज्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मज्जा<BR>मज्जा f. (r. मज्ज् s. आ) id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मञ्च्|मंच्<BR>1. मञ्च् 1. A. (धारणे K. उच्छ्रायधृत्यर्चाभाःसु V.; scribitur<BR>मच्) tenere, altum esse vel fieri, venerari, splendere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मञ्च्|मंच्<BR>2. मञ्च् 1. P. (गत्याम्) ire, se movere. Cf. मङ्क् sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मञ्च|मंच|मंचः|मञ्चः<BR>मञ्च m. (r. 1. मञ्च् s. अ) lectus, cubile. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मञ्ज्|मंज्<BR>मञ्ज् 10. P. (मृजाध्वनयोः K. मृजाध्वन्योः V.) abstergere,<BR>purificare; sonare. (Cf. मुज्, मुञ्ज्, मार्ज्, मृज् i. e.<BR>मर्ज्, unde मञ्ज् ortum esse videtur, mutatis liquidis; v.<BR>मज्ज्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

