मञ्जरी<BR>मञ्जरी f. (r. मञ्ज् s. अर in fem. cf. suff. अल)<BR>1) surculus.<BR>UR. 59.14.<BR>2) unio, margarita. (Cf. gr. μάϱγαϱον, μαϱγαϱίτης,<BR>lat. margarita; v. radd. मञ्ज्, मज्ज् e<BR>मर्ज्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

