मणि|मणिः<BR>मणि m. f.<BR>1) gemma.<BR>2) margarita. (Cf. gr.<BR>μάννος, μόννος, lat. monile.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

