मति|मतिः<BR>मति f. (r. मन् cogitare s. ति)<BR>1) animus, mens. N. 11.36. 22.21.<BR>in fine compos. BAH.<BR>2) opinio. H. 1.26. N. 19.32.<BR>BH. 18.78.<BR>3) consilium, propositum. SU. 2.12. N. 18.16.<BR>In fine comp. BAH. BH. 12.19. 18.64. (Gr. μῆτις;<BR>goth. ga-mun-ds, Them. ga-mun-di memoria; lat.<BR>mentis, mens.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=255-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

