मदन|मदनः<BR>मदन m. (qui inebriat a r. मद् s. अन)<BR>1) potus fervidus,<BR>inebrians. IN. 5.13.<BR>2) amor, deus amoris. UR. 41.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=256-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

