मदीय|मदीयं<BR>मदीय Pron. poss. (v. gr. 289.) meus. N. 14.15. A. 3.50.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=256-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

