मद्विध<BR>मद्विध (BAH. e मत् q. v. et विध vel विधा species, genus)<BR>mei genus, speciem, naturam, indolem habens, mihi aequalis.<BR>H. 2.33.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=256-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मधु|मधुः<BR>मधु (fortasse a r. मद्, mutato द् in ध्) I. n.<BR>1) mel.<BR>2) potus inebrians, vinum. RAGH. 4.60. II. m. ver.<BR>(Gr. μέϑυ, μέλι, mutato ϑ vel δ in λ; lat. mel, mellis<BR>fortasse per assim. e melvis pro medvis; lith. medù-s mel;<BR>slav. med id.; anglo-sax. medu, medo; germ. vet. meto<BR>mulsum; hib. mil, gen. meala mel.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=256-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

