महीभृत्<BR>महीभृत् m. (terram sustinens e मही et भृत् q. v.)<BR>mons. N. 12.73.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=261-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

महेश्वर|महेश्वरः<BR>महेश्वर m. (magnus dominus KARM. महा et ईश्वर) deus<BR>Sivus. SU. 3.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=261-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

महोदधि|महोदधिः<BR>महोदधि m. (KARM. e महा et उदधि mare) magnum mare.<BR>SU. 2.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=261-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मा<BR>1. मा 2. P. 3. et 4. A. मामि, मिमे (gr. 270.), माये.<BR>1) metiri.<BR>मित mensuratus, praesertim modicus, paucus,<BR>exiguus. SA. 1.6. (cf. मिताशन, मितम्पच apud Wils.).<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-a" target="_blank">Page262-a+ 37</a>]<BR>2) in dial. Vêd. dare. RIGV. 120.9.: {#rAyeca no mimItam<BR>vAjavatyE . izeca no mimItam#} «opulentiaeque<BR>nos date, vigore clarae, ciboque nos date». — Caus.<BR>1) metandum curare. MAH. 1.2024.: {#tan deSam mApayAmAsur<BR>yajYAyatanakAraRAt#}; 1.5319.: मापयामास मेदिनीम्.<BR>2) metiri, transmeare. MAH. 1.5842.: {#pARqavAn<BR>dadfSe…mApayAnAn nadIjalam#}. (V. मस्,<BR>3. मी et cf. gr. μέ-τϱον, μῖμος, μιμέομαι; v. मा praef.<BR>उप et सम्, ἄ-μοτος, quasi अमितम् pro अमातम्;<BR>lat. mê-tior, mo-dus, im-mâ-nis; goth. MAT metiri, mita,<BR>mat, adjecto t, v. gr. comp. 109^b).1.; lith. mattóju metior,<BR>más-tas euphon. pro mát-tas cubitus, máćius e<BR>matius modus, mensura, mé-tas annus, v. समा; russ.<BR>mje-ra modus, mensura, mje-ritj mensurare; hib. mead<BR>«a balance, a scale», meadaighim «I weigh, balance,<BR>consider».)<BR>c. उप उपमित similis. BHAR. 3.17.<BR>c. निस् efficere, creare. SU. 3.12.: निर्ममे योषितन् दिव्याम्;<BR>18.: निर्मिता; MAN. 1.13.: दिवम् भूमिञ्च निर्ममे.<BR>HIT. 21.20.: स्नायुनिर्मिता एते पाशाः.<BR>c. निस् praef. वि id. N. 17.7.: धात्रा विनिर्मितः.<BR>c. परि admetiri, transl. destinare. BHAR. 3.50.: {#Ayur<BR>varzaSatan nfRAm parimitam#}. — परिमित modicus,<BR>paucus, exiguus. SA. 1.5.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. अप्रमेय non mensurabilis, immensus.<BR>DR. 1.8. BH. 11.17.<BR>c. सम् सम्मित<BR>1) similis. N. 16.4.: ग्रामान् नगरसम्मितान्.<BR>2) consentaneus, congruens. SA. 5.50.: {#yaTA yaTA<BR>BAzasi Darmasammitam manonukUlam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=261-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मा<BR>2. मा 3. P. A. sonare. RIGV. 38.8.: वाश्रे ऽव विद्युन् मिमाति<BR>«mugientis instar vaccae fulmen sonat».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मा<BR>3. मा ne, particula prohibitiva, quae construitur cum Imperativo<BR>vel temporibus, quae loco Imperativi ponuntur. H. 3.7.<BR>Imperativo subintellecto. DR. 4.23. (Gr. μή.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मांस|मांसं|मांसः<BR>मांस n. caro. H. 2.2. 7. (Salv. mjaso neut. id.; lith. miếsà<BR>fem. id.; germ. vet. môs neut., Them. môsa, cibus; nostrum<BR>Mus, Ge-müse; hib. maise «food, victuals».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

माक्ष<BR>माक्ष m. (ut videtur, a मक्षा, quod etiam apem significare<BR>videtur, suff. इक; secundum Wils. a मक्षिका apis) mel.<BR>(Huc trahi posset germ. vet. wahs neut. cera; angio-sax.<BR>väx, vex, veax; lith. waszka-s masc.; russ. vosk, mutato<BR>m in v.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

माक्षज<BR>माक्षज n. (e praec. et ज natus) cera.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

माङ्क्ष्|मांक्ष्<BR>माङ्क्ष् 1. P. (काङ्घायाम् K. स्पृहि V.; scribitur माक्ष्) desiderare.<BR>Cf. काङ्क्ष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मागध|मागधः<BR>मागध (f. ई, a मगध nomen regionis s. अ) magadhensis.<BR>RAGH. 1.57.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

माचिरम्<BR>माचिरम् Adv. (e मा et चिरम् diu) sine morâ, statim, c.<BR>Imperativo vel ejus vice fungentibus temporibus. H. 4.13.<BR>N. 3.9. 18.17. M. 47. SA. 5.99.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मातङ्ग|मातंग|मातंगः|मातङ्गः<BR>मातङ्ग m. elephantus (cf. मतङ्ग). DR. 8.29.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मातलि|मातलिः<BR>मातलि m. Mâtalis, Indri auriga.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मातुल|मातुलः<BR>मातुल m. (fortasse e मातुर, a मातृ i. e. मातर्, attenuato<BR>अ in उ suff. अ) avunculus. BH. 1.26.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मातृ<BR>मातृ f. (ut mihi videtur, a r. मा s. तृ, v. मा praef. निस्)<BR>mater. (Verum thema est मातर्, v. gr. 179. et cf. lat.<BR>mâter; dor. μᾱτηϱ; germ. vet. muoter; slav. nom. mati<BR>= माता, them. mater = मातर्, gen. mater-e; lith.<BR>motế uxor, genit. moter-s; hib. mathair mater.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मातृषष्ठ<BR>मातृषष्ठ (BAH. e मातृ et षष्ठ sextus, v. gr. 666.) matrem<BR>tanquam sextam habens. H. 1.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मात्र|मात्रं<BR>मात्र n. (r. मा s. त्र)<BR>1) mensura. A. 8.1.<BR>2) materies, elementum,<BR>res. BH. 2.14.<BR>3) in fine compositorum, ubi a<BR>grammaticis pro suffixo Taddhitico habetur (v. gr. 652.)<BR>solus, solum, tantummodo. N. 9.10. 11.39. DR. 5.12. 14.<BR>A. 10.46. (Gr. μέ-τϱον.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

