मात्स्यक<BR>मात्स्यक (a मत्स्य m. piscis s. क vel अक) ad piscem attinens,<BR>piscarius. M. 56. (Hib. measach «fishy», v. मत्स्य.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=262-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

