मानद<BR>मानद m. (e praec. et द qui dat) qui honorem tribuit, in<BR>Vocativo fere solum invenitur, ad venerationem erga áliquem<BR>exprimendam. IN. 5.44. N. 4.4. SA. 5.51.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=263-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

