मानव|मानवः<BR>मानव m. (a Manu oriundus, e मनु s. अ, v. gr. 650.)<BR>homo. IN. 5.6. BR. 2.2. (Goth. manna id., them. mannan,<BR>quod fortasse per assimil. e manvan; nostrum<BR>Mann.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=263-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

