मार्गशीर्ष|मार्गशीर्षः<BR>मार्गशीर्ष m. (a मृगशीर्ष - dorcadis caputhabens,<BR>nomen astri, in quo luna est plena - s. अ) nomen mensis,<BR>November-December. BH. 10.35.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=263-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मार्ज्<BR>मार्ज् 10. P. (शब्दे K. मृजाध्वन्योः V.) sonare; abstergere,<BR>purificare. N. 13.46.: अमार्जिताम्. V. मृज् i. e.<BR>मर्ज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=263-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

