माल्य|माल्यं<BR>माल्य n. (a माला s. य) id. SU. 4.4. N. 2.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=263-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मास्<BR>मास् m. (r. मस्)<BR>1) luna.<BR>2) mensis (Cf. gr. μήν, μην-ός<BR>e μηνσ-ος ejecto σ sicut e. c. in χήν = हंस anser;<BR>russ. mjesjaz luna; lith. mếnů luna, mensis, a them.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">Page264-a+ 36</a>]<BR>MENES, genit. menesio a them. MENESIA, v. gr. comp. 147.;<BR>goth. mêna; germ. vet. mâno luna; v. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=263-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मास|मासं|मासः<BR>मास m. (r. मस् metiri s. अ) mensis. (Lat. mensi-s insertâ<BR>nasali, attenuato a finali in i; hib. mios id.; cambro-brit.<BR>mis, v. मास्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

