मिथ्<BR>मिथ् 1. P. A. (वधे K. वधे मेधायाम् V.)<BR>1) ferire, laedere,<BR>occidere. RIGV. V. (v. Westerg.): {#saM yan mahI miTatI<BR>sparDamAne#} (Schol. {#mahatyO parasparaM hiMsantyO<BR>sene#}.)<BR>2) intelligere. Cf. मेथ्, 1. मिद्, मेद्, मेध्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिथुन|मिथुनं<BR>मिथुन n. (r. मिथ्, v. मेथ्, suff. उन) par animantium diversi<BR>sexus, ut puer et puella. BR. 2.10. N. 5.39. 23.24.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिथ्या<BR>मिथ्या Adv. falso, fallaciter, frustra. N. 12.14. 13.17. SA. 6.14.<BR>BH. 18.59.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिद्<BR>1. मिद् 1. P. A. i. q. मिथ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिद्<BR>2. मिद् 1. A. 4. et 10. P. मेदे, मेद्यामि (gr. 332.), मेदयामि<BR>(स्नेहने K. स्निहि V.)<BR>1) pinguem, adiposum, unctum<BR>esse vel fieri. K.: श्रमेण कायो न मेद्यति.<BR>2) amare.<BR>K.: मेदते पुत्रे पिता. — Part. pass. मिन्न, मेदित.<BR>(Cf. मिन्द्, मन्द्; lith. myliu amo, miếlas carus, mutato<BR>d in l; russ. milyĭ comis, benignus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिन्द्|मिंद्<BR>मिन्द् 10. P. (scribitur मिद्, gr. 110^a).) i. q. 2. मिद्. (Cf.<BR>मिद्, मन्द्; germ. vet. minna, minni amor, fortasse<BR>per assimil. e. minda, mindi.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिन्व्<BR>मिन्व् 1. P. मिन्वामि (सेके, scribitur मिव्) irrigare. Cf.<BR>पिन्व्, निन्व्, मिह्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिल्<BR>मिल् 6. P. A. obviam fieri, obviam venire, occurrere, convenire, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-b" target="_blank">Page264-b+ 36</a>]<BR>societatem inire. HIT. 43.11.: {#yecA 'nye suhfdaH<BR>samfdDisamaye dravyABilAzAkulAH…te sarvatra milanti#};<BR>67.19.: सर्वैः पशुभिर्, मिलित्वा, सिंहो विज्ञप्तः;<BR>38.9.: {#kadAcic citrANganAmA mfgaH, kenA 'pi<BR>trAsitas, tatrA 'gatya militaH#}. (Fortasse मिल् e<BR>मिद् mutato द् in ल्, cf. मेथ्, मिथुन्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिश्<BR>मिश् 1. P. i. q. मश्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिश्र्<BR>मिश्र् 10. P. miscere (ut videtur, Denom. a मिश्र). MAH. 1.5724.:<BR>लाक्षयाचा ऽप्य् अनल्पया मृत्तिकाम् मिश्रयित्वा;<BR>SAK. 24.1.: वाचन् न मिश्रयति यद्य् अपि मद्वचोभिः.<BR>(Cf. 1. मिष्; gr. μίγνυμι; lat. misceo; lith.<BR>maiszau; slav. mjesʽû; germ. vet. miskiu; hib. measgaim<BR>«I mix»; measg «among, amongst», cambro-brit. ymmusk.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिश्र|मिश्रं|मिश्रः<BR>मिश्र (ut videtur, a r. मिश्, cf. मिष्, suff. र) mixtus. BH. 18.12.<BR>IN. 2.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिष्<BR>1. मिष् 1. P. conspergere. मिष्ट<BR>1) conspersus.<BR>2) dulcis,<BR>suavis. मिष्ट n. cibus lautior, delicatior. N. 18.6.<BR>Cf. मृष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिष्<BR>2. मिष् 6. P. (स्पधीयाम् K. स्पर्धे V.) aemulari, certare. — Part.<BR>praes. in gen. abso. invito. MAH. 1.7179.:<BR>{#tO pArTivAnAm mizatAn narendra kfzRAm upAdAya<BR>gatO narAgryO#}; 8159.: {#tvan Dakzyase 'naGa kARqavan<BR>dAvam adyE 'va mizato 'sya SacIpateH#}; 2.2535.: {#DArtarAzwrAn<BR>raRe hatvA mizatAM sarvaDanvinAm SamaN gantAsmi<BR>na cirAt#}; 3.10464.: {#tena dvAdaSavArzikyAm<BR>anAvfzwyAm mahAtmanA vfzwam…mizato vajrapARinaH#}.<BR>(V. praef. उत् et नि et cf. मील्; russ. migaju et<BR>mischu nictor; lith. mirkloju id., mếgmi dormio; fortasse<BR>lat. nico, nic-to e nimic-0, nimic-to = निमिषामि. — Benfey<BR>huc trahit lat. micare.)<BR>c. उत् aperire oculos, proprie aufschlagen. BH. 5.9.:<BR>उन्मिषन् निमिषन्न् अपि.<BR>c. नि claudere oculos, proprie niederschlagen. MAH. 3.10649.:<BR>मत्स्यः सुप्तो न निमिषति.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मिह्<BR>मिह् 1. P. मेहामि, fut. aux. मेक्ष्यामि, part. pass. मीढ<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-a" target="_blank">Page265-a+ 36</a>]<BR>(gr. 102.) Effundere, praesertim mingere. R. Schl. II.75.21.:<BR>सूर्यम् प्रति मेहतु; MAN. 4.52.: {#praty agnim prati<BR>sUryaYca…mehataH#}. (Cf. मिन्व्, lat. mingo, mejo; gr.<BR>ὀ-μιχέω, μοιχός, μοιχάω; lith. myźu mingo, mếszlas<BR>fimus, mếźu stercus egero, mig-la nebula, v. मेघ; anglo-sax.<BR>MIG mingere, mîge, mâh, migon; island. vet.<BR>MIG id.; goth. maihs-tus fimus, adjectâ sibilante; nostrum<BR>Mist.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=264-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मी<BR>1. मी 9. P. A. मीनामि, मीने, in dial. Vêd. मिनामि, मिने<BR>(हिंसायाम् K. वधे V.) Ferire, occidere, delere.<BR>RIGV. 71.10.: रूपञ् जरिमा मिनाति; 92.12.: {#aminatI<BR>dEvyAni vratAni#}; 117.3.: {#minantA (= minantO)<BR>dasyor aSivasya mAyAH#}. — Part. pass. मीन.<BR>c. आ i. q. simpl. RIGV. 79.2.: {#A te suparRA aminanta<BR>evEH#} «tuae bene alatae luces feriunt nubem cum properantibus<BR>ventis». ATM. sibi mutuo aliquid delere. RIGV. 113.2.:<BR>द्यावा वर्णञ् चरत आमिमाने «coelum percurrunt<BR>(nox et aurora) suum mutuo colorem delentes».<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. RIGV. 32.4.: {#mAyinAm aminAH pro 'ta<BR>mAyAH#} «praestigiatorum fregisti praestigias»; 25.1. 92.11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मी<BR>2. मी 4. A. perire. RIGV. V. (v. Westerg.): {#durmitrAso mimAnA<BR>jahur BojanA#}. — Caus. मापयामि, v. gr. 521.<BR>(Cf. म्रिये morior, unde fortasse मीये ejecto र्<BR>producto इ.)<BR>c. प्र perire, mori. MAN. 9.247.: बालाश्च न प्रमीयन्ते;<BR>R. Schl. II.75.28.: अनपत्यः प्रमीयताम्. प्रमीत mortuus.<BR>MAN. 3.245. — Caus. occidere, delere. MAN. 1.57.:<BR>{#idaM sarvaY carAcaraM saYjIvayaticA 'jasram pramApayaticA<BR>'vyayaH#}; 8.295.: स चेत्…प्रमापयेत् प्राणभृतः;<BR>11.89. 129. MAH. 3.13322.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मी<BR>3. मी 1. P. (गतौ) ire. (V. sq. et cf. मा sgf. 2.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मी<BR>4. मी 10. P. (गतौ मत्याम्) ire; intelligere. (V. 3. मी et<BR>cf. lat. meare.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मीढ|मीढं<BR>मीढ v. मिह्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मीन|मीनः<BR>मीन m. piscis.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मीम्<BR>मीम् 1. P. (ut videtur, forma redupl. a r. 3. मी) ire; sonare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मीमांस्<BR>मीमांस् v. मान्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मील्<BR>मील् 1. P. (निमेषणे K. निमेषे V.) nictari, connivere.<BR>GITA-GOV. 10.16.: यत्र स्विद्यति, मीलति (Schol.<BR>श्रीकृष्णे क्षणं स्विद्यति मीलति सति). Se claudere,<BR>de oculis. BHATT. 14.54.: तस्या मिमीलतुर् नेत्रे. — Caus.<BR>claudere, de oculis. MEGH. 109.: लोचने मीलयित्वा.<BR>c. उत् aperire oculos, aufschlagen. BHATT. 15.102.:<BR>उदमीलील् लोचने; MAH. 3.11155.: ईषद् उन्मील्य (*)<BR>लोचने. Se aperire, de oculis. BHATT. 16.8.: {#unmIlizyati<BR>cakzur me vfTA#}. — Caus. aperire oculos. UR. 5.14.:<BR>एतद् उन्मीलय चक्षुर् आयतम्.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) claudere oculos, niederschlagen. UR. 5.9.:<BR>भयनिमीलिताक्षी. Etiam omissâ oculos exprimente<BR>voce. RAGH. 8.37.: {#nimimIla narottamapriyA hftacandrA<BR>tamase 'va kOmudI#}. निमीलित = निमीलिताक्ष clausos<BR>oculos habens. RAGH. 1.68.: प्रजालोपनिमीलितः<BR>(*).<BR>2) dormire. MAN. 1.52.: {#yadA svapiti DarmAtmA<BR>tadA sarvan nimIlati#}; HIT. 107.13.: {#nareSvare<BR>jagat sarvan nimIlati nimIlati#}. — Caus. claudere<BR>oculos, expressâ vel omissâ oculos significante voce.<BR>MAH. 3.400.: सन्त्रासान् न्यमीलयत लोचने; 1.4278.:<BR>देवी न्यमीलयत्.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. GITA-GOV. 4.19.: प्रमीलति पतति.<BR>c. सम् se claudere. SAK. 45.4.: {#sammIlanti na tAvad<BR>banDanakozAs tayA 'vacitapuzpAH#}.<BR>(*) उन्मील्य et निमीलित etiam ad Caus. referri possunt.<BR>(*) उन्मील्य et निमीलित etiam ad Caus. referri possunt.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मीव्<BR>मीव् 1. P. i. q. पीव्, unde ortum esse videtur mutato प्<BR>in nasalem ejusdem organi.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=265-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

