मुर्छ्<BR>मुर्छ् 1. P. (proprie मूर्छ्, vocalis brevis enim nusquam apparet)<BR>1) animo conturbari; deliquium animi pati, animo<BR>linqui. GITA-GOV. 4.19.: {#pataty udyAti mUrCaty<BR>api#}; BHATT. 15.55.: अमूर्छीद् असौ क्षतः; R. Schl. II.34.17.:<BR>पपात भुवि मूर्छितः; IN. 5.48.: क्रोधमूर्छिता.<BR>2) implere, penetrare, occupare. RAGH. 6.9.: {#parito<BR>digantAn tUryasvane mUrCati#} (Shol. व्याप्नुवति सति).<BR>3) crescere. RAGH. 12.57.: {#mumUrCa saKyaM rAmasya<BR>samAnavyasane harO#} (Schol. ववृधे); 10.80.: {#svABAvikam<BR>vinItatvan tezAm vinayakarmaRA mumUrCe#}<BR>(Schol. वृद्धिम् प्राप) सहजन् तेजो हविषे ऽव हविर्भुजाम्.<BR>4) valere, potentem esse. RAGH. 2.34.: न<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-a" target="_blank">Page268-a+ 36</a>]<BR>पादपोन्मूलनशक्ति रंहः शिलोच्चये मूर्छति मारुतस्य.<BR>c. अभि i. q. simpl. sgf. 1. MAH. 1.7794.: कन्दर्पेणा ऽभिमूर्छिता.<BR>c. सम् valere, magnum, potentem esse. RAGH. 16.64.:<BR>श्रोत्रेषु सम्मूर्छति…वारिमृदङ्गवाद्यम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=267-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मुर्व्<BR>मुर्व् 1. P. (बन्धने K. नहि V.) ligare, nectere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मुशल<BR>मुशल v. मुषल.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मुष्<BR>1. मुष् 9. P. furari, rapere. N. 5.7.: {#muzRantI praBayA rAjYAY<BR>cakzUMzica manAMsica#}; H. 42.12.: {#mahatA Bayena<BR>muzitaH#}. Cum acc. pers. RIGV. 93.4.: {#amuzRItam<BR>avasam paRiN gAH#} «cripuistis alimentum Pani, nempe<BR>vaccas». — मुष् cl. 4. v. मुस्. (V. मूष्, मूष.)<BR>c. परि furtum alicui facere, c. acc. pers. MAH. 3.13030.:<BR>अन्योन्यम् परिमुष्णन्तो हिंसयन्तश्च मानवाः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मुष्<BR>2. मुष् 1. P. (वधे) ferire, occidere, laedere. Cf. मष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

