मुष्टी<BR>मुष्टी m. f. (ut videtur, a r. 2. मुष् s. ति) pugnus. (Huc traxerim<BR>germ. vet. fûst id., them. fûsti, mutatâ labiali nasali<BR>in mutam.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मुह्<BR>मुह् 4. P. interdum A. Part. pass. मुग्ध et मूढ, gerund.<BR>मुग्ध्वा et मूढ्वा (v. euph. r. 102.a.).<BR>1) animo conturbari,<BR>mentis errore affici, mente capi. BH. 2.13.: {#DIras<BR>tatra na muhyati#}; 5.15.: तेन मुह्यन्ति जन्तवः; MAH. 4.425.:<BR>मा मुह्यस्व.<BR>2) deliquium animi pati, animo<BR>linqui. R. Schl. I.21.21.: {#Sokena mahatA ''vizwaS cacAlaca<BR>mumohaca#}; MAH. 3.709.: मुमोहच पपातच. - मूढ<BR>animo conturbatus, mente captus, stultus, amens.<BR>N. 6.12. 18.10. — मुग्ध amore captus. RAGH. 9.44. — Intens.<BR>valde conturbari. MAH. 3.402.: मोमुह्यमान. — Caus.<BR>conturbare, stupefacere. N. 19.24.: {#raTinam mohayann<BR>iva#}; DEV. 1.66.: मोहयै ऽतौ दुराधर्षाव् असुरौ.<BR>— मोहित conturbatus, stupefactus, mentis suae non<BR>compos, mente captus. N. 8.16. 9.4. 10.28. SU. 4.18.<BR>(Pottius huc trahit gr. μῶ-ϱος, lat. mô-rus.)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-b" target="_blank">Page268-b+ 37</a>]<BR>c. आ praef. वि Caus. conturbare. MAH. 3.12138.<BR>c. परि Caus. id. MAH. 1.3571.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. प्रमूढ animo conturbatus. M. 54. — Caus.<BR>conturbare. DR. 6.21.<BR>c. प्र praef. वि Caus. conturbare. विप्रमोहित i. q. मोहित.<BR>H. 3.17.<BR>c. वि i. q. simpl. R. Schl. I.9.1. 39.: {#sukumArESca tEr aNgEs<BR>tABiH spfzwo vyamuhyata#}. BH. 2.72. — विमुग्ध conturbatus.<BR>HIT. ed. Ser. p. 49.: महता भयेन विमुग्धः.<BR>विमूढ id. BH. 3.27.: अहङ्कारविमूढात्मा. — विमूढ<BR>m. Geniorum ordo. SU. 3.5. — Caus. conturbare. A. 8.7.:<BR>व्यमोहयन्त माम्; 10.22.: {#vyamohayaYca tAn<BR>sarvAn raTamArgES caran raRe#}.<BR>c. सम् i. q. simpl. BH. 3.7.: धर्मसम्मूढचेताः; DR. 6.29.:<BR>दिशः सम्मुमुहुः परेषाम्. — Caus. conturbare. MAH. 2.1949.<BR>c. सम् praef. अभि अभिसम्मूढः conturbatus. A. 10.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मुहुस्<BR>मुहुस् Adv. identidem, iterum iterumque. N. 10.26. Saepe<BR>bis ponitus (मुहुर्मुहुस्) IN. 2.25. N. 15.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मुहूर्त|मुहूर्तं|मुहूर्तः|मुहूर्त्त|मुहूर्त्तः<BR>मुहूर्त m. n.<BR>1) momentum. H. 2.21. N. 17.12. SA. 5.6.<BR>2) hora (Wils.: The thirtieth part of a day and night, or<BR>an hour of forty - eight minutes). H. 4.46.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=268-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

