मृग्<BR>मृग् 10. A. interdum P. etiam 4. A. मृगयामि, मृगये (gr. 342.),<BR>मृग्ये. Quaerere. H. 1.25.: पानीयम् मृगयामि;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=269-b" target="_blank">Page269-b+ 37</a>]<BR>N. 12.118.: किम् वा मृगयसेवने; 13.65.: {#mfgayizyanti<BR>te Badre BartAram#}; 16.2.: मृगयध्वन् नलम्.<BR>मृगयाण quaerens (gr. 598.). N. 18.2. — Perscrutari.<BR>MAH. 4.865.: मृगयित्वा बहून् ग्रामान्. Cf. मार्ग्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=269-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मृग|मृगः<BR>मृग m. (r. मृग् s. अ)<BR>1) actio quaerendi.<BR>2) venatio. DR. 6.4.<BR>3) quadrupes in universum et specialiter dorcas,<BR>antilope. (Wils.:<BR>1) A deer, an antelope.<BR>2) an animal<BR>in general.). N. 11.25. SA. 5.74. H. 1.17. DR. 6.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=269-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

