मृगतृष्णा<BR>मृगतृष्णा f. (e मृग et तृष्णा sitis) vapores supra desertorum<BR>arenam, aquae speciem habentes, quâ animalia decipiuntur.<BR>UR. 15.5.infr. 17.3.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=269-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

