मेढ्र|मेढ्रः<BR>मेढ्र m. (r. मिह् s. त्र)<BR>1) penis.<BR>2) hircus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मेथ्<BR>मेथ् 1. P. (सङ्गे K. सङ्गे वधे मेधायाम् V.)<BR>1) adhaerere.<BR>In dial. Vêd. A. sibi obviam venire. RIGV. 113.3.:<BR>न मेथेथे न तस्थतुः सुमेके नक्तोषासा «non sibi obviam<BR>veniunt (Rosen. «se laedunt», cf. Westerg.) non<BR>subsistunt grato rore stillantes Nox et Aurora».<BR>2) laedere,<BR>occidere; in dial. Vêd. conviciari. RIGV. 42.10.:<BR>न पूषणम् मेथामसि.<BR>3) intelligere. (Cf. मिथ्, मेध्,<BR>1. मिद्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मेदस्<BR>मेदस् n. (r. 2. मिद् s. अस्) medulla. A. 10.54. (Fortasse<BR>medulla per assimil. e medusla vel medurla, v. मेदुर्; gr.<BR>μῡελός fortasse litteris transpositis e μεδυλος, ejecto δ,<BR>productâ antecedente vocali.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मेदिनी<BR>मेदिनी f. terra. N. 11.39.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मेदुर|मेदुरः<BR>मेदुर (r. 2. मिद् s. उर) adiposus, unctus. AM. (V. मेदस्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मेध्<BR>मेध् 1. P. A. (सङ्गमे K. वधमेधसङ्गेषु V.) convenire; laedere,<BR>occidere; inteligere. (V. मेधस्, मेधा et cf.<BR>मेथ्, मिथ्, 1. मिद्; lat. meditor; gr.<BR>ΜΑΘ, μανϑάνω, μήδομαι, μῆδος.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मेधस्<BR>मेधस् n. (r. मेध् s. अस्) mens, intellectus. BH. 18.35. in<BR>fine comp. BAH. (Cf. gr. μῆδος, v. मेध्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मेधा<BR>मेधा f. (r. मेध् s. आ) mens, intellectus (cf. मेधस्). IN. 4.9.<BR>BH. 10.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मेधाविन्<BR>मेधाविन् (a praec. s. विन्) mente, intellectu praeditus.<BR>BH. 18.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

