मोह|मोहं|मोहः<BR>मोह m. (r. मुह् s. अ)<BR>1) stultitia, mentis error. DR. 7.20.<BR>M. 53. BH. 4.35.<BR>2) animi defectus, animi deliquium.<BR>UR. 6.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

