मौल|मौलः<BR>मौल (fem. ई, a मूल s. अ)<BR>1) radicalis.<BR>2) generosâ stripe<BR>oriundus, nobilis, generosus. HIT. 84.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=272-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मौलि|मौलिः<BR>मौलि m. f. (a मूल s. इ)<BR>1) caput. HEM.<BR>2) diadema, tiara.<BR>SA. 5.7.: बद्धमौलि; v. चन्द्रमौलि.<BR>3) cincinnus, coma<BR>crispata. (Cf. germ. vet. muâla f., island. vet. mûli m. os,<BR>nostrum Maul.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

