म्रद्<BR>म्रद् 1. A. conterere. Cf. मृद् i. e. मर्द्, रद्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

