म्लेड्<BR>म्लेड् 1. P. id.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

म्लै<BR>म्लै 1. P. म्लायामि. Part. pass. म्लान.<BR>1) Flaccescere,<BR>marcescere. MAH. 3.15455.: म्लायन्ति स्रजः; N. 5.26.:<BR>म्लानस्रक्; MAH. 3.15683.: म्लान्ति वृक्षाः (pro<BR>म्लायन्ति).<BR>2) languescere, fatigari. RAGH. 11.9.: {#paTi<BR>…mamlatur na#}. (Cf. मृ; gr. μαϱαίνω; lat. marc-esco<BR>adjectâ gutturali; fortasse flacc-esco mutatâ labiali nasali<BR>in aspiratam; huc etiam referri posset germ. vet. welh<BR>marcidus, welchên marcescere, mutato m in w, v. Graff. I.816.)<BR>c. परि i. q. simpl. परिम्लान flaccidus. R. Schl. II.59.8.:<BR>वृक्षाः परिम्लानाः<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

य|यं|यः<BR>य v. 3. यत्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यकन्<BR>यकन् v. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यकृत्<BR>यकृत् n. (in casibus debil. etiam यकन्, v. gr. 205.) jecur.<BR>(Lat. jecur; gr. ἧπaϱ(τ), ἧπα(ϱ)τ-ος, mutatâ gutt. in<BR>lab.; germ. vet. lebara, lebera f., mutatâ sem. य् in ल्,<BR>v. gr. comp. 20., Graff. 2.80.; slav. jatra neut. pl.; huc fortasse [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-1b" target="_blank">Page273-1b+ 6</a>]<BR>etiam scot. cruthan pertinet, abjectâ syllabâ initiali.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यक्ष्<BR>यक्ष् 10. A. (पूजायाम् K. महि V., ut mihi videtur, a यज्<BR>adjectâ sibilante) honorare, colere, venerari.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यक्ष|यक्षः<BR>यक्ष m. Yakschus, nomen Geniorum, qui Kuvêri, Dei divitiarum,<BR>sunt ministri ejusque horti divitiarumque custodes.<BR>IN. 5.25. SU. 2.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=273-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यक्षराज्<BR>यक्षराज् m. (Yakṣorum rex e praec. et राज्, nom. राट्)<BR>nomen Kuvêri.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यक्षी<BR>यक्षी f. (a यक्ष signo fem. ई) Yakschia. N. 12.120.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यछ्<BR>यछ् v. यम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यज्<BR>1. यज् 1. P. A. (in formis puris, Precativo A. excepto, nec<BR>non in syllabâ repetitâ praet. redupl., syllaba य corripitur<BR>in इ)<BR>1) colere deos. BH. 9.23.: {#ye 'py anyA<BR>devatA BaktA yajante…te 'pi mAm eva…yajanti#}.<BR>2) sacrificare. MAH. 1.4687.: {#asmiMSca yajamAne…upAgamaMs<BR>tato devAH#}; R. Schl. I.15.14.: {#lapsyase putrAn<BR>yadarTaM yajase#}. C. instr. sacrificii. SU. 2.13.: {#yajYEr yajanti<BR>ye kecid yAjayantica ye dvijAH#}; N. 5.45.: {#IjecA<BR>'py aSvameDena#}; 12.14.: अश्वमेधादिभिर् वीर क्रतुभिः…इष्ट्वा;<BR>36.38.: ईजेच विविधैर् यज्ञैः. Etiam<BR>c. acc. sacrificii. R. Schl. I.31.5.: यज्ञं यजमाने; 15.3.:<BR>अयजत् पुत्रीयाम् इष्टिम् पुत्रेप्सुः. C. acc. pers. R. Schl. I.14.7.:<BR>इष्टवान् अश्वमेधेन भवतः (cf. हु c.<BR>acc.).<BR>3) initiare, inaugurare. R. Schl. II.56.18. 21.: {#SAlAM<BR>yakzyAmahe#}<BR>4) dare. BHATT. 8.49.: यजन्तीभिः स्वविग्रहान्<BR>(Schol. ददतीभिः कामिभ्यः). — Caus. sacrificium<BR>alicujus peragere, de sacerdote. SU. 2.13.: R. Schl. I.10.26.:<BR>{#putrakAmam iman tAta tvaM yAjayitum<BR>arhasi#}. — Desid. sacrificare velle. MAH. 2.59.: यियक्षमाण.<BR>(Gr. ἅζω, ἅγιος = यज्य e यग्य, v. याग.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यज्<BR>2. यज् (r. यज्) colens, adorans deos, in fine compos. BH. 7.23.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यजुस्<BR>यजुस् n. (r. यज् s. उस्) nomen unius quatuor Vêdorum.<BR>BH. 9.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यज्ञ|यज्ञः<BR>यज्ञ m. (r. यज् s. न, v. euph. r. 93.) sacrificium. BR. 2.24.<BR>BH. 9.15. 20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यज्वन्<BR>यज्वन् m. (r. यज् s. वन्) sacrificator. IN. 1.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्|यन्त्<BR>1. यत् 1. A. interdum P. operam dare, niti, studere, c. loc.<BR>vel infin. N. 15.4.: सर्वं यतिष्ये तत् कर्तुम्; 17.29.:<BR>नलस्या ऽऽनयने यत; 34.: यतध्वन् नलमार्गणे; H. 4.33.:<BR>अपनेतुञ्च यतितो नचै ऽव शकितो मम. — Absol.<BR>H. 1.4.: यतमाना वनं राजन् गहनम् प्रतिपेदिरे.<BR>(Cf. यस्, gr. ζητέω = Caus. vel cl. 10. यातयामि.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-b" target="_blank">Page274-b+ 37</a>]<BR>Cum Pottio huc traxerim lat. nîtor = नि + यत्,<BR>ejectâ syllabâ य, vel correpto ya in i.)<BR>c. आ niti, inniti aliquâ re, pendere ex aliquâ re. HIT. 52.9.:<BR>स्वयत्नायत्तः; 48.7.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् id., cum loc. MAH. 3.10484.: {#AsAm<BR>prARAH samAyattA mamacA 'trE 'kaputrake#}.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. N. 17.33.: {#prayatantu tava prezyAH puRyaSlokasya<BR>mArgaRe#}; 18.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्|यन्त्<BR>2. यत् 10. P. (निकारोपस्कारयोः K. खेदोपस्करयोः V.)<BR>offendere, vexare; parare.<BR>c. निस्<BR>1) reddere, restituere. MAH. 3.16596.: {#tasmE tad<BR>Barato rAjyam…niryAtayAmAsa#}; 13182.<BR>2) condonare,<BR>ignoscere. MAH. 1.3018.: {#yamaH…tasya niryAtayati<BR>duzkftam#}.<BR>c. निस् praef. प्रति reddere. MAH. 3.13183.<BR>c. प्रति removere, abjicere, finire. MAH. 3.14728.: {#DArtarAzwravaDaN<BR>kftvA vErARi pratiyAtyaca#}.<BR>c. वि non condonare, punire, c. acc. pers. et rei. M. 1.3019.:<BR>तं यमः पापकर्माणम् वियातयति दुष्कृतम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्|यन्त्<BR>3. यत् (nom. यस्, या, यत्, gr. 272.) qui. DR. 2.5. 6.7. — Repetitum,<BR>quicunque. N. 5.12. BH. 3.21. — Antecedente<BR>vel sequente Relativo vi attractionis etiam notio<BR>aliquis per Relativum exprimitur (cf. locutiones ut<BR>कः कम् quis aliquem, v. किम्), e. c. HITOP. 20.60.:<BR>यो ऽत्ति यस्य यदा मांसम् qui alicujus; 53.2.:<BR>यद् एव रोचते यस्मै quod alicui; 17.9.: {#yad yena<BR>yujyate#} quo aliquid. Repetitum, HIT. 53.3.: {#yasya yasya<BR>hi yo BAvaH#} quae alicujus est natura. — Cum sequente<BR>को ऽपि quivis, quisque. N. 26.9. Cum sequente<BR>कश्चित् quicunque, wer irgend. SU. 2.13. — De constructionibus<BR>ut यस् त्वम् quia tu, यान् इमान् quia<BR>hos v. p. 39. s. v. इदम्. (Gr. ὅς c. spir. asp. pro य् sicut<BR>in ἅζω, ὑμεῖς, ὑσμίνη = यज्, युष्मे dial. Vêd.,<BR>युध्; lith. ji-s is pro ja-s, dat. ja-m = यस्मै, loc. ja-me<BR>= यस्मिन्; slav. i eum, jû eam, i-she qui, ja-sche<BR>quae; goth. ja-bai si, jau an. Huc etiam pertinet particula<BR>enclitica ei = î, quod cum demonstrativo conjungitur [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">Page275-a+ 37</a>]<BR>ad exprimendum Relativum, e. c. saei qui, than-ei<BR>quem. V. gr. comp. 282. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=274-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्|यन्त्<BR>4. यत् Conj. (acc. neut. praec.)<BR>1) quod, daʃs. H. 1.5. 29. 2.4.<BR>BR. 3.16. In recentioribus scriptis etiam sicut gr.<BR>ὅτι, pers. keh ad introducendem orationem directam adhibetur.<BR>Lass. 45.5.: {#tvam mamA 'gra iti jalpasi yat<BR>tvAm vinA mamA 'nyA vallaBA nA 'sti#} (cf. यथा).<BR>2) quam ob rem, quâ de causâ. N. 24.18.<BR>3) quia. H. 4.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत|यतः<BR>यत v. यम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यतस्<BR>यतस् Adv. (a stirpe Relativi य, v. gr. 272. suff. तस्)<BR>1) unde, relative.<BR>2) ex quo, de tempore, seitdem. R. Schl. II.7.1.:<BR>यतो जाता ex quo nata.<BR>3) ubi, relative.<BR>BR. 1.20.<BR>4) quo, quem in locum, relative. SA. 5.28.<BR>5) nam. HIT. 27.5. SAK. 53.16. (Gr. ὅ-ϑεν, slav. jûdû-sche,<BR>v. gr. comp. 421.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यति|यतिः<BR>यति m. (r. यम् cohibere, refraenare suff. ति) cujus animi<BR>appetitus cohibiti sunt, temperans. BH. 4.28.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यतिन्<BR>यतिन् m. i. q. praec. (ut videtur, a यत cohibitum, refraenatum,<BR>suff. इन्). BH. 5.26.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्न|यत्नः<BR>यत्न m. (r. यत् s. न) opera, nisus, studium. N. 1.6. 4.16. 9.36. 20.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्नतस्<BR>यत्नतस् Adv. (a praec. s. तस्) studiose, diligenter. HIT. 30.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्र<BR>यत्र Adv. et Conj. (a stirpe Relativi य s. त्र)<BR>1) ubi, relative<BR>H. 2.16. Interdum pro Locativo यस्मिन् ponitur, e. c.<BR>यत्र काले. BH. 8.23.<BR>2) quia. N. 11.7.<BR>3) quod, daʃs.<BR>N. 8.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्रक्वचन<BR>यत्रक्वचन Adv. (e यत्र et क्वचन alicubi - a क्व suff. चन)<BR>ubicunque, quoquo versus. BR. 3.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथा<BR>यथा (a stirpe Relat. य s. था)<BR>1) Adv. sicut. DR. 2.7. Repetitum,<BR>utcunque, quomodocunque. N. 18.14.<BR>2) Conj.<BR>ut. H. 4.51. SU. 3.21. N. 1.21.<BR>3) in recentioribus scriptis<BR>sicut यत् adhibetur ad introducendam orationem directam.<BR>UR. 13.4.infr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथाकामम्<BR>यथाकामम् Adv. (AVY. et यथा sicut et काम m. desiderium)<BR>ad arbitrium, ad libidinem, ex optato, ad voluntatem.<BR>IN. 4.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथातथम्<BR>यथातथम् Adv. (AVY. e यथा et तथा sic, quod hac in compositione<BR>Substantivi loco fungitur et veritatem significat,<BR>v. gr. 675.) secundum veritatem. IN. 5.52. N. 3.2. 16.39. 21.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथान्यायम्<BR>यथान्यायम् Adv. (AVY. e यथा et न्याय m. convenientia,<BR>decentia, apta ratio) sicut convenientia, secundum convenientiam.<BR>IN. 1.21. BR. 1.26.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथावत्<BR>यथावत् Adv. (e यथा sicut et वत् sicut in fine compos.)<BR>apte, convenienter, congruenter. SA. 4.16. SU. 1.26.<BR>N. 6.8. 8.16. 24.44. 25.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथाविधि<BR>यथाविधि Adv. (AVY. e यथा et विधि praescriptum, praeceptum,<BR>lex) secundum legem. IN. 1.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथावृत्तम्<BR>यथावृत्तम् Adv. (AVY. e यथा et वृत्त n. quod fuit, accidit,<BR>evenit) sicut evenit, secundum veritatem. IN. 5.52. N. 11.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथासुखम्<BR>यथासुखम् Adv. (AVY. e यथा et सुख voluptas) ad voluptatem,<BR>ad libidinem. H. 4.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथेप्सित|यथेप्सितं<BR>यथेप्सित Adj. (KRAM. e यथा et ईप्सित optatus) sicut<BR>optatus. SU. 4.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यदा<BR>यदा Adv. (a stirpe Relativi य s. दा) quando, quo tempore.<BR>BH. 2.52. यदा यदा quandocunque. BH. 4.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यदि<BR>यदि Conj. (ut mihi videtur, a stirpe Relat. य suff. दि pro<BR>ति, cf. इति, nisi a neutro यत् adjecto इ)<BR>1) si. SA. 4.22. 5.97.;<BR>c. Potent. N. 17.44.<BR>2) an, num, germanice<BR>ob, e. c. H. 1.6.: न जानीमो यदि दग्धः पुरोचनः.<BR>(Fortasse gr. εἰ ex ἐδι.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यदिवा<BR>यदिवा Conj. (e यदि et वा vel)<BR>1) vel, sive. BH. 2.6.<BR>2) utrum in antecedente et an in consequente orationis<BR>membro. H. 4.28. N. 17.47.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यदृच्छा<BR>यदृच्छा f. (e Relativo यत् et ऋच्छा, quod hac in compositione<BR>solum invenitur, a r. ऋछ् ire s. अ in fem.) libera<BR>voluntas. BH. 4.22. — यदृच्छया sponte, cum liberâ voluntate,<BR>cum voluptate. BH. 2.32. H. 2.4. R. Schl. II.7.1.<BR>RAGH. 3.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यद्वत्<BR>यद्वत् Adv. (e Relat. यत् et वत् sicut in fine compos.) sicut.<BR>BH. 2.70.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यद्वा<BR>यद्वा (e Relativo यत् et वा) vel, sive.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=275-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यन्तृ|यंतृ<BR>यन्तृ m. (r. यम् refraenare s. तृ) auriga. N. 20.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=276-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यन्त्र|यंत्र|यंत्रं|यन्त्रं<BR>यन्त्र n. (r. यम् s. त्र) machina, machinamentum, compages.<BR>BH. 18.61.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=276-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यम्<BR>1. यम् 1. P. interdum A. (in tempp. special. यछ्, gr. 328.;<BR>praet. mtf. अयंसम्, fut. aux. यंस्यामि, part. pass.<BR>यत) refrenare, cohibere. रश्मीन् habenas. N. 20.15.:<BR>रश्मीन् यच्छतु वाजिनाम्. — हयान् flectere, moderari<BR>equous. IN. 1.19.: हयान् येमेच रशिमभिः. — रथम्<BR>currum flectere. A. 4.32.: {#apaSyaM hariyujaM raTam…yatam<BR>mAtalinA#}.<BR>2) dare. HIT. 59.2.: {#aBayavAcam me<BR>yacCa#}; MAN. 2.55.: {#pUjitaM hy aSanan nityam balam<BR>UrjaYca yacCati#}.<BR>3) A. prehendere, sumere (sibi dare, v.<BR>दा praef. आ). RIGV. 52.8.: {#ayacCaTA bAhvor vajram<BR>Ayasam#}. (Cf. gr. ζημία, ἥμεϱος; lat. jêjûnus ad Intens.<BR>यंयम् referri posset; Pottius apte huc trahit emo<BR>proprie sumo, quod e sub-imo, ex-imo; demo e de-imo;<BR>fortasse premo ex pra-imo = प्रयम्; lith. immu sumo,<BR>per assimil. ex imju, v. gr. comp. 501., praet. ếmjau, fut.<BR>im-su; slav. imamj habeo; russ. imaju capio, deprehendo;<BR>fortasse goth. NAM sumere (nima, nam, nêmum) ex<BR>praep. in, abjecto i et AM pro JAM; hib.<BR>1) ivmainim «I<BR>drive, toss, twirl»,<BR>2) iomainim «I force, compel, oblige»;<BR>scot. iomain «a driving, act of driving or urging».)<BR>c. आ extendere, v. आयत longus. ATM. SAK. 73.4.:<BR>स्वाङ्गम् आयच्छमानः. — धनुस् arcum intendere.<BR>MAH. 3.8665.: धनुर् आयच्छ.<BR>c. आ praef. निस् extendere. SAK. 4.17.: निरायतपूर्वकायाः…वाजिनः.<BR>c. आ praef. वि extendere, व्यायत longus. RAGH. 3.34.<BR>ATM. se extendere, vires contendere, niti, conniti. MAH. 3.12740.:<BR>इदं श्रेयः परमम् मन्यमाना व्यायमन्ते मुनयः.<BR>c. उत्<BR>1) tollere, extollere, sublevare. BH. 5.20.: {#Danur<BR>udyamya#}; DR. 9.1.: भ्रातराव् उद्यतायुधौ; R. Schl. I.28.2.:<BR>उद्यम्य बाहू.<BR>2) offerre. R. Schl. I.52.14.: {#satkriyAM<BR>hi BavAn etAm pratICatu mayo 'dyatAm#}.<BR>3) contendere, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=276-b" target="_blank">Page276-b+ 37</a>]<BR>operam dare, niti, studere. BH. 1.45.: {#hantuM<BR>svajanam udyatAH#}; RAGH. 10.50.: {#surakAryodyatam…<BR>vizRum#}. — उद्यत festinans. N. 10.25.: आतिष्ठद् उद्यतः<BR>(v. Subst. उद्यम).<BR>4) luctari. UR. 18.12.: {#srotase<BR>'vo dyamAnasya (= udyamamAnasya)#}.<BR>c. उत् praef. अभि<BR>1) tollere, sublevare, extollere. MR. 327.5.:<BR>अभ्युद्यते शस्त्रे.<BR>2) offerre. MAN. 4.247.: {#annam<BR>aByudyatam#}.<BR>c. उत् praef. सम्<BR>1) tollere, sublevare, extollere. DR. 9.3.:<BR>समुद्यम्यच तम् भीमो निष्पिपेष महीतले; MAH. 1.6278.:<BR>समुद्यम्य कराव् उभौ.<BR>2) contendere, operam<BR>dare, studere. R. Schl. I.14.8.: इष्टिम्…कर्तुं समुद्यतः.<BR>3) i. q. simpl. sgf. 1. N. 19.23.: {#aSvAn…raSmiBiSca<BR>samudyamya#}.<BR>c. उप 1. A. capere, sumere (sibi dare). BHATT. 15.21.:<BR>उपायंस्त महास्त्राणि. Praesertim uxorem accipere, in<BR>matrimonium ducere. MAN. 3.11.: {#no 'payacCeta tAm<BR>prAjYaH#}; MAH. 1.1047.: {#BEkzyavat tAm aham upayaMsye<BR>viDAnataH#}; 3765. 3791. 5181. Etiam PAR. MAN. 11.172.:<BR>एतास् तिस्रस् तु भार्यार्थे नो ऽपयच्छेत्.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) opprimere, coërcere, cohibere. N. 20.38.: {#nyayacCat<BR>kopam AtmanaH#}; BH. 3.7.: {#indriyARi manasA<BR>niyamya#}; BH. 7.20.: प्रकृत्या नियताः स्वया; RAGH. 3.45.<BR>— अश्वान् equos refraenare, domare. MAH. 4.1953.:<BR>ना ऽहं शक्ष्यामि…नियन्तुन् ते हयोत्तमान्. — नियत<BR>demissus, submissus, humilis. SA. 3.5. 4.11.<BR>2) ligare,<BR>constringere. R. Schl. I.13.33.: {#paSUnAn triSatan<BR>tva AsId yUpezu niyatam#} (v. संयम्). TROP.<BR>नियत necessarius. BH. 3.8.: नियतङ् कुरु कर्म त्वम्.<BR>— नियतम् Adv. necessario, utique. BH. 1.44.: {#utsannakulaDarmARAm<BR>… narake niyatam vAsaH#}.<BR>3) celare.<BR>MAN. 10.59.: न कथञ्चन दुर्योनिः प्रकृतिं स्वान् नियच्छति.<BR>4) adipisci. MAN. 2.93. et 12.11.: {#tataH sidDin<BR>niyacCati#}; 10.93.<BR>5) facere, perficere. MAN. 5.44.:<BR>या वेदविहिता हिंसा नियता.<BR>c. नि praef. सम् id. sgf. 1. BH. 12.4.: सन्नियम्ये ऽन्द्रियग्रामम्;<BR>MAN. 2.93.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=277-a" target="_blank">Page277-a+ 37</a>]<BR>c. प्र dare. A. 4.27.: तानि दिव्यानि मे ऽस्त्राणि प्रयच्छ;<BR>11.4.: इदम् मे तनुत्राणम् प्रायच्छत्; BH. 9.26. MAN. 8.158.<BR>Reddere. MAN. 8.183.: {#yo nikzepan nikzeptur<BR>na prayacCati#}. — प्रयत deditus, demissus, devotus. N. 25.2.<BR>MAH. 3.5001.<BR>c. प्र praef. सम् id. R. Schl. II.7.7.: {#DanaN kinnu janeByaH<BR>samprayacCati#}. Uxorem ducere. SA. 2.4.: {#kimarTaM yuvatIm<BR>BartA nacE 'nAM samprayacCati#}.<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) coërcere, cohibere, opprimere. इन्द्रियाणि<BR>sensus. BH. 2.61. SA. 2.10. कोपम् iram. N. 20.33. हयान्<BR>equos regere. MAH. 3.12110. द्वाराणि portas occludere.<BR>BH. 8.12.<BR>2) ligare, colligare. M. 40.: {#saMyatas<BR>tena pASena#}; SA. 5.101.: केशान् संयम्य.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=276-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

