याजिन्<BR>याजिन् (r. यज् s. इन्) colens, venerans. BH. 9.34.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

याज्ञसेनी<BR>याज्ञसेनी f. (patronym. a यज्ञसेन s. अ in fem.) nomen<BR>Draupadiae.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यातना<BR>यातना f. (a Caus. r. यत् s. अन in fem.) tormentum, cruciatus.<BR>MAN. 12.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यातयाम|यातयामं<BR>यातयाम (BAH. e यात praeteritus et याम q. v. praeteritam<BR>vigiliam, vel praeteritas vigilias habens)<BR>vetustus, corruptus, de cibo. BH. 17.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यातु|यातुः<BR>यातु m. (a r. या s. unâd. तु)<BR>1) viator.<BR>2) Daemonum genus<BR>(Wils.: A demon, a goblin, an imp or evil spirit).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यातुधान|यातुधानः<BR>यातुधान m. (e praec. et धान, quod seorsum non invenitur,<BR>a r. धा s. अन) i. q. praec. sgnf. 2. A. 10.52.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यातृ<BR>यातृ f. (ut videtur, a r. यम्, abjecto म्, producto अ, suff.<BR>तृ, v. यम् praef. उप in matrimonium ducere) mariti<BR>fratris uxor. AM. (Polon. jatrew (jaṅtrew) fratris<BR>uxor.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यात्रा<BR>यात्रा f. (r. या s. त्र in fem.)<BR>1) itus, iter. RAGH. 18.15. 17.56.<BR>2) victus. N. 18.11. BH. 3.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

याथातथ्य|याथातथ्यं<BR>याथातथ्य n. (a यथातथम् s. य) veritas. HIT. 130.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

याथात्म्य<BR>याथात्म्य n. (a यथात्मन् - यथा + आत्मन् - s. य) natura,<BR>indoles. RAGH. 10.25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यादस्<BR>यादस् n. bestia aquatilis. BH. 10.29.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यादृश्<BR>यादृश् m. f. n. (v. gr. 287.) qualis. BH. 13.3. (Gr. ἧλιξ,<BR>v. gr. comp. 415.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यादृश|यादृशः<BR>यादृश (fem. ई, v. gr. 287.) id. MAH. 3.1370. (Gr. ἡλίϰος,<BR>v. gr. comp. 415.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यान|यानं<BR>यान n. (r. या s. अन)<BR>1) itio, incessus, ingressus, cursus.<BR>DR. 8.18. N. 18.6.<BR>2) vehiculum, currus. N. 7.9. 17.21. 23.<BR>(Cf. lat. janua.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यापन|यापनं<BR>यापन n. (a Caus. r. या s. अन) actio faciendi ut eat, transeat.<BR>कालयापन temporis profusio. HIT. 54.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

याम|यामः<BR>याम m. (r. यम् s. अ) vigilia, quae tertiam noctis partem<BR>complecti videtur, appellatur enim nox त्रियामा tres<BR>vigilias habens. UP. 44.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=278-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यामन<BR>यामन m. (r. यम् s. अन) Dual. gemini. H. 1.38. Cf. {#yama,<BR>yamaja#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यामिक|यामिकः<BR>यामिक (a याम s. इक) vigilias spectans. यामिकः पुरुषः<BR>vigil nocturnus. P. 18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यामिनी<BR>यामिनी f. (a याम s. इन् in fem.) nox. RAGH. 15.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यायिन्<BR>यायिन् (r. या s. इन् inserto य् euphonico) iens. N. 22.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यावत्|यावन्त्<BR>1. यावत् Adj. (v. gr. 283.) quantus, quot. BH. 2.46. BR. 1.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यावत्|यावन्त्<BR>2. यावत् Adv. et Conj. (acc. neut. praecedentis)<BR>1) quatenus.<BR>SA. 5.19.<BR>2) quam diu. N. 5.33. 14.16. SA. 5.87.<BR>3) quoties. BH. 13.26.<BR>4) dum, quo tempore, antecedente<BR>न, sequente तावत्. HIT. 42.7.: {#ekasya duHKasya<BR>na yAvad antaN gacCAmi…tAvad dvitIyaM samupasTitam<BR>me#}; 43.12.<BR>5) quum, de tempore, sequente<BR>तावत्. HIT. 12.1. 43.21. UP. 34. Lass. 6.18. 7.1. 16.2.<BR>6) donec. N. 14.6.<BR>7) nunc. SAK. 8.3. 45.13. UR. 15.1.infr.<BR>8) ut, daʃs. BH. 1.22. A. 10.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यियक्षु<BR>यियक्षु (a यियक्ष् Desid. r. यज् s. उ) sacrificare cupiens.<BR>RAGH. 13.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यु<BR>1. यु 2. P. et 9. P. A. यौमि (gr. 343.), युनामि, युने. Conjungere.<BR>युत conjunctus, praeditus. N. 12.2.: {#vanam<BR>…mahizarkzagaREr yutam#}; 12.10.: {#lakzmyA sTityAca<BR>parayA yutA#}. (Cf. युज्. Fortasse lat. jûs, jûro ab obligando;<BR>huc etiam traxerim, juvare, ita ut proprie significet<BR>se adjungere alicui; formâ pertinere videtur ad<BR>Caus. यावयामि; lith. jau-tis bos tanquam jumentum,<BR>jůs-mi vel jůs-u cinctus sum; gr. ζώννυ-μι, ζώ-σω<BR>(ζ = य्, v. gr. comp. 19., ω = औ abjecto उ); cf. Pott. 1.213.;<BR>cambro-brit. ieuad «a putting in a team, a yoking»,<BR>ieuaeth «a yoked state», ieuaw «to put in a team,<BR>to yoke».)<BR>c. आ i. q. simpl. N. 12.39.: वराहर्क्षमृगायुतम्; 65.:<BR>शाखामृगगणायुतम्.<BR>c. प्र प्रयुत n. millio.<BR>c. सम् i. q. simpl. SA. 5.33.: नियमेन संयुताः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यु<BR>2. यु 10. P. arcere. RIGV. 5.10.: यवया (= यवय) वधम्;<BR>RIGV. 5. (v. Westerg.): विश्वा ऽस्मद् दुरिता यावयन्तु.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">Page279-b+ 36</a>]<BR>In dial. Vêd. etiam cl. 3. P. YAJURV. (v. Westerg.):<BR>युयोध्य् अस्मज् जुहुराणम् एनः.<BR>c. अप cl. 3. P. in dial. Vêd. arcere, repellere (proprie<BR>disjungere). RIGV. 92.11.<BR>c. वि cl. 3. P. privare (disjungere) in dial. Vêd. RIGV. 39.8.:<BR>वि तं युयोत शवसा «eum private cibo».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युक्त|युक्तं|युक्तः<BR>युक्त v. युज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युग|युगं|युगः<BR>युग n. (r. युज् jungere s. अ)<BR>1) par. N. 14.25.<BR>2) mundi<BR>aetas. BH. 8.17. (Lat. jugum; gr. ζυγόν, ζυγός; goth.<BR>juk n., them. juka jugum; lith. junga-s jugum; slav. igo<BR>n. id.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युगपद्<BR>युगपद् Adv. simul, una. BH. 11.12. A. 3.22. RAGH. 4.15. 5.68.<BR>(Cf. यौगपद्येन.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युगमात्र<BR>युगमात्र (e praec. et मात्र q. v.) in initio comp. commodum,<BR>commodo, tantum quod, proxime. SA. 4.10.: {#yugamAtrodite<BR>sUrye#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युग्य|युग्यं|युग्यः<BR>युग्य (r. युज् s. य)<BR>1) m. jumentum. RAGH. 5.49.<BR>2) n. vehiculum,<BR>currus. N. 17.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युङ्ग्<BR>युङ्ग् 1. P. (वर्जने) relinquere. Cf. जुङ्ग्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युछ्|युच्छ्<BR>युछ् 1. P. i. q. पुछ्, मुछ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युज्<BR>1. युज् 7. P. A.<BR>1) jungere, conjungere. DR. 4.24.: {#vAkyEr<BR>vAkyAni yuYjatI#} (sic cum ed. Calc. pro योजती<BR>cl. 1. legendum esse videtur); N. 12.89.: {#AtmAnaM SreyasA<BR>yokzye#}. Jungere currum equis etc. vel jungere equos<BR>etc. currum. MAH. 3.11761.: युज्यताम् (रथः); 3.13035.:<BR>योक्ष्यन्ति धुरि धेनुकाः; RIGV. 14.12.: {#yuNkzva hy aruzI<BR>raTe#} «junge utique impigras currui equas». Se conjungere<BR>matrimonio cum aliquâ (ATM.). MAH. 1.4421.:<BR>तया…युयुजे. Instruere aliquem aliqû re. R. Schl. I.9.68.:<BR>भोगैर् एनं युयोज; MAH. 1.7982.: {#tAm ASIrBir<BR>yuYjata#}. Alligare. A. 11.5.: {#kirIwam me svayam<BR>indro yuyoja#}. — युक्त junctus, de curru. N. 19.20.<BR>Praeditus. H. 4.8.: तेजसा युक्तः.<BR>2) injungere, adhibere,<BR>praeficere, c. loc. rei (v. praef. नि). MAH. 2.1290.:<BR>तान् सर्वान्…युयोज स यथायोगम् अधिकारोषु.<BR>3) emittere, conjicere, jaculari sagittas. MAH. 3.12309.:<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=280-a" target="_blank">Page280-a+ 36</a>]<BR>मा युङ्क्ष्व दिव्यान्य् अस्त्राणि.<BR>4) dirigere, attendere,<BR>intendere, applicare, colligere cogitationem, mentem,<BR>animum (aut expresso aut omisso animi nomine). BH. 6.10.:<BR>युञ्जीत…आत्मानम् (Schol. {#yuYjIta samAhitaN<BR>kuryAt#}); 12.: योगं युञ्ज्यात् cogitationem, animi<BR>collectionem intendat; 15.: युञ्जन्न् आत्मानम् colligens,<BR>intendens animum (Schol. समाहितङ् कुर्वन्).<BR>युक्त intentus meditationi, defixus in meditatione. BH. 6.14.<BR>5) cogitare. SA. 5.6.: {#tam muhUrtaN kzaRam velAn<BR>divasaYca yuyoja ha#}. — Pass.<BR>1) jungi, conjungi, instrui;<BR>alligari (v. supra).<BR>2) cum loc. convenire, congruere,<BR>aptum, idoneum esse alicui rei. BH. 17.26.: {#praSaste<BR>karmaRi taTA sac CabdaH pArTa yujyate#}; RAGH. 18.41.:<BR>शब्दो महाराज इति…तस्मिन् युयुजे; SA. 3.10.:<BR>न मद्विधे युज्यति वाक्यम् ईदृशम् (metri causâ<BR>termin. P.). युक्त conveniens, aptus, idoneus. SA. 3.12. 4.7.<BR>H. 2.29.<BR>3) c. dat. se dedere, applicare alicui rei.<BR>BH. 2.38.: युद्धाय युज्यस्व; 50.: योगाय युज्यस्व. — In<BR>dial. Vêd. युज् etiam cl. 1 mam sequitur, e. c. RIGV. 82.1.<BR>(Cf. यु; lat. jungo, conjux, jugum; gr. ΖΥΓ, ζεύγνυμι, ζυγόν, ζυγός;<BR>lith. jungiu jugum impono, junga-s<BR>jugum; slav. igo, v. युग. Huc etiam traxerim goth.<BR>liuga nubeo, liugaith nubet = योजयति (v. युज् cl. 10.<BR>et gr. comp. 109^a).6.) mutatâ semivocali य् in l, v. यकृत्,<BR>servatâ mediâ contra generalem legem, sicut e. c. in<BR>BUG = 1. भुज्.)<BR>c. अनु<BR>1) interrogare. MAN. 8.79.: साक्षिणः…अनुयुञ्जीत;<BR>8.259.: इमान् अप्य् अनुयुञ्जीत (साक्षिणः);<BR>RAGH. 5.18.: {#kim vastu vidvan gurave pradeyam…iti<BR>tam anvayuNkta#}.<BR>2) jubere. MAH. 4.105.: {#yad yad<BR>BatI 'nuyuYjIta tat tad evA 'nuvartayet#}.<BR>c. अभि<BR>1) i. q. simpl. sgf. 3. अभियुक्त in cogitatione defixus.<BR>BH. 9.22.<BR>2) aggredi, impugnare, offendere, conturbare,<BR>perturbare. R. Schl. II.10.27.: {#kenA 'BiyuktA<BR>'si kena vA 'si vimAnitA#}; MAN. 8.50. 183. V. {#aBiyoga,<BR>aBiyoktf#}.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=280-b" target="_blank">Page280-b+ 36</a>]<BR>c. आ jungere equos. MAH. 1.7948.: तुरगान् केचिद् आयुञ्जन्.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् conjungere. N. 25.8.: दमयन्त्या समायुङ्क्तम्.<BR>c. उत् उद्युक्त excitatus. R. Schl. I.1.: {#sUrpaRaKavAkyAd<BR>udyuktAn sarvarAkzasAn#}. — Caus. excitare. MAH. 5.70.:<BR>बलान्य् उद्योजयन्तु नः.<BR>c. उप ATM.<BR>1) jungere equos. RIGV. 39.6.: {#upo raTezu<BR>pfzatIr ayugDvam#} (pro अयुङ्ग्ध्वम्) «vehiculis maculatas<BR>cervas junxistis».<BR>2) sibi adjungere alqm. DR. 4.19.:<BR>{#na vE prAjYA gataSrIkam BartAram upayuYjate . yuYjAnam<BR>upayuYjIta na SriyaH prakzaye vaset#}.<BR>3) sibi assumere,<BR>suum facere alqd. MAN. 8.40.: {#dAtavyaM sarvavarReByo<BR>rAjYA cOrEr hftan Danam . rAjA tad upayuYjAnaS<BR>cOrasyA ''pnoti kilvizam#}.<BR>4) adhibere, uti. MAH. 3.12739.:<BR>यच्चै ऽव द्रव्यम् उपयुज्यते; RAGH. 8.21.:<BR>गुणान् षड् उपायुङ्क्त. उपयुक्त utilis. HIT. 98.14.<BR>5) convertere, impendere, collocare. MAH. 2.1223.: {#icCAmi<BR>tat sarvam (Danam)…upayoktun dvijAgreByo<BR>havyavAheca#}.<BR>6) consumere, edere. MAH. 1.702.: {#BEkzyan<BR>no 'payoktavyam#}; 709.: {#nE 'tan nyAyyam paya<BR>upayoktum#}; 3.57.: अन्नानि उपयोक्ष्यामहे वयम्.<BR>Etiam P. MAH. 3.6221.: उपयोक्ष्यति; 12410.: उपयोक्ष्यामि.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) alligare. R. Schl. I.13.31.: नियुक्तास् तत्र पशवः.<BR>2) coërcere. R. Schl. I.2.92.: {#caturvarRyaYca loke<BR>'smin sve sve Darme niyokzyati#}.<BR>3) ponere, collocare.<BR>IN. 5.42.: {#gurusTAne na mAm vIra niyoktun<BR>tvam ihA 'rhasi#}; BR. 2.14.: {#kaTam…imAm bAlAm<BR>anAgasam pitfpEtAmahe mArge niyoktum aham utsahe#}.<BR>4) adhibere, uti, praeficer, c. loc. rei. MAN. 1.28.:<BR>यन् तु कर्मणि यस्मिन् स न्ययुङ्क्त प्रथमम् प्रभुः;<BR>7.62.: {#niyuYjIta SUrAn…SucIn AkarakarmAnte BIrUn<BR>antarniveSane#}; 8.9.: {#niyuYjyAd brAhmaRam vidvAMsaN<BR>kAryadarSane#}; R. Schl. I.1.92.<BR>5) mandare, jubere.<BR>N. 18.15.: नियोक्ष्ये ऽहं सुदेवम्. R. Schl. I.54.16.:<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=281-a" target="_blank">Page281-a+ 37</a>]<BR>नियुङ्क्ष्व माम्. — नियुक्त jussus. R. Schl. I.14.34. 35. V. नियोग.<BR>c. नि praef. वि mandare, jubere. MAH. 1.4152.: {#kArye<BR>tvAm viniyokzyAmi#}.<BR>c. नि praef. सम् id. MAH. 1.2500.<BR>c. निस् praef. वि emittere, conjicere, jaculari. R. Schl. II.23.37.:<BR>विनिर्योक्ष्याम्य् अहम् वाणान् नृवाजिगजमर्मसु.<BR>c. प्र<BR>1) jungere. R. Schl. I.17.14.: {#yAnena…goBiH SvetEH<BR>prayuktena#}.<BR>2) adhibere, applicare. MAN. 2.159.: {#vAkcE<BR>'va maDurA SlakzRA prayojyA Darmam icCatA#}; 8.130.:<BR>एषु सर्वम् अप्य् एतत् प्रयुञ्जीत चतुष्टयम् (दण्डम्).<BR>3) emittere, conjicere, jaculari sagittas. A. 4.26.: {#nA<BR>'han divyAny astrARi…mAnuzezu prayokzyAmi#}; RAGH. 7.58.:<BR>प्रायुङ्क्त राजसु…गान्धर्वम् अस्त्रम्; MAH. 1.6734.:<BR>शापः प्रयुक्तो ऽयम् मयि त्वया.<BR>4) dare. RAGH. 11.5.:<BR>आशिषम् प्रयुयुजे न वाहिनीम् «benedictionem<BR>dedit, non exercitum»; R. Schl. I.13.38.: {#kOSalyAyAH…prAyuYjanta<BR>tadA ''SizaH#}.<BR>5) jubere. BH. 3.36.:<BR>केन प्रयुक्तो ऽयम् पापञ् चरति.<BR>6) facere. IN. 5.19.:<BR>गुरुपूजाम् प्रयुक्तवान्; MAN. 2.248.: प्रयुञ्जानो ऽग्निशुश्रूषाम्.<BR>c. प्र praef. वि disjungere, privare, c. instr. R. Schl. I.22.8.:<BR>विप्रयुक्तो हि रामेण; II.53.20.: {#mayA…viprAyujyata<BR>kOSalyA#}; N. 15.14.<BR>c. प्र praef. सम् conjungere. MAH. 1.4475.<BR>c. वि disjungere, privare, c. instr. vel abl. N. 15.13.: {#tayA<BR>mando vyayujyata#}; MAN. 7.46.: वियुज्यते ऽर्थधर्माभ्याम्;<BR>MAH. 3.10924.: एनम्…वियुनज्मि देहात्.<BR>c. सम् conjungere. IN. 1.2. Instruere, c. instr. rei. R. Schl. I.1.21.:<BR>रामम्…यौवराज्येन संयोक्तुम् ऐच्छत्.<BR>c. सम् praef. वि disjungere, privare. MAN. 2.80.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=279-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युज्<BR>2. युज् 10. P.<BR>1) jungere equos, currum. N. 8.19.: {#aSvAn<BR>yojayitvA manojavAn#}; 19.18. 19. 20.; R. Schl. II.82.31.:<BR>अयूयुजन्न् उष्ट्रखरान् रथांश्च नागान् हयांश्चै ऽव.<BR>2) conjungere, instruere. MAN. 1.26.: {#dvandvEr ayojayacce<BR>'mAH suKaduHKAdiBiH prajAH#}; 7.218.: विषघ्नैर् अगदैश्चा ऽस्य सर्वद्रव्याणि योजयेत्;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=281-b" target="_blank">Page281-b+ 37</a>]<BR>MAH. 1.3582.: {#tapasA<BR>yojya deham#}. Donare alqm aliquâ re. MAH. 1.6477.:<BR>यो रिपुं योजयेत् प्राणैः.<BR>3) adhibere, praeficere,<BR>c. loc. rei. MAH. 2.1290.: {#BakzyaBojyADikArezu duHSAsanam<BR>ayojayat#}.<BR>4) emittere, conjicere, jaculari sagittas.<BR>A. 10.35.: दिव्यान्य् अस्त्राण्य् अयोजयम्.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् conjungere, instruere. MAH. 1.7200.: {#na<BR>tad Danur mandabalena Sakyam mOrvyA samAyojayitum#}.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) mandare. R. Schl. I.38.10.: {#agnin niyojayAmAsuH<BR>putrArTam#}.<BR>2) ducere, dirigere, impellere. c.<BR>loc. rei. BR. 3.11.: माञ्च धर्मे नियोजय; BH. 3.1.: {#karmaRi<BR>Gore mAn niyojayasi#}; 3.36.: बलाद् इव नियोजितः.<BR>c. नि praef. वि<BR>1) adhibere. HIT. 20.19.: तन् तत्र नियोजयेत्.<BR>2) imponere, committere alicui negotium, c.<BR>loc. pers. MAN. 7.226.: सर्वम् एतत् तु भृत्येषु विनियोजयेत्.<BR>c. नि praef. सम् mandare, c. acc. pers. MAH. 2.1291. R. Schl. I.38.23.<BR>c. प्र facere, exercere. MAN. 3.112.: आनृशंस्यम् प्रयोजयन्.<BR>c. प्र praef. सम् conjungere. MAH. 3.1153.: {#samprayojya<BR>viyojya#}.<BR>c. वि disjungere, privare c. instr. rei. RAGH. 9.66.: {#tAn<BR>(camarAn) viyojya sadyaH sitabAlavyajanEH#}. Solvere,<BR>resolvere. MAH. 1.6225.: प्राणान् वियोजयन् (v.<BR>मुच्).<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) jungere, equis currum. MAH. 3.11762.: {#raTaM saMyojayAmAsur<BR>ganDarvEH (= hayEH)#}.<BR>2) adjungere, annectere.<BR>A. 5.15.: ज्याम्…गाण्डीवे समयोजयत्.<BR>3) instruere,<BR>c. instr. rei. MAH. 1.6474.: {#gAnDarvyA mAyaye<BR>'Cami saMyojayitum arjunam#}.<BR>4) emittere, conjicere,<BR>jaculari sagittas. MAH. 3.816.: प्रज्ञास्त्रम् समयोजयम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=281-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युज्<BR>3. युज् 10. A. (निन्दे) reprehendere, vituperare; spernere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=281-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युज्<BR>4. युज् Adj. (Nom. युक्) junctus, conjunctus, in fine compos.<BR>A. 4.32. (Cf. lat. con-jug, conjux.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=281-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युत्<BR>युत् 1. A. (भासने K. दीप्तौ V. splendere. (Cf. {#dyut, jyut,<BR>jut#}; hib. iudh «a day», an-iudh «to-day», an =<BR>अन; iodhna subst. «brightness, purity»; adj. «clean,<BR>pure, undefiled».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युद्ध|युद्धं<BR>युद्ध n. (r. युध् s. त) punga. IN. 2.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युध्<BR>1. युध् 4. A. interdum P. (fut. aux. योत्स्ये, praet. mtf. अयुत्सि)<BR>pugnare. BH. 11.34.: युध्यस्व; DEV. 2.42.:<BR>अयुतानां शतैः षद्भिर्…युयुधे रणे; 43.: {#yudDe tasmin<BR>ayuDyata#}; MAH. 1.177.: न योत्स्ये; 3.15172.: {#yotsyanti<BR>…SatruBis tava#}. Cum acc. impugnare. MAH. 3.15175.:<BR>योत्स्यते केशवार्जुनौ. Pass. impers. HIT. 96.13.: {#yuDyate<BR>Buvi mAnavEH#}. Caus. योधयामि<BR>1) pugnare jubeo.<BR>MAN. 7.193.: {#dIrGAl laGUMScE 'va narAn agrAnIkezu<BR>yoDayet#}.<BR>2) impugno, c. acc. MAH. 1.3190.: {#yoDayAYcakrire<BR>surAn#}; 2.2120.: मा यूयुधो भारत पाण्डवेयान्.<BR>Desid. युयुत्से pugnare volo. MAH. 4.1252.:<BR>किमर्थन् न युयुत्ससे. (Hib. iodhna «spears, arms», v.<BR>आयुध; iodnach «valiant, warlike, martial»; iodhlan «a<BR>hero»; gr. ὑσ-μίνη, ὑσ-μίν e ὑϑ- sicut e. c. πέπεισ-μαι<BR>e πέπειϑ-μαι. Huc etiam trahi possent anglo-sax.<BR>gudh f., island. vet. gudh-r, gunn-r m., germ. vet.<BR>gund f. pugna, nisi pertinent ad हन्.)<BR>c. आ P. c. acc. impugnare alqm. DR. 5.7.: {#krudDam Ayotsyasi<BR>jizRum#}. — Caus. id. MAH. 3.15054.: {#AyoDitAstu<BR>ganDarvAH suciraM sodarEr mama#}.<BR>c. प्र Desid. pugnare velle. DR. 5.8.: {#yaH pARqavAByAm<BR>…prayuyutsase tvam#}.<BR>c. प्रति P. A. c. acc. impugnare alqm. BH. 2.4. MAH. 1.1703.<BR>— Caus. id. MAH. 1.7116.: {#ko duryoDanaM SaktaH<BR>pratiyoDayitum#}.<BR>c. सम् A. c. acc. impugnare. MAH. 1.5177. — Caus. id.<BR>MAH. 1.7098.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युध्<BR>2. युध् f. (r. युध्) pugna. IN. 1.35. (V. r. युध्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युधिष्ठिर|युधिष्ठिरः<BR>युधिष्ठिर m. (e loc. युधि et स्थिर firmus, v. euphon. r. 80.<BR>annot.) nom. pr. natu maximi Pândavorum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

