युव<BR>युव Thema pronominis 2^dae pers. in Du.; v. gr. 265.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युवती<BR>युवती f. (ab obsoleto युवत् signo fem. ई, v. gr. 225.) femina<BR>juvenis, a decimo sexto usque and tricesimum annum,<BR>virgo nubilis, virgo matura. SA. 2.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युवन्<BR>युवन् (ut videtur, pro द्युवन् abjecto द्, a r. दिव् vel द्यु<BR>splendere, sicut युत् = द्युत्; v. ओजस्. In casibus<BR>debilissimis यून्, fem. यूनी vel युवती, v. gr. 225.) juvenis.<BR>DR. 2.9. N. 12.123. (Lat. juveni-s, adjecto i,<BR>jûn-ior = correptae formae यून्; Lith. jauna-s juvenis;<BR>slav. jûn juvenis, jûnostj juventus; anglo-sax. iung, iong,<BR>geong juvenis; goth. juggs i. e. jung-s, them. jugga, e<BR>यून् adjectâ syllabâ ga; cambro-brit. ieuanc, ieuant juvenis,<BR>iau junior, ieuav natu minimus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युवराज|युवराजः<BR>युवराज m. (juvenisrex e praec. et राज rex in fine compos.)<BR>princeps juventutis, heres regni.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युष्मत्|युष्मन्त्<BR>युष्मत् (e युष्म, euphonice pro युस्म, et ablativi signo त्)<BR>pronominis 2^dae pers. ablat. plur., qui in initio compositorum<BR>Thematis loco fungitur et a grammaticis tanquam<BR>Thema proponitur; scribunt tamen युष्मद्. (Cf. aeol.<BR>ὔμμες per assimil. ex ὔσμες; goth. IZVA, correpto ju<BR>in i (nom. jus), mutato m in v, v. gr. 265. gr. comp. 167. 334. 335.; v. sq.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

युष्मे<BR>युष्मे nom. pl. pronom. 2^dae pers. in. dial. Vêd. (Zend. yûs,<BR>lith. jûs, goth. jus, germ. vet. ir, correpto ju in i, mutato<BR>s in r; v. युष्मत् et gr. comp. 335.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=282-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

