योषणा<BR>योषणा f. (fortasse a r. यु jungere adjectâ sibilante, suff.<BR>अन in fem.; ita योषा suff. आ, योषित् suff. इत्; cf.<BR>lat. uxor pro juxor, con-jux) mulier, femina, in dial.<BR>Vêd. Lass. 99.8.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=283-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

