रजत|रजतं<BR>रजत (r. रञ्ज् ejectâ nasali vel राज् correpto आ, suff. अत)<BR>1) Adj. albus.<BR>2) n. argentum. (Cf. lat. argentum; gr.<BR>ἀϱγός, ἄϱγυϱος; hib. airgiod argentum; ut videtur, litteris<BR>transpositis e ragentum etc.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=284-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

