रजनीचयनाथ<BR>रजनीचयनाथ m. (noctis dominus e {#rajanIcaya - rajanI<BR>+ caya#} cumulus, ut videtur i. q. simpl. रजनी - et<BR>नाथ) luna. HIT. 64.10. Cf. निशापति.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=284-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

