रजस्<BR>रजस् n. (r. रञ्ज् ejecto ञ् s. अस्)<BR>1) pulvis. H. 4.39.<BR>2) menstrua.<BR>3) affectuum impetus. BH. 3.37. 6.27. (V.<BR>रजनी nox et cf. goth. riquis n., Them. riquisa tenebrae,<BR>caligo; v. रजोबल)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=284-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

