रज्जु|रज्जुः<BR>रज्जु m. funis. N. 4.4. Etiam fem. MAN. 8.299. (Cf. lat.<BR>ligare; v. रञ्ज्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रञ्ज्|रंज्<BR>रञ्ज् 1. et 4. P. A. रञ्जामि, रञ्जे, रज्यामि, रज्ये (gr. 331^b).)<BR>1) tingere, colorare. रक्त ruber. H. 2.3.<BR>2) adhaerere,<BR>deditum, addictum esse (fortasse primitive ligare,<BR>cl. 4. A. vel Pass. ligari, cf. रज्जु funis et v. युज् Pass.<BR>sgf. 3.). Caus. tingere, collustrare. MAH. 1.6772.: {#nfpas<BR>tad vanam mahat tejasA raYjayAmAsa sanDyABram iva<BR>BAskaraH#}.<BR>2) deditum sibi facere, sibi conciliare. MAN. 7.19.:<BR>सर्वा रञ्जयति प्रजाः (Schol. सानुरागाः करोति);<BR>MAH. 1.4009.: {#pOravAn SAntanoH putraH pitaraYca…<BR>rAzwraYca raYjayAmAsa vfttena#}; 6264.: प्रजा रञ्जयते. (Cf.<BR>राज्, gr. ϱ̔έζω, ϱ̔ηγεύς, ϱ̔ῆγος; cum रक्त ruber cf. hib.<BR>rot, gr. ϱ̔όδον, ejectâ gutturali, mutatâ tenui in mediam<BR>sicut in ὄγδοος pro ὄϰτοος; de germ. rôt v. रोहित, रुधिर.)<BR>c. अनु 4. P. A. deditum, addictum esse. BH. 11.36.: {#jagat<BR>prahrizyaty anurajyateca#}. C. loc. MAN. 3.173.: {#BrAtur<BR>mftasya BAryAyAM yo 'nurajyeta kAmataH#}. — अनुरक्त<BR>deditus. N. 22.18.: उत्सृज्य…अनुरक्ताम् प्रियाम्; R. Schl. I.7.2.:<BR>अनुरक्ताश्च राज्यकार्येषु. C. acc. R. Schl. II.21.16.:<BR>अनुरक्तो ऽस्मि भावेन भ्रातरम्. C. instr.<BR>R. Schl. II.1.10.: अनुरक्तः प्रजाभिः (v. praef. अभि). — Caus.<BR>deditum sibi facere, sibi conciliare. R. Schl. II.1.10.:<BR>प्रजाश्चै ऽवा ऽनुरञ्जयन्; MAH. 1.3504.: {#atiTIn<BR>annapAnESca viSaSca paripAlanEH…DarmeRa prajAH sarvA<BR>yaTAvad anuraYjayan#}.<BR>c. अभि 4. A. deditum, addictum, studiosum esse, c. instr.<BR>R. Schl. II.67.13.: कथाभिर् अभिरज्यन्ते. — Caus.<BR>tingere, collustrare. R. Schl. I.38.21.: तेजोभिर् अभिरञ्जितम्.<BR>c. उप उपरक्त obscuratus. R. Schl. I.55.9.: {#uparakta ivA<BR>''dityaH#}; II.34.3.: {#uparaktam ivA ''dityam BaSmacCannam<BR>ivA 'nalam#}.<BR>c. वि 4. A. averti, alienum, alienatum fieri. MR. 45.13.:<BR>चिरानुरक्तो ऽपि विरज्यते जनः; HIT. 24.10.: यो विश्वसिति शत्रुषु भार्यासुच विरक्तासु;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">Page285-b+ 36</a>]<BR>27.16.: {#mama kaTAvirakto<BR>'nyAsakto BavAn#}.<BR>c. सम् tingere, collustrare. H. 4.46. Pass.: {#purA saMrajyate<BR>prAcI#}; MAH. 1.6443.: सन्ध्या संरज्यते घोरा; 5.273.:<BR>क्रोधसंरक्तनयनः.<BR>c. सम् praef. अनु अनुसंरक्त deditus. R. Schl. I.17.16.:<BR>भर्तारम् अनुसंरक्ता.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रट्<BR>1. रट् 1. P. vociferari, mugire, ululare. BHATT. 14.81.:<BR>पपात राक्षसो भूमौ रराटच भयङ्करम्; 14.5.: {#santrastAH<BR>karaBA rewuH#} (Schol. करभा उष्ट्राः); 15.27.:<BR>घोराश्चा ऽराटिषुः शिवाः; MR. 297.11.: रटन्तः…वायसाः.<BR>V. sq. et रठ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रट्<BR>2. रट् 10. P. रटयामि (परिभाषणे) loqui. V. sq.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रठ्<BR>रठ् 1. P. (भाषणे) loqui. (V. 1. et 2. रट् et cf. germ. vet.<BR>rediôn, redinôn; sax. vet rethjôn, rethinôn loqui; goth.<BR>raz-da sermo, loquela, ut mihi videtur, e rath-da, mutato<BR>th in sibilantem sonoram, propter sequens d, v. gr.<BR>comp. 102.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रण्<BR>1. रण् 1. P.<BR>1) sonare, clamare, inclamare. In dial. Vêd.<BR>cl. 4. RIGV. 38.2.: क्व वो गावो न रण्यन्ति «ubi<BR>vos, vaccae veluti, inclamant?»; 10.5.: {#Sakro yaTA sutezu<BR>no rAraRat#} «ut potens ille inter filios nostros resonet».<BR>(Intens. in dial. Vêd. रारण् pro रंरण् sicut रारम्<BR>a रम् q. v.). — रणित n. sonitus. UR. 67.7.infr.<BR>2) gaudere<BR>(cf. रम्). RIGV. 91.14.: {#yaH soma saKye tava rAraRad<BR>deva martyaH#} «Lucide Soma! qui consortio tuo<BR>gaudet mortalis». (Cf. ध्रण्, भ्रण्, ध्वण्, hib. ran «a<BR>squeal, a roar», ranach «a squealing, roaring».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रण्<BR>2. रण् 1. P. ire. (Cf. goth. RANN currere, fluere; rinna,<BR>rann, runnum; nostrum renne, rinne.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रण|रणं|रणः<BR>रण m. n. (r. रण् s. अ) bellum, pugna. N. 12.83.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रण्व्<BR>रण्व् 1. P. (व्रजे; scribitur रव्) ire. Cf. {#raR, riRv,<BR>ramb, rimb#}<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रत|रतं<BR>रत v. रम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रति|रतिः<BR>रति f. (r. रम् gaudere s. ति) voluptas. BR. I.22.<BR>2) uxor<BR>dei Anangi; dicitur etiam रती. N. 16.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=285-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

