रस्<BR>1. रस् 1. P. sonare, strepere, vociferari, clamare, ululare.<BR>GITA-GOV. 10.6.: रसतु रसना; RAGH. 16.78.: {#hradaH…karI<BR>'va vanyaH paruzaM rarAsa#}; BHATT. 3.26.: गोमायुशारङ्गगणाश्च…अरासिषुः;<BR>14.9.: {#resur vavalguSca<BR>padAtayaH#}. Etiam A. NALOD. 1.22.: रसमानः स विहङ्गगणः. — रसित<BR>n. fragor. GHAT. 14.: गम्भीरमेघरसित.<BR>c. आ i. q. simpl. NALOD. 1.11.: {#ajayad dvizatAm paNktim<BR>ArasamAnAm#}; 3.14.<BR>c. वि id. BHATT. 15.42.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=287-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रस्<BR>2. रस् 10. P. रारयामि (आस्वादे K. आस्वादे स्नेहे V.)<BR>gustare, amare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=287-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रस|रसं|रसः<BR>रस m. (r. 2. रस् s. अ)<BR>1) sapor, gustus. N. 5.38.<BR>2) succus,<BR>liquidum, aqua.<BR>3) animi affectus. UR. 28.9. (Cf.<BR>lith. rassà ros; russ. rosa id.; lat. ros, ror-is e ros-is; gr.<BR>δϱόσος praefixo δ, sicut in ἀνδϱός etc.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=287-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रसन|रसनं<BR>रसन n. (r. 2. रस् s. अन) sapor, gustus. BH. 15.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=287-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

