रह्<BR>रह् 1. et 10. P. रहामि, रहयामि. Relinquere, deserere.<BR>रहित relictus; N. 18.9.: {#rahitA BartfBiScE 'va na kruDyanti<BR>(kulastriyaH)#}. Privatus, orbatus. c. instrum. R. Schl. I.70.35.:<BR>{#patinA rahitA tasmAt putran devI<BR>vyajAyata#}; II.47.17.: रामेण नगरी रहिता ना ऽतिशोभते;<BR>N. 16.19. (V. रहस् secretum et cf. gr. ΛΑΘ, λανϑάνω, λάϑϱα,<BR>v. gr. 104.; lat. lateo; lith. léidmi vel<BR>léidźiu linquo, at-léidźiu exsolvo, remitto; goth. LÊT;<BR>germ. vet. LAZ (lâz) sinere; cf. Benf. II.24. sq.)<BR>c. वि i. q. simpl. RAGH. ed. Calc. 9.26.: विरहयन् मलयाद्रिम्. — विरहित<BR>relictus, privatus. N. 10.23.: {#kaTam…mayA<BR>virahitA SuBA carizyati vane#}; BH. 17.13.:<BR>श्रद्धाविरहितो यज्ञः. Separatus, disjunctus. UR. 92.5.:<BR>अविरहितौ दम्पती भूयास्ताम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=287-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रहस्<BR>रहस् (r. रह् s. अस्)<BR>1) Subst. n. secretum, occultum, locus<BR>occultus. BH. 6.10.<BR>2) Adv. secreto, clam. IN. 4.1.<BR>N. 1.18. 18.14. (V. r. रह्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रहस्य|रहस्यं<BR>रहस्य (a praec. s. य) Adj. secretus. Subst. n. secretum. SA. 6.35.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रा<BR>रा 2. P. A. dare, in dial. Vêd. RIGV. 114.6.: {#rAsvAca no<BR>amfta martaBojanam#}; 114.9. 117.23. Adjectâ sibilante:<BR>रास् cl. 1. P. A. RIGV. 96.8.: रासते दीर्घम् आयुः;<BR>RIGV. V. (v. Westerg.): ता नो रासन् वसूनि.<BR>Etiam cl. 2. RIGV. 46.6.: ताम् अस्मे रासाथाम् इषम्<BR>«talem nobis date cibum (Asvini!)». (Cf. दा, दास्, unde<BR>रा, रास् orta esse censeo, mutato द् in र्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राक्षस|राक्षसः<BR>राक्षस m. (a रक्षस् q. v. s. अ) i. q. रक्षस्. H. 2.29.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राक्षसी<BR>राक्षसी Fem. praeced. H. 2.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राक्ष्<BR>राक्ष् 1. P. (शोषाणालमर्थयोः) arescere, ornare. Cf.<BR>लाख्, ओख्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राग|रागः<BR>राग m. (r. रञ्ज्, ejecto ञ्, s. अ)<BR>1) amor, cupido, studium,<BR>affectus. N. 5.24. BH. 2.56. 64. 3.34. 7.11. 8.11.<BR>2) rubor<BR>(cf. रक्त a r. रञ्ज् tingere). DR. 5.1. (V. रञ्ज्; et<BR>cf. gr. ὀϱγή, quod fortasse per metath. e ϱ̔ογή.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

