राघ्<BR>राघ् 1. A. (सामर्थ्ये K. शक्तौ V.) potentem, valentem esse.<BR>V. लाघ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राज्<BR>1. राज् 1. P. A.<BR>1) splendere. N. 1.12.: {#tatra sma rAjate BEmI…vidyut<BR>sOdAminI yaTA#}; IN. 5.11.: {#sUkzmavastraDaraM<BR>reje jaGanan niravadyayA#} (रेजे gr. 441.); R. Schl. I.1.32.:<BR>चित्रकूटो रराज. In dial. Vêd. etiam. cl. 2.<BR>RIGV. 104.4.: राष्टि.<BR>2) c. gen. in dial. Vêd. regere, imperare.<BR>RIGV. 25.20.: {#tvaM viSvasya moDira divaSca gmaSca<BR>rAjasi#} «tu universi, sapiens! coelique terraeque imperium<BR>habes»; 36.12. (V. राजन् et cf. रञ्ज्, भ्राज्;<BR>lat. rego, rex; goth. raginô rego, impero, servatâ mediâ<BR>sicut in BUG = भुज्; reiki, them. reikja n. imperium<BR>= राज्य, attenuato â in ei i. e. î; reik-s princeps; germ.<BR>vet. rîchi dives.)<BR>c. अभि splendere. MAH. 3.10960.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">Page288-b+ 37</a>]<BR>c. वि id. MAH. 3.8106.: विराजति यथा सोमो मेघैर् मुक्तः;<BR>IN. 5.6. N. 12.37. — Caus. facere ut alqus splendeat,<BR>collustrare. R. Schl. II.26.2.: {#virAjayan rAjasuto<BR>rAjamArgam#}; II.39.18.: व्यराजयत…वेश्म तत्. - विराजित<BR>collustratus, splendens, splendidus. N. 5.3.<BR>c. सम् in dial. Vêd. regere, imperare. RIGV. 27.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राज्<BR>2. राज् m. (Nom. राट्, a r. राज्) rex, in fine compos. (Lat.<BR>rex.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राज|राजः<BR>राज m. (r. राज् s. अ) rex in fine compos. IN. 1.24.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राजत|राजतं<BR>राजत (fem. ई, a रजत s. अ) argenteus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राजन्<BR>राजन् m. (r. राज् s. अन्) rex. N. 1.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राजमार्ग|राजमार्गः<BR>राजमार्ग m. (e praec., v. euph. r. 67., et मार्ग via) regis via,<BR>via regia, via praecipua. N. 25.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राजर्षि|राजर्षिः<BR>राजर्षि m. (e राजन् et ऋषि sapiens, sanctus, v. euph. r. 67.)<BR>regius sapiens. IN. 5.25. SU. 2.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राजसूय|राजसूयः<BR>राजसूय n. (e राजन् et सूय quod seorsum non invenitur, a<BR>r. सु vel सू s. य) sacrificium regium, quod rex victor<BR>conficit, ita ut in eo reges subacti ministrent. IN. 1.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राजहंस|राजहंसः<BR>राजहंस m. (e राजन् et हंस anser) anseris genus, Wils. «a<BR>white goose with red legs and bill, or more properly perhaps<BR>the flamingo». MEGH. 11.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राजि|राजिः<BR>राजि f. (r. राज् s. इ) linea, series.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

