रात्र|रात्रं<BR>रात्र n. nox in fine compos. (v. gr. 681.). N. 13.6. V. sq. et<BR>चिररात्राय.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रात्रि|रात्रिः<BR>रात्रि f. (ut videtur, a r. रम् quiescere - v. रम् praef. {#A,<BR>upa + A, upa, vi#} - abjecto म्, productâ vocali, suff.<BR>त्र attenuato अ in इ) nox. SA. 5.56. V. निश्, निशीथ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=288-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राध्<BR>राध् 4. et 5. P.<BR>1) cl. 5., in dial. Vêd. cl. 1. facere, efficere,<BR>perficere. RIGV. 41.7.: {#kaTA rADAma saKAyaH stoma<BR>mitrasya#} «quomodo efficiamus, amici! laudem Mitrae?»<BR>2) 4. P. राध्यामि perfici.<BR>c. अप cl. 5. et 4.<BR>1) offendere, injuriam facere, c. gen.<BR>MAH. 1.1885.: कथन् ना ऽस्या ऽपराधुयाम्; 3.11415.:<BR>पुरा स ना ऽपराध्नोति सिद्धनाम् ब्रह्मवादिनाम्; 3.5988.:<BR>तव नै ऽषा ऽपराध्यति.<BR>2) peccare. R. Schl. II.18.11.:<BR>कच्चिन् मया ना ऽपराद्धम् अज्ञानात्; MAH. 4.1611.:<BR>कथन् धर्मे ऽपराधुयुः; MR. 277.7.: {#yOvanam<BR>atrA 'parADyati na cAritryam#}.<BR>c. अभि Caus. propitiare, propitium facere, sibi conciliare.<BR>R. Schl. II.30.33. et. 34.: अभिराध्यते. V. sq.<BR>c. आ Caus.<BR>1) id. MAH. 1.6368.: {#ArADayizyan drupadaH<BR>sa tam paryacarat punaH#}; RAGH. 10.86.: {#guREr ArADayAmAsus<BR>te gurum#}; R. Schl. I.17.31.: {#DarmeRA ''rADaya<BR>prajAH#}; A. 3.5.<BR>2) colere, servire. MAN. 10.122.: {#svargArTam…viprAn<BR>ArADayet tu saH (SUdraH)#}.<BR>c. आ praef. उप Caus. servire. MAN. 10.121.b.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् Caus. sibi conciliare. MAH. 3.10344.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राम|रामं|रामः<BR>राम (r. रम् s. अ)<BR>1) Adj. amoenus, pulcher. UR. 71.7.<BR>2) m. nom. pr.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रावण|रावणः<BR>रावण m. (Caus. r. रु s. अन) nom. pr. Râkschasi.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राश्<BR>राश् 1. A. (शब्दे) sonare. Vid. रास्, रस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राशि|राशिः<BR>राशि m. cumulus. N. 13.17.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राष्ट्र|राष्ट्रं<BR>राष्ट्र n. (r. राज् s. त्र, v. euph. r. 89.b.) regnum. BR. 1.1.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रास्<BR>रास् 1. A. (शब्दे) sonare. Cf. रस्, राश्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रासभ|रासभः<BR>रासभ m. (r. रास् s. अभ) asinus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

राहु|राहुः<BR>राहु m. Daemon, e Daityorum stirpe, serpenti posticâ corporis<BR>parte similis, a quo lunam et solem eclipsis tempore<BR>voratos mythologia fingit. N. 16.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रि<BR>1. रि 5. P. i. q. ऋ cl. 5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रि<BR>2. रि 6. P. रियामि (गतौ) ire. — In dial. Vêd. रि cl. 9.<BR>educere. RIGV. 56.6.: त्वं सुतस्य मदे अरिणा अपः<BR>«tu libaminis gaudio e nube elicuisti aquas».<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-b" target="_blank">Page289-b+ 36</a>]<BR>c. सम् cl. 9. in dial. Vêd. sanare. RIGV. 117.19.: स्रामम्<BR>(vulneratum) …संरिणीथः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिक्थ|रिक्थं<BR>रिक्थ n. (r. रिच् s. थ) facultates, bona, divitiae, opes. MAN. 9.104.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिख्<BR>रिख् 1. P. ire. V. रख्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिङ्ख्|रिंख्<BR>रिङ्ख् 1. P. id. V. रख्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिङ्ग्|रिंग्<BR>रिङ्ग् 1. P. id. V. रख्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिच्<BR>1. रिच् 7. P. A. रिणच्मि, रिञ्चे disjungere, separare, liberare.<BR>RAGH. 14.85.: राज्यं रजोरिक्तमनाः शशास;<BR>BHATT. 6.36.: रिनच्मि जलधेस् (disjungo a mari) {#toyam<BR>vivinacmi divaH surAn#}. (V. 2. रिच् et cf. lat.<BR>LIC, linquo; gr. ΛΙΠ, λείπω, mutatâ gutt. in lab.; lith.<BR>pa-lếkmi relinquo; goth. af-lifnan relinqui, superesse;<BR>laibôs reliquiae cum mediâ pro aspir.; island. vet. leifar<BR>reliquiae; germ. vet. LIB, bi-lîbu remaneo, bi-leib, bi-libumês,<BR>nostrum bleibe).<BR>c. अति Pass. proprie disjungi, inde conspici, excellere,<BR>praecellere, praevalere, dominari; potiorem esse. HIT. 12.7.:<BR>{#svaBAva evA 'tra taTA 'tiricyate yaTA prakftyA<BR>maDuraN gavAm payaH#}; 35.7.: दैवम् अत्रा ऽतिरिच्यते;<BR>MAN. 12.25.: यो यदै ऽऽषाङ् गुणो देहे साकल्येना ऽतिरिच्यते.<BR>C. acc. superare, excedere. MAN. 2.145.: {#sahasran<BR>tu pitFn mAtA gOraveRA 'tiricyate#}. C. ablat.<BR>potiorem, meliorem, praestantiorem esse aliquâ re, excedere<BR>alqm rem. HIT. 133.2.: {#aSvameDasahasrAd Di<BR>satyam evA 'tiricyate#}; BH. 2.34.: {#akIrtir maraRAd<BR>atiricyate#} «infamia ultra obitum porrigitur». Etiam<BR>c. instr. (cf. युज् praef. वि) MAH. 3.10588.: {#kapotas<BR>tu mAMsenA 'tyatiricyate#} «columba vero carne regis<BR>multo gravior est». V. praef. प्र.<BR>c. उत् Pass. id. MAH. 1.3070.: {#mamE 'vo 'dricyate janma<BR>duzyanta tava janmanaH#} (praestantior est).<BR>c. प्र Passiv. c. abl. excedere aliquam rem, porrigi ultra<BR>aliquam rem. RIGV. दिवश्चित् ते…प्ररिरिचे महित्वम्<BR>«ultra coelum tua exporrecta est magnitudo»; 61.9.:<BR>अस्येद् (अस्य इत्) एव प्ररिरिचे महित्वन् दिवस्पृथिव्याः<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">Page290-a+ 35</a>]<BR>«illius utique excedit magnitudo coelum et terram».<BR>c. वि alvum exonerare. विरिक्त qui alvum exoneravit.<BR>MAN. 5.144.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=289-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिच्<BR>2. रिच् 1. et 10. P. (वियोजनसम्पर्कनयोः K.) relinquere;<BR>conjungere. रेचित relictus. RAGH. 6.7.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिज्<BR>रिज् 1. A. frigere, assare. Cf. भृज्, भ्रज्ज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिण्व्<BR>रिण्व् 1. P. (व्रजे, scribitur रिव्, gr. 110^a)) ire. V. रण्व्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिपु|रिपुः<BR>रिपु m. hostis. N. 6.93. Cf. radd. रिफ्, रिम्फ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिप्स्<BR>रिप्स् v. रभ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिफ्<BR>रिफ् 6. P. (कत्थनयुद्धनिन्दाहिंसादानेषु K.) gloriari;<BR>pugnare; reprehendere; laedere, occidere; dare. Cf.<BR>रिम्फ्, ऋफ्, ऋम्फ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिम्फ्|रिंफ्<BR>रिम्फ् 6. P. (वधे) ferire, occidere. V. रिफ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिश्<BR>रिश् 6. P. (हिंसायाम्) ferire, laedere, occidere. Cf. रिष्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिष्<BR>रिष् 1. et 4. P. laedere, vulnerare, occidere. DR. 7.20.: अरिष्टदेहः.<BR>— In dialecto Vêd. etiam cum productâ vocali.<BR>RIGV. 36.15.: पाहि रीषतः «serva nos ab occisore».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रिह्<BR>रिह् 1. P. in dialecto Vêd.<BR>1) colere, laudare (cf. अर्ह्).<BR>2) rogare.<BR>3) dare. V. Westerg. — In dialecto Vêd.<BR>etiam रिह् cl. 2. = लिह् q. v.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

री<BR>1. री 4. A. fluere. RIGV. 85.3.: {#vartmARy ezAm anu rIyate<BR>Gftam#} «in tramite eorum post ipsos manat aqua».<BR>Cf. रि, ऋ.<BR>c. आ affluere, adire. RIGV. 30.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

री<BR>2. री 9. P. रिणामि (gr. 385.) ire. V. 1. री.<BR>c. नि adoriri. RIGV. 61.13.: निरिणाति शत्रून्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रु|रुः<BR>1. रु 2. P. रौमि, रवीमि (v. gr. 343. 350.) sonare, strepere,<BR>murmurare, susurrare, clamare, vociferari, ululare, ejulare.<BR>HIT. 23.2.: कर्णे कलङ् किमपि रौति; H. 1.25.:<BR>एते रुवन्ति (sic legendum pro ब्रुवन्ति) सारसा जलचारिणः;<BR>MAH. 1.3022.: न खल्व् अहम् इदं शून्ये रौमि;<BR>3.11716.: रुवन्तश्च महारवान्…राक्षसाः; 4.1463.:<BR>गोमायुर् एष…रुवन्; MAN. 4.115.: श्वखरोष्ट्रेच रुवति…न पठेद् द्विजः.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-b" target="_blank">Page290-b+ 37</a>]<BR>— Part. pass. रुत personitus.<BR>MAH. 3.1535.: नदीः…पुंस्कोकिलरुताः. — रुत n. sonus,<BR>cantus aviam, susurrus apum. Lass. 52.: {#pAdapAMScE<BR>'va vihaNgarutahlAditAn#}; Ritu-S. 1.5.: हंसरुत;<BR>BHATT. 2.10.: रुतानि षट्पदानाम्. — Intens. MAH. 1.7806.:<BR>शरणम् अभ्येमि रोरवीमिच दुःखिता; 2.2308.:<BR>द्रौपदी…रोरवीति त्व् अनाथवत्. (Cf. रुद्; russ.<BR>revu rudo, rugio, Infin. revje-tj, ad Caus. रावयामि retulerim<BR>(v. gr. comp. 505.); fortasse etiam lith. lóju latro,<BR>fut. ló-su, et russ. laju latro, clamo (infin. la-ja-tj)<BR>ad Caus. radicis रु pertinent, mutato r in l; etiam lat.<BR>rûmor ad Caus. trahi potest, ita ut â debilitatum sit in û<BR>et v mutatum in m, sicut in clamo = Caus. श्रावयामि<BR>radicis श्रु q. v.; gr. ὠ-ϱύ-ο-μαι cum Pottio ad रु praef.<BR>आ retulerim.<BR>c. अभि i. q. simpl. Part. pass. अभिरुत personitus, circumsonitus.<BR>MAH. 3.1535.: नदीः…सारसाभिरुताः.<BR>c. आ i. q. simpl. BHATT. 17.24.: वीरौ राघवाव् आरुताम्.<BR>c. वि id. SA. 5.75.: एता घोरान् शिवा नादान्…विरुवन्ति;<BR>UR. 67.14.; HIT. 55.22.<BR>c. सम् id. BHATT. 17.71.: समरौद् इतरो जनः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रु|रुः<BR>2. रु 1. A. (रोषे K. वधे गत्याम् V.) irasci; occidere; ire.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुकम<BR>रुकम n. (ut videtur, a r. रुच् e रुक्, servatâ primitivâ gutturali,<BR>sicut e. c. in वाक्य a वच् e वक्) aurum. HIT. 39.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुक्ष|रुक्षः<BR>रुक्ष i. q. रूक्ष.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुच्<BR>1. रुच् 1. A.<BR>1) lucere, splendere. RIGV. 6.1.: {#rocante rocanA<BR>divi#} «fulgent fulgores ejus in coelo»; MAH. 1.6613.:<BR>{#ruruce sA 'Dikam suBrUr ApatantI naBastalAt<BR>sOdAminI 'va#}.<BR>2) placere. HIT. 53.2.: {#yad eva<BR>rocate yasmE Bavet tat tasya sundaram#}; MAH. 1.7442.:<BR>न रोचते विग्रहो मे. — रुचित n. libitum, gratum. SA. 5.80.:<BR>रुचितं यदि ते; MAH. 1.7952.: {#yad asya rucitaM<BR>kartun tat kuruDvam#}.<BR>3) approbare, gaudere. MAH. 1.7444.:<BR>विग्रहं तैर् न रोचे. — Caus. P. A.<BR>1) velle, cupere,<BR>appetere. MAN. 2.243.: यदि त्व् आत्यन्तिकं<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=291-a" target="_blank">Page291-a+ 37</a>]<BR>वासं रोचयेत गुरोः कुले (schol. इच्छेत्); R. Schl. I.36.3.:<BR>गमनं रोचयामास; MAH. 1.5741.: {#nahi pApam<BR>apApAtmA rocayizyati#}. (Cf. लोच्, लोक्, lat. LUC,<BR>luc-s; lûceo = Caus. रोचयामि - v. gr. comp. 109^a).6.<BR>gr. λευ-ϰός, λύχ-νος, goth. liuh-ath lumen, ubi iu respondet<BR>sancrito ओ = अ + उ, debilitato gunae incremento<BR>a in u - v. gr. comp. 27. - germ. vet. liuh-tjan<BR>lucere, nostrum leuch-ten; slav. Λоуча lûća radius,<BR>Λоуна lû-na luna; hib. loiche, loichead «a light, candle,<BR>lamp; lightning, flame, splendour», logha «splendid»,<BR>logh-mhar «bright». Huc etiam trahi possunt hib. leos<BR>«light», leosaim «I light up, kindle»; les «light, illumination»<BR>mutatâ gutturali in sibilantem, nisi pertinent ad<BR>लस्; v. लोक्.)<BR>c. अति P. splendore vincere, überstrahlen. MAH. 3.486.:<BR>अत्यरोचश्च भूतात्मन् भास्करं स्वेन तेजसा.<BR>c. अनु Caus. i. q. Caus. simpl. MAH. 3.12679.: {#vanam<BR>evA 'nvarocayat#}.<BR>c. अभि Caus. id. R. Schl. II.30.27.: {#na devi tava duHKena<BR>svagmi evA 'nurocaye#}. Cum infin. vel nomine actionis<BR>in अन R. Schl. II.29.19.: {#nA 'Birocayase netun tvam<BR>mAN kenE 'va hetunA#}; R. Schl. I.36.2.: गमनाया ऽभिरोचय<BR>(cf. गमनायो ऽपचक्रमे p. 87.).<BR>c. आ Caus. id. R. Schl. II.30.28.<BR>c. प्रति Caus. id. MAH. 3.11546.: प्रस्थानम् प्रत्यरोचयन्<BR>sie beliebten fortzugehen.<BR>c. वि splendere. N. 17.11.: {#piplus tasyA vyarocata…<BR>vyaBre naBasI 'va niSAkaraH#}; IN. 1.40.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=290-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुच्<BR>2. रुच् f. (r. रुच्) splendor. MEGH. 45. (Cf. lat. luc-s.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=291-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुचि|रुचिः<BR>रुचि f. (r. रुच् s. इ)<BR>1) id. MEGH. 15.<BR>2) desiderium, appetitus.<BR>HIT. 19.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=291-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुचिर|रुचिरं<BR>रुचिर (r. रुच् s. इर) splendens, pulcher, amoenus. N. 4.28. 5.3.<BR>A. 4.52.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=291-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुज्<BR>1. रुज् 6. P. frangere. रुग्न fractus. MAH. 3.678.: {#vAtarugna<BR>iva…vanaspatiH#}. — Cl. 10. (हिंसे) ferire, laedere,<BR>occidere. (V. रुजा, रोग aegritudo et cf. lith. láuźu<BR>frango, praet. láuźiau = Caus. vel. 10. cl. रोजयामि, mutato<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=291-b" target="_blank">Page291-b+ 35</a>]<BR>r in l, j i. e. g in ź v. p. 99. not.; germ. vet. LUCH<BR>vellere, ar-liuhhan evellere, v. Graff. II.137.; lat. lûgeo<BR>= Caus. vel. cl. 10. रोजयामि (gr. comp. §. 109^a).6.);<BR>gr. λυγϱός, ο-ΡΥΓ, ὀ-ϱύσσω, ὄ-ϱυγμα, ὀ-ϱυϰτή, ὀϱυχή,<BR>praefixâ vocali, sicut in ὄνομα, ὀϕϱύς, ἐ-λαχύς etc.)<BR>c. अव i. q. simpl. HID. 1.12.: अवरुज्य…गुल्मान्.<BR>c. आ A. id. MAH. 2.2113.: {#vizARaN gOr iva madAt<BR>svayam Arujate 'tmanaH#}.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् id. MAH. 4.1082.<BR>c. वि diffringere. SAK. 24.16.: धर्मारण्यं विरुजति गजः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=291-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुज्<BR>2. रुज् f. (N. रुक्, r. रुज्) morbus, aegritudo. UR. 42.4.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=291-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

