रुद्<BR>रुद् 2. P. interdum A. (anom. v. gr. 354.) Praet. mltf. अरोदिषम्<BR>et अरुदम्. Flere. N. 11.14.: क्रोशति रोदिति;<BR>16.34.: रुदिते भृशम्; BR. 3.20.: रुरुदुस् त्रयः; MAH. 3.593.:<BR>मा रोदीः; R. Schl. I.46.20.: मा रुदो मा रुदः;<BR>II.52.19.: रुरुदे. — Etiam cl. 6. P. A. BR. 3.22.: {#mA pitA<BR>ruda#}; MAH. 1.5597.: शोचेतच रुदेतच. — Trans.<BR>deflere, c. acc. BHATT. 5.5.: अरोदीत् सा भ्रातरौ. — Intens.<BR>valde flere. BR. 3.2.: {#kim evam BfSaduHKartO<BR>rorudyeTAm#}; 1.4.: रोरुद्यमानास् तान् दृष्ट्वा. (Cf. रु,<BR>lat. rudo, germ. vet. RUZ flere, — riuzu, rôz, ruzumês;<BR>lith. raudoju lamentor et slav. rydajû fleo = Caus. रोदयामि,<BR>v. gr. comp. 505. 506.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=292-a" target="_blank">Page292-a+ 37</a>]<BR>c. अनु i. q. simpl. RAM. II.55.21.: अनुरुदन्ति; NALOD. 3.32.:<BR>अनुरुरोद.<BR>c. प्र id. N. 17.31. 22.30.: प्ररुदित flens. BR. 3.21.: {#praruditAn<BR>sarvAn niSamya#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=291-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुद्र|रुद्रः<BR>रुद्र m. (r. रुद् s. र्)<BR>1) cognomen Sivi.<BR>2) quidam ordo undecim<BR>Geniorum. IN. 5.24. N. 10.24.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=292-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुध्<BR>1. रुध् 7. P. A. रुणध्मि रुन्धे.<BR>1) impedire, praecludere, retinere,<BR>obstruere. BH. 4.29.: प्राणापानगती रुद्ध्वा;<BR>RAGH. 7.32.: {#tAm udvahantam paTi BojakanyAM ruroDa<BR>rAjanyagaRaH#}; UR. 68.1.: इदं रुणद्धि माम् पद्मम्.<BR>2) arcere.<BR>R. Schl. I.28.22.: {#yakzIm aSmavarzABivarziRIm<BR>…ruroDa sa sAyakEH#}.<BR>3) includere. MAN. 9.12.: {#gfhe<BR>rudDAH#}. Obsidere. MAH. 3.638.: {#arunDat tAM (purIM) suduzwAtmA<BR>sarvataH#}. (De formâ अरुन्धत् pro अरुणत् v.<BR>gramm. min. ed. 2. §. 341^b.). — Caus. includi jubere.<BR>RAGH. 12.71.: लङ्कां रोधयामास पिङ्गलैः (वानरैः). — (Fortasse<BR>hib. rundha «secret, mysterious» a रुन्ध्, sicut<BR>lat. arcanus ab arcendo; rundhachd «secrecy», ruindiamhar<BR>«a mystery, a dark secret», ruine «secrecy» abjecto<BR>d; goth. runa mysterium. Germ. vet. rânên susurrare<BR>- nostrum raunen - rûnazjan mussitare ad रु sonare<BR>referri possunt. Ag. Benary huc trahit lat. rudens,<BR>Röm. Lautlehre p. 223.<BR>c. अनु impedire, retinere. SAK. 151.1.: {#ayam anuruDyamAnas<BR>tApasIByAm…bAlaH#}.<BR>c. अभि perturbare. SAK. 33.3.: {#yaTAca sEnikAs tapovanan<BR>nA 'BirunDanti#}.<BR>c. अव impedire, cohibere, refrenare. R. Schl. II.30.9.:<BR>यस्यचा ऽर्थे ऽवरुध्यसे; MAN. 8.236. — Intens. R. Schl. II.58.20.:<BR>मा स्मै ऽनम् अवरोरुधः.<BR>c. आ id. BHATT. 17.49.: बन्धुता शुचम् आरुणत्. — Caus.<BR>impedire, incommodare, molestum esse, perturbare.<BR>R. Schl. II.96.40.: {#kAkenA ''roDyamAnAn tAM<BR>rAmo 'vAhasat#}.<BR>c. उप impedire, incommodare, perturbare. MAN. 8.348.:<BR>धर्मो यत्रो ऽपरुध्यते; RAM. Schl. II.36.14.: {#anArye kftyam<BR>ArabDaN kin na pUrvam upAruDaH#}; MAN. 7.125.:<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=292-b" target="_blank">Page292-b+ 37</a>]<BR>उपरुध्या ऽरिम्. Arcere, praecludere. RAGH. 7.36.: {#reRuH…uparuroDa<BR>sUryam#}.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) impedire, retinere. UP. 34.: {#yAvat kiYcid gatA<BR>tAvan nirudDA sA puroDasA#}.<BR>2) praecludere, obstruere,<BR>e. c. viam. BHATT. 17.49.<BR>3) coërcere, refrenare,<BR>comprimere. HIT. 34.1.: निजसौख्यन् निरुन्धानः;<BR>MAH. 3.13633.: निरुध्यचे ऽन्द्रियग्रामम्.<BR>4) includere.<BR>MAN. 11.1176.: {#vipraduzwAM striyam BartA nirunDyAd<BR>ekaveSmani#}.<BR>c. नि praef. सम् retinere, inhibere, sistere. MAN. 8.83.:<BR>सा सद्यः सन्निरोद्धव्या.<BR>c. प्रति impedire. MAN. 11.11.<BR>c. वि impedire, retinere, prohibere. MAH. 2.227.: {#kaccit<BR>pOrA na…viruDyante parEH krItAH#}; R. Schl. II.36.10.:<BR>स्वरश्चा ऽपि व्यरुध्यत. — विरुद्ध impeditus, prohibitus,<BR>vetitus. R. Schl. I.7.8.: परस्परेण विरुद्धाः; MAN. 7.152.:<BR>परस्परविरुद्धानाम्; BH. 7.11.: {#DarmAvirudDo BUtezu<BR>kAmo 'smi#}.<BR>c. सम् i. q. simpl. N. 13.10.: मार्गं संरुध्य; SA. 5.82.: {#mAtA<BR>saMruRadDi mAm#}; MAH. 3.13633.: मनः संरुध्य; MAN. 8.235.:<BR>अजाविके तु संरुद्धे वृकैः (schol. परिवृते).<BR>c. अभि praef. सम् arcere. R. Schl. II.14.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=292-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुध्<BR>2. रुध् 4. A. interdum P. (primitive Pass. praecedentis, v.<BR>gr. 492. annot.)<BR>c. अनु amare. DR. 4.18.: {#pArTAn nA 'nurodDun tvam<BR>arhasi#}; MAH. 3.13891.: दोषन् ना ऽनुरुध्यते; N. 4.10.:<BR>धर्मम् एवा ऽनुरुध्यन्ति; MAH. 4.492.: भर्तारम् अनुरुध्यन्त्यः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=292-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुधिर|रुधिरं|रुधिरः<BR>रुधिर n. (r. रुह् crescere - servato primitivo ध् pro ह्, v.<BR>gr. 315. et cf. रोहित ruber - suff. इर) sanguis. H. 2.11.<BR>(रुधिर n. a perdito Adj. रुधिर ruber, cf. रोहित e<BR>रोधित, gr. ἐ-ϱυϑϱός, lat. ruber, cujus b pro f - v. gr.<BR>comp. 18. - respondet scrto ध्, graeco ϑ sicut in fumus<BR>= धूम, q. v.; radice etiam huc pertinent lat. rûfus; lith.<BR>raudà color ruber, raudónas ruber, ruddas subruber,<BR>rudis rubigo, aerugo; slav. vet. rd-je-ti rubescere, ryschdj<BR>πυϱ̓ϱ̔ός, rschda rubigo in segetibus (Miklosich p.<BR>75);<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-a" target="_blank">Page293-a+ 36</a>]<BR>russ. рыжій ryschiĭ rufus, polon. rusy id.; island. vet.<BR>raud-r ruber, saxon. vet. rod id., german. vet. rôt, nostrum<BR>roth; hib. ruadh «red, reddish, Welsh rhydh»;<BR>ruaid id., ruaidhim «I redden».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=292-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुप्<BR>रुप् 4. P. (व्याकुलत्वे K. विमोहे V.) perturbari, conturbari,<BR>mentis errore affici.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुरु|रुरुः<BR>रुरु m. (ut videtur, a r. रु per redupl.) capreae genus (Wils:<BR>A kind of a deer). DR. 4.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुश्<BR>रुश् 6. P. (हिंसायाम् K. हिंसे V.) ferire, laedere, occidere,<BR>(cf. रुष्, रिश्) — रुशत् in dial. Vêd. rutilans. RIGV. 58.4. 62.8. 113.2.<BR>(cf. रुच्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुष्<BR>1. रुष् 1. et 4. P. ferire, laedere, occidere. Cf. रुश्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुष्<BR>2. रुष् 4. et 10. P. irasci. रुष्ट iratus. SRINGARA-T. 7.; रुषित<BR>id. MAN. 9.83.; रोषित id. H. 1.12. (Cf. gr.<BR>λύσσα, λυσσάω, λυσσαίνω.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुष्<BR>3. रुष् f. (Nom. रुट्, r. रुष्) ira, furor. N. 11.37.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुह्<BR>रुह् 1. P.<BR>1) prodire, nasci, crescere. MAN. 9.36.: {#yAdfSan<BR>tU 'pyate vIjaY kzetre…tAdfg rohati tat tasmin<BR>vIjam#}; MAH. 3.12855.: {#nacA 'pi sarvavIjAni<BR>samyag rohanti#}.<BR>2) adire, adipisci (v. p. 36. rad. इ).<BR>RIGV. 110.6.: ऋभवो वाजम् अरुहन् दिवो रजः «Ribhues<BR>cibum nacti sunt coelestis mundi». — Caus. रोहयामि<BR>et रोपयामि (gr. 521. 6.) serere, plantare. MAH. 3.13116.:<BR>प्रयन्ति सर्ववोजानि रोप्यमाणानि; R. Schl. II.80.7.:<BR>अवृक्षेषुच देशेषु केचिद् वृक्षान् अरोपयन्.<BR>(रुह् mutilatum est e रुध् sicut वृह् crescere ex<BR>idem valente वृध्; v. रुधिर et gr. 315. — Cum primitivâ<BR>formâ रुध् cf. ऋध् i. e. अर्ध् crescere; goth. LUD crescere,<BR>liudith crescit = रोहति pro रोधति, iu = ओ i. e.<BR>अ + उ debilitato gunae incremento a in i (v. gramm.<BR>comp. 27. 109^a).) lauths, gen. laudi-s homo; germ. vet.<BR>liut populus, liuti homines (nostrum Leute), sumarlota<BR>virgulta, palmites (Grimm II.21.), ruota pertica,<BR>virga, sax. vet. ruoda, anglo-sax. rod (Graff. II.491.);<BR>slav. vet. rod-i-ti parere, generare = Caus. रोहायितुम्<BR>e रोधयितुम्, na-rod populus (Miklosich p. 74.); scot.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-b" target="_blank">Page293-b+ 37</a>]<BR>ros semen, rosach semine abundans; hib. rosan «a shrub»;<BR>rud «a wood, a forest»; ruadh «strength, power, value»,<BR>Adj. «strong, valiant»; romho «very much, great», romhoide<BR>«greatness, excess»; ruidh «running, a race»; roid<BR>«a race»; ruaidhneach «hair» v. रोमन्. Laidir «strong,<BR>stout», laidireacht, laidireas «strength»; lat. rôb-ur, ubi<BR>b = ध् sicut in ruber = रुधिर q. v. et gr. ϱ̔ώ-μη, ϱ̔ών-νυμι<BR>aut huc aut ad ऋध् pertinent, cf. Pott. I.250., Benary<BR>«Römische Lautlehre» p. 218. Fortasse lat. rûs,<BR>rûr-is a crescendo dictum, mutato d in r vel in s deinde<BR>in r. Cum रुह् adire (अधिरुह्, आरुह् उपरुह् adscendere)<BR>cf. hib. roidhim «I run», ruidh «running».)<BR>c. अधि P. A. adscendere. R. Schl. II.83.2.: {#aDiruhya…<BR>raTAn#}; MAH. 3.4095.: विमानञ्चा ऽधिरोहति; 14943.:<BR>अधिरोहध्वम्…इमान् रथान्. Intrans. evolare, subvolare,<BR>alis se levare, sublime petere. R. Schl. II.95.11.:<BR>द्विजा अधिरोहन्ति. — Caus. tollere, levare, elevare.<BR>RAGH. 11.81. (v. आरुह् Caus.)<BR>c. अप praef. वि Caus. privare c. ablat. MAH. 3.1579.:<BR>जीविताद् व्यपरोपितः; 10246.: {#putrAn apApAn vyaparopya<BR>rAjyAt#}.<BR>c. अभि adscendere. R. Schl. I.44.3.: {#himavataH SfNgam<BR>aBiruhya#}.<BR>c. अव descendere. A. 2.6.: रथाद् अवरुरोह; 1.4. — Caus.<BR>P.<BR>1) facere ut alqs descendat. RAGH. 1.54.: {#tAm<BR>avAropayat patnIM raTAd avatatAraca#}.<BR>2) deferre, deorsum<BR>ferre, tollere. MAH. 4.1318.: {#avaropaya vfkzAgrAd<BR>DanUMzi#}.<BR>3) facere ut quis perdat, privare. MAN. 1.82.:<BR>इतरेष्व् (युगेषु) आगमाद् धर्मः पादशस् त्व अवरोपितः<BR>(schol. हीनः कृतः). — Caus. A. अवरोपये<BR>descendo (me descendere facio). DR. 3.8.: {#vimucya vAhAn<BR>avarohayaDvam#}.<BR>c. अव praef. प्रति Caus. privare. MAH. 4.536.: प्रत्यवरोपितः<BR>privatus.<BR>c. आ P. A. adscendere, c. acc. vel loc. IN. 1.11.: {#Arohatu<BR>BavAn…raTam#}; 14.: देवलोकम्…आरोहस्व; N. 13.14.:<BR>वृक्षेष्व् आरुह्य; H. 3.5.: आरुहे ऽमाम् मम श्रोणीम्;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-a" target="_blank">Page294-a+ 36</a>]<BR>M. 30.: तत्र…आरुहेथाः (*). Adire, adipisci. HIT. 10.16.:<BR>संशयम् पुनर् आरुह्य; BH. 6.4.: योगारूढः. — Caus.<BR>efficere ut quis adscendat; tollere, levare, collocare<BR>in aliquo loco. N. 8.19. 13.52. IN. 2.21. SA. 5.62.<BR>DR. 8.34. 9.13. M. 31.<BR>c. आ praef. अधि adscendere. MAH. 1.6395. Caus. efficere<BR>ut quis adscendat. R. Schl. II.55.16.<BR>c. आ praef. अनु post aliquem ascendere. MAH. 2.36.:<BR>अन्वारुरोहचा ऽप्य् एनम्.<BR>c. आ praef. अनु praef. सम् id. MAH. 1.3818.: {#tatra 'naY<BR>citrAgnisTam mAdrI samanvAruroha#}.<BR>c. आ praef. उप ascendere. MAH. 2.37.: {#upAruhyA 'rjunaScA<BR>'pi#}. Adire, adipisci. RAGH. 17.30.<BR>c. आ praef. प्र id. MAH. 3.10594.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् adscendere. N. 19.20. Adire, adipisci.<BR>RAGH. 8.15.<BR>c. उप id. MAH. 2.37.<BR>c. प्र prodire, crescere. HIT. 14.7.: {#tuzeRA 'pi parityaktA<BR>na prarohanti taRqulAH#}.<BR>c. प्रति Caus. facere ut quis iterum crescat. RAGH. 17.42.:<BR>शत्रून् उद्धृत्य प्रतिरोपयन् (schol. {#SatrUn udDftya<BR>utKAya pratiropayan punaH sTApayan#}).<BR>c. वि se dispandere, diffundere. BH. 15.3.: {#aSvatTam<BR>enaM suvirUQamUlam…CittvA#}; RAGH. 2.26.: विरूढशष्प.<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) crescere. BHATT. 11.5.<BR>2) se colligere, animum<BR>confirmare. संरूढ confirmatus, animo promtus.<BR>A. 11.1. Caus. facere ut quis crescat, augeatur, progeniem<BR>habeat. SAK. 130.1.: {#saMropite ''tmani DarmapatnI<BR>mayA tyaktA#}.<BR>(*) आरुह est Imperat. et आरुहेथास् Potentialis praeter.<BR>multiformis formationis sextae respondentque formis graecis<BR>ut τύπε, τύποιο; v. gramm. min. ed. 2. §. 381^b). et 374^b).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=293-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुह|रुहः<BR>रुह (r. रुह् s. अ) crescens, in fine compp., v. तनूरुह, शिरोरुह.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुह्वन्<BR>रुह्वन् m. (r. रुह् s. वन्) arbor.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रूक्ष्<BR>रूक्ष् 10. P. (पारुष्ये; ut videtur, Denom. a रूक्ष q. v.) horridum,<BR>asperum, durum esse.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रूक्ष|रूक्षं|रूक्षः<BR>रूक्ष (ut videtur, a रुह् crescere) Adj. asper, horridus, immitis,<BR>durus, acerbus, austerus. H. 2.6. BH. 17.9. Subst.<BR>m. arbor. HEM. (Scribitur etiam रुक्ष. Cf. germ. vet.<BR>rûh, nostrum rauh, anglo-sax. ruh, rug, reoh, angl.<BR>rough.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रूढ|रूढं|रूढः<BR>रूढ v. रुह् et gr. §. 107^b).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रूप्<BR>रूप् 10. P. (ut videtur, Denom. a रूप forma)<BR>1) formare.<BR>2) gestibus exprimere, indicare, repraesentare, proponere,<BR>oculis subjicere. SAK. 7.2.: रथवेगं रूपयति (v.<BR>नट्); UR. 21.11.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) facere, perficere, peragere. MAN. 6.38.: {#nirUpye<BR>'zwim#}.<BR>2) percipere, videre, animadvertere. HIT. 23.3.:<BR>छिद्रन् निरूप्य.<BR>3) considerare, reputare, perpendere.<BR>HIT. 10.3.: तन् निरूप्यताम्; 10.17.: {#tan nirUpayAmi<BR>tAvat#}.<BR>4) examinare, inquirere, explorare, investigare.<BR>HIT. 20.15.: {#pakziBir itas tato nirUpayadBis<BR>tarukoware SAvakAsTIni prAptAni#}; 90.1.: {#aham api<BR>gatvA kim etad iti nirUpayAmi#}. Pervestigare,<BR>perquirere, perscrutari. HIT. 68.14.: कोटरे निरूप्यमाणे.<BR>5) eligere, ausersehen. HIT. 41.2.: {#awavIrAjye<BR>'Bizektum BavAn…nirUpitaH#}.<BR>c. वि (Denom. a विरूप deformis) deformare. HIT. 65.1.<BR>R. Schl. I.1.44.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रूप|रूपं<BR>रूप n. (ut videtur, a r. रुह् crescere, Caus. रोपयामि)<BR>1) forma.<BR>H. 2.5.<BR>2) pulchritudo. SA. 2.18.<BR>3) natura, indoles.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रूपतस्<BR>रूपतस् Adv. (a praec. s. तस्, v. gr. 652. suff. तस्) formâ.<BR>N. 19.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रूपवत्|रूपवन्त्<BR>रूपवत् (a रूप s. वत्) formosus, pulcher. IN. 4.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

