रूष्<BR>रूष् 1. P. ornare. IN. 5.8.: दिव्यच्छन्दनरूषितौ…स्तनौ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

