रेक्<BR>रेक् 1. A. (शङ्कायाम्) suspicari; dubitare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=294-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

