लग्<BR>1. लग् 1. P. (सङ्गे) adhaerere. लग्न;<BR>1) adjunctus, adhaerens.<BR>HIT. 4.: {#yan nave BAjane lagnaH saMskAro<BR>nA 'nyaTA Bavet#}; 35.12.: {#kodaRqAwanIlagnaM snAyubanDaN<BR>KAdAmi#}.<BR>2) secutus (v. लग् praef. अनु).<BR>Lass. 25.6.: पृष्ठतो लग्नः; — Subst. n. ortus signi Zodiaci.<BR>Lass. 20.8.: शुभे लग्ने; HIT. 97.13. (Huc trahi<BR>potest lat. ligare, nisi pertinet ad रज्जु.)<BR>c. अनु अनुलग्न secutus. Lass. 30.10.: {#SabdAnulaganaH<BR>SmaSAnaBUmiN gataH#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=296-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

