लङ्ग्|लंग्<BR>लङ्ग् 1. P. (गतिखञ्जनयोः K. गतौ खञ्जने V.; scribitur<BR>लग्, gr. 110^a).) ire, claudicare. Cf. रङ्ग्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=296-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लङ्घ्|लंघ्<BR>1. लङ्घ् 1. P. (scribitur लघ्, gr. 110^a).) salire, insilire.<BR>BHATT. 15.32.: अन्ये (कपयः) शैलान् अलङ्घिषुः<BR>(schol. आरूढाः); v. 2. लङ्घ् et cf. रङ्क्, रह्,<BR>goth. laika salio; fortasse graec. λαγώ sicut scrt. शश<BR>nostrum Hase, a saliendo dictum; v. Pott. I.232.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=296-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लङ्घ्|लंघ्<BR>2. लङ्घ् 10. P. interdum A. transsilire, transgredi. MAH. 3.11173.:<BR>{#nA 'sti Saktir mamo 'tTAtum…laNGayitvA<BR>prayAhi mAm#}; 11174.: तम्…न लङ्घये; 11178.:<BR>सागरः प्लवगेन्द्रेण क्रमेणै ऽकेन लङ्घितः. TROP. UR. 36.7.infr.:<BR>येन मम त्वयो ऽपदेशो लङ्घितः; MAN. 5.151.:<BR>{#tam (patim) SuSrUzeta jIvantaM saMsTitaYja na<BR>laNGayet#} «mortuum non transgrediatur» (novo matrimonio),<BR>cf. BR. 2.34.; aliter Kullùkabhattus hoc praeceptum<BR>explicat: {#mftaYca nA 'tikrAmed vyaBicAreRa tadIyaSrAdDatarpaRAdi<BR>virahitayA pAralOkikakftyaKaRqanenaca#});<BR>MAH. 8.371.: भर्तारं लङ्घयेद् या तु स्त्री (schol.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=297-a" target="_blank">Page297-a+ 35</a>]<BR>या स्त्री…पतिम् पुरुषान्तरोपगमनाल् लङ्घयेत्).<BR>c. अभि transsilire. MAN. 4.54.<BR>c. अव कालम् अव॰ tempus transigere. GHAT. 7.<BR>c. वि transgredi, peccare. RAGH. 9.741. Relinquere, abjicere.<BR>RAGH. 3.4.: {#aBilAze…taTAviDe mano babanDA<BR>'nyarasAn vilaNGya#} (schol. त्यक्त्वा).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=296-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लङ्घन|लंघन|लंघनं|लङ्घनं<BR>लङ्घन n. (r. लङ्घ् s. अन)<BR>1) transgressio. BR. 2.34.<BR>2) contemtio, repudiatio, rejectio. UR. 33.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=297-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

