लज्ज्<BR>लज्ज् 6. P. A. (scribitur लस्ज्, gr. 110^b).) erubescere, pudere.<BR>DR. 5.2.: {#mahAraTAn atibruvan mUQa na lajjase<BR>kaTam#}; MAN. 12.35. 37.: लज्जति; MAH. 3.13837.:<BR>लज्जन्ति. — Part. pass. लग्न et लज्जित pudore affectus,<BR>pudibundus. V. 1. लज्.<BR>c. वि id. MAH. 3.2217.: विलज्जमाना.<BR>c. सम् id. R. Schl. II.55.16.: संलज्जमाना.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=297-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

