लड्<BR>4. लड् 10. P. लाडयामि (उपसेवायाम् K. उपसेवने V.)<BR>colere, venerari; ministrare. Cf. लल्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=297-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

