लल्<BR>लल् 1. P. interdum A. lascivire, ludere, hilarem esse, voluptate<BR>frui. R. Schl. I.9.19.: ललमाना वराङ्गनाः;<BR>IN. 1.27.: {#SiSur yaTA pitur aNke susuKaM vartate…<BR>taTA tavA 'Nke lalitaM SElarAja mayA praBo#}. — ललित<BR>amoenus, gratus, suavis, venustus, pulcher. Lass. 65.16. 70.2. 91.14.<BR>SAK. 34.15. MEGH. 33, 65. Subst. n. venustas.<BR>R. Schl. I.9.16. — ललितम् Adv. pulchre, belle,<BR>suaviter. DEV. 10.27.: गन्धर्वा ललितञ् जगुः. — Caus.<BR>exhilarare, gaudio afficere. R. Schl. II.47.6.: {#yo naH sadA<BR>lAlayati pitA putrAn ivO ''rasAn#}; 43.15.;<BR>MAH. 2.1797.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=299-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

