लिङ्ग|लिंग|लिंगं|लिङ्गं<BR>लिङ्ग n. (r. लिङ्ग् s. अ)<BR>1) signum, indicium. N. 5.14.<BR>BH. 14.21.<BR>2) penis.<BR>3) phallus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=300-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लिप्<BR>लिप् 6. P. A. लिम्पामि, लिम्पे (gr. 335.) ungere, oblinere,<BR>contaminare, polluere. BHATT. 19.11.: {#ramyEr<BR>limpeta#} (schol. विलेप्स्यथ) वर्णकैः; HIT. 21.14.: {#mAMsAsfgliptAny<BR>asTIni#}. TROP. BH. 4.14.: {#na mAN<BR>karmARi limpanti#}; 5.10.: लिप्यते न स पापेन. (Cf.<BR>gr. λίπος, λιπάζω, ἀ-λείϕω, lat. li-no, lî-mus, de-lîbuo,<BR>lith. pri-lip-ti adhaerere, ankleben, praes. pri-limpù =<BR>प्रलिम्पामि; slav. ljep-i-ti glutinare; hib. laib, laibe<BR>«mire, dirt, clay»; germ. vet. lîm gluten; Pottius I.258.<BR>huc trahit goth. salbôn - sa-lbôn - nostrum salben, ita<BR>ut sa respondeat praep. सम् vel स et lb radici लिप्.<BR>c. अनु i. q. simpl. HIT. 42.1.: राजपुत्रेण स्नातानुलिप्तेन;<BR>N. 16.13.: मलपङ्कानुलिप्ताङ्गीम्.<BR>c. अव अवलिप्त vanus, fastuosus, superbus. BR. 1.11. 19.<BR>c. आ i. q. simpl. MAH. 2624.<BR>c. उप id. MAH. 2.2625.: पांशूपलिप्तसर्वाङ्गः; BH. 13.32.<BR>Caus. oblinendum curare. MAN. 3.206.<BR>c. वि i. q. simpl. HIT. 128.12.<BR>c. सम् Caus. ungere. MAH. 1.4950.: चन्दनेन…समलेपयन्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=300-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लिप्स्<BR>लिप्स् Desid. rad. लभ् (gr. 552.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=300-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लिश्<BR>1. लिश् 6. P. (गतौ K. गत्याम् V.) ire.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=300-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लिश्<BR>2. लिश् 4. P. (अल्पीभावे K. तौछ्ये V.) parvum, exiguum<BR>esse. V. लेश. (Benfey huc trahit gr. ὀ-λίγος,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-a" target="_blank">Page301-a+ 37</a>]<BR>lith. lếsas macer; cf. boruss. vet. likuts parvus; v. लेश.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=300-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लिह्<BR>लिह् 2. P. A. lingere, lambere (लेढि, लीढे v. gr. 102.).<BR>HIT. 28.13.: अस्थि निर्दशनः श्वे ऽव जिह्वया लेढि.<BR>— Intens. लेलिह्, लेलिह्य. MAH. 3.10394.: लेलिहज्जिह्वया;<BR>A. 10.43.: लेलिहानैर् महानागैः; BH. 11.30.:<BR>लेलिह्यसे…लोकान् समग्रान् वदनैर् ज्वलद्भिः.<BR>— In dial. Vêd. रिह् pro लिह्, RIGV. 22.14.: {#payo<BR>viprA rihanti#}. (Cf. gr. ΛΙΧ, λείχω, λίχνος, λιχανός;<BR>hib. lighim, im-lighim «I lick»; lat. lingo; goth.<BR>laigô lingo = Caus. लेहयामि, v. gr. comp. 109^a).6.;<BR>lith. laiźau lingo, liếźuwis lingua; slav. ob-liζ-a-ti lingere.)<BR>c. अव i. q. simpl. DR. 6.21.: {#purA somo 'Dvarago 'valihyate<BR>SunA#}; MAH. 1.667.<BR>c. आ id. RAGH. 2.37.: सेनान्यम् आलीढम् इवा ऽसुरास्त्रैः.<BR>c. परि circumlambere, part. pass. परिलीढ. R. Schl. II.61.16.<BR>c. सम् i. q. simpl. MAH. 3.10653.<BR>c. सम् praef. परि circumlambere. MAH. 3.11500.: {#BImaH<BR>sfkkaRI parisaMlihan#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ली<BR>1. ली 1. P. (द्रवीकरणे K. द्रावणे V.) liquefacere, solvere.<BR>लीन solutus, dirutus, exstinctus. R. ed. Ser. II.46.10.:<BR>लीनपुष्करपत्र. (Cf. 1. री, lith. ly-ti pluere, lyj-a<BR>pluit (y = i), ly-tus pluvia; slav. li-ja-ti fundere; hib.<BR>leaghaim «I melt, thaw, dissolve» = लयामि cum gh<BR>pro य्; leaghan «liquor»; lat. liqueo, liquo.)<BR>c. आ Pass. dissolvi, tabescere. N. 11.14.: {#muhur AlIyate<BR>BItA#}.<BR>c. प्र Pass. dissolvi, perire, evanescere, mori. BH. 8.18.:<BR>रात्र्यागमे प्रलयन्ते; MAN. 4.240.: {#ekaH prajAyate jantur<BR>ekaH pralIyate#} (schol. म्रियते); प्रलीन mortuus.<BR>BH. 14.15.<BR>c. वि Pass. id. v. sq.<BR>c. वि praef. प्र Pass. id. BH. 4.23.: कर्म समग्रम् प्रविलीयते;<BR>MAH. 1.6462.: फेनवत् प्रविलीयते.<BR>c. सम् v. 2. ली.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ली<BR>2. ली 9. P. 4. A. लिनामि (gr. 385.) adhaerere, inhaerere, insidere<BR>(secundum K. et V. amplecti, श्लेषणे K. श्लिषि<BR>V. cf. लिङ्ग्) लीन adjunctus, adhaerens, inhaerens,<BR>insidens, morans. BHATT. 2.19.: {#na paNkajan tad<BR>yad alInazawpadam#}; RAGH. 9.65.: {#kuYjalInAn…<BR>siMhAn#}; MAH. 1.4310. 4314.: {#dadfSus tatra (ASrame)<BR>lInAMs tAMS cOrAn#}.<BR>c. अभि incumbere, inniti, c. acc. MEGH. 37.: भुजतरुवनम्…अभिलीनः.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) considere, c. acc. vel loc. MAH. 3.10560.: {#UruM<BR>rAjYaH, samAsAdya, kapotaH SyenajAd BayAt…nililye#};<BR>BHATT. 14.76.: निलिल्ये मूर्ध्नि गृध्रो ऽस्य. निलीन<BR>insidens. BHATT. 2.5.: पुष्पैः…निलीनभृङ्गैः.<BR>Incessus, habitatus. R. Schl. II.46.3.: {#araRyAni…nilInAni<BR>mfgadvijEH#}. निलीयमान sedens. UR. 86.4.infr.:<BR>आश्रमपादपशिखरे निलीयमानः.<BR>2) procidere,<BR>procumbere. MAH. 3.11109.: {#nililyur vanavAsinaH<BR>samutpetuH KagAs trastAH#}; 10975.: भीता वायोर् निलिल्यिरे;<BR>A. 6.13.: वित्रेसुश्च निलिल्युश्च भूतानि (sic<BR>legendum pro विलिल्युश्च).<BR>c. नि praef. सम् sedere. MAH. 3.13654.: {#uparizwAcca vfkzasya<BR>valAkA sannyalIyata#}.<BR>c. सम् morari, versari. SU. 2.20.: {#saMlInam api durgezu<BR>ninyatur yamasAdanam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लीढ|लीढः<BR>लीढ v. लिह् (gr. 102.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लीला<BR>लीला f.<BR>1) ludus, praesertim feminarum amore captarum.<BR>MEGH. 36. 66. SRINGARA-T. 1.8. 9.<BR>2) derisus. R. Schl. I.62.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुञ्च्|लुंच्<BR>लुञ्च् 1. P. evellere. BHATT. 14.59.: केशान् लुलुञ्च. (Cf.<BR>रुप्, लुप्; slav. luć-i-ti separare; goth. raupja evello,<BR>nostrum raufe.)<BR>c. अव id. MAH. 3.10760.: अवलुञ्च्य जटाम् एकाम्;<BR>10761.: अवलुञ्च्य पराम्.<BR>c. वि BHATT. 18.38.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुञ्ज्<BR>लुञ्ज् 10. P. (scribitur लुज्; gr. 110^a).) i. q. 2. लञ्ज्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुट्<BR>1. लुट् 1. et 4. P. se volutare. BHATT. 3.32.: {#luwyan saSoko<BR>Buvi#}; 18.11.: भूमौ लुट्यन्ति. V. लुठ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=301-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुट्<BR>2. लुट् 1. A. i. q. 1. रुट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुट्<BR>3. लुट् 10. P. (भाषार्थे K. भाषे V.) loqui. Cf. 2. रट्, रठ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुठ्<BR>1. लुठ् 6. P. se volutare. HIT. 123.18.: {#patitaH pfTivItale<BR>luloWa#}; 55.11.: मणिर् लुठति पादेषु. (V.<BR>1. लुट् et cf. hib. liuth «I move, I hasten».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुठ्<BR>2. लुठ् 1. P. (उपघाते K. प्रतीघाते V.) ferire, occidere,<BR>perturbare; arcere, avertere. Cf. रुठ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुठ्<BR>3. लुठ् 1. A. (प्रतीघाते) arcere, avertere. Cf. रुठ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुठ्<BR>4. लुठ् 10. P. furari. Cf. लुण्ट्, लुण्ठ्, लुण्ड्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुड्<BR>1. लुड् 1. P. agitare, perturbare. Caus. id. MAH. 1.2833.:<BR>तद् वनम्…लोडयामास दुष्यन्तः; R. Schl. II.95.18.:<BR>मृगयूथलोडिताम्. Cf. 1. लुट्, 1. लुठ्, लुल्.<BR>c. आ Caus.<BR>1) agitare. MAH. 1.7921.: {#kAmenA ''loqyate<BR>manaH#}.<BR>2) miscere. R. Schl. II.48.24.: {#vizam pivatA<BR>''loqya#}; MAH. 4.689.: विषम् आलोड्य पास्यामि;<BR>v. sq.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् Caus. miscere. MAH. 3.11477.: {#vizam<BR>etat samAloqya prASitan tvayA#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुड्<BR>2. लुड् 6. P. (संवृतौ K. श्लिषि V.) tegere; amplecti.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुण्ट्|लुंट्<BR>1. लुण्ट् 1. P. (स्तेये K. ह्नुतौ V.; scribitur लुट्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>furari. Cf. रुण्ट्, लुण्ड्, 4. लुठ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुण्ट्|लुंट्<BR>2. लुण्ट् 1. et 10. P. (स्तेये K. अवज्ञाचौर्ये V.) furari; spernere,<BR>despicere. V. 1. लुण्ट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुण्ठ्|लुंठ्<BR>लुण्ठ् 1. P. (scribitur लुठ्, gr. 110^a).) i. q. रुण्ठ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुण्ड्|लुंड्<BR>लुण्ड् 10. P. (चौर्ये) furari. V. 1. लुण्ट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुण्थ्<BR>लुण्थ् 1. P. हिंसासङ्क्लेशयोः; scribitur लुथ्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>ferire, laedere, occidere; dolore afficere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुप्<BR>1. लुप् 6. P. A. लुम्पामि, लुम्पे (gr. 335.). Findere, rumpere,<BR>interrumpere, irrumpere, conturbare, perdere,<BR>destruere. MAH. 1.5560.: {#lokAn viSvAsayitvE<BR>'va tato lumped yaTA vfkaH#}; HIT. 113.3.: {#svAminaM<BR>loptum icCAmi#}; MAN. 2.189.: तस्य व्रतन् न लुप्यते;<BR>9.211.: तस्य भागो न लुप्यते; BR. 2.15.: {#bAle 'smin<BR>anATe…sarvato lupte#}; BH. 1.42. — Caus. laedere,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-b" target="_blank">Page302-b+ 37</a>]<BR>violare, turbare. MAN. 8.16.: धर्मन् न लोपयेत्; R. Schl. II.35.9.<BR>— Cum abl. avertere. RAGH. 12.9.: {#satyAd<BR>gurum alopayan#}. (Cf. lat. rumpo, ruptus =<BR>लुप्तस्; lith. luppù glubo, cutem, pellem detraho; russ.<BR>luplju id.; polon. łup-a-ć scindere, łupiez̕ praeda, rapina<BR>(v. लोप्त्र); slav. lom-i-ti frangere; goth. raubô rapio,<BR>raupja evello (v. लुञ्च्) = Caus. रोपयामि; fortasse<BR>etiam lat. rapio ad Caus. referendum est, abjecto posteriore<BR>diphthongi ओ elemento; gr. λέπω; hib. reubaim<BR>«I tear, lacerate», reuban «plundering, destroying, robbery»;<BR>lomaim «I sheer, shave, make bare» = लुम्पामि<BR>ejecto प्.)<BR>c. अव irrumpere. MAN. 7.106.: वृकवच्चा ऽवलुम्पेत.<BR>c. प्र disturbare, destruere. MAH. 1.7750.: {#brAhmaRasya…<BR>havir DvANGEH pralupyate#}.<BR>c. प्र praef. वि perturbare, disturbare, destruere. MAN. 3.225.:<BR>तद् (अन्नम्) विप्रलुम्पन्त्य् असुराः.<BR>c. वि id. MAN. 3.204.: {#rakzAMsi hi vilumpanti SrAdDam<BR>Arakzavarjitam#}; R. Schl. I.20.3.: {#tasya yajYo hi rakzoBis<BR>tadA vilulupe#}; II.64.63.: स्मृतिर् मम विलुप्यते.<BR>— Caus. id. MAH. 1.7752. Exstinguere. MAH. 1.5233.:<BR>तेन (वायुना) तत्र प्रदीपः स दीप्यमानो विलोपितः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुप्<BR>2. लुप् 4. P. i. q. रुप् 4. P.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुब्ध|लुब्धः<BR>लुब्ध v. लुभ् (gr. 83.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुब्धक|लुब्धकः<BR>लुब्धक m. (a praec. s. क) venator. N. 11.33.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुभ्<BR>1. लुभ् 4. P. cupere, desiderare. लुब्ध cupidus, avidus.<BR>HIT. 10.2.: तण्डुलकणलुब्धान् कपोतान्;<BR>BH. 18.27. — Caus. pellicere, excitare. R. Schl. I.64.8.:<BR>लोभयामास ललिता विश्वामित्रम्; 12.: {#yan mAm<BR>loBayase ramBe#}. (Cf. lith. lûbju appeto, concupisco, praesertim<BR>nuptias; slav. liub-i-ti amare; germ. vet. liubiu amo<BR>= Caus. लोभयामि, liub carus, dilectus, liubi amor; lat.<BR>lubet, libet, libido.)<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. MAN. 9.20.: प्रलुलुभे. Caus. pellicere.<BR>SU. 1.12.: रत्नैः प्रलोभयामासुः स्त्रीभिश्चो ऽभौ.<BR>c. वि Caus. pellicere, excitare. RAGH. 19.10.: अङ्गनास्<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=303-a" target="_blank">Page303-a+ 36</a>]<BR>तम् अधिकं व्यलोभयन्. Concitare in iram; DR. 4.24.:<BR>विलोभयामास परं वाक्यैर् वाक्यानि योजती.<BR>Delectare. R. Schl. II.94.1.: स्वञ्च चित्तं विलोभयन्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=302-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुभ्<BR>2. लुभ् 6. P. perturbare. Part. pass. लुभित. Cf. लुप्.<BR>c. वि id. BHATT. 9.40.: विलुभितं वातैः केशरम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=303-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुम्ब्|लुंब्<BR>लुम्ब् 1. et 10. P. (अर्दने; scribitur लुब्) vexare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=303-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लुल्<BR>लुल् 1. P. agitare, perturbare. R. Schl. II.42.29.: {#baBUva<BR>lulitam manaH#}; 65.18.: शोकाश्रुलुलितानना. Cf.<BR>लुड्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=303-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

