लुह्<BR>लुह् 1. P. (गार्ध्ये) desiderare, appetere. (Cf. 1. लुभ् et v.<BR>gr. 104.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=303-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

लू<BR>लू 9. P. A. लुनामि, लुने (v. gr. 385.) findere, abscindere,<BR>desecare, evellere. RAGH. 3.59.: {#patatriRA SarAsanajyAm<BR>alunAt#}; DR. 5.6.: {#siMhasya pakzmARi muKAl<BR>lunAsi#}. BHATT. 9.80.: नासाम्…लुलाव. — Part.<BR>pass. लून. R. Schl. I.55.10.: लूनपक्ष इव द्विजः. (Cf.<BR>लुप्, gr. λύω, lat. so-lvo, so-lû-tum = संलू; goth. LUS<BR>(fra-liusa perdo, laus, lusum) adjectâ sibilante; lausja<BR>solvo; lith. láuju desino, cesso = Caus. लावयामि; slav.<BR>rv-a-ti evellere, runo, gen. runes-e vellus, v. Miklosich<BR>p. 75.; rusʽ-i-ti evertere.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=303-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

