वङ्क्|वंक्<BR>वङ्क् 1. A. (कौटिल्ये K. कौटिल्ये गतौ V.; scribitur वक्)<BR>tortuose ire; incedere; ire. वङ्कु tortuose incedens.<BR>RIGV. 114.4. (V. वङ्क, वक्र et cf. lith. wingis flexus<BR>fluminis, germ. vet. winkil, anglo-sax. vincel angulus,<BR>gr. ἀγϰή, ἄγϰος, ἀγϰών, ἀγϰύλος, ἄγϰυϱα; lat. angulus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=305-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

