वयस्<BR>वयस् n. (r. वय् s. अस्)<BR>1) aetas, praesertim florens, integra<BR>aetas, adolescentia, juventus. N. 1.11. SA. 1.4.<BR>RAGH. 3.70.<BR>2) avis (v. वि). NALOD. 1.27. schol. (Cambro-brit.<BR>aes avis, nisi hoc a lat. avis, v. Pictet p. 60.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=309-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

