वा<BR>1. वा 2. P. flare, spirare, de vento. N. 24.40.: {#vavOca pavanaH<BR>SuciH#}; A. 4.51.: शीतन् तत्र ववौ वायुः. - वात<BR>m. ventus. A. 11.12.; deus venti. H. 1.34. (Cf.<BR>वै; goth. VO flare, spirare (vaia, vaivô v. gr. comp. 617.),<BR>vinds, Them. vinda ventus; germ. vet. wa-dal flabellum,<BR>wat, wait, waiet, wahet flat; slav. vje-ja-ti flare, vje-tr<BR>ventus; lith. wếjas ventus; gr. ἄημι, ut videtur, ex ἀ-Ϝημι<BR>= वामि praef. आ, ἀήϱ; αὔϱα ex ἀϜϱα, οὖϱος ex ὀϜϱος;<BR>de αὔω v. वै; lat. ventus, aër aura; hib. bad ventus =<BR>वात, pers. bâd.)<BR>c. निस् extingui, de igne. SAK. 91.11.: {#nirvAsyataH pradIpasya<BR>SiKA#}. V. निर्वाण. — Caus. extinguere ignem.<BR>MAH. 1.1608.: {#samidDaY jAtavedasaM varzEr nirvApayizyAmo<BR>meGA BUtAH#}. — V. निर्वापन.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. R. Schl. II.71.25.: प्रवाति पवनः श्रीमान्.<BR>c. सम् id. MAH. 4.1288.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=314-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वा<BR>2. वा 10. P. (सुखाप्तिगतिसेवासु) voluptate frui; ire;<BR>colere.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=314-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वा<BR>3. वा Adv.<BR>1) vel, sicut Latinorum ve postponitur. BR. 1.19.:<BR>वा-वा sive-sive (entweder-oder). N. 26.10. Cum<BR>antecedente अथ vel यदि saepe ita construitur ut hae<BR>voces sensu vacent atque particulae वा solum ut fulcrum<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=315-a" target="_blank">Page315-a+ 37</a>]<BR>inserviant.<BR>2) sicut. DR. 7.15. Interdum redundat, e. c.<BR>H. 4.2. 52.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=314-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

