वाध्<BR>वाध्, बाध् 1. A. vexare, perturbare. A. 4.47.: {#na bADate<BR>tatra rajaH#}; R. Schl. I.14.13.: {#rAvaRo nAma rAkzasaH sarvAn<BR>no bADate#}; DR. 6.3.: महावनं शत्रुभिर् बाध्यमानम्;<BR>HIT. 57.5.: महति शङ्का माम् बाधते; MAN. 9.226. 10.129.<BR>— Caus. p. id. R. Schl. I.14.15.: {#sa vADayati<BR>lokAMs trIn#}. (Cf. वध्, व्यध्; lith. bếda miseria,<BR>aerumna, bednas miser; russ. bjeda miseria; fortasse<BR>goth. balvja vexo e badvja; gr. ΠΑΘ, ἔπαϑον,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=316-a" target="_blank">Page316-a+ 37</a>]<BR>ὠϑέω, ἀπωϑέω, v. praef. अप, fortasse hib. buairim «I<BR>vex, aggrieve, trouble» e buaidim.)<BR>c. अधि i. q. simpl. MAH. 1.5693.: {#nacE 'kaH sa samarTo<BR>'smAn pARqavArTe 'DibADitum#}.<BR>c. अप in dial. Vêd. abigere, removere, repellere. RIGV. 35.3.:<BR>अप विश्वा दुरिता बाधमानः «omnia scelera removens»;<BR>9.: अपा ऽमीवाम् बाधते «dolorem repellit».<BR>c. आ i. q. simpl. SAK. 58.9. 10.<BR>c. परि id. MAH. 3.8743.<BR>c. प्र<BR>1) id. MAH. 1.5808. R. Schl. II.53.15. HIT. 59.5.<BR>2) arcere, prohibere, cohibere. DR. 9.8.: {#tvam…sadE<BR>'vA 'smAn prabADase#}; MAH. 2.1648.: {#kaTan tu dEvaM Sakyate<BR>pOruzeRa prabADitum#}.<BR>c. प्रति repellere, arcere. SA. 1.24.: {#tAm…na kaScid<BR>varayAmAsa tejasA pratibADitaH#}; R. Schl. II.52.46.;<BR>MAH. 3.1081.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=315-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

