वारि|वारिः<BR>वारि n. aqua. N. 24.5. (Cf. वार्, वरुण, hib. burn aqua;<BR>fairge mare, fual «urine, water», mutato r in l; lat.<BR>mare, Them. mari, mutato v in m, v. gr. comp. 63.; lith.<BR>márếs (Plur. fem., gen. mari-û); slav. more id. (neut.<BR>sg. a Thema morjo, v. gr. comp. 259.); germ. vet.<BR>mari m. et n. (Them. marja); hib. muir, cambro-brit.<BR>mor id. Cf. etiam lat. urina, correpto वा in u, urceus,<BR>urna; gr. ὀϱός, οὖϱον, οὐϱέω.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=316-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

