वृक|वृकः<BR>वृक m. lupus. (E वर्क (v. gr. min. 12.) unde lith. wilka-s,<BR>debilitato a in i, mutato r in l, russ. volk, goth. vulf-s,<BR>Them. vulfa, mutatâ gutt. in lab.; gr. λύϰος per metath.<BR>ex ὔλϰος pro Ϝαλϰος, correptâ syllabâ Ϝα in υ, lat. lupus<BR>ex ulpus pro ulcus; hib. breach, brech; pers. ڭرك gurk,<BR>mutato v in g.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=329-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

