वृध्<BR>वृध् 1. A. interdum P. crescere. M. 11.: {#sa tatra vavfDe…<BR>matsyaH#}; MAH. 1.4865.: सर्वे ववृधुर् अल्पेन कालेन;<BR>HIT. 133.14.: सुकृतिनाङ् कीर्तिश् चिरं वर्धताम्.<BR>TROP. felicem esse, florere. MAH. 2.1601.: दिष्ट्या वर्धसि<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=334-a" target="_blank">Page334-a+ 37</a>]<BR>धर्मज्ञ साम्राज्यम् प्राप्तवान् असि; 3.12286.: {#dizwyA<BR>varDAmahe pArTA dizwyA 'si punar AgataH#}.<BR>2) augere,<BR>amplificare. MAH. 1.5540.: {#pararAzwrARi nirjitya svarAjyaM<BR>vavfDuH purA#}; RIGV. 52.7. — वृद्ध<BR>1) adultus. H. 4.50.<BR>2) auctus, dives. N. 12.68.<BR>3) senex. BR. 1.22. — Caus.<BR>augere. SU. 2.10.: तेजो बलञ्च देवानां वर्धयन्ति.<BR>(Cf. ऋध्, वृह्, वृंह्, रुह्, anglo-sax. vridian<BR>crescere, goth. vaur-ts radix (v. ऋध्); fortasse valda<BR>impero a crescendo, potestate dictum sicut mah-ts potestas,<BR>mag possum, praet. mah-ta, pertinent ad मह् crescere;<BR>slav. vladû impero (vid. Miklosich), vlas capillus<BR>(vid. रोमन्), russ. volos id., hib. folt id., fridh «a forest,<BR>a park» fortasse for-bair «grow thou, increase»,<BR>for-bairt «increase, profit, emolument» = वृध् praef.<BR>प्र; slav. rastû cresco e vradtû, nisi pertinet ad ऋध् i. e.<BR>अर्ध्; russ. vroschdaju ingenero, ingigno = Caus. वर्धयामि;<BR>gr. βλασ-τός, βλάσ-τη, βλασ-τάνω e<BR>βλαϑ-τός vel βλαδ-τός etc.; etiam ϱ̔ίζα propter aeol. βϱίζα<BR>nunc potius huc quam ad ऋध् traxerim (v. Benfey I.78. 79.).<BR>Huc etiam trahi posset lat. grandis, insertâ nasali,<BR>sicut in वृंह्, mutato v in g; anglo-sax. great magnus,<BR>germ. vet. grôz id.).<BR>c. अभि i. q. simpl. N. 8.14.: {#asya vE dyUte BUyo rAgo<BR>'BivarDate#}.<BR>c. प्र id. H. 1.20. DR. 5.7.<BR>c. वि id. N. 1.17. SA. 1.19. 6.23.<BR>c. वि praef. सम् id. MAH. 1.4977.<BR>c. सम् id. SA. 2.10. — Caus.<BR>1) augere. MAH. 1.8279.<BR>2) alere, nutrire, educare, aufziehen. HIT. 26.16.: {#saca<BR>matsyAhAraviSezEr mAM saMvarDayizyati#}; 58.10.: {#mAMsAhAradAnena<BR>taM viqAlaM saMvarDayati#}. Educare, educere. R. Schl. I.39.18.:<BR>घृतपूर्णेषु कुम्भेषु धात्र्यस् तान् समवर्धयन्;<BR>MAH. 1.4264.: {#tasmAd garBaM samADatsva BIzmaH<BR>saMvarDayizyati#}; 5087.: संवर्धयामास (मिथुनम्);<BR>5089.: मया बालाव् इमौ संवर्धितौ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=333-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृन्त|वृंत|वृंतं|वृन्तं<BR>वृन्त n. petiolus, pediculus. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=334-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृन्द|वृंद|वृन्दं|वृन्दः<BR>वृन्द m. n. grex, caterva. RITU-S. 1.23. Lass. 45.10. MEGH. 64.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=334-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृश्<BR>वृश् 4. P. (वृत्याम्) eligere. Cf. वृ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=334-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृष्<BR>1. वृष् 1. P. interdum A.<BR>1) pluere, pluviam demittere. R. Schl. I.9.56.:<BR>ववर्ष सहसा देवः; MAH. 1.6621.: {#na<BR>vavarza sahasrAkzo rAzwrecE 'vA 'sya#}; 5464.: वर्षमाणा घनाः.<BR>Cum acc. pluere aliquid. MAH. 1.1419.: {#so 'py<BR>avarzata SoRitam#}; 3.796.: मय्य् अवर्षत दुर्धर्षः शरधाराः.<BR>Cum acc. et instr. irrigare, perfundere alqd aliquâ<BR>re (beregnen). DR. 8.16.: {#nakulam…kzemaNkaramahAmuKO…SaravarzEr<BR>avarzatAm#}; DEV. 3.2. — Caus. facere<BR>ut pluviam demittat. MAH. 3.9991.: {#tapaso yaH praBAveRa<BR>varzayAmAsa vAsavam#}. (Fortasse वृष् mutilatum<BR>e वृक्ष् et hoc ortum e वृज् adjectâ sibilante; cf. gr.<BR>βϱέχω, ἕϱση, v. वर्ष; fortasse οὐϱανός a pluendo dictum,<BR>v. Benfey I.324.; lat. rigo, goth. rig-n pluviu, rigneith<BR>pluit; germ. vet. regan pluvia, reganôn pluere, v.<BR>Graff. 2.441. sq.; nisi pertinent ad सृज् effundere. Hib.<BR>fras «a shower, hail»; lith. rokia pluvia tenuissima; wers-inế,<BR>wers-mế fons. Vid. वृष, वृषण.)<BR>c. अभि<BR>1) pluere, c. acc. vel instr. rei. R. Schl. I.52.23.:<BR>तत् सर्वङ् कामधुग् दिव्ये अभिवर्ष कृते मम; MAH. 1.4062.:<BR>देवाः…अभ्यवर्षन्त कुसुमैः.<BR>2) c. acc. et<BR>instr. irrigare alqd aliquâ re (beregnen). IN. 4.11.: {#suhfdaScA<BR>'nnapAnena viviDenA 'Bivarzati#}. PASS. A. 7.27.:<BR>अभिवृष्टानि शृङ्गाणि…धराभृताम्.<BR>c. प्र pluere, pluviam demittere. MAH. 1.6630.<BR>c. प्र praef. अभि iä. MAN. 1.304.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=334-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृष्<BR>2. वृष् 10. A. (शक्तिबन्धने K. प्रजनैश्ये V.) potentem esse,<BR>ligare (ut mihi videtur, Denom. a sq.), generare, imperare.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=334-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृष|वृषं|वृषः<BR>वृष m. (r. वृष् irrigare semine s. अ) taurus. (Primitive<BR>mas in universum, v. वृषण. Ad rad. वृष् i. e. वर्ष् nunc<BR>etiam traxerim gr. ἄϱσην, ἄϱ̓ϱ̔ν, quod supra (p. 57.)<BR>minus apte cum ऋषभ comparavimus, quod ipsum e वृषभ<BR>mutilatum esse videtur; lat. verres, nisi pertinet ad<BR>घृष्टि q. v., per assim. e verses explicaverim; fortasse hircus<BR>e vircus pro varcus, vid. r. वृष्; lith. werszis vitulus; [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=335-a" target="_blank">Page335-a+ 37</a>]<BR>russ. vol taurus, cum l pro r; fortasse germ. vet. far,<BR>Them. farri taurus, mutato v in f, rs in rr per assimil.;<BR>hib. braiche «a stag, a buffalo», v. वृषभ.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=334-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृषण|वृषणः<BR>वृषण m. (r. वृष् s. अन) scrotum, testiculus. AM.: {#muzko<BR>'Rqakozo vfzaRaH#}. (Vid. वृष्, वृष et cf. gr. ὄϱχις,<BR>vid. Benfey. I.329.; fortasse lat. verêtrum mutilatum est<BR>e versêtrum e perdito verbo verseo = Caus. वर्षयामि,<BR>- v. gr. comp. 109^a).6. - ita ut proprie sit instrumentum<BR>irrigandi semine, cf. verres et v. वृष.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=335-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृषन्<BR>वृषन् m. (qui pluit, pluviam demittit, r. वृष् s.<BR>अन्) cognomen dei Indri. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=335-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

