व्ये<BR>व्ये 1. P. A. tegere. Part. pass. वीत, v. gr. 610.<BR>c. परि id. परिवीत tectus, indutus. RAGH. 15.77.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-a" target="_blank">Page340-a+ 32</a>]<BR>c. सम् id. संवीत tectus. N. 9.6. 13.46.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=339-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्योमन्<BR>व्योमन् n. (fortasse a r. दिव् splendere, abjecto द्, praef.<BR>वि, suff. मन्, v. द्यो, द्यु, द्युत्, विद्युत्) coelum. IN. 2.27. 5.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रज्<BR>1. व्रज् 1. P. interdum A.<BR>1) ire, procedere. H. 1.7.: {#punar<BR>asmAn upAdAya taTE 'va vraja#}; N. 3.9.: {#vraja nEzaDa<BR>mAciram#}; 9.35.: ज्ञातीन् व्रजेत्; MAH. 1.2263.:<BR>व्रजध्वम्.<BR>2) facere (v. चर्). UR. 49.10.: {#vyApAraM vrajasi<BR>me SarIre#} du machst Anspruch. V. वृज् i. e. वर्ज्.<BR>c. अनु<BR>1) sequi. N. 13.61.<BR>2) i. q. simpl. MAH. 3.8266.<BR>MAN. 2.241.<BR>c. अनु praef. सम् sequi. MAH. 2.1606.<BR>c. आ adire. N. 8.6.<BR>c. उत् praef. प्रति obviam ire. RAGH. 1.90.; v. गम् c.<BR>उत् praef. प्रति.<BR>c. परि ambulare, oberrare, huc illuc migrare. MAN. 6.33. 41.<BR>c. प्र progredi, abire, ire. MAH. 2.2613.: वनाय प्रवव्रजुः.<BR>— Caus. in exilium mittere. RAGH. 12.6.: रामम् प्राव्राजयत्.<BR>c. सम् praef. उप intrare. MAN. 6.51.: आगारम् उपसंव्रजेत्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रज्<BR>2. व्रज् 10. P. व्राजयामि (संस्कृतौ त्यागे K. संस्कृतौ गतौ<BR>V.) ornare, relinquere, ire. (Vid. 1. {#vraj, vfj,<BR>vfYj#}.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रण्<BR>1. व्रण् 1. P. (शब्दे K. रुतौ V.; scribitur etiam ब्रण्) sonare.<BR>(V. रण्, ध्रण्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रण्<BR>2. व्रण् 10. P. (ut videtur, Denom. a व्रण; scribitur etiam<BR>ब्रण्) vulnerare. (V. व्रण et cf. lat. vuln-us, slav.<BR>rana vulnus, lith. róna id., iṅ-roniju vulnero; hib. leon<BR>«affliction, a wound, a moth»; leonaim «I wound,<BR>sprain»; fortasse etiam nostrum Wun-de, germ. vet.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">Page340-b+ 30</a>]<BR>wun-da, wun-ta huc pertinet, mutatis liquidis r et n, v.<BR>Graff. I.896.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रण|व्रणं|व्रणः<BR>व्रण m. n. vulnus. (V. व्रण् et cf. व्रश्च्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रत|व्रतं|व्रतः<BR>व्रत m. n. (fortasse a r. वृ i. e. वर् eligere, transposito वर्<BR>in व्र, suff. त) votum, devotio, pietas. SA. 4.3. 6. BH. 6.14.<BR>N. 5.21. 13.69. IN. 4.7. Saepe in fine compos. BAH. e. c.<BR>पतिव्रता erga conjugem pietatem, devotionem habens,<BR>conjugi devota, addicta. N. 10.14. 13.43. देवव्रत diis<BR>addictus. BH. 9.25. दृढव्रत firma vota habens, votorum<BR>tenax. BH. 7.28. 9.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रश्च्<BR>व्रश्च् 6. P. (छेदने K. छेदे V.; in tempp. spec. corripitur in<BR>वृश्च्; part. pass. वृक्ण) scindere, abscindere. BHATT. 14.77.:<BR>वव्रश्चुः; 9.41.: व्रश्चित्वा…अपांतयत् तरून्.<BR>c. अव id. RIGV. 51.7.: वृश्चा शत्रोर् अव विश्वानि वृष्ट्या<BR>«frange inimici cunctas vires».<BR>c. आ A. id. RIGV. 27.13.: मा ज्यायसः शंसम् आवृक्षि<BR>«nunquam optimi cujusque dei laudem interrumpam».<BR>c. वि id. RIGV. 61.10.: विवृश्चद् वज्रेण वृत्रम् इन्द्रः;<BR>32.5.: स्कन्धांसी ऽव कुलिशेना विवृक्णा «arbores<BR>quasi securi caesae».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्री<BR>व्री 4. A. et 9. P. (वरणे K. वृत्याम् V.) eligere. Cf. वृ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रीड्<BR>व्रीड् 4. P. pudore affici. व्रीडित pudibundus. N. 7.18.<BR>SA. 1.35.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रीस्<BR>व्रीस् 1. et 10. P. (वधे) pulsare, occidere. Cf. व्रूस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रुड्<BR>व्रुड् 6. P. (संवृतिसंहतिमज्जनेषु) tegere, colligere, accumulare,<BR>mergi.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्रूस्<BR>व्रूस् 1. et 10. P. i. q. व्रीस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्ली<BR>व्ली 9. P. व्लिणामि (धरणे K. गत्यां वृत्याम् V.) tenere,<BR>ire, eligere. Cf. व्री.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

व्लेक्ष्<BR>व्लेक्ष् 10. P. (दृशि) videre.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

श्<BR>श् Haec littera orta est e क् et respondet graeco k, lat. c,<BR>lith. k et sz, slav. k et s, hib. c, ch et s; germ. h; v. gr.<BR>comp. §§. 21. 87.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शंस्<BR>1. शंस् 1. P. interdum A.<BR>1) dicere, indicare, narrare. N. 13.53.:<BR>शंस मे का ऽसि कस्य वा; 12.35.: {#nalaM<BR>yadi na SaMsasi#}; 12.126.: यदि जानीथ नृपतिङ् क्षिप्रं<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=341-a" target="_blank">Page341-a+ 37</a>]<BR>शंसत मे प्रियम्; R. Schl. II.68.8.: {#mAcA 'smE pitaram<BR>mftam BavantaH SaMsizuH#}; SU. 3.11.: {#sundopasundayoH<BR>karma…SaSaMsire#}.<BR>2) laudare. BH. 5.1.: {#punar yogaYca<BR>SaMsasi#}; MAH. 2.2298.: {#SaSaMsur drOpadIn tatra kutsanto<BR>DftarAzwrajam#}. (Cf. शास्. Fortasse lith. sakau<BR>dico, loquor, litteris transpositis e kasau; ita etiam germ.<BR>vet. sagên dicere, anglo-sax. sagan, sœgan, cum g pro<BR>h, quod pro श् = क् exspectaveris. Cf. etiam SANG<BR>canere (v. Graff. 6.91.). Pottius huc refert lat. cano<BR>(v. क्वण्), Cas-menœ, Ca-menœ, car-men. Cum शंस्<BR>conferatur etiam pers. خواندن kân-den recitare, cantare,<BR>nisi pertinet ad क्वण् vel स्वन्, v. gr. comp. 35.<BR>De خاستن kâs-ten cupere v. 2. शंस्.)<BR>c. अभि calumniari, conviciari, maledicere, objurgare, accusare,<BR>criminari; अभिशस्त increpatus. MAN. 8.116.:<BR>वत्सस्या ऽभिशस्तस्य पुरा भ्रात्रा यवीयसा; AM. III.1.43.:<BR>आक्षारितः क्षारितो ऽभिशस्ते; MAN. 2.185.: {#aBiSastAMs<BR>tu varjayet#}; 3.159.<BR>c. आ<BR>1) indicare. RAGH. 1.86.<BR>2) implorare. DR. 5.12.:<BR>आशंस…सौवीरराजस्य पुनः प्रसादम्.<BR>c. प्र laudare, celebrare. N. 1.16. 3.16.<BR>c. प्र praef. अभि id. A. 1.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=340-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शंस्<BR>2. शंस् 1. A. interdum P. (इच्छायाम् K. आशिषि V.; scribitur<BR>शस्, gr. 110^a).) cupere, desiderare, fausta<BR>precari. (V. शास् praef. आ et cf. pers. خاستن kâsten<BR>cupere, velle, rogare, خواهم kâh-em cupio etc., hib.<BR>sant «greediness, covetousness, cupidity, lust», santaighim<BR>«I desire, covet, lust» V. Pictet p. 64.; lat. censeo,<BR>v. praef. आ sgf. 3.)<BR>c. आ<BR>1) cupere, desiderare. MAH. 1.7148.: {#kurupravIrAn<BR>ASaMsamAnaH…jagAma tAm BArgavakarmaSAlAM yatrA<BR>''sate te kurupravIrAH#}; 3.17171.: {#yodDum ASaMsate nityam<BR>PAlgunena#}.<BR>2) sperare. BR. 1.29.: {#yayA dOhitrajA~l<BR>lokAn ASaMse#}; MAH. 3.13647.: {#ASaMsate hi<BR>putrezu pitA…yaSaH#}. Cum dat. MAH. 1.148.: {#nA ''SaMse<BR>vijayAya#}. Cum infin. R. Schl. II.12.70.: {#na…ciraY<BR>jIvitum ASaMse#}. ATM. DR. 5.5.: जेतुम् आशंससि<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=341-b" target="_blank">Page341-b+ 36</a>]<BR>धर्मराजम्.<BR>3) credere, putare, c. यदि. R. Schl. II.51.14.:<BR>{#kOSalyAcE 'va rAjAca taTE 'va jananI mama nA<BR>''SaMse yadi jIvanti#}; II.86.15.: {#nA ''SaMse yadi te<BR>sarve jIveyuH#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=341-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शंसिन्<BR>शंसिन् (r. शंस् s. इन्) dicens, indicans, nuntians. UR. 69.15.<BR>SAK. 46.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=341-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शंस्त्<BR>शंस्त् 2. P. (scribitur शस्त्) dormire. Vid. 2. शस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=341-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शक्<BR>शक् 5. P. et 4. P. A. posse, valere. H. 1.6.: {#gantuYcE 'va<BR>na SaknumaH#}; R. Schl. I.20.4.: {#na hi Saknoti…samAptuN<BR>kratum#}; BR. 1.24.: {#na hi SakzyAmi kiYcana parityaktum<BR>aham banDum#}; 27.: {#parityaktun na SakyAmi<BR>BAryAm#}; 28.: कुत एव परित्यक्तुं सुतं शक्यामि; N. 11.6.:<BR>शक्यसे ता गिरः सत्याः कर्तुम् मयि; A. 3.31.: {#nacE<BR>'nam aSakaM hantum#}. Cum locat. abstracti in अन<BR>loco infin. R. Schl. I.66.19.: न शेकुर् ग्रहणे तस्य धनुषः;<BR>N. 7.10.: {#suhfdAn na tu kaScana nivAraRe 'Bavac<BR>Cakto dIvyamAnam#}. Participia in त sunt शक्त et<BR>शकित, quorum prius active cum sgf. potens, alterum<BR>passive usurpatur. BR. 2.8. N. 7.10. H. 4.33. — Pass.<BR>impers. MAH. 1.6678.: स्थीयतां यदि शक्यते. — Notetur<BR>Passivi usus in constructione cum Infin., quippe<BR>qui passivâ formâ careat, ita ut passivam vim verbo auxiliari<BR>exprimere necesse sit. Dicitur e. c. ना ऽऽहर्तुं शक्यते<BR>(N. 20.5.) quasi latine dicas afferre nequitur<BR>ad exprimendum non afferri potest. Part. fut. pass.<BR>शक्य saepissime in hujusmodi constructionibus invenitur,<BR>e. c. IN. 1.17. 2.4. H. 1.35. 47. Etiam part. praet.<BR>शकित. H. 4.33.: {#apanetuYca yatito nacE 'va Sakito<BR>mayA#}. Dicitur etiam शक्य pro जेतुं शक्य qui vinci potest,<BR>vincendus. DR. 5.12. — Desid. शिक्ष् correptum e<BR>शिशक्ष्, v. gr. 552. (V. शिक्ष् et cf. hib. ceach-t «power,<BR>eminence» = शक्ति, v. Pictet p. 63. Fortasse lat. co-nâri<BR>e coc-na-ri, ita ut ना respondeat characteri nonae<BR>classis et graeco νη in verbis ut δάμ-νη-μι; queo; cf. nequi-nont<BR>apud Fest. cum शक्-नुवन्ति; island. vet. hag-r<BR>dexter, hagna prodesse, hoegja moderare (Grimm. II.12. n. 96.);<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">Page342-a+ 37</a>]<BR>gr. ϰίϰυς; v. Pott. I.232. Benfey II.160.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=341-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकट|शकटं|शकटः<BR>शकट m. n. currus. HIT. 24.8.: शकटम् (nom.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकटार<BR>शकटार etiam शकटाल nom. pr. (Wils. «the minister of<BR>Nanda»). HIT. 61.20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकल|शकलं|शकलः<BR>शकल m. n. pars, portio, frustum. RAGH. 2.46.: शकलानि.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकन्<BR>शकन् v. शकृत्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकुन|शकुनं|शकुनः<BR>शकुन m. (fortasse a r. शक् s. unâd. उन)<BR>1) avis species<BR>(Wils.: either the Indian vulture or the common kite-<BR>Falco cheela-; it is also applied to the Pondicherry eagle).<BR>N. 9.12.<BR>2) avis in universum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकुनि|शकुनिः<BR>शकुनि<BR>1) i. q. praec. MAH. 3.10437.<BR>2) nom. pr. IN. 1.4.<BR>(Cf. lat. ciconia.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकृत्<BR>शकृत् n. (शकन् v. gr. 205.; fortasse forma redupl. cum {#Sa<BR>= ka#}, a r. कृत्) excrementum, stercus. (Fortasse gr.<BR>ϰόπϱος e ϰόϰϱος, lat. stercus, stercor-is fortasse per metath.<BR>e secort-is = शकृतस् e शकर्तस्; hib. seachraith<BR>«filth, dirt», cac «animal excrement», cacah «dirty,<BR>filthy», cacaim «I go to stool», lat. caco, gr. ϰαϰϰάω.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शक्ति|शक्तिः<BR>शक्ति f. (r. शक् posse s. ति)<BR>1) potestas, facultas, vis. SA. 2.17. 5.4.<BR>2) lancea ferrea. IN. 1.4. (Hib. ceach-t, v. r.<BR>शक्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शक्तु|शक्तुः<BR>शक्तु m. n. farina. (Wils.: According to some authorities<BR>only m. pl. (शक्तवः). The powder or flour of barley<BR>and other grain, first fried and then ground). HIT. 114.22.:<BR>शक्तुभूतः शारवः; 115.2. 7.: शक्तुशारव.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शक्य|शक्यः<BR>शक्य (part. fut. pass. r. शक्) possibilis. V. शक्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शक्र|शक्रः<BR>शक्र m. (ut videtur, a r. शक् posse s. र) cognomen Indri.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शङ्क्|शंक्<BR>शङ्क् 1. A. (scribitur शक्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>1) suspicari, opinari.<BR>N. 23.1.: शङ्कमाना नलन् तम्; 23.28.: {#tvAY<BR>janaH SaNketa dozataH#}; H. 3.15.: ताम्…पुंस्कामां शङ्कमानः.<BR>2) timere. N. 9.31.: किमर्थम् भीरु शङ्कसे. - शङ्कित<BR>suspicans, timens. N. 12.32. IN. 5.18. (शङ्क्<BR>primitive possibile habere significaverit; a शक् posse<BR>insertâ nasali; cf. goth. hugjan cogitare, opinari, putare,<BR>germ. vet. hugu animus, intellectus, sensus, hugjan<BR>cogitare, recordari, considerare.)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">Page342-b+ 37</a>]<BR>c. अभि dubitare. M. 34.: ना ऽभिशङ्क्यम् इदञ्चा ऽपि वचनम्.<BR>c. आ P. A. timere. MAN. 7.188.: {#yataSca Bayam ASaNket<BR>tato vistArayed balam#}; R. Schl. I.90.15.: {#matto<BR>na dozam ASaNkIH#}; I.1.39.: आशङ्कमानश्च पुनः पौरजानपदागमम्;<BR>N. 13.30.: आशङ्कमाना तत् पापम्.<BR>— आशङ्कित metutus. R. Schl. I.65.15.: {#yat tad ASaNkitam<BR>pApam#}.<BR>c. परि suspicari. N. 24.26.: {#na mAm arhasi kalyAna<BR>dozeRa pariSaNkitum#}.<BR>c. वि dubitare. MAH. 1.2966.: {#gAnDarvarAkzasO (vivAhO)<BR>kzatre DarmyO tO mA viSaNkiTAH#} (pro विशङ्किष्ठास् praet.<BR>mltf. 3., sic. MAH. 3. 10356: पर्यशाङ्किथाम् - sic legendum<BR>pro ॰था - pro ॰ष्ठाम्.)<BR>c. सम् suspicari. MAH. 4.568.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शङ्कर|शंकर|शङ्करः<BR>शङ्कर m. cognomen Sivi.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शङ्का|शंका<BR>शङ्का f. (r. शङ्क् s. आ)<BR>1) suspicio, conjectura. N. 24.3.<BR>SA. 6.4.<BR>2) dubitatio. N. 24.39.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

