शङ्किन्|शंकिन्<BR>शङ्किन् (r. शङ्क् s. इन्) suspicans. UR. 80.1.infra.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शङ्कु|शंकु|शंकुः|शङ्कुः<BR>शङ्कु m. (r. शङ्क् s. उ)<BR>1) timor.<BR>2) acus.<BR>3) palus,<BR>stipes.<BR>4) jaculum, pilum.<BR>6) piscis species (Wils.: the<BR>scate fish).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शङ्कुकर्ण|शंकुकर्ण|शङ्कुकर्णः<BR>शङ्कुकर्ण (BAH. e praec. et कर्ण auris)<BR>1) Adj. jaculo vel<BR>palo similes aures habens. H. 2.4.<BR>2) Subst. m. asinus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शङ्ख|शंख|शंखं|शंखः|शङ्खः<BR>शङ्ख m. n. concha. BH. 1.12.: शङ्खम् acc., 13.: शङ्खाः nom. pl.<BR>m. (Gr. ϰόγχος, ϰόγχη, lat. concha; fortasse hib.<BR>slige, sligean id. per metath. e silge, mutatis liquidis n et<BR>l, v. gr. comp. 20.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शच्<BR>शच् 1. A. (व्यक्तायां वाचि K. वाचि V.) loqui, distincte<BR>loqui. Cf. 1. शुच्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

