शट्<BR>1. शट् 1. P. (रुजाविशरणगत्यवसादनेषु K. {#sAde SIrRe<BR>gatO ruji#} V.) aegrotare, diffringi, ire, perire, considere,<BR>tabescere. Cf. शण्ड्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=342-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शट्<BR>2. शट् 10. A. शाटये. (श्लाघे) laudare. Cf. 3. शठ्, शाड्,<BR>3. शल्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शठ्<BR>1. शठ् 1. P. (कैतवे K. वधक्लेशकैतवे V.) fallere, decipere,<BR>laedere, occidere, vexare. V. शठ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शठ्<BR>2. शठ् 10. P. शाठयामि (संस्कारगत्योः K. आलस्ये गत्यसंस्कृतसंस्कृते<BR>V.) ornatum esse, ire, pigrum esse, inornatum<BR>esse. Cf. शुठ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शठ्<BR>3. शठ् 10. A. i. q. 2. शट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शठ|शठं|शठः<BR>शठ (r. 1. शठ् s. अ) falsus, fallax, pravus. HIT. 67.10.: {#SaWam<BR>mitram#}. (Hib. sath «evil», saith «vulgar, vile,<BR>despicable, ill».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

