शण|शणं|शणः<BR>शण n. cannabis. (Cf. gr. ϰάνναβις, lat. cannabis, lith.<BR>kanápế, russ. konopla, hib. canaib, island. vet. hanp,<BR>anglo-sax. hœnep, germ. vet. hanaf.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शण्ड्|शंड्<BR>शण्ड् 1. A. (रुजायाम् K. सङ्घरुजोः V.; scribitur शड्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>aegrotare, colligere, coacervare. Cf. 1. शट्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शण्ढ|शंढ|शंढः|शण्ढः<BR>शण्ढ m. eunuchus. AM. Scribitur etiam षण्ढ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शत|शतं<BR>शत n. (ut mihi videtur, mutilatum e दशत a दशन् decem,<BR>v. gr. comp. 320. annot.) centum. शत m. nisi शता f.<BR>N. 15.5.: शतं शताः. (Lat. centum, gr. ἑ-ϰατόν - ἑ pro<BR>ἕν unum -, lith. szimta-s masc., slav. sto neut., hib. céat,<BR>cambro-brit. cant, armor. kant.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

