शतघ्नी<BR>शतघ्नी f. (centenos occidens e शत centum et घ्नी<BR>Fem. vocis घ्न occidens) teli species. A. 6.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

