शत्रुतस्<BR>शत्रुतस् Adv. (e शत्रु s. तस्) ab hoste vel hostibus (v. gr. 652.).<BR>N. 14.18.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शद्<BR>1. शद् 1. P. (गतौ; nonnisi cum आ occurrere dicitur) ire.<BR>Caus. ducere, popellere. PAN. VII.3.42.: {#gAH SAdayati<BR>gopAlaH#}. (Cf. पद्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शद्<BR>2. शद् in tempp. spec. A. in ceteris P. (a grammaticis refertur<BR>ad cl. 1. et 6., sequitur autem normam classis<BR>4., ita tamen ut anomale conson. fin. ante syllabam य<BR>abjiciatur et अ producatur in ई, quod ex आ ortum esse<BR>censeo in analogiâ cum Passivis ut दोयते datur pro दायते<BR>- v. gr. 494. - ita शीयते pro शायते. Quod attinet<BR>ad omissam radicis litteram finalem, शीयते convenit<BR>cum जायते nascitur pro जन्यते, gr. 332. Vera radicis<BR>forma शत् esse videtur, unde Caus. शातयामि e generali<BR>reg. explicari posset; cf. etiam nomen abstractum<BR>शातन apud Wils., quod non a शो sed a शत् deduxerim;<BR>ita शात quo radix शद् a Vôp. explicatur) cadere, perire.<BR>BHATT. 17.77.: अशीयत नृमांसादाम् बलं सुग्रीववाधितम्<BR>(schol. JAY. अवसन्नम्, BHAR. {#avasAdam<BR>prAptam#}). — Caus. शातयामि (gr. 524.) facere ut alq.<BR>cadat, caedere. R. Schl. I.66.10.: {#varANgAni mahArhARi<BR>DanuzA SAtayAmi vaH#}; II.43.16. 96.52. N. 20.13.: {#SAtayitvA<BR>viBItakam#}; 14.: शातयिष्ये विभीतकम्;<BR>23.: शातयामास तन् द्रुमम्. (Cf. पद्, पत्, lat. cado.)<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">Page344-a+ 37</a>]<BR>c. प्र Caus. facere ut alq. cadat. MAH. 1.5561.: {#AnAmya<BR>PalitAM SAKAm pakvam pakvam praSAtayet#}.<BR>c. वि Caus. discutere, disjicere. MAH. 3.11971.<BR>c. सम् Caus. facere ut alq. cadat. MAH. 3.865.: {#vajram<BR>udyamya tAn sarvAn parvatAn samaSAtayam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=343-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शनकैस्<BR>शनकैस् Adv. (Instr. pl. ab inusitato शनक, quod derivatur<BR>a शन - v. शनैस् - suff. क) lente, tarde, paulatim,<BR>gradatim. N. 17.13.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शनैस्<BR>शनैस् Adv. (Instr. ab inusitato शन) lente, tarde. IN. 2.24.<BR>H. 2.22. 4.26. SU. 4.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शप्<BR>1. शप् 1. P. A.<BR>1) A. jurare. MAN. 8.110.: {#vaSizWaScA 'pi<BR>SapaTaM Sepe pEyavane nfpe#} (Loc. pro Dat.); R. Schl. II.75.40.:<BR>{#SapaTEH kazwEH SapamAnam…Baratam…kOSalyA<BR>vAkyam abravIt#}. Cum instr. rei vel pers. per<BR>quam quis jurat. GHAT. 22.; R. Schl. II.21.16.: {#satyena<BR>DanuzAcE 'va dattene 'zwena te Sape#}; II.11.8.: {#tena rAmeRa<BR>kEkeyi Sape te vacanakriyAm#}; 34.47. 48.21. MAH. 1.5178.<BR>2) P. A. maledicere, exsecrari. IN. 5.48.: {#SaSApA<BR>'Ta DanaYjayam#}; N. 20.34.: कुपिता मा ऽशपत्; MAH. 1.4583.:<BR>तस्मात् त्वाम् अप्य् अहं शपे; 3.351.: {#putran<BR>te Sapsyate#}. — Absol. R. Schl. I.58.8.: {#SepuH paramasaNkrudDAS<BR>caRqAlatvaN gamizyasi#}. — Caus. शापयामि<BR>jurare jubeo. MAN. 8.113. (Fortasse शप् primitive<BR>dicere, loqui significavit, cf. शब्द sonus, quod fortasse<BR>e शप् + द dans; hib. cubhais «an oath», cubhas<BR>«a word, a promise», cab «a mouth».)<BR>c. अभि maledicere, exsecrari. R. Schl. II.49.48.: {#tvAm<BR>aBiSapsye 'haM suduHKam atidAruRam#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शप्<BR>2. शप् 4. P. A. i. q. 1. शप्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शपथ|शपथः<BR>शपथ m. (r. शप् s. अथ) jusjurandum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शफ|शफं|शफः<BR>शफ n. ungula equi. AM. (Germ. vet. huof, island. vet. et<BR>anglo-sax. hôf.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शफर|शफरः<BR>शफर m. शफरी f. piscis species. (Wils. a sort of carp,<BR>Cyprinus chrysoparius). AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शब्द्<BR>शब्द् 10. P. शब्दयामि (ut videtur, Denom. a seq.) dicere.<BR>MAH. 3.14400.: {#zaRRAn tu pravaran tasya SIrzARAm<BR>iha Sabdyate#}. — Caus. शब्दापयामि facio ut quis vocetur, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-b" target="_blank">Page344-b+ 37</a>]<BR>advocetur, arcesso. R. Schl. II.59.7.: {#yadi mAM rAmaH<BR>punaH SabdApayet#}. (V. शप् et cf. Caus. r. दा, दापयामि,<BR>cf. etiam जीवापयामि p. 140. annot.)<BR>c. अभि dicere. MAN. 6.82.: यद् एतद् अभिशब्दितम्.<BR>Nominare. MAH. 1.3927.: {#dakzasya duhitA yA tu suraBI<BR>'ty aBiSabditA#}.<BR>c. सम् dicere, loqui. MAH. 1.3215.: अयम् एती ऽति संशब्द्य.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शब्द|शब्दः<BR>शब्द m. sonus, clamor, strepitus. H. 4.21. BR. 1.3. SU. 1.32.<BR>(Vid. शप्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शम्<BR>1. शम् 4. P. शाम्यामि (gr. 331^a).) sedari, tranquillari, placari,<BR>extingui. GITA-GOV. 7.41.: शाम्यतु देहदाहः;<BR>RAGH. 2.14.: शशाम वृष्द्या ऽपि विना दवाग्निः;<BR>MAN. 2.94.: {#na jAtu kAmaH kAmAnAm upaBogena<BR>SAmyati#}; MAH. 2.1936.: शाम्य मा शुचः; RAGH. 7.3.:<BR>समत्सरो ऽपि शशाम तेन क्षितिपाललोकः. — शान्त<BR>1) sedatus, pacatus, tranquillus, placidus. H. 1.49.: {#SAntArcir<BR>iva pAvakaH#}; HIT. 80.21.: शान्ते पानीयतोये;<BR>N. 12.112.: सुशान्ततोयाम्…ह्रदिनीम्; 24.53.:<BR>शान्तज्वरा; SA. 6.18.: शान्तायान् दिशि.<BR>2) interfectus<BR>(v. Caus.). MAH. 1.7523.: दिष्ट्या शान्तः पुरोचनः.<BR>— Caus. शमयामि<BR>1) sedare, tranquillare, domare,<BR>extinguere. MAH. 3.72.: {#mAnasaM (duHKam) Samayet<BR>tasmAj jYAnenA 'gnim ivA 'mbunA#}; HIT. 24.6.: {#sutaptam<BR>api pAnIyaM Samayaty eva pAvakam#}.<BR>2) occidere,<BR>interficere. MAH. 3.14620.: {#so 'yan tvayA mahAbAho<BR>Samito deva kaRwakaH#}. (Hib. samh «pleasant,<BR>still, calm, tranquil»; lith. kenćiu, kentếju patior, tolero,<BR>kanćia dolor, kantrùs patiens, tolerans, pa-kintu patientiam<BR>adhibeo, v. शान्ति; fortasse nostrum san-f-t, inserto<BR>f, - v. gr. comp. 96. - mutatà gutturali in sib.; germ.<BR>vet. samft, angl. soft, fortasse etiam germ. vet. sûmjan<BR>tardare (nostrum säumen), sûmig negligens; island. vet.<BR>sems tardatio; gr. ϰηλέω. Cf. क्षम्.)<BR>c. उप i. q. simpl. MAH. 3.72. et 1008.: {#no 'paSAmyati me<BR>manaH#}. — Caus. उपशामयामि<BR>1) sedare, tranquillare.<BR>MAH. 1.6577.: पुष्पायुधम्…उपशामय कल्याणि आत्मदानेन.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=345-a" target="_blank">Page345-a+ 37</a>]<BR>2) occidere, interficere. MAH. 3.8541.: {#agastyene<BR>'ha vAtApiH kimarTam upaSAmitaH#}.<BR>c. नि Caus. निशामयमि<BR>1) videre, conspicere. R. Schl. I.2.6.:<BR>अकर्दमम् इदन् तीर्थन् निशामय. Gerund.<BR>निशाम्य et निशम्य (v. Caus. rad. simpl. शमयामि);<BR>R. Schl. I.69.18.: राघवौ पुत्रौ निशाम्य; II.46.18.: {#prakftIs<BR>tA niSAmya#}; MAH. 1.1137.: {#niSAmya te duHKam<BR>idam#}; N. 26.6.: निशम्या ऽथ हयज्ञस्य लिङ्गानि; A. 10.57. 58.:<BR>रौद्रास्त्रनिष्पिष्टान्…निशम्य; R. Schl. II.52.14.:<BR>सरथम् मान् निशम्यै ऽकम्.<BR>2) audire. R. Schl. II.57.21.:<BR>तद् वाक्यं राजस्त्रीणान् निशामयन्.<BR>Gerund. निशम्य. BR. 3.1.: तयोर् दुःखितयोर् वाक्यम्…निशम्य;<BR>R. Schl. I.2.17. II.44.25. 52.4. 66.10. RAGH. 2.61.<BR>c. नि praef. वि Caus. audire. Gerund. विनिशम्य. IN. 5.62.<BR>c. नि praef. सम् Caus. id. MAH. 2.1658. सन्निशम्य.<BR>c. परि Caus. परिशमयामि sedare. GITA-GOV. 7.20.: परिशमितम्.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. R. Schl. II.40.33.: {#pOrajanASruBir aByavahitam<BR>praSaSAma mahIrajaH#}; MAH. 2.1944.: प्रशाम्य भरतर्षभ. — प्रशान्त<BR>sedatus. N. 26.34. A. 9.34. — Caus.<BR>प्रशमयामि<BR>1) sedare, tranquillare, extinguere.<BR>MAH. 3.12978.: {#pravizwo mAnuzan dehaM sarvam praSamayAmy<BR>aham#}; MAH. 1.8156.: प्रशमितः खाण्डवे हव्यवाहनः.<BR>Interficere, occidere. MAH. 3.2031. Expugnare.<BR>A. 9.35.: प्रशाम्य नगरम् (productâ vocali, v.<BR>praef. उप et नि).<BR>c. सम् i. q. simpl. R. Schl. II.66.1.: {#tam agnim iva<BR>saMSAntam#}. Caus. sedare, tranquillare. R. Schl. II.98.1.:<BR>लक्ष्मणङ् क्रोधमूर्छितं रामः संशमयामास.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=344-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शम्<BR>2. शम् 10. P. A. शामयामि, ॰ये (आलोचने K. आलोचे V.;<BR>proprie Caus. r. 1. शम्, v. praef. नि) videre, conspicere.<BR>(Cf. goth. gaumja observo, video.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=345-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

