शरासन|शरासनं<BR>शरासन n. (sagittarum conjectionem habens e शर<BR>sagitta et असन conjectio) arcus. A. 5.25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=345-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

