शरीरिन्<BR>शरीरिन् m. (corpus habens, i. e. inhabitans, a praec.<BR>s. इन्) anima. BH. 2.18. (cf. देहिन्).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=345-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शर्करा<BR>शर्करा f.<BR>1) glarea.<BR>2) saccharum; Wils.: «Clayed or candied<BR>sugar». (Cf. χάλιξ, σάϰχαϱ, σάϰχαϱον; lat.<BR>calx, calculus, saccharum.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=345-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

