शि|शिः<BR>शि 5. P. A. acuere. In dial. Vêd. cl. 3. productâ vocali.<BR>1) acuere. RIGV. 55.1.: शिशीते वज्रन् तेजसे; 81.7.:<BR>शिशीहि राय आभर «alacres redde nos, opes affer nobis».<BR>Part. pass. शित (निशित संशित) tam huc quam ad<BR>शो referri potest; a Pân. (VII.4.41.) refertur ad शो q. v.<BR>c. सम् In dial. Vêd. excitare, incitare. RIGV. 102.10.:<BR>त्वाम् उग्रम् अवसे संशिशीमसि «te horrendum ad<BR>opem nobis ferendam excitamus».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=348-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शिक्ष्<BR>शिक्ष् 1. A. interdum P. (nihil aliud quam Desid. radicis<BR>शक्, v. gr. 552.) discere. MAN. 2.20.: {#svaM svaY<BR>caritraM Sikzeran#}; MAH. 1.6326.: {#kaTan droRAt…sarvAstrARy<BR>aSikzata#}; A. 4.29.: {#Sikza me BavanaN gatvA<BR>sarvARy astrARi#}. Part. praes. A. शिक्षाण pro शिक्षमाण.<BR>A. 4.57. (v. gramm. min. ed. 2. 533.n.). — Caus.<BR>docere c. 2. acc. MAH. 1.5238.: {#droRo 'rjunam…raRaSikzAm<BR>aSikzayat#}. Pass. c. acc. rei. IN. 3.11.: {#sa<BR>Sikzito nftyaguRAn#}.<BR>c. अनु Caus. docere. MAH. 1.5761.<BR>c. अभि Caus. id. MAH. 1.8033.<BR>c. उप discere. IN. 3.3. N. 21.33. A. 1.12.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=348-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

