शिरस्<BR>शिरस् n. caput. IN. 2.19. 5.20. (Fortasse शिरस् e शरस्,<BR>debilitato अ in इ sicut in पितृ q. v.; cf. gr. ϰάϱα, ϰέϱας, ϰϱανίον;<BR>lat. cranium, cere-brum, quod capite<BR>fertur, mutato f in b, v. gr. comp. 18., cer-vix, v. {#SiroDarA,<BR>SiroDi#}; crinis, v. शिरसिज, केश; शिरोरुह, cornu,<BR>v. शृङ्ग; fortasse crista primitive in capite stans, ita<BR>ut cri-sta = शिरःस्थ; fortasse calva e carva; goth.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=349-a" target="_blank">Page349-a+ 36</a>]<BR>hvairnei calva, haurn cornu; germ. vet. hirni cerebrum,<BR>horn cornu; lith. karcźei m. pl. jubae equorum, szerai<BR>m. pl. setae; hib. ceann caput, fortasse per assim. e cearn.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=348-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शिरसिज|शिरसिजः<BR>शिरसिज m. (in capite natus e loc. शिरसि et ज) capillus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=349-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शिरोधरा<BR>शिरोधरा f. (e शिरस् et धर ferens in fem.) cervix. HEM.;<BR>v. sq. (Sic lat. cer-vix explicari potest e cer = शिरस्<BR>et vic-s a vincio, ejectâ nasali, sicut in conjux a conjungo.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=349-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शिरोधि|शिरोधिः<BR>शिरोधि m. (e शिरस् et धि tenens, sustentans, a r. धा s. इ)<BR>cervix. AM.; v. praec.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=349-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शिरोरुह|शिरोरुहः<BR>शिरोरुह m. (in capite crescens, e शिरस् et रुह crescens,<BR>v. euph. r. 76^b).) capillus. H. 2.6.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=349-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

