शिष्य|शिष्यः<BR>शिष्य (r. शास् s. य) Part. fut. pass. r. शास्. Subst. m.<BR>discipulus.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=350-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शी<BR>शी 2. A. (anom. v. gr. 348. 496. 572.)<BR>1) jacere. MAH. 4.826.:<BR>{#paYcADikaM Satan tacca nihatan tatra BArata .<BR>mahAvanam iva cCinnaM SiSye#}; R. Schl. II.9.18.: {#SezvA<BR>'nantarhitAyAn tvam BUmO#}; N. 12.27.: {#SayAnam upavizwaM<BR>vA sTitaM vA#}; 14.3.: {#dadarSa nAgarAjAnaM SayAnaN<BR>kuRqalIkftam#}. Etiam P. MAH. 5.63.: {#nihatA vA<BR>mayA sarve Sezyanti vasuDAtale#}. Etiam cl. 1. P. MAH. 3.1215.:<BR>शयेत्.<BR>2) dormire. H. 1.34.: {#se 'yam BUmO pariSrAntA<BR>Sete#}; 1.36. 37.; 2.11.: {#gacCa jAnIhi ke nv<BR>ete Serate vanam ASritAH#}; 17.: {#dadarSa…pARqavAn<BR>pfTayA saha SayAnAn BImasenan tu jAgratam#}. — शयित<BR>jacens, dormiens. MAH. 1.2949. — Caus. शाययामि<BR>pono. R. Schl. II.66.16.: {#tEladroRyAn tu sacivEH<BR>SAyitan narADipam#}. (Gr. ϰεῖμαι, ϰεῖσαι =<BR>शेषे, ϰεῖται = शेते, ϰοῖ-τη, ϰῶ-μα, ϰώ-μη; lat.<BR>quies, quiesco; goth. hê-thjô cubiculum, hei-wa domus in<BR>comp. heiva-frauja; island. vet. hei-mr domus; german.<BR>vet. hai-m, hei-m; angl. home, v. Graff III.944. et 705.;<BR>germ. vet. hi-wo conjux, maritus, hi-wa uxor, hijan, hiwjan<BR>nubere, Graff III.1063. (cf. gr. ἄϰοιτις, ἀϰοίτης),<BR>hî-rât connubium, nostrum Heirath; lith. szế-tra tugurium,<BR>kiế-ma vicus.)<BR>c. अति<BR>1) dormiendo aliquem superare, antecellere, plus<BR>quam alius dormire, c. acc. MAH. 3.14686.: {#aham patIn<BR>nA 'tiSaye nA 'tyaSne nA 'tiBUzaye#}.<BR>2) superare<BR>in universum. RAGH. 5.14.: पूर्वान् महाभाग तया ऽतिशेषे;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=350-b" target="_blank">Page350-b+ 36</a>]<BR>BHATT. 8.1.: अत्यशेरत तद्वेगन् न सुपर्णार्कमारुताः.<BR>c. अधि<BR>1) incubare, c. acc. loci. R. Schl. II.88.12.: {#IdfSIM<BR>rAGavaH SayyAm aDiSete#}.<BR>2) indormire, c. acc. loci.<BR>RAGH. 5.28.: अधिशिश्ये…प्रदोषे रथं रघुः.<BR>c. प्रति exadversum cubare vel dormire. MAH. 3.16300.:<BR>प्रतिशिश्ये जलनिधिन् विधिवत् कुशसंस्तरे. Etiam<BR>P. MAH. 3.16398.: प्रतिशेष्यामि.<BR>c. सम् dubitare. HIT. 116.2.: न हि संशयितुङ् कुर्यात्<BR>(nisi legendum संशयितम्). Vid. संशय, संशयित.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=350-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शीक्<BR>1. शीक् 1. A. (सेचने K. सेके सर्पे V.) humectare, irrigare,<BR>ire. Vid. सीक्, सेक् et cf. सिच्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=350-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

