शुच्<BR>1. शुच् 1. P. interdum A. dolere, moerere, lugere, miserari<BR>(Praet. mltf. अशोचिषम् et अशुचम्). N. 12.73.:<BR>समाश्वसिहि मा शुचः; BH. 16.5.: मा शुचः. C. acc.<BR>N. 8.24.: शोचन् नलन् नृपम्; 11.11.: {#na SocAmy aham<BR>AtmAnam…kaTan tuBavitAsy eka iti tvAn<BR>nfpa Socimi#} (शोचिमि pro शोचामि, ut videtur, metri<BR>causâ, cf. रोदिमि etc. gr. 354.); 11.22.; 15.12.: {#kAm<BR>enAM Socase nityam#}. — Caus.<BR>1) moerore afficere.<BR>MAH. 4.581.: शोचयति माम्.<BR>2) i. q. primit. MAH. 1.5649.:<BR>शोचयन् प्रेतकार्याणि चकार. (Cf. 2. {#kuc, ku,<BR>Ku#}, gr. ϰωϰύω, lith. kauk-iu ululo; fortasse hib. caoine<BR>«cry or lamentation for the dead, bewailing, mourning»<BR>= शोचन.)<BR>c. अनु lugere, miserari. N. 15.12. BH. 2.11. 25. — Caus.<BR>id. MAH. 2.9524.<BR>c. परि i. q. simpl. MAH. 1.4025. 3.13656.<BR>c. प्र praef. अनु id. MAH. 1.3229.: {#mE 'vaM Suco mA ruda<BR>devayAni na tvAdfSI martyam anupraSocate#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=351-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शुच्<BR>2. शुच् 4. P. A. lucere. In dial. Vêd. cl. 1. RIGV. 36.9.:<BR>शोचस्व…अग्ने.<BR>c. अप in dial. Vêd. Intens. extingui. RIGV. 97.1.: {#apa<BR>naH SoSucad aGam#}.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=351-b" target="_blank">Page351-b+ 36</a>]<BR>c. आ in dial. Vêd. collustrare. RIGV. 97.1.: {#SuSugDy A<BR>rayim#} (v. gr. min. ed. 2. 389^b).).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=351-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शुचि|शुचिः<BR>शुचि (r. 2. शुच् s. इ)<BR>1) purus, albus. IN. 5.62.<BR>2) m. planeta<BR>Venus aut ejus moderator.<BR>3) m. nomen mensis<BR>(Maius-Junius). H. 1.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=351-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

