शुन्ध्|शुंध्<BR>शुन्ध् 1. et 10. P. A. in dial. Vêd. 1. et 10. P. purificare. 1. A.<BR>purificari. (Cf. शुध् et v. Westerg.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=352-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शुभ्<BR>1. शुभ् 1. A. interdum P. splendere. N. 16.19.: {#ezA hi rahitA<BR>tena SoBamAnA na SoBate#}; IN. 5.12.: {#gUQagulPaDarO<BR>pAdO…SoBete kiNkiRIkinO#}; MAH. 1.7137.:<BR>त्वयै ऽव शोभिष्यति राजपुत्री; 4.498.: {#SuSuBe vadanan<BR>tasyA rudantyAH#}. — Caus.<BR>1) facere ut quid splendeat,<BR>collustrare. IN. 2.27.: {#SoBayAYcakratuH saBAM sUryacandramasO<BR>vyoma…iva#}.<BR>2) ornare. N. 25.6.: {#aSoBayanta<BR>nagaram#}; IN. 5.9. 10. (Vid. {#SumB, sumB,<BR>simB#} et cf. शुध्; gr. ϰομψός, ϰομ-μός, ϰομέω; germ.<BR>vet. sûbar purus, v. शुभ्रः lith. źibbu luceo, nisi pertinet<BR>ad दीप्.)<BR>c. उप Caus. ornare. IN. 2.1. N. 12.40.<BR>c. वि splendere. HIT. 55.22.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=352-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

