श्यै<BR>श्यै 1. A. (गतौ) ire. Part. pass. शीन coagulatus. शीत<BR>frigidus. PAN. VIII.2.47.<BR>c. आ siccari, arescere. RAGH. 17.37.: {#yAvan nA ''SyAyate<BR>vedir aBizekajalAplutA#}. Part. pass. आश्यान siccatus. [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=355-a" target="_blank">Page355-a+ 35</a>]<BR>RAGH. 4.24.: सरितो कुर्वती गाधाः पथश्चा ऽऽश्यानकर्दमान्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=354-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

