श्रङ्ग्|श्रंग्<BR>श्रङ्ग् 1. P. (व्रजे; scribitur श्रग्) ire. Cf. {#SlaNg, SvaNg,<BR>SraNk, SlaNk, Sri#}, germ. vet. slange serpens, slenga<BR>funda.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=355-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

