श्रथ्<BR>1. श्रथ् 1. et 10. P. (बन्धने K. बन्धे मोक्षे वधे V.) ligare,<BR>nectere, solvere, occidere. Cf. {#granT, SranT, SlaT,<BR>SnaT#}, lat. crâtes, rete, res-tis e ret-tis, v. Ag. Benary<BR>p. 222. et. 262.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=355-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

