श्रन्थ्|श्रंथ्<BR>1. श्रन्थ् 1. A. (शैथिल्ये; scribitur श्रथ्) laxum, solutum<BR>esse. Cf. श्रथ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=355-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

श्रन्थ्|श्रंथ्<BR>2. श्रन्थ् 1. et 10. P. (सन्दर्भे K. दर्भे वधे V.) jungere, nectere,<BR>serere; occidere. Cf. 2. ग्रन्थ्, 1. श्रथ्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=355-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

