श्री<BR>2. श्री f.<BR>1) dea Lakschmia, Vischnûs uxor. N. 1.13.<BR>2) fortuna, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=357-a" target="_blank">Page357-a+ 37</a>]<BR>felicitas. SU. 2.10. BH. 10.34.<BR>3) pulchritudo, gratia,<BR>venustas. IN. 4.7. N. 3.11.<BR>4) reverentiae causâ nominibus<BR>personarum vel rerum venerandarum anteponitur,<BR>e. c. श्रीगणेश quasi sanctus Ganêsus vel summe<BR>venerandus Ganêsus, श्रीमहाभारत summe venerandum<BR>Mahâ-Bhâratum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=356-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

