ष्ठिव्<BR>1. ष्ठिव् 1. P. (in tempp. spec. vocalem producit; part. pass.<BR>ष्ठ्यूत, gerund. ष्ठेवित्वा et ष्ठ्यूत्वा) spuere.<BR>(Fortasse ष्ठिव् pro स्थिव् e स्फिव् vel स्पिव्; cf.<BR>germ. vet. SPIW, spiw-i-t spuit = ष्ठीवति, lat. spuo,<BR>correpto iv in u; gr. πτύω per metath. e σπύω, mutato<BR>σ in τ sicut e. c. in ἄϱϰτος, v. ऋक्ष; lith. spjau-ju spuo,<BR>fut. spjau-su.)<BR>c. नि despuere. MAH. 3.11797.: {#nyazWIvad AkASagato<BR>maharzes tasya mUrDani#}; BHATT. 14.100.: {#rAkzasASca nitizWivuH<BR>(raktam)#}. — Part. pass. निष्ठ्यूत. MAN. 4.132.<BR>RAGH. 2.75.<BR>c. नि praef. अव id. MAN. 8.282.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=361-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ष्ठिव्<BR>2. ष्ठिव् 4. P. ष्ठीव्यामि (V. gr. 331^a).) i. q. 1. ष्ठिव्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=361-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ष्ठीव्<BR>ष्ठीव् 1. P. id.<BR>c. नि despuere. MAN. 5.145.: निष्ठीव्य.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=361-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

स|सं|सः<BR>स<BR>1) Stirps nominat. sing. masc. pronominis तत् - v. gr. 266.<BR>- unde Fem. सा.<BR>2) in initio compositorum cum.<BR>H. 1.45. 46. (De pron. स v. p. 147. s. v. 1. तत्, cf.<BR>etiam lat. sum eum, sam eam, sos eos, sapsa = sa ipsa.<BR>Cf. etiam priorem partem graeci σήμεϱον et σῆτες v.<BR>gr. comp. 345. Ad stirpem pronom. स nunc retulerim<BR>etiam partem priorem vocis सम्प्रति nunc, hoc tempore,<BR>ita ut proprie versus hunc vel hoc significet; cf. lat. sem<BR>in sem-per, v. सदा. Cum praep. स cf. lith. praep. insep.<BR>sa, e. c. in sa-darbininkas socius operis, συνεϱγός,<BR>sa-karawis socius pugnae; su tam simpl. quam in comp.<BR>cum, nisi hoc sicut gr. σύν nititur cognatâ formâ सम्<BR>q. v.; slav. с'ъ ś ad स, сᴕ sû autem ad सम् retulerim, v.<BR>gr. comp. 255. g.; gr. σα in σα-ϕής (cf. ϕάος, ϕῶς),<BR>ἀ in compp. ut ἄ-λοχος, ἄ-ϰοιτις, ἀ-ϰοίτης, ἀ-δελϕός,<BR>sicut scr. सोदर e स + उदर; fortasse goth. ga-cum-nostrum<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=361-1b" target="_blank">Page361-1b+ 16</a>]<BR>ge- in compp. ut ga-vaurstva συνεϱγός, ortum<BR>est e स vel सम्, mutatâ sibilante in gutturalem; v.<BR>Grimm II.735. et 1018. Vid. सम्, सह.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=361-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

संयत|संयतः<BR>संयत V. यम् praef. सम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=361-1b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

