सत्य|सत्यं|सत्यः<BR>सत्य (a सत् quod est suff. य, nisi potius a pron. स q. v.<BR>suff. त्य, sicut तत्त्व a तत्)<BR>1) Adj. verus. IN. 4.12.<BR>2) Subst. n. veritas. IN. 5.45. (Cf. gr. ἐτεός.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=365-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

