सत्यसन्ध|सत्यसंध|सत्यसंधः|सत्यसन्धः<BR>सत्यसन्ध Adj. (BAH. e सत्य verus et सन्धा fides, promissum)<BR>qui vera promissa habet, qui stat promissis (cf.<BR>स्थिरसङ्गर). N. 12.56. SA. 1.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=366-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

