सन्तोष|संतोष|संतोषः|सन्तोषः<BR>सन्तोष m. (r. तुष् praef. सम् s. अ) animus contentus,<BR>Zufriedenheit. HIT. 45.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=367-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

