सन्निकर्ष|संनिकर्ष|संनिकर्षः|सन्निकर्षः<BR>सन्निकर्ष m. (r. कृष् c. नि praef. सम् s. अ) propinquitas.<BR>HIT. 8.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सन्निधान|संनिधान|संनिधानं|सन्निधानं<BR>सन्निधान n. (r. धा c. नि praef. सम् s. अन)<BR>1) conjunctio.<BR>HIT. 7.17.<BR>2) propinquitas. HIT. 18.15.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सन्निधि|संनिधि|संनिधिः|सन्निधिः<BR>सन्निधि f. (r. धा ponere c. नि praef. सम् s. इ) propinquitas.<BR>N. 4.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सन्निपात|संनिपात|संनिपातः|सन्निपातः<BR>सन्निपात m. (r. पत् c. नि praef. सम् s. अ)<BR>1) conjunctio,<BR>mixtio.<BR>2) morbus quidam, Wils. «morbid state of<BR>the three humours».<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सन्निभ|संनिभ|सन्निभः<BR>सन्निभ similis (nisi potius Substantivum सन्निभा statuendum,<BR>quod in fine compositorum BAH. ponitur, simplex<BR>autem non conservatum videtur, a rad. भा splendere<BR>praef. सम् + नि) e. c. वसुधाधरसन्निभ montium similitudinem<BR>habens. H. 4.40. काञ्चनसन्निभ auri similitudinem<BR>habens. N. 17.8. vid. etiam N. 12.57. et SA. 5.26.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सन्निहित|संनिहित|सन्निहितं<BR>सन्निहित v. धा c. नि praef. सम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सन्न्यसन|संन्यसन|संन्यसनं<BR>सन्न्यसन n. (r. अस् deponere c. नि praef. सम् s. अन) abdicatio,<BR>renuntiatio. BH. 3.4. (cf. सन्न्यास).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

