सप्<BR>सप् 1. P. sequi (?). RIGV. 67.4.: ऋता सपन्तः «sacra<BR>obeuntes»; 68.2.: सपन्तो अमृतम् एवैः «adeuntes<BR>te immortalem procedentibus hymnis». (Vid. Westerg.<BR>et cf. सच् e सक्, gr. ἕπομαι, goth. sipôneis discipulus.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सपत्न|सपत्नः<BR>सपत्न m. hostis. N. 12.82.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सपदि<BR>सपदि Adv. (fortasse e स cum et पदि loc. vocis पद् pes)<BR>subito. RAGH. 5.75.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सप्तति|सप्ततिः<BR>सप्तति f. (a सप्तन् s. ति pro दशति, v. gr. 227. gr. comp. 320. annot.)<BR>septuaginta.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सप्तन्<BR>सप्तन् septem (gr. 256.; lat. septem a सप्तम septimus, unde<BR>etiam slav. sedmj, Them. sedmi (v. gr. comp. 315.); goth.<BR>sibun; lith. septyni, n. pl. m.; fem. septynios; hib. seacht,<BR>mutatâ lab. in gutt. sicut in lith. sekmas septimus; cambro-brit.<BR>saith, armor. seiz, zend. hapta, gr. ἑπτά.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सप्तपर्ण|सप्तपर्णं|सप्तपर्णः<BR>सप्तपर्ण m. (BAH. e सप्तन् et पर्ण folium) nomen arboris.<BR>Wils. «Echites scholaris». AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सप्तम|सप्तमः<BR>सप्तम (f. ई, a सप्तन् s. म) septimus. (Lat. septimus, lith.<BR>sekma-s pro sepma-s, slav. sedmyĭ, germ. vet. sibunto(n),<BR>hib. seachtmad, zend. 𐬵𐬀𐬞𐬙𐬀𐬚𐬀 haptatha, gr.<BR>ἕβδομος.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सभा<BR>सभा f. (ut videtur, BAH. e स cum et भा lumen)<BR>1) domus.<BR>2) conventus, coetus. HIT. 7.7. 10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सभार्य<BR>सभार्य Adj. (BAH. e स cum et भार्या uxor) cum uxore (v.<BR>gr. 668. not.). BR. 1.11. 2.36. N. 1.3.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सम्<BR>1. सम् 1. et 10. P. समामि, सामयामि (वैक्लव्ये) agitari,<BR>conturbari, vexari. Cf. स्तम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सम्<BR>2. सम् Praep. insep. (ut videtur, acc. stirpis pronom. स<BR>q. v.) cum. (Gr. σύν, ξύν, boruss. vet. sen cum, slav. sû, ś,<BR>vid. स; fortasse lat. cum, goth. ga, nostrum ge in comp.<BR>cum verbis, vid. स; de germ. vet. samant v. समन्त.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सम|समः<BR>सम Adj. (ut mihi videtur, e स cum et म in fine comp. metiens, [<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=369-a" target="_blank">Page369-a+ 37</a>]<BR>a r. मा s. अ, cf. उपमा, समान)<BR>1) similis, aequalis.<BR>H. 1.50. BR. 1.25.; c. Instr. SU. 1.22.<BR>2) aequus, planus<BR>(v. विषम). SU. 4.6.<BR>3) omnis, totus, integer. AM.<BR>(Gr. ὁμός, goth. sama idem, Them. saman, angl. same,<BR>goth. sums quidam, Them. suma, slav. sam ipse; hib.<BR>samhuil «like», samhladh «resemblance, type», samhlaim<BR>«I liken, compare, resemble»; lat. similis.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=368-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

समक्षम्<BR>समक्षम् Adv. (AVY. e सम् et अक्ष oculus, v. gr. 675.) in<BR>conspectu, coram. N. 12.15. 16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=369-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

समग्र|समग्रः<BR>समग्र (ut videtur, e सम् et अग्र cuspis, quasi duas cuspides<BR>conjunctas habens<BR>1) plenus, de lunâ. H. 3.13.<BR>2) totus, integer. BH. 4.23. 11.30. DR. 6.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=369-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

