सर्वथा|सर्व्वथा<BR>सर्वथा Adv. (a सर्व s. था) quovis modo. BR. 2.21. 3.5. N. 17.44.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=371-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

