सर्वमङ्गला|सर्वमंगला|सर्व्वमङ्गला<BR>सर्वमङ्गला f. (BAH. e सर्व et मङ्गल) cognomen Durgae.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=371-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सर्वशस्|सर्व्वशस्<BR>सर्वशस् Adv. (a सर्व s. शस्, v. h. suff. in gr. 652.) omnino.<BR>N. 2.22. 9.26. 10.9. 12.8. 85.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=371-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सल्<BR>सल् 1. P. (गतौ) ire. (Vid. सलिल et cf. सृ i. e. सर्, hib.<BR>silim<BR>1) «I drop, distil, sow»,<BR>2) «I spit»; lith. selu<BR>repo, serpo, gradu suspenso eo; slav. sl-a-ti mittere; lat.<BR>salio, gr. ἅλλομαι, ἅλ-μα.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=371-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सलिल|सलिलं<BR>सलिल n. (r. सल् s. unâd. इल) aqua. (Cf. gr.<BR>σάλος, ἅλς; lat. salum, sal, saliva; slav. sol sal.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=371-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सवितृ<BR>सवितृ m. (r. सु vel सू generare suff. तृ) sol. N. 23.13.<BR>HIT. 17.21.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=371-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सव्य|सव्यः<BR>सव्य laevus, sinister. (Slav. ṣûi id., Them. ṣûjo, fem. ṣûja<BR>= सव्या, v. gr. comp. 255.f. 258.; lat. scaevus, adjectâ<BR>gutturali sicut in escit pro esit, unde erit, cf. gr.<BR>ἔσϰον; gr. σϰαιός e σϰαϜιος vel e σϰαιϜος, transposito<BR>ι. Fortasse etiam sinister, sinistimus - cf. dexter,<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-a" target="_blank">Page372-a+ 36</a>]<BR>dextimus, gr. comp. 293. - et gr. ἀϱιστεϱός huc pertinent,<BR>ita ut sinis- ortum sit e sivis- et ἀϱιστεϱός e<BR>σαϜιστεϱός, cum semivocales vel liquidae facile inter se<BR>mutentur, v. gr. comp. 20.) (*)<BR>(*) De cognatis formis in linguis Malayicis v. librum<BR>meum Über die Verwandtschaft der malayisch-polynesischen<BR>Sprachen mit den indisch-europäischen p. 86. et 148.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=371-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सव्यसाचिन्<BR>सव्यसाचिन् m. (e praec. et साचिन् a r. सच् sequi s.<BR>इन्) cognomen Ardschuni.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सव्येतर<BR>सव्येतर (e सव्य laevus et इतर alius) dexter. RAGH. 12.90.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सश्च्<BR>सश्च् in dial. Vêd. i. q. सच् i. e. sequi; faqui; favere. Vid. Westerg.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सस्<BR>सस् 2. P. (स्वप्ने) dormire. RIGV. 29.4.: ससन्तु «dormiunto»;<BR>29.3.: सस्ताम् «dormiunto» (dual.); 53.1.:<BR>ससताम् «dormientium»; 103.7.: ससन्तम् «dormientem».<BR>Cf. 2. शस्, संस्त्, शंस्त्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सस्य|सस्यं<BR>सस्य n. (ut videtur, pro शस्य) granum, fructus. N. 24.52.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सह्<BR>सह् 1. P. A. सहामि, सहे (etiam cl. 4. et 10. P. {#sahyAmi,<BR>sAhayAmi#}) fut. part. सहिता et सोढा, part. pass.<BR>सोढ, infin. सहितुम् et सोढुम् (v. gr. min. ed. 2. §. 102.)<BR>1) sustinere, perferre, tolerare. SA. 3.9.: {#kaTam…ASrame<BR>sahizyate kleSam imam#}; R. Schl. I.43.25.: {#gaNgAyAH<BR>patanam pfTivI na sahizyate#}; MAH. 3.15371.: {#duHKam<BR>uttamaM sehire#}; 15376.: सेहुर् दुःखम्; H. 2.36.:<BR>न हि मे राक्षसा भीरु सोढुं शक्ताः पराक्रमम्; 3.8. — {#vAzpaM<BR>soQum#} lacrymas retinere. R. Schl. II.40.27.<BR>2) patientem esse, quiescere, exspectare, sich gedulden.<BR>RAGH. 5.25.: द्वित्राण्य् अहान्य् (schol. {#dve trIRi vA<BR>dinAni#}) अर्हसि सोढुम् (schol. क्षन्तुम्).<BR>3) ignoscere,<BR>condonare. SAK. 56.1.: अपराधम् इमन् ततः सहिष्ये.<BR>4) indulgere, favere, propitium esse, c. dat. vel<BR>gen. BH. 11.44.: {#pite 'va putrasya saKe 'va saKyuH priyaH<BR>priyAyA 'rhasi deva soQum#}.<BR>5) posse. MAH. 3.8812.:<BR>न सेहिरे…वेगन् तदा धारयितुम्; HIT. 71.21.: {#ciran<BR>na sahate sTAtum#}. Vid. praef. उत्. (Cf. सुह्, gr.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-b" target="_blank">Page372-b+ 37</a>]<BR>σχή-σω, ἔσχη-ϰα, ἔσχημαι, ἔσχον, σχέ-σις, σχε-τός, σχή-μα, ἴσχω, ἰσχάνω;<BR>v. gr. comp. 483. not. 3.;<BR>de ἔχω, ὄχος v. वह्. Ἄχος, ἄχομαι, ἄχνυμι, ἀχέω, ἄχϑος, ἄχϑομαι<BR>tam e सह् quam e वह् abjectâ litterâ<BR>initiali explicari possunt. Ag. Benary huc trahit lat.<BR>sag-ax, sâgus, sâgio, l. c. p. 117. 235.<BR>c. अभि vim inferre, अभिषह्य vim inferendo, cum vi,<BR>violenter. MAN. 8.367. Vid. प्र.<BR>c. उत् posse. N. 6.14.: संहर्तुन् नो ऽत्सहे कोपम्; BR. 1.32. 33.<BR>— Cum dat. nominis abstr. loco infin. MAH. 3.16543.:<BR>{#tvAm aham mETili no 'tsahe pariBogAya<BR>SvAvalIQaM havir yaTA#}.<BR>c. उत् praef. अभि id. RAGH. 5.22.<BR>c. उत् praef. प्र Caus. incitare, excitare, instigare. R. Schl. II.9.46.:<BR>तथा प्रोत्साहिता देवी; 21.12.: {#protsAhito<BR>'yaN kEkeyyA#}.<BR>c. उत् praef. सम् Caus. id. MAH. 2.1412.<BR>c. प्र<BR>1) sustinere. R. Schl. II.51.7. 10.<BR>2) posse. MAH. 1.4842.<BR>3) vim inferre, प्रसह्य vim inferendo, cum vi,<BR>violenter. DR. 6.8.: पाषैः कृतो ऽभिमर्दः कुरुभिः प्रसह्य;<BR>MAN. 7.108. 8.235.<BR>c. प्रति sustinere. R. Schl. I.37.8.<BR>c. वि sustinere. RAGH. 4.49.: प्रतापन् न विषेहिरे. C.<BR>infin. cum acc. R. Schl. II.12.106.: {#na jIvitun tvAM<BR>vizahe 'manoramAm#}. — विषह्य<BR>1) sustinendus. A. 10.75.<BR>2) possibilis. A. 5.9.: {#vizahyaM yan mayA kartuN kftam<BR>eva niboDa tat#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सह|सहं|सहः<BR>1. सह Adj. (r. सह् s. अ) sustinens, perferens, in fine comp.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

सह|सहं|सहः<BR>2. सह Praep. (ut mihi videtur, a stirpe pronom. स suff. ह<BR>e ध, sicut इह q. v. ab इ) cum, c. instr. IN. 1.23. In dial.<BR>Vêd. सध (vid. gr. comp. 420.).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=372-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

