साक्षात्<BR>साक्षात् Adv. (e स cum et अक्ष oculus in ablat., v. gr. 675.<BR>not. 2.) in conspectu, coram, palam. IN. 2.16. SU. 1.17.<BR>N. 24.13. SA. 6.38. A. 1.12. — साक्षाद् इव plane ut.<BR>N. 1.4. 2.28.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=373-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

