साङ्ख्य|सांख्य|सांख्यं|साङ्ख्यः<BR>साङ्ख्य (a सङ्ख्या s. अ) Adj. cogitans, ratiocinans. BH. 3.3. 5.5. 13.24.<BR>Subst. n.<BR>1) doctrina rationalis, ratiocinatio.<BR>BH. 2.39. 5.4.<BR>2) systema philosophicum, Kapilo<BR>adscriptum.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=373-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

