सि<BR>सि 5. et 9. P. A. सिनोमि, सिन्वे, सिनामि, सिने (बन्धने)<BR>ligare, vincire. RIGV. V. 84.2.: {#setfBiH sinITaH<BR>pApakftaH#} (v. Westerg.); RIGV. 112.5.: सितम् vinctum.<BR>(Lett. ʃsee-t ligare, ʃsai-te funis, vinculum; sax. vet. simo,<BR>Them. si-mon, quod ligat, restis, laqueus, vinculum;<BR>germ. vet. sai-d, sei-d laqueus, tendicula, sai-to(n) funis,<BR>fidis, chorda; sai-l laqueus; slav. sje-tj tendicula, si-lo laqueus;<BR>gr. σει-ϱά, ἱ-μάς, v. Pott. I.206. II.174. Graff VI.157. sq. 187.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=375-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

