सिव्<BR>सिव् 4. P. सीव्यामि (gr. 331^a).) suere. Part. pass. स्यूत.<BR>RIGV. 31.15.: वर्मे ऽव स्यूतम्. (Goth. siuja suo, siujith<BR>suit Marc. 2.21.; germ. vet. siwu suo, sarcio, consuo,<BR>praet. siwita et sûta; siut sutura, sutari sutor, saum limbus,<BR>ora, sarcina, sagma, swila subula; slav. sʽivû suo,<BR>lith. suwù suo, infin. sú-ti; sulế sutura; lat. suo; gr.<BR>ϰασσύω.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=376-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

