सूर|सूरः<BR>सूर m. (ut videtur, a स्वर् primitivâ formâ radicis सुर्<BR>splendere, correpto व in ऊ, suff. अ) sol. (Fortasse<BR>goth. sunna m. sol, Them. sunnan, per assimil. e surnan,<BR>sunnô(n) f. e surnô(n), germ. vet. sunno(n) m., sunna(n)<BR>f.; fortasse lith. saulế f. per metath. e swalế, de graec.<BR>ἥλιος et goth. sauil vid. सूर्य, de lat. sol vid. स्वर्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=379-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

