स्खल्<BR>स्खल् 1. P. titubare, vacillare. HIT. 105.15. TROP. HIT. 55.2.:<BR>प्रभुसमीपम् उपागतानां वाचः स्खलन्ति. Errare,<BR>peccare. R. Schl. I.13.10.: {#nA 'nAhutam aBUt<BR>tatra sKalitaM vA 'pi kiYcana#}. (Cf. स्फल्, चल्, lat.<BR>scelus, nisi hoc pertinet ad छल; gr. σϕάλλω; lat.<BR>fallo.)<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. A. 8.14.: {#harayo vimuKAScA 'san prAsKalaccA<BR>'pi mAtaliH#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=384-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

