स्तन्<BR>1. स्तन् 1. P. gemere, suspirare. BHATT. 14.30.: {#tastanuH<BR>kzatAH#}. (Gr. στένω, lith. stenu id., slav. stenajû id.)<BR>c. नि i. q. simpl. MAH. 3.14060.: {#tam ugratapasaM vipran<BR>nizwanantam mahItale#}. Cum acc. gemere alqd. R. Schl. II.77.8.:<BR>पितुः शरीरनिर्वाणं निष्टनन् विषसाद.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=384-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

