स्तिघ्<BR>स्तिघ् 5. P. (आस्कन्दने, v. Westerg. p. 365.) ascendere.<BR>(Gr. ΣΤΙΧ, στείχω, ἔστιχον, germ. vet. STIG scandere,<BR>ascendere, stîgu, steig, stigumês; lith. staigùs celer,<BR>staigey cito, staigio-s festino, russ. stignu (cf. स्तिघ्नोमि)<BR>assequor, consequor, slav. vet. стчза stiζa semita,<BR>goth. staigs id., hib. staighre «a step, stair».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=385-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

