स्तैन्य|स्तैन्यं|स्तैन्यः<BR>स्तैन्य n. (a praec. s. य) id. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=386-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

