स्वेदन|स्वेदनं<BR>स्वेदन n.<BR>1) (r. स्विद् s. अन) sudatio.<BR>2) (Caus. r. स्विद्<BR>s. अन) actio faciendi ut quis sudet, actio calefaciendi.<BR>HIT. 70.16.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=397-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

स्वैर|स्वैरः<BR>स्वैर (ut videtur, e स्व et obsoleto derivato radicis ईर्)<BR>Adj. liber, qui sui juris, suae potestatis. Subst. n. liberum<BR>arbitrium. N. 21.13. SA. 5.98. — स्वैरम् Adv. ad<BR>suum arbitrium. SAK. 25.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=397-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

