हंस|हंसः<BR>हंस m. anser. N. 1.19. — Fem. हंसी. (Gr. χήν abjectâ<BR>syllabâ finali, lat. anser abjectâ litterâ initiali; germ. vet.<BR>gans f., Them. gansi, gensi, pertinet ad fem. हंसी, ita<BR>lith. źasi-s f. et slav. gûsj e gonsj (v. gr. comp. 255.g.).<BR>Hib. geadh «a goose», ganra «a gander» mutilatum esse<BR>videtur e gandra, cf. anglo-sax. gandra(n) anser mas,<BR>germ. vet. ganzo(n) id. e ganto(n); cambro-brit. gwyz,<BR>armor. gwaz, cum z = d.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=397-1a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

