हार्द|हार्दं|हार्द्द|हार्द्दं<BR>हार्द n. (a हृद् cor s. अ) amor. UR. 85.10.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हालहल|हालहलं<BR>हालहल etiam हालहाल et हालाहल n. veneni genus.<BR>HIT. 23.5.: हलाहलं विषम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हाव|हावः<BR>हाव m. (ut videtur, a r. ह्वे clamare s. अ, cf. gr. 449.) nugae,<BR>ineptiae, deliciae feminarum. (Wils.: Any feminine<BR>act of amorous pastime, or tending to excite amorous<BR>sensations, coquetry, blandishment, dalliance.). IN. 2.32.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हासिन्<BR>हासिन् (r. हस् s. इन्) ridens, subridens, in fine comp. N. 3.14.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हाहाभूत<BR>हाहाभूत Adj. (e हाहा heu! heu! et भूत qui est) heu! heu!<BR>clamans. SA. 2.23. N. 17.31.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हि<BR>1. हि 5. P. (anom. v. gr. 443. 444. 572. गतौ K. गतौ वर्द्धने<BR>V.)<BR>1) ire.<BR>2) mittere. RIGV. 34.11.: वज्रं हिन्वन्ति;<BR>BHATT. 14.36.: गदा शक्रजिता जिघ्ये (schol.<BR>प्रहिता, प्रेषिता). Vid. praef. प्र.<BR>3) augere, amplificare.<BR>RIGV. 23.17.: ता नो हिन्वन्त्व् अध्वरम्.<BR>4) tueri. RIGV. 18.4.<BR>(Cf. 2. हा, गा; fortasse lat. cieo, gr. ϰίω cum c,<BR>ϰ = ह् sicut in cor, ϰέαϱ; v. हिम.)<BR>c. प्र प्रहिणोमि (v. gr. min. 94^b). annot.) mittere. A. 8.30.:<BR>तान् अहम्…प्राहिण्वं यमसादनम्; 8.8.: {#astram…<BR>prAhiRavam#}; 9.17. IN. 4.2. — MAH. 2.1244.: {#sa dUtAn<BR>prAhiRot#}; RAGH. 12.84.: रथन् तस्मै प्रजिघाय पुरन्दरः.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हि<BR>2. हि Conj.<BR>1) enim. BR. 1.16. BH. 3.5.<BR>2) particula interrogativa.<BR>H. 3.17.<BR>3) quidem, certe. M. 6.22. 26.27.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हिंस्<BR>हिंस् 7. 1. et 10. P. interdum 1. A. {#hinasmi, hiMsAmi, hiMse,<BR>hiMsayAmi#} (scribitur हिस्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>1) ferire, pulsare,<BR>offendere, laedere, violare, vexare, affligere. BHATT. 17.13.:<BR>अहिंसन् मुष्टिभिः; MAH. 3.1091.: हिंस्याच्च हिंसितः;<BR>13685.: हिंसितो न हिंसेत; MAN. 4.162.: {#na hiMsyAd<BR>brAhmaRAn#}; 7.73.: अरयो न हिंसन्ति नृपन् दुर्गसमाश्रितम्;<BR>2.180.: हिनस्ति व्रतम् आत्मनः. Occidere,<BR>interficere. H. 4.15.: न तावद् एतान् हिंसिष्ये;<BR>MAN. 5.42.: पशून् हिंसन्; MAH. 3.13289.: {#tvaM hy enam<BR>mA hiMsIH#}; 13030.: {#anyonyam parimuzRanto hiMsayantaSca<BR>mAnavAH#}. (Cf. हन् unde हिंस्, sicut e. c. लिप्स्<BR>pro लिलप्स् a लभ्, v. gr. 552. Huc trahi posset germ.<BR>vet. geis-la flagellum, nostrum Geiʃsel.)<BR>c. उप laedere, violare, vexare, affligere, damnum facere.<BR>MAN. 2.73. 11.26. R. Schl. II.9.4.<BR>c. वि i. q. simpl. sgf. 2. et 3. MAN. 8.238. R. Schl. I.14.15. II.72.44.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हिंसा<BR>हिंसा f. (r. हिंस् s. आ) offensio. BH. 18.25. (cf. अहिंसा.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=400-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हिंस्र|हिंस्रः<BR>हिंस्र (r. हिंस् s. र) Adj. internecivus, perniciosus, atrox,<BR>saevus. Subst. m. bestia rapax, perniciosa. RAGH. 2.62.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=401-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हिक्क्<BR>1. हिक्क् 1. P. A. (अव्यक्ते शब्दे K. कूजे V.) singultire.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=401-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हिक्क्<BR>2. हिक्क् 10. A. (हिंसायाम् K. हिंसे V.) i. q. हिंस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=401-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

