हिमांशु|हिमांशुः<BR>हिमांशु m. (frigidos radios habens, BAH. e हिम et<BR>अंशु) luna. AM.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=401-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

हिमानी<BR>हिमानी f. (a हिम s. आन in fem.) nix. NALOD. 2.5.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=401-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

