हिरण्यकशिपु|हिरण्यकशिपुः<BR>हिरण्यकशिपु m. (e praec. et कशिपु<BR>1) cibus.<BR>2) vestimentum,<BR>in Du. cibus et vestimentum) nom. pr. Asuri.<BR>SU. 1.2.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=401-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

