हिल्<BR>हिल् 6. P. (हावकरणे K. हावकृतौ V.) nugari, ineptire,<BR>ludicra agere, de feminis amore captis. Wils. «to express<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=401-b" target="_blank">Page401-b+ 36</a>]<BR>amorous inclination, to dally, to wanton, to sport<BR>amorously» (v. हाव).<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=401-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

