हेष्<BR>हेष् 1. A. hinnire. BHATT. 14.5.: हया जिहेषिरे. — हेशित<BR>n. hinnitus. MAH. 1.2820.: हेषितस्वन. (Cf. ह्रेष्;<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=405-b" target="_blank">Page405-b+ 36</a>]<BR>fortasse lat. hinnio per assim. e hisnio, quod deduci posset<BR>a nomine actionis हेषण ejecto अ.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=405-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

