ह्रस्<BR>ह्रस् 1. P. (शब्दे K. रवे V.) sonare. Cf. ह्लस्, रस्. — ATM.<BR>diminui (fortasse Denom. a ह्रस्व brevis). MAN. 1.83.:<BR>आयुर् ह्रसते पादशः. Caus. ह्रासयामि diminuere.<BR>MAN. 11.216. Cf. हृ.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=405-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

