ह्रस्व|ह्रस्वं|ह्रस्वः<BR>ह्रस्व<BR>1) brevis. N. 18.6.<BR>2) angustus, arctus. N. 23.9.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

