ह्री<BR>1. ह्री 3. P. जिह्रेमि, part. pass. ह्रीत et ह्रीण. Pudere,<BR>erubescere. RAGH. 15.44.: जिह्राय राघवः. — ह्रीत<BR>pudens, pudibundus. N. 13.30. (Cf. ह्रीछ्, slav. srami-ti<BR>pudore afficere c. s = ह् sicut in srjdjze cor, v. हृदय;<BR>fortasse germ. vet. HRU, RU poenitere, hriwu,<BR>riwu, hrau, rou, hruumês, ruun; hriuwa, riuwa, riwa<BR>poenitentia, anglo-sax. hreova id.; v. Pott. 1.209. Graff 4.1142.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ह्री<BR>2. ह्री f. pudor.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ह्रीछ्|ह्रीच्छ्<BR>ह्रीछ् 1. P. i. q. ह्री. (Huc trahi posset goth. id-reiga poenitentia,<BR>nisi pertinet ad रञ्ज्.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

