ह्रेष्<BR>ह्रेष् 1. A. hinnire. MAH. 4.2000.: ह्रेषमाणैर् वाजिभिः. — ह्रेशित<BR>n. hinnitus. MAH. 3.11764. — Caus. adhinnire<BR>alicui c. acc. MAH. 3.11764.: {#hrezayAmAsur anyonyaM<BR>hrezitEH#}. (V. हेष्, हेषिन् et cf. germ. vet. hros equus,<BR>angl. horse, nostrum Roʃs, gr.<BR>χϱό-μη, χϱεμέϑω, χϱεμίζω.)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

