ह्लस्<BR>ह्लस् 1. P. sonare. Vid. ह्रस्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ह्लाद्<BR>ह्लाद् 1. A. gaudere, laetari. MAH. 1.3036.: {#hlAdate janitA<BR>prekzya (putram)#}. — C. loc. rei. MAH. 1.3037.: {#hlAdante<BR>(narAH) svezu dArezu GarmArtAH salilezv iva#}. — Caus.<BR>exhilarare. R. Schl. II.44.10.: {#SayAnam anaGaM rAtrO…<BR>raSimaBiH saMspfSan SItES candramA hlAdayizyati#}. (Cf.<BR>anglo-sax. glæd laetus, splendens; angl. glad, germ. vet.<BR>glat splendens; hib. gairdim «I rejoice», nisi pertinet ad<BR>गृध् q. v.; slav. rad laetus, radosʽća laetitia; fortasse gr.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-b" target="_blank">Page406-b+ 37</a>]<BR>γῆϑος, γηϑέω, ejectâ liquidâ, transpositâ aspiratione;<BR>fortasse γαίω e γαίϑω vel γαϑίω; lat. gaudeo.)<BR>c. आ Caus. exhilarare. N. 21.8.: ममा ऽऽह्लादयते चेतः.<BR>c. प्र Caus. P. A. id. R. Schl. I.9.56.: प्रह्लादयन्; MAH. 1.7190.:<BR>प्रह्लादयध्वम्; UR. 86.14.: प्रह्लादयस्व.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-a" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ह्वल्<BR>ह्वल् 1. P. (चलने K. चाले V.) vacillare, titubare. (Cf.<BR>germ. vet. wallôn ambulare, errare, volitare.)<BR>c. वि id. MAH. 1.214.: {#saYjYAM no 'palaBe sUta mano vihvalatI<BR>'va me#}; R. Schl. II.13.4.: {#pratyuvAca tataH krudDo<BR>muhUrtaM vihvalann iva#}. — विह्वलित vacillans, titubans.<BR>R. Schl. I.9.15.: {#madavihvalitAH kAScit prapatanty<BR>utpatantica#}.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ह्वृ<BR>ह्वृ 1. P. (कौटिल्ये) curvum, flexuosum esse. (Vid. {#prahva,<BR>upahvara#} et cf. ध्वृ i. e. ध्वर्, lat. vârus, hib. fiar «crooked,<BR>inclined», fiaraim «I incline, bend», fiaras «crookedness».)<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ह्वे<BR>ह्वे 1. P. A. (हु, हू v. gr. 694.) vocare, advocare. SU. 3.10.:<BR>विश्वकर्माणम् अह्वयत् (ed. Calc. आह्वयत्); R. Schl. II.34.11.:<BR>आर्यो ह्वयति वो राजा; MAH. 1.3393.: {#mAcE<BR>'nAM Sayane hvaye#}. (Slav. ζv-a-ti vocare; island. vet.<BR>hvîa hinnire, germ. vet. hwaijôn id., hwaijôt, hweijôt,<BR>weiôt hinnit, v. Graff IV.1223.; fortasse goth. hrôpja<BR>voco = ह्वापयामि, sicut Caus. secundum generalem<BR>regulam sonaret, pro quo anomale ह्वाययामि (gr. 519.),<BR>mutato v in r (v. gr. comp. 20.), servatâ tenui p, sicut in<BR>slêpa dormio, v. स्वप्; germ. vet. hrôfu, ruafu cet.,<BR>nostrum rufe; fortasse hib. guilim «I weep, cry, bewail»<BR>= ह्वयामि, mutato य् in l (v. यकृत्), nisi pertinet ad<BR>2. गॄ i. e. गर्.)<BR>c. आ<BR>1) advocare. R. Schl. II.58.1.: आजुहाव तं सूतम्;<BR>91.12.: आह्वये विश्वकर्माणम्; N. 5.1.: {#AjuhAva<BR>mahIpAlAn…svayaMvare#}.<BR>2) provocare ad pugnam<BR>vel ludum. MAH. 2.879.: {#tvAm AhvayAmahe rAjan<BR>sTiro yuDyasva#}; 4.342.: सर्वमल्लान् अथा ऽऽह्वयत्;<BR>RIGV. 32.6.: आ हि जुह्वे महावीर्यम्; IN. 5.7.: {#SaSinaM<BR>vaktracandreRa sA ''hvayantI 'va#}; N. 12.83.: आहूय<BR>provocando, post provocationem. — Caus. आह्वाययामि<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=407-a" target="_blank">Page407-a+ 5</a>]<BR>advocari jubeo. RAGH. 15.75.: कविम् आह्वाययामास.<BR>c. आ praef. उप id. sgf. 2. MAH. 2.1765.: {#upAhvayasva<BR>tam#}.<BR>c. आ praef. सम्<BR>1) convocare. SU. 2.9.: सैनिकांश्च समाहूय.<BR>[<a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=407-b" target="_blank">Page407-b+ 4</a>]<BR>2) provocare ad pugnam vel ludum. MAH. 2.1518.:<BR>त्वां समाह्वयते; 4.346.: भीमो मल्लं समाह्वयत्;<BR>5.35.: गान्धारराजस्य सुतम् मताक्षं समाह्वयद् देवितुम्.<BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslp?dict=BOP&page=406-b" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://dub.sh/cslc?dict=bop" target="_blank">Correction</a>

